NK052(zi)001:1: // sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba mkha'
NK052(zi)001:2: 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog ces bya ba'i
NK052(zi)001:4: lho brag nyi sde dgon nas byung ba karma pa
NK052(zi)001:5: zhwa dmar spyan snga chos grags phyag dpe las bshus
NK052(zi)001:6: pa / sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin dngos //
NK052(zi)001:7: skye dgu kun gyi mgon gcig pu //
NK052(zi)001:8: bde chen rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK052(zi)001:9: btud nas de rgyud dgrol bar 'dod //
NK052(zi)001:10: bcom ldan rang byung gcig pu ni //
NK052(zi)001:11: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:12: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog de //
NK052(zi)001:13: gang zhig ci 'dra ji ltar bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:14: de yi mthu yang ci 'dra ste //
NK052(zi)001:15: gzhan yang ci rigs rnam 'phrul pa'ang //
NK052(zi)001:16: gang rnams ci 'dra de bzhin du //
NK052(zi)001:17: rang don las rnams gang bsgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:19: ma lus kun nas bsdus par 'dod //
NK052(zi)001:20: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i cho ga'ang //
NK052(zi)001:21: rnam pa gsum dang drug dngos te //
NK052(zi)001:22: 'on kyang gdul bya'i bye brag gis //
NK052(zi)001:23: gcig gnyis gsum bcas drug dgu bcas //
NK052(zi)001:25: thabs kyi cho ga ma lus bsdus //
NK052(zi)001:26: de la thabs dngos phyag rgya ste //
NK052(zi)001:27: gnyis la gsum drug nyi shu brgyad //
NK052(zi)001:28: de dag gang zhig gang gi yin //
NK052(zi)001:29: gang du sbyar bar bya zhes sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:30: de bas 'di ni phyag rgya'i rgyud //
NK052(zi)001:31: phyag rgya'i cho ga zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:33: rab tu dbye ba shes par 'dod //
NK052(zi)001:34: rab tu rnam phye gzhung rgyas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:35: de la dpal sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par
NK052(zi)001:36: sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog
NK052(zi)001:37: ces bya ba'i rgyud 'di'i gdul bya'i skye bo'ang /
NK052(zi)001:40: rab tu rnam par phye ste bshad pa la dga' ba'i bye brag gis rnam pa gsum nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:41: de la kun nas bsdus pa la dga' ba'i gang zag rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:42: bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par
NK052(zi)001:43: sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog
NK052(zi)001:44: ces bya ba 'di'i rang gi ngo bo na gang
NK052(zi)001:45: zhig yin / de'i mtshan nyid dang rnam pa ni ci 'dra bar bzhugs /
NK052(zi)001:46: de yongs su mnyes par bya ba'i cho ga gang gis ji ltar mnyes shing bsgrub par bya /
NK052(zi)001:47: de yongs su mnyes shing grub pa las mthu dang
NK052(zi)001:48: yon tan gyi rnam pa ni ci 'dra zhig 'grub
NK052(zi)001:51: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen po de
NK052(zi)001:52: nyid 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang gis ji ltar rigs
NK052(zi)001:53: pa rnam par 'phrul ba 'byung ba yang gang dang
NK052(zi)001:54: gang rnams yin / gang dang gang rnams su rnam
NK052(zi)001:55: par 'phrul pa de dang de rnams kyi mtshan nyid
NK052(zi)001:56: dam rnam pa ni ci 'dra ba 'byung bar 'gyur
NK052(zi)001:57: gang rnams yin / / de ltar rnam par 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:58: pa'i dkyil 'khor de rnams mnyes par bya ba'i cho
NK052(zi)001:59: ga gang gis mnyes par byas shing bsgrubs pas rang
NK052(zi)001:60: rang gi don gyi las kyi 'bras bu ci dang
NK052(zi)001:63: dris tshig rnam pa bdun po 'di dag nyid kyi
NK052(zi)001:64: lan rjes su bstan pa tsam gyis dbu zhabs kyi
NK052(zi)001:65: don khong du chud par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:66: de la lan rjes su bstan par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:67: bcom ldan 'das rang byung gcig pus sangs rgyas thams
NK052(zi)001:68: cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma
NK052(zi)001:69: bde ba'i mchog ces bya ba 'di'i rang gi ngo
NK052(zi)001:70: bo ni / thog ma nyid nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa /
NK052(zi)001:71: phyi ma'i mthar thug pa med par 'gyur ba med pa /
NK052(zi)001:72: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:73: g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad
NK052(zi)001:74: kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa gang yin pa de
NK052(zi)001:75: ni 'di'i rang gi ngo bo nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:76: de'i mtshan nyid dam rnam pa ci 'dra bar bzhugs she na /
NK052(zi)001:77: rnam pa gsum gyi bdag nyid du 'di ltar /
NK052(zi)001:78: ji skad bstan pa'i rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK052(zi)001:79: pa'i bde ba chen po'i mtshan nyid du bzhugs pa
NK052(zi)001:80: dang / rnam par dag pa'i dbang gi sku gdod
NK052(zi)001:81: ma dang tha ma med par rtag tu da ltar
NK052(zi)001:82: byung ba lta bu'i mtshan nyid can /
NK052(zi)001:83: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang byang
NK052(zi)001:84: chub sems dpa' dang nyan thos dang rang rgyal ba
NK052(zi)001:85: dang / g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i bsdus pa'i
NK052(zi)001:86: dngos po thams cad kyi gzugs kyis thams cad du
NK052(zi)001:87: rnam par 'phrul ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi rnam par
NK052(zi)001:88: dang / bzhugs pa dang / mkha' 'gro ma bde
NK052(zi)001:89: ba mchog gi phyi dang nang gi dkyil 'khor dag
NK052(zi)001:90: na rtag tu bde ba chen po la longs spyod
NK052(zi)001:91: pa'i mtshan can gyi rnam par bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:92: de yongs su mnyes par bya ba'i thabs kyi cho ga yang rnam pa gsum yin te /
NK052(zi)001:93: shin tu spros pa med pa'i cho ga dang /
NK052(zi)001:94: spros pa med pa'i cho ga dang /
NK052(zi)001:95: spros pa dang bcas pa'i cho ga'o //
NK052(zi)001:96: de yongs su bsgrubs pa las mthu dang yon tan
NK052(zi)001:97: gyi rnam pa ci 'dra ba zhig 'byung zhe na
NK052(zi)001:99: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' mnyes par gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:100: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dpal rnams la spyod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:101: dbang phyug chen po dang tshangs pa la sogs te
NK052(zi)001:102: 'jig rten gyi dbang phyug thams cad kyi dpal rnams
NK052(zi)001:103: la spyod pas bsdus pa sna tshogs thams cad kyi
NK052(zi)001:104: skal ba bzang po mchog gi dngos grub thams cad
NK052(zi)001:106: de ltar dris pa rnam pa bzhi po'i lan bstan pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:107: gzhung 'di'i rtog pa bzhi pa yan chad bstan par 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:108: 'di ltar bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas thams cad dang
NK052(zi)001:109: mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde
NK052(zi)001:110: ba'i mchog ces bya ba 'di'i rang gi ngo bo
NK052(zi)001:111: dang / de'i rnam pa ci 'dra bar bzhugs pa rnam pa gsum du bstan pa'i bdag nyid dang /
NK052(zi)001:112: de ji ltar bsgrub pa'i cho ga rnam pa gsum du bstan pa'i bdag nyid rnams kyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:113: gzhung 'di'i rtog pa gsum ji skad bstan pa'i go rim bzhin du bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:114: de yongs su mnyes par byas shing bsgrub pa las
NK052(zi)001:115: mthu dang yon tan gyi rnam pa ci 'dra ba
NK052(zi)001:116: zhig 'grub par 'gyur ba bstan pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:117: 'dir rtog pa bzhi pa bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:118: da ni de'i rnam par 'phrul pa ji ltar 'byung
NK052(zi)001:119: ba'i dri ba rnam pa gsum dris pa'i lan rjes
NK052(zi)001:121: de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni /
NK052(zi)001:122: sprul pa thams cad kyi bdag po zhes rnal 'byor gyi rgyud phal cher grags na /
NK052(zi)001:123: 'dir de'i rnam par 'phrul pa ni gang dang gang rnams yin zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:124: gdul bya'i skye bo rnams kyi bag la nyal ba
NK052(zi)001:125: dang bsam pa'i khams kyi bye brag gi 'phrul pa
NK052(zi)001:126: rnams kyang mtha' yas pa yin mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:127: de dag kyang mdor bsdus na rnam pa drug gi bdag nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:128: 'di ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen
NK052(zi)001:129: po'i dkyil 'khor chen por rnam par 'phrul ba dang
NK052(zi)001:130: / dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor du rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:131: dpal rdo rje 'dzin pa he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:132: dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gam dkyil 'khor du rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:133: dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:134: dpal rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor du rnam par 'phrul pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:135: de la rnam pa 'phrul pa de dag gi mtshan
NK052(zi)001:136: nyid dam rnam pa ci 'dra ba zhig tu 'byung
NK052(zi)001:138: 'di'i lan rjes su bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:139: sngon byung ba'i gtam gyi phyag rgya las shes so //
NK052(zi)001:140: de ltar rnam par 'phrul pa de lta bur byung
NK052(zi)001:141: bar gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag mnyes par bya
NK052(zi)001:142: ba'i cho ga gang gis mnyes par byas shing bsgrubs
NK052(zi)001:143: pas rang rang gi las kyi 'bras bu ci 'dra
NK052(zi)001:145: de la de dag sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga ni 'di nyid las /
NK052(zi)001:147: yang na de bzhin lo re ni //
NK052(zi)001:148: ji bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK052(zi)001:149: sangs rgyas bde mchog gar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:150: khams kyi rang bzhin thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:151: de bzhin srog dang rtsa las byung //
NK052(zi)001:152: rang gi lha yi cha lugs su //
NK052(zi)001:153: bsgrubs pa'i phyag rgya rab tu byas //
NK052(zi)001:154: dkyil 'khor gang dang gang bsten pa //
NK052(zi)001:155: sna tshogs phyag rgya'i mchod pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:156: slob ma'i tshogs kun de dang der //
NK052(zi)001:157: mchod pa byas na de bsgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:158: zhes gsungs pa 'dis ma lus bar bsdus te bstan pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:159: de la thabs kyi cho ga de yang rnam pa lnga'i bdag nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:160: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul pa thabs kyi dngos gzhi dang /
NK052(zi)001:161: de'i yan lag dang grogs su gyur pa'i 'khor lo rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:162: mchod par rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:163: phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:164: phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul pa kun nas bsdus pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:165: 'di dag gis ni rnam par 'phrul pa rnams kyi thabs kyi cho ga kun bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:166: de dag rang rang don gyi las kyi 'bras bu ci 'dra ba zhig 'grub pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:167: skabs 'dir gzhung gud du bstan pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:168: phyag rgya rang rang gi las kyi skabs dang gong
NK052(zi)001:169: du bstan pa nyid du yang 'du bas de bas
NK052(zi)001:170: 'dir dri ba rnam pa gsum gyi lan rjes su
NK052(zi)001:172: de lta bas na rnam par 'phrul pa drug po
NK052(zi)001:173: 'di dag gis ni gzhung 'di'i rtog pa lnga pa
NK052(zi)001:174: man chad go rim bzhin du bsdus par shes so
NK052(zi)001:175: // da ni gdul bya'i skye bo de'i rab tu
NK052(zi)001:176: dbye ba la dga' ba rnams kyi phyir ji ltar
NK052(zi)001:177: bsgrub pa'i rab tu dbye ba bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:178: de yang ngo bo nyid du gsungs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:179: gong du bstan pa ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK052(zi)001:180: mtshan nyid dam rnam pa ji ltar bzhugs pa rnam
NK052(zi)001:181: pa gsum bstan pa'i dbang gis phye ba'i sgrub pa'i
NK052(zi)001:182: thabs rnam pa gsum bstan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:183: rnam par 'phrul pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po rnam pa
NK052(zi)001:184: drug gi dbang gis phye ba'i bsgrub pa'i cho ga'ang
NK052(zi)001:185: rnam pa drug yin mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:186: 'on kyang gdul bya'i skye bo'i dbang gis de bsgrub pa'i thabs kyang sna tshogs su 'gyur ba na /
NK052(zi)001:187: 'di ltar gzhung 'di'i dbu zhabs kyis kyang gdul bya'i
NK052(zi)001:188: skye bo lta ba dang mos pa mthun pas bsdus
NK052(zi)001:189: pa'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po gcig tu gtogs
NK052(zi)001:190: rnams kyis dus gcig tu bsgrub par bya ba yang
NK052(zi)001:191: yin te / 'di ltar gar ye shes kyi phyag
NK052(zi)001:192: rgya'i skabs nas gsungs pa bzhin dkyil 'khor gang yang
NK052(zi)001:193: rung ba zhig gi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas
NK052(zi)001:194: yin te / kyang / gar ye shes kyi phyag rgya'i mchod pa'i skabs su /
NK052(zi)001:195: dkyil 'khor drug gi lha thams cad kyi phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:196: thams cad du rim par bsgyur zhing bsgrub par bya
NK052(zi)001:198: gzhung thams cad kyis kyang bsgrub pa'i cho ga gcig bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:200: sngon gyi slob dpon in+d+ra b+h+au ti la sogs pa'i gdams ngag las grags pa bzhin du /
NK052(zi)001:201: dpal he ru ka'i 'akyila 'khor dbus su bkod la /
NK052(zi)001:202: de'i dkyil du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor bkod de /
NK052(zi)001:203: de nas shar phyogs su dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor bkod nas /
NK052(zi)001:204: de bzhin du lhor dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i dang /
NK052(zi)001:205: nub tu dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi dang /
NK052(zi)001:206: byang du dpal rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor rnams bkod de /
NK052(zi)001:207: dus gcig tu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub par gsungs
NK052(zi)001:208: pas de bas bsgrub thabs kyi cho ga gcig yin
NK052(zi)001:209: no // yang gcig yin te slob dpon h+aum mdzad la sogs pa'i gdams ngag las grags pa bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:210: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:211: lnga'i sgo nas ni sngon du bsnyen pa bya ba
NK052(zi)001:212: yin la / dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor gyis ni bsgrub par bya ba yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:213: de bas na dus tha dad du rnams par bstan
NK052(zi)001:214: kyang gang zag bye brag tu gyur pa med pa'i
NK052(zi)001:215: phyir thabs kyi cho ga gcig yin no //
NK052(zi)001:216: de bas na gzhung 'di ni bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga gcig dang bcas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:217: gzhan yang 'di ni bsgrub pa'i thabs gnyis dang bcas pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:218: 'di ltar ji ltar bstan pa bzhin du gcig tu bsgrub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:219: so sor ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du tha dad du bsgrub pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:220: yang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:221: mtshan ma med pa'i phyag rgya'i sgo nas bsgrub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:222: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i phyag rgya'i sgo nas bsgrub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:223: gzhan yang 'di ni bsgrub pa'i cho ga gsum pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:224: 'di ltar yul dang dus gcig tu bsgrub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:225: yul dang dus tha dad du bsgrub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:226: yul dang dus dang gang zag tha dad du bsgrub pa rnams kyis rnam pa gsum pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:228: spros pa dang bcas pa'i sbyod pa la dga' ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:229: de bzhin spros pa med pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:230: shin tu spros pa med pa rnams kyis gsum mo //
NK052(zi)001:231: gzhan yang 'di ni thabs kyi cho ga drug pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:232: 'di ltar dkyil 'khor chen po drug gi dbang gis so //
NK052(zi)001:233: gzhan yang dgu pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:234: dkyil 'khor chen po drug gi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK052(zi)001:235: shin tu spros pa dang bcas pa'i spyod pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:236: de las cung zad bye brag tu gyur pa phyi
NK052(zi)001:237: rol gyi phyag rgya 'ga' zhig la brten pa spros
NK052(zi)001:239: phyi rol gyi phyag rgya la brten pa dang bral
NK052(zi)001:240: ba rang gi ting nge 'dzin las skyes pa'i ye
NK052(zi)001:241: shes kyi phyag rgya dang snyoms par 'jug pa tsam
NK052(zi)001:242: la brten pa spros pa med pa'i spyod pa dang
NK052(zi)001:243: / rten thams cad bral ba dmigs pa dang rnam pa thams cad las yongs su 'das pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:244: 'phags pa so so rang rig pa'i spyod yul tsam
NK052(zi)001:245: dang mthun par 'jug pa 'di ni shin tu spros
NK052(zi)001:246: pa med pa'i spyod pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:247: de bas na 'di ni sgrub thabs kyi cho ga dgu dang ldan pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:248: gzhan yang mos pa dman pa kha cig ni /
NK052(zi)001:249: sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya 'ga' zhig la brten nas
NK052(zi)001:250: rang gi don gyi bya ba sgrub pa yod de
NK052(zi)001:251: / 'di ltar mnyam med mi g.yo'i glu'i phyag rgya'i
NK052(zi)001:252: sgo nas skabs las byung ba'i bsgrub pa gsungs pa
NK052(zi)001:253: / lta bu'o // 'di dag gis ni gzhung 'dir
NK052(zi)001:254: gsungs pa'i sgrub thabs kyi cho ga ma lus par
NK052(zi)001:256: de la sgrub thabs kyi cho ga de dag gi thabs kyi dngos po ni phyag rgya yin te /
NK052(zi)001:257: de yang mdor bsdu na phyag rgya rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:258: de kho na snang ba dam pa'i yul la 'jug pa'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:259: sna tshogs thams cad kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya'i tshogs so //
NK052(zi)001:260: de la sna tshogs thams cad kyi mtshan ma'i phyag
NK052(zi)001:261: rgya las kyang phyag rgya rnam pa gsum du 'gyur
NK052(zi)001:262: te / dpal rdo rje sems dpar kun tu sbyor ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:263: dpal rdo rje dam tshig ces bya ba rjes su sbyor ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:264: sna tshogs thams cad kyi rnam par 'phrul pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:265: de la sna tshogs thams cad kyi rnam par 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:266: pa'i phyag rgya'ang dbye ba'i rnam pa drug tu 'gyur
NK052(zi)001:267: te / sna tshogs thams cad rnam par 'phrul pa'i gtam gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:268: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul pa zhes
NK052(zi)001:269: bya ba byin rlabs bsgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i
NK052(zi)001:270: phyag rgya 'khor lo rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:271: ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:272: dang / mchod pa rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:273: ba phyag 'tshal ba dang gar gyi phyag rgya dang
NK052(zi)001:274: dang / / phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul ba zhes
NK052(zi)001:275: bya ba rnam par sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya dang
NK052(zi)001:276: dang / / / phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul ba
NK052(zi)001:277: bsdus pa zhes bya ba phyag rgya dgrol ba dang
NK052(zi)001:278: bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya ste drug gi rnam pa bdag
NK052(zi)001:279: dang / / / nyid do // de la rnam
NK052(zi)001:280: par sgrub byed kyi phyag rgya la yang dbye bas
NK052(zi)001:281: nyi shu rtsa brgyad du 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:282: 'di ltar thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:283: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:284: dam tshig chen po ye shes kyi phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:286: dngos grub thams cad kyi phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:287: zhes bya ba'i bar du ji skad gsungs pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:288: phyag rgya de dag thams cad kyang rang rig ngo bo ji lta bu zhig yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:289: phyag rgya de dag gi bdag po dang gtso bo gang dag gang gi phyag rgya yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:290: de dag gi dgos pa'i bya ba gang dang gang
NK052(zi)001:291: gi skabs su gang dang gang sbyar bar bya ba
NK052(zi)001:292: yin zhes thams cad la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:293: de ltar phyag rgya 'di rnams rnam pa gsum du 'di ltar shes pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:294: ji skad du bstan pa'i thabs kyi cho ga rnams shes par 'gyur la /
NK052(zi)001:295: des dri ba bdun po legs par khong du chud par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:296: ji skad du bstan pa'i dri ba bdun po de
NK052(zi)001:297: dag kyang rgyud las ji skad gsungs pa'ii go rim
NK052(zi)001:298: mdzad pa'i dbang du bstan pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:299: de dag kyang mdor bsdu na /
NK052(zi)001:300: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' rigs drug rnam par 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:301: ba dang bcas pa'i rang gi ngo bo ci 'dra
NK052(zi)001:302: ba dang / de ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga dang /
NK052(zi)001:303: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan
NK052(zi)001:304: bstan pa rnams kyis gzhung mtha' dag kun nas bsdus
NK052(zi)001:306: de ni phyag rgya rnams kyi rang gi ngo bo
NK052(zi)001:307: dang bdag po dang bya ba rnams rim pa bzhin
NK052(zi)001:309: de la ji skad du bstan pa'i rnam grangs de
NK052(zi)001:310: dag kyang yan lag sum cu rtsa drug yin la
NK052(zi)001:311: / rdzas su ni de kho na nyid snang ba
NK052(zi)001:312: dam pa'i yul la 'jug pa'i ye shes kyi phyag
NK052(zi)001:313: / rgya dang / rnam par sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK052(zi)001:314: de ltar rnam pa gnyis ni thabs kyi dngos gzhi yin la /
NK052(zi)001:315: dkyil 'khor du dgod pa'i mtshan ma'i phyag rgya rnams ni bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya yin te /
NK052(zi)001:316: de ltar na rdzas su ni rnam pa 'di gsum tsam gyis bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:317: de la de kho na nyid snang bas dam pa'i
NK052(zi)001:318: yul la 'jug pa'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya ni
NK052(zi)001:319: / gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems te dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:320: 'di gang du sbyar ba'i dus ni rnam pa gnyis te /
NK052(zi)001:321: shin tu spros pa med pa la dga' ba rnams kyi thabs kyi cho ga la sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:322: rnam pa sna tshogs kyi mtshan ma'i phyag rgya la yang 'dir yongs su zin par sbyar ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:323: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' kun tu sbyor ba'i phyag
NK052(zi)001:324: rgya ni gzugs kyi sku yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyag
NK052(zi)001:325: rgya ste / 'di yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i 'o //
NK052(zi)001:326: 'di gang du sbyar ba'i skabs kyang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:327: spros pa med pa la dga' ba rnams kyi bsgrub pa'i tshe sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:328: spros pa dang bcas pa rnams la yang 'dis zin par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:329: dpal rdo rje dam tshig ces bya ba rjes sbyor ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:330: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' gtso bo dang mkha' 'gro
NK052(zi)001:331: ma dang bcas pa'i yongs rdzogs pa'i sku phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:332: ste / bdag po'ang de rnams nyid yin no //
NK052(zi)001:333: gang du sbyar ba'i dus kyang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:334: spros pa dang bcas pa la dga' ba rnams phyi
NK052(zi)001:335: rol gyi gzungs ma 'ga' zhig la brten nas sgrub
NK052(zi)001:336: par byed pa rnams kyi tshe sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:337: shin tu spros pa dang bcas pa la dga' ba
NK052(zi)001:338: lha mo nyi shu la sogs pas sgrub par sbyor
NK052(zi)001:339: ba na yang 'dis zin par bya ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:340: sna tshogs thams cad kyi gtam gyi phyag rgya ni
NK052(zi)001:341: rigs drug po rnams gang zhig ci 'dra bar 'byung
NK052(zi)001:342: ba'i gtam gyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:343: bdag po'ang de rnams nyid yin zhing gang gis de ltar shes pa bya ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:344: 'dis 'debs par byed pa ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:345: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul ba'i byin
NK052(zi)001:346: gyis rlabs sgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:347: ni / rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya rnams
NK052(zi)001:348: la rnam par sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:349: byin gyis brlabs shing rgyas btab pa'i phyag rgya ste
NK052(zi)001:350: ni / / de bas na dngos gzhi yin gyi 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:351: 'khor lo rnam par sprul pa'i mtshan ma'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:352: sgrub pa dang mchod pa'i rten gyi phyag rgya yin te /
NK052(zi)001:353: 'di yang 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:354: mchod pa rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba phyag dang gar gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:355: dkyil 'khor rnams la mchod pa'i dus na phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:356: 'di gnyis kyi sgo nas mchod pa thams cad 'bul
NK052(zi)001:358: 'di yang 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:359: 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya ma yin pa 'di dag
NK052(zi)001:360: dus gang du sbyar ba ni ji skad du bstan
NK052(zi)001:361: pa de dag nyid kyis shes so //
NK052(zi)001:362: phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK052(zi)001:363: 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya yin te /
NK052(zi)001:364: thabs kyi dngos po bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:365: de la yig 'bru dgod pa ye shes kyi phyag
NK052(zi)001:366: rgya lta bu dkyil 'khor bri ba bstan pa'ang bstod
NK052(zi)001:367: pa dang bcas pa'i ming brjod pa'i dbang gis 'debs
NK052(zi)001:369: gso ba dang bsrung ba la sogs pa las so
NK052(zi)001:370: so la sbyar ba rnams kyang tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:371: chen por kun kyang gar ye shes kyi phyag rgyar
NK052(zi)001:372: skur bar bya ba yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:373: so so rang rang gi bya ba la sbyor ba'i
NK052(zi)001:374: dus na'ang rgyas 'debs par byed pa'i mtshan nyid can
NK052(zi)001:375: no // de la sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi
NK052(zi)001:376: shu rtsa brgyad po 'di rang gi ngo bo gang
NK052(zi)001:377: no // yin pa dang / rigs dang bdag po gang yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:378: dus gang du sbyar ba rnams ni le'u dgu pa nyid du sbyor bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:380: phyag rgya chen po dang dam tshig gi phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:381: 'di'i bdag po ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid
NK052(zi)001:382: do // dus gang du sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:383: phyag rgya thams cad yongs su dgrol ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:384: phyag rgya chen po bca' ba thams cad bsdus pa
NK052(zi)001:385: yin pas ji skad du bstan pa rnams las gud
NK052(zi)001:387: dpal rdo rje spyan gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:388: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bsdus pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:389: 'di ni gang dag zab cing rgya che ba la
NK052(zi)001:390: mi mos shing kho re chung ba rnams phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:392: rdo rje sems dpar byin gyis brlabs dngos grub thams cad sgrub par byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:393: de ltar na phyag rgya 'di rnams ngo bo dang
NK052(zi)001:394: bdag po dang dgos pa gang du sbyar ba yongs
NK052(zi)001:395: su shes pa tsam las rgyud kyi don gzhan med
NK052(zi)001:396: de / dbang bskur ba dang dam tshig dpog pa
NK052(zi)001:397: lta bu gsungs pa yang sngon du 'gro ba'i cho
NK052(zi)001:399: dkyil 'khor dag tu ma zhugs shing //
NK052(zi)001:400: dam tshig rnam pa spangs ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:401: gsang ba de nyid mi shes pas //
NK052(zi)001:402: bsgrub pa ci yang mi 'grub bo /
NK052(zi)001:404: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga 'di dag dang ldan pas bsgrub pa'i cho ga bya ba yin la /
NK052(zi)001:405: cho ga de dag kyang phyag rgya'i cho gas bsdus pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:406: de bas na gzhung 'di yang phyag rgya'i rtog pa zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:407: de ltar gdul bya'i skye bo rnam pa gnyis kyi don /
NK052(zi)001:409: rab tu phye ba'i don bshad nas //
NK052(zi)001:410: da rab tu rnam par phye ba la dga' ba
NK052(zi)001:411: rnams kyi don du gzhung rgyas par bshad pa la
NK052(zi)001:413: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:414: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:415: gsang ba mchog gis dgyes pa na //
NK052(zi)001:416: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:418: gcig pu rab tu phye ba'i lha //
NK052(zi)001:419: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:420: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:421: ces bya ba'i yi ge drug cu rtsa bzhi po 'dis ni /
NK052(zi)001:422: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang gi ngo bo ji lta bu zhig yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:423: de'i mtshan nyid dam rnam pa ji lta bur bzhugs
NK052(zi)001:424: par smos pa tsam gyi sgo nas bsdus te bstan
NK052(zi)001:426: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes bya ba la sogs pa ma smos pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:427: rgyud 'di'i spyi'i gzhung tshad 'bum sde drug pa zhig
NK052(zi)001:428: rig pa 'dzin pa'i gnas mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs kyi
NK052(zi)001:430: mi'i gnas su khri brgyad stong pa zhig grags te /
NK052(zi)001:431: de las rtog pa phyogs gcig pa 'di'i rgyud phyi
NK052(zi)001:432: mar byung ba yin pas de dag 'dir mi smos
NK052(zi)001:433: so zhe'o // rnam pa gcig tu ston pa 'jig rten du 'byung ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:434: mya ngan las 'das pa yod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:435: mngon du gyur pa 'dod pa'i lkog tu gyur pa 'dod pa'i skabs su yang dag par byed pas /
NK052(zi)001:436: lkog tu gyur pa'i gnas skabs gzung nas sdud par byed pa na /
NK052(zi)001:437: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes smos par rigs kyi /
NK052(zi)001:438: 'dir ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa' tshul rnam pa
NK052(zi)001:439: du ma'i sgo nas kyang gdul bya rnams la rtag
NK052(zi)001:440: tu mngon sum par bzhugs pa 'dod de /
NK052(zi)001:441: de'i phyir gzhung 'dir 'di ni zhes smos kyi 'di skad ces mi smos so //
NK052(zi)001:442: de bzhin du rtag tu bzhugs zhes smos kyi bdag
NK052(zi)001:443: gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes mi smos so
NK052(zi)001:444: // 'di lta bu ni gzhung 'ba' zhig tu ma zad kyi /
NK052(zi)001:445: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud
NK052(zi)001:446: la sogs pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku gtsor mdzad
NK052(zi)001:447: pa phal las kyang mi smos so //
NK052(zi)001:448: 'o na bshad pa'i rgyud dag las /
NK052(zi)001:449: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi phung po brgyad khri
NK052(zi)001:450: bzhi stong pa thams cad kyi thog mar yi ge
NK052(zi)001:451: e bam gnyis smos pa ni thabs dang shes rab
NK052(zi)001:452: kyi bdag nyid rgyal ba kun gyi pha ma yin
NK052(zi)001:455: ma ni shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK052(zi)001:456: pha ni thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:457: rgyal ba rnams ni 'di las skyes //
NK052(zi)001:459: 'di nyid kyi rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma las kyang /
NK052(zi)001:460: de la ji ltar na dang po'i rigs 'byung ba yin zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:461: ma ni shes rab phal rol phyin //
NK052(zi)001:462: pha ni thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:463: gdul phyir rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK052(zi)001:464: skye ba dag ni rigs yin no //
NK052(zi)001:465: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir na 'di thams cad la dgos pa kho na yin pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:466: 'di skad ces bya ba ni thams cad du smos pa dgos pa yin no zhes na /
NK052(zi)001:467: 'di ni de ltar ma yin te /
NK052(zi)001:468: thabs dang shes rab rnam pa gnyis ni thams cad kyi thams cad du dgos pa bden mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:469: de ston pa'i phyag rgya ni yi ge e bmo rnam pa gnyis kho nar nges pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:470: gsang ba mchog gis dgyes pa bya ba la sogs pas kyang ston par nus pa nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:471: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong zhes grags
NK052(zi)001:472: pa'ang sprul pa'i sku gtsor mdzad pa'i thun mong gi
NK052(zi)001:474: yi ge e bam gnyis kyang thun mong du grags pa'i dbang du bstan par mdzad par zad do //
NK052(zi)001:475: yang ni chos kyi sgo gcig la'ang rnam par grol
NK052(zi)001:476: ba'i sgo mtha' yas pa can yin pas phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:477: gcig la'ang rnam pa grol ba'i sgo gcig tu mi
NK052(zi)001:478: 'gyur ba mtshon pa ma yin la rnam par grol
NK052(zi)001:479: ba'i sgo gang zhig kyang phyag rgya 'ga' zhig kho
NK052(zi)001:480: nas ston pa ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:481: de bas na phyogs 'di la nyes pa brjod par mi bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:482: ha cang spros pas chog go //
NK052(zi)001:483: gzhung nyid brjod par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:484: bzhugs zhes bya ba'i tshig 'di las /
NK052(zi)001:488: de la gang bzhugs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:489: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:490: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:492: de la sems dpa'i sgra ni mu stegs can rnams
NK052(zi)001:493: kyi sems can zhes bya ba grol ba dang bcings
NK052(zi)001:494: pa'i gnas skabs chad na rtag par gnas pa /
NK052(zi)001:495: de yongs su dag pa las bde ba mchog gi gnas la /
NK052(zi)001:497: de lta bu'i sems dpa' de ni nyan thos dag kyang 'dod pa ma yin na /
NK052(zi)001:498: thabs dang shes rab mo'i tshul la gnas pa rnams lta ci smos /
NK052(zi)001:499: de bas na 'dir na mi gnyis pa'i ye shes ni sems dpa'i sgras brjod de /
NK052(zi)001:500: de'i phyir rgyal ba thams cad kyang 'dus ma byas kyis rab tu phye ba yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:501: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi ni gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so //
NK052(zi)001:502: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud phal che ba las /
NK052(zi)001:503: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dbang phyug chen po rdo
NK052(zi)001:504: rje snying po kun tu bzang po gdod ma'i sangs
NK052(zi)001:505: rgyas bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde
NK052(zi)001:506: ba chen po / zhes grags pa yang 'di nyid yin pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:507: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:509: ji skad bstan pa'i sems dpa' de rdo rje ltar thams cad du mi 'gyur ba bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:510: mi phyed cing rang byung ba'i rdo rje sems dpa' 'o //
NK052(zi)001:511: rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba ma lus pa las 'das pas bde ba'i mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:512: yang 'dus pa'i dbang gis bde mchog gi longs spyod
NK052(zi)001:513: rnams la kun nas rol bas kyang de skad ces
NK052(zi)001:514: bya'o // gang na bzhugs zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:515: gsang ba mchog gis dgyes pa na /
NK052(zi)001:517: gnas kyi tshig 'dis ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das
NK052(zi)001:518: rnams kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i gnas zab cing
NK052(zi)001:519: rgya che ba'i spyod yul can /
NK052(zi)001:520: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul las 'das pa /
NK052(zi)001:521: rang bzhin dang rnam par 'phrul ba'i bstan pa ji snyed pa bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:522: de la gsang ba mchog ni gtso bor phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK052(zi)001:523: mtshan ma thams cad las 'das pa spyod yul du mi rung ba' phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:524: de nyid dgyes pa ste sdug bsngal gyi 'tshe ba dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:525: de bas na bzhugs pa'i tshig 'di yang rang byung
NK052(zi)001:526: gi sems dpa' de nyid phyag rgya chen po'i mtshan
NK052(zi)001:528: zhes sbyar gyi gnyis su ni ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:529: yang rnam par 'phrul pa' dbang gis na dpal bde
NK052(zi)001:530: mchog ma la sogs pa mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi
NK052(zi)001:531: dkyil 'khor ni gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa yin
NK052(zi)001:532: te / skal pa med pa rnams kyi spyod yul ma yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:533: longs spyod kyi bde ba'i gnas yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:534: thar pa mchog gi gnas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:535: de na bzhugs pa'ang bcom ldan bde ba chen po
NK052(zi)001:536: de nyid mkha' 'gro ma'i dkyil 'khor na bde ba
NK052(zi)001:537: mchog gi longs spyod la rol cing 'du 'bral med
NK052(zi)001:538: par bzhugs so // zhes sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:539: yang nang gi bde ba la gnas par 'dod pa
NK052(zi)001:540: rnams lam dang 'bras bu dang de'i thabs phyag rgya'i
NK052(zi)001:541: cho ga gcig tu rdzogs par 'dod pa'i dbang du
NK052(zi)001:542: ni / gsang ba ni pad+ma'i b+ha ga'o //
NK052(zi)001:543: de nyid kyang snying po bde ba mchog gi gnas ni dgyes pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:544: de la brten pa' byang chub kyi sems las byung
NK052(zi)001:545: ba bsam pa las 'das pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK052(zi)001:546: bde ba ni mchog gi sgrar brjod do //
NK052(zi)001:547: de bas na der bzhugs pa'i tshig kyang sems dpa'
NK052(zi)001:548: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin de nyid bde ba mchog
NK052(zi)001:549: gi gnas la bde ba dang gnyis su med par
NK052(zi)001:550: bzhugs te / de bas na 'dir go 'phang de
NK052(zi)001:551: bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya'i cho ga yang 'di nyid yin
NK052(zi)001:554: thams cad bdag nyid ces smos te /
NK052(zi)001:555: gnyis su med par bzhugs zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:557: ji skad bstan pa'i don de dag gis /
NK052(zi)001:558: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni rgyal ba thams cad kyi bdag nyid dang /
NK052(zi)001:559: brtan pa dang g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad kyi
NK052(zi)001:560: bdag nyid du rang bzhin rnam par 'phrul pa'i sgo
NK052(zi)001:561: nas gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:563: gang gi tshe bzhugs zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:564: rtag tu bzhugs zhes smos te /
NK052(zi)001:565: ji skad du bstan pa'i tshul rnams ni dus mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK052(zi)001:566: dus yongs su chad pa med pa nyid kyi phyir rtag tu bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:567: de nyid kyi phyir 'di ni zhes te /
NK052(zi)001:568: ji skad bstan pa'i tshul de rnams kyang so so
NK052(zi)001:569: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul du mngon
NK052(zi)001:571: mdzad pa rnams kyang yongs su dag pa'i 'khor rnams
NK052(zi)001:572: la rtag tu de ltar snang ba'i phyir 'di ni
NK052(zi)001:573: zhes bya ba mngon sum gyi sgrar bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:574: de nyid rang byung yin te /
NK052(zi)001:575: rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'i bcom ldan 'das so //
NK052(zi)001:577: byang chub kyi sems ni rigs dang bshes gnyen gyi stobs kyis bskyed pa ma yin /
NK052(zi)001:578: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs kyis mngon par bsgrub pa ma yin /
NK052(zi)001:579: 'bras bu'i ngo bo bla na med pa'i sems dang /
NK052(zi)001:580: thog ma med pa'i rigs kyi sems dag kyang rang bzhin bye brag tu gyur pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:581: thams cad du mi phyed pas de'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:582: kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:583: gang yang de'i dbang du mdzad pa'i gzugs kyi sku rnams la'ang de skad ces bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:584: de nyid bcom ldan 'das te bdud thams cad las 'das pa mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:585: yang b+ha ga ni phyag rgya chen po ste mtshan ma thams cad las 'das pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:586: de dang ldan pas b+ha ga ban no //
NK052(zi)001:587: yang pad+ma b+ha ga'i bde bas kun tu mi gnyis par bzhugs pa ni b+ha ga ban no //
NK052(zi)001:588: yang b+ha ga ni mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs te dbang phyug phun sum tshogs pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:589: 'di rnams la mnga' mdzad pas b+ha ga ban no //
NK052(zi)001:590: gcig pu rab tu che ba'i lha zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:591: ji skad bstan pa'i don gyi dpal rdo rje sems dpa' las gzhan pa'i lha mi dmigs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:592: dbang phyug gzhan med pa'i phyir te /
NK052(zi)001:593: gang gi phyir byang chub sems ni thams cad kyi
NK052(zi)001:594: rang bzhin yin pa dang gtso bo yin pa'i phyir
NK052(zi)001:596: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:597: zhes bshad pa yang yin te /
NK052(zi)001:598: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad dang /
NK052(zi)001:599: brtan pa dang g.yo bas bsdus pa'i dngos po'i yul dang /
NK052(zi)001:600: dus dang gang zag la sogs pa ji skad du
NK052(zi)001:601: grags pa thams cad kyang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK052(zi)001:602: rang bzhin dang mdzad pa rnams kyi phyag rgyar ma
NK052(zi)001:603: gyur pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:607: de la mkha' 'gro ma ni dpal rdo rje bde
NK052(zi)001:608: mchog ma la sogs pa'i lha mo rnams yin te
NK052(zi)001:609: / de yang grags pa dang brdar rtags pa'i phyir mkha' 'a gro ma zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:610: mkha' 'gro ma de rnams nyid sgyu ma yin te
NK052(zi)001:611: 'di ltar dza la zhes bya ba sngon 'jig rten
NK052(zi)001:612: du bud med kyi chu dong du rnga ba btsug
NK052(zi)001:613: nas skyes pa rnams bslus pas de la bud med
NK052(zi)001:615: de nas bud med rnams kyis 'jo ba dang sgeg
NK052(zi)001:616: pa dang rgod pa dang lta ba la sogs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:617: sgyu 'phrul rnams kyis skyes pa bslus pas bud med
NK052(zi)001:618: rnams kyi sgyu 'phrul zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:619: 'dir bcom ldan 'das thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyis
NK052(zi)001:620: bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul de nyid kyis bsdu ba'i
NK052(zi)001:621: dngos po bsdus pa dang thar pa'i lam gyi gtsor
NK052(zi)001:622: sbyar te / lam 'di nyid kyis ba cings pa
NK052(zi)001:623: las grol bar mdzad pas na mkha' 'gro ma sgyu
NK052(zi)001:624: sbyar te / ma zhes bya'o // de nyid bde ba'i mchog yin te /
NK052(zi)001:625: bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi 'dod pa dang chags
NK052(zi)001:626: pa la brten nas bde ba dang yid bde ba
NK052(zi)001:627: zhes bya ba sems gnas pa'i yan lag dang mthun
NK052(zi)001:628: par bskyed do // de'i dbang dang bla ma'i bka'i dbang gis /
NK052(zi)001:629: mi gnas pa'i ye shes thob par 'gyur bas bde ba'i mchog ces bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:630: yang dbang po drug gi longs spyod kyi bde ba
NK052(zi)001:631: thams cad kyis kyang thar ba'i go 'phang gi bde
NK052(zi)001:632: ba chen po thob par byed pas kyang de skad
NK052(zi)001:634: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog gi bdag
NK052(zi)001:635: nyid de nyid kyang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid
NK052(zi)001:636: yin pas / tshig rkang pa brgyad po 'dis dpal
NK052(zi)001:637: rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo gang zhig yin pa
NK052(zi)001:638: yin pas / dang / de'i mtshan nyid dam rnam pa ci 'dra bar bzhugs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:639: tshig gi don 'brel ba'i sgo nas bsdus te bstan pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:640: yi ge yan lag gi don 'brel pa med pa
NK052(zi)001:641: rnams ni 'di dang 'adi'o zhes ris su chad pa
NK052(zi)001:643: gang du khab len g.yo ba ltar //
NK052(zi)001:644: der ni lcags rnams 'du ba bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:645: gang na don dang ldan pa der //
NK052(zi)001:648: de la yi ge'i yan lag gi don 'brel ba
NK052(zi)001:649: med pas bzhugs pa'i tshig 'di dag bstan pa ni
NK052(zi)001:650: / 'di nyid kyi rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma las /
NK052(zi)001:651: de la ji ltar bcom ldan 'das 'dod pa'i thar pa yin zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:652: dngos grub thams cad rjes chags phyir //
NK052(zi)001:654: kun grub zad med bde ba ni //
NK052(zi)001:655: bde ba chen po zhes 'dod do //
NK052(zi)001:656: gsang ba khrag 'thung zhes bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:657: phyag rgya chen po 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:659: dam tshig dam pa shes ldan phyir //
NK052(zi)001:660: dgyes pa dam pa'i nyi ma ste //
NK052(zi)001:661: sprin pa la sogs mchog sgrub phyir //
NK052(zi)001:662: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:663: rdo rje rta mchog las nyid phyir //
NK052(zi)001:664: sangs rgyas kun dngos sems dpa' ste //
NK052(zi)001:665: rdzogs sangs rgyas phyir rnam snang mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:666: rdo rje sems dpa' rgyal po chen //
NK052(zi)001:667: ye shes rdo rje 'dzin mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:669: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' ni dngos grub
NK052(zi)001:670: thams cad la rjes su chags pa'i phyir chags pa
NK052(zi)001:671: zhes bya'o // dngos grub kyi bden pa mi zad pa mnga' bas bden pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:672: de nyid kyi mtshan nyid kyi bye brag sangs rgyas lnga yin te /
NK052(zi)001:674: ra ha s+ya pa ra me ra mye sar+b+aa t+ma ni sa d+aa s+thi ta /
NK052(zi)001:676: ra ha s+ya zhes bya ba ni chags pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:677: ha s+ye ni dga' ba ste chags pa la dga' zhes so //
NK052(zi)001:678: he ru ka ni he he ru ru ka zhes bya ste chags pa'ang dmar ba la dga' ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:680: ra ha s+ye ni gsang ba'i b+ha ga ste /
NK052(zi)001:681: 'di lta bu mtshan nyid kyi chags pa la brten
NK052(zi)001:682: nas gnyis su med pa'i phyag rgya 'grub pa'i phyir
NK052(zi)001:683: / de gnyis ka'ang chags zhes bya bas bsdus pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:684: pa ra me zhes bya ba ni chags pa chen
NK052(zi)001:685: po las byung ba'i dam tshig gi rdzas su gyur
NK052(zi)001:686: pa / mtshal chen po dang byang chub kyi sems la sogs pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:688: pad ma 'dzin pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:689: pad b+ha gas 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:690: pad ma'i rigs 'byung zhes kyang bya ste de'i rigs su byung ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:691: chos de gnyis ni pad ma 'dzin gyis bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:692: ra mye zhes bya ba ni gzi brjid kyi don te dam tshig rdzas kyi yon tan no //
NK052(zi)001:693: rdo rje nyi ma'ang sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin
NK052(zi)001:694: pa'i bdag nyid kyi nyi ma'i gzugs dang spyod lam
NK052(zi)001:695: dang tshul dang gzi brjid ston pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:696: de bas na chos de nyid ni gzi brjid kyis yongs su bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:697: sar+b+b+aa t+ma nam sad+aa s+thi te zhes bya ba ni
NK052(zi)001:698: dpal rta mchog ste las thams cad pa yin pa'i
NK052(zi)001:699: phyir bdag nyid thams cad pas bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:700: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:701: zhes bya ba ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad de
NK052(zi)001:702: mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa nyid kyi phyir
NK052(zi)001:703: ro // de bas na dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK052(zi)001:704: ni chags pa chen po'i dbang gis 'dod pa'i bdag
NK052(zi)001:706: de nyid rigs drug gi rang bzhin du 'gro ba yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:709: 'dod pa dang ni grol ba'ang yin //
NK052(zi)001:711: sngon gyi mkhan po rnams kyi ngan ngag las /
NK052(zi)001:712: ra ha se ni byang chub sems te rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK052(zi)001:713: pa ra me ni rta mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:714: ra me ni rnam pa ra snang mdzad do //
NK052(zi)001:716: rba ni pad ma'i rigs 'byung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:717: ma ni rdo rje nyi ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:718: sa d+aa s+thi te ni de'i bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' bzhugs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:719: 'di ltar rnam pa gang dang gang gis bde ba
NK052(zi)001:720: chen po'i bdag nyid du lus la khyab par bzhugs
NK052(zi)001:721: so zhe'o // yang yi ge bcu drug po 'di ni lus kya khams bcu drug yin la /
NK052(zi)001:722: 'di nyid rang gi lha'i sbyor bas rang nyid lhar
NK052(zi)001:723: sbyar zhing dam tshig gi rdzas su 'ang bsten na
NK052(zi)001:724: / mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi gtso bo rdo rje 'chang du 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:735: de bzhin dus la sogs pa'i yi ger gzhan yang /
NK052(zi)001:749: khu ba rnams te thams cad kyang byang chub sems las byung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:750: 'di dag ni rang bzhin gyi rdzas te /
NK052(zi)001:751: rang gi lus la gnas shing srog 'dzin te bde ba chen po'i bzhir gyur pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:752: de dag nyid dam tshig gi rdzas su spyad pas
NK052(zi)001:753: kyang nam mkha' la 'gro ba sogs pa'i dngos grub
NK052(zi)001:755: rang gi bdag nyid rang gi lhar sbyar bas rdo rje 'chang chen po nyid du 'gyur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:756: de bas na dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni yi
NK052(zi)001:757: ge bcu drug gi bdag nyid khams bcu drug gi
NK052(zi)001:760: de dag la sogs pa yi ge yan lag gi
NK052(zi)001:761: don bshad pa rnams ni gdul bya'i dbang gis yi
NK052(zi)001:762: ge'i yan lag gi sgra la brten nas bshad pa
NK052(zi)001:763: tsam ste / 'on kyang gzhung gi tshogs ni 'brel
NK052(zi)001:764: pa grub pa'i tshig gis khong du chud par bya'o
NK052(zi)001:765: tsam ste / // de ltar dpal rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:766: dpa'i rang gi ngo bo dang rnam pa ci 'dra
NK052(zi)001:767: bar bzhugs pa bsdus pa'i tshul gyis bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:768: de nyid rgyas par bstan pa'i spyir /
NK052(zi)001:769: chags med chags dang bral ba'ang min /
NK052(zi)001:770: dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs so //
NK052(zi)001:772: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:773: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:774: zhes bya ba'i bar dag gsungs pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:775: de la 'di'i bsdus pa'i don ni /
NK052(zi)001:776: gnyis su med pa'i theg pas nges par 'byung ba'i
NK052(zi)001:777: thabs kyii phyag rgya ni bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:778: yin no // sgyu ma'i phyag rgya de nyid na 'kha' 'gro ma zhes bya ba'i brdar bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:779: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma de dang rol pa las
NK052(zi)001:780: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK052(zi)001:781: bde ba chen po thob cing lhag pa'i byang chub
NK052(zi)001:782: kyi sems las skyes bde ba mchog las kyang rtag
NK052(zi)001:783: tu ma 'bral bar bzhugs pas na dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:784: sems dpa' ni mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'
NK052(zi)001:786: de'i rang bzhin ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas la
NK052(zi)001:787: sogs pa brtan pa dang g.yo ba kun gyi rang
NK052(zi)001:788: bzhin du gnas pas sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par
NK052(zi)001:790: de bas na dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang gi ngo bo gang yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:791: rnam pa ci 'dra bar bzhugs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:792: sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:793: zhes bya ba 'di'i don gyis shes so //
NK052(zi)001:794: de la dang po sgyu ma zhes bya ba'i rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:795: chags med chags dang bral ba'ang min //
NK052(zi)001:796: dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs so //
NK052(zi)001:797: bud med kun gyi sgyu ma'i rgyu //
NK052(zi)001:798: 'di ni gnyis med theg pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:800: 'di ltar theg pa chen po ni /
NK052(zi)001:801: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa ste chos
NK052(zi)001:802: thams cad sgyu ma lta bur rtogs pas ngo bo
NK052(zi)001:803: nyid med pa'i phyir 'jig rten ltar chags pa ma
NK052(zi)001:804: yin no // sgyu ma tsam du snang ba'i dbang gis sems can gyi don bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:805: dge ba chos bsdu ba mi gtong bas nyan thos ltar chags pa dang bral ba ma yin no //
NK052(zi)001:806: don du gnyer bas bya ba mi dmigs pas dbu ma yang mi dmigs so //
NK052(zi)001:807: de lta bu'i theg pa de gang zhig yin zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:808: bud med kun gyi sgyu ma'i rgyu //
NK052(zi)001:809: zhes te sgyu ma'i phyag rgya 'di la brten nas nges par 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:810: de yang phyi nang gi bde ba gnyis la rol pa'i sgo nas grub ste /
NK052(zi)001:811: 'di ltar bud med la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon
NK052(zi)001:812: tan gyi bde ba thams cad la thabs dang shes
NK052(zi)001:813: rab kyis zin par spyad pas grub par 'gyur ro
NK052(zi)001:815: rdo rje dang pad ma zung du 'brel ba'i bde
NK052(zi)001:816: ba las gang gi tshe bde ba chen po skye
NK052(zi)001:818: 'di ltar shin tu bde ba la chags pa'i dus
NK052(zi)001:819: na'ang tshor ba bde ba la zhen pas rnam par
NK052(zi)001:820: mi rtog pa'i bde ba chen po mi thob pa'i
NK052(zi)001:821: phyir chags pa med ces bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:822: chags pa dang bral ba'i dus na yang sems 'dzin
NK052(zi)001:823: par byed pa med pas de mi thob pa'i phyir
NK052(zi)001:824: chags pa dang bral ba min zhes bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:825: de gnyis dbus su rang bzhin gyis bde ba bzung bar bya 'o zhes gsungs kyang /
NK052(zi)001:826: dmigs par bya ba thams cad dang bral bar dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs so zhes bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:827: de ni bu da med kyi sgyu 'phrul la brten pas 'grub bo zhes sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:828: thabs dang shes rab kyis yongs su zin no cog theg pa chen po yin no //
NK052(zi)001:829: 'dir bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul kho na lhag par basngagasa pa mdzad ce na /
NK052(zi)001:830: sgyu ma dag ni thams cad pas //
NK052(zi)001:831: bud med sgyu mar khyad par che //
NK052(zi)001:832: ngo bo nyid kyi mthu dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:833: rang bzhin gyis ni de grub bo //
NK052(zi)001:835: phyag rgya'i dngos grub grub par bya ba la thabs
NK052(zi)001:836: kyi sgyu 'phrul gzhan pas bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:838: 'di ltar ngo bo nyid kyi mthu yod cing rang bzhin gyis grub pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:839: de yang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:840: ma chags pa la phyag rgya 'grub pa med pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:841: rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i rdzas su gyur pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:842: gzhan yang de'i yon tan ni thabs dang sems can thams cad bsdus pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:843: bde bas byang chub 'grub pa'ang yin pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:845: gus pas dag tu byed par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:846: rnyed dang bde dang dga' kun gyis //
NK052(zi)001:849: phyir dngos grub rgyu dka' thub dang gtsang sbra dang
NK052(zi)001:850: sdom pas dang skal ba la sogs pas grub par
NK052(zi)001:851: bshad pa rnams / 'dir smad 'tshong la sogs par
NK052(zi)001:852: spyod pas kyang 'grub par 'gyur na gzhan lta ci
NK052(zi)001:853: smos zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:855: du tsa ra zhes bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:856: u yig bar sbyar na dwa zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:857: rdo rje dang pad ma gnyis spyod pas 'grub bo zhes sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:859: du tsa ra na rigs gnyis so //
NK052(zi)001:860: ra ni bral ba ste gnyis bral bas grub bo zhe'o //
NK052(zi)001:861: ji ltar spyad na 'grub ce na //
NK052(zi)001:862: rang gi ngo bo yongs bsgyur nas //
NK052(zi)001:863: bud med kun gyi sgyu mas 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:865: 'dir rang gi ngo bo bsgyur ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:866: sgrub pa po dang bud med rnams kyi phung po
NK052(zi)001:867: dang khams rnams dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dang dpal
NK052(zi)001:868: rdo rje shin tu dga' ma la sogs pa rnams
NK052(zi)001:869: su yongs su bsgyur nas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen
NK052(zi)001:872: rnam pa gcig tu bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul la
NK052(zi)001:873: brten nas bde ba chen po'i ye shes skyes pa'i
NK052(zi)001:874: tshe / dngos po lta ba'ang mtshan mar 'dzin pa
NK052(zi)001:875: dang smon cing chags pa thams cad las 'das te
NK052(zi)001:876: mi dmigs par gyur pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:877: rang gi ngo bo yongs su sgyur ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:879: de lta bu'i sgyu ma'i phyag rgya de nyid mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya'i brdar bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:881: ngo mtshar sgyu ma'i phyag rgya 'di //
NK052(zi)001:882: mkha' 'gro ma zhes brdar bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:884: brdar bstan pa yang mkha' 'gro ma rnams dang phyogs gcig mtshungs pa'i phyir te /
NK052(zi)001:887: da ni nam mkha' 'gro ma zhes //
NK052(zi)001:888: khams las mngon par rtags pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:889: nam mkha' kun tu spyod 'grub pas //
NK052(zi)001:890: mkha' 'gro ma zhes rab tu grags //
NK052(zi)001:892: yi ge da ni nam mkha' la 'gro ba zhes grags te /
NK052(zi)001:894: khams las mngon du brtsags pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:896: 'jig rten gyi b+y+aa ka ra na'i skad kyis dbyings las /
NK052(zi)001:897: d+aa ki n+ai zhes mngon du brtags shing grags so //
NK052(zi)001:898: ji lta bu zhig las grags zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:899: nam mkha' kun tu spyod 'grub pas //
NK052(zi)001:901: nam mkha' la kun tu spyod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:902: sa dang chu la bya ba bzhin 'gro zhing 'ong
NK052(zi)001:903: ba dang 'dzul ba la sogs pa kun tu spyod
NK052(zi)001:905: sa dang chu la sogs pa la yang nam mkha'
NK052(zi)001:906: la bya bzhin chags thogs med par spyod pa 'grub
NK052(zi)001:907: pas de'i phyir mkha' 'gro ma zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:908: de bzhin du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:909: ma'i tshogs la yang mkha' 'gro ma zhes brdar grags
NK052(zi)001:910: pa'i phyir / thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yin //
NK052(zi)001:911: thams cad ma lus bde mchog gi //
NK052(zi)001:912: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:913: mkha' 'gro ma zhes rab tu grags //
NK052(zi)001:915: 'dir phyag rgya dang bde ba mchog kyang don mtshungs te /
NK052(zi)001:917: bde mchog bde mchog ces gsungs pa //
NK052(zi)001:918: sangs rgyas bde mchog thams cad kyi //
NK052(zi)001:919: phyag rgya bde ba'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK052(zi)001:920: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyi phyir na dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:921: sems dpa' phyag rgyar gyur pa gsang ba'i lha mo
NK052(zi)001:922: rnams ni / chos thams cad la khyad par 'jug
NK052(zi)001:923: cing mthu dang rdzu 'a phrul gyis thams cad ngo
NK052(zi)001:924: mtshar bskyed cing 'dul bar byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma
NK052(zi)001:925: rnams dang yid kyis 'dra ba'i phyir 'dir yang 'kha'
NK052(zi)001:929: 'jig rten du grags pa'ang ci zhig las ci lta
NK052(zi)001:930: bu zhig tu grub nas mkha' 'gro zhes grags zhe
NK052(zi)001:931: na / de la ci zhig las grub pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:932: khams las mngon du brtags pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:934: de la khams ni ji skad du bstan pa'i khrag dang /
NK052(zi)001:938: mngon du brtags pa ni de rnams dam tshig gi
NK052(zi)001:939: rdzas su spyad cing bstan te zos pa las grub
NK052(zi)001:940: pa'o // ji lta bu zhig grub ce na /
NK052(zi)001:941: nam mkha' kun tu spyod 'grub pas //
NK052(zi)001:943: nam mkha' la dbang bsgyur bar 'grub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:944: thogs dang bcas pa'i gzugs rnams la ni mkha' bzhin
NK052(zi)001:945: dbang bsgyur ba grub pas de'i phyir de dag gi
NK052(zi)001:946: ming mkha' 'gro ma zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:947: de bzhin du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya'i
NK052(zi)001:948: lha mo rnams kyang mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi grub
NK052(zi)001:949: lugs dang mthun pa'i rol pa'i bde bas mnyes par
NK052(zi)001:950: byed cing de las byung ba'i khams rnams kyang dam
NK052(zi)001:951: tshig gi rdzas su spyad cing bsgrub pa las chos
NK052(zi)001:952: thams cad la dbang sgyur ba'i dngos grub thob pas
NK052(zi)001:953: de bas na mkha' 'gro ma rnams dang /
NK052(zi)001:954: de dang thabs dang 'bras bu rnams mkha' 'gro ma
NK052(zi)001:955: dang yid kyi 'dra bas 'dir yang mkha' 'gro ma
NK052(zi)001:956: zhes grags so // mkha' 'gro ma'i sgra bzhan yang bshad pa /
NK052(zi)001:957: dem ni nam mkhar 'gro ma zhes //
NK052(zi)001:958: sangs rgyas khams las rnam par brtags //
NK052(zi)001:959: kun tu 'gro ba grub pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:960: sangs rgyas kun bdag mkha' 'gro ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:963: dem ba ha ya zhes bya ba sangs rgyas kyi bka' las grags pas /
NK052(zi)001:964: sangs rgyas khams las rnam par brtags //
NK052(zi)001:966: don de dag gis kyang 'dir mkha' 'gro ma zhes
NK052(zi)001:967: bya ba ni thams cad du khyab par 'jug pa'i
NK052(zi)001:969: sangs rgyas kun bdag mkha' 'gro ma //
NK052(zi)001:971: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid las mi gzhan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:973: dem ni de ha ste rang gi lus so //
NK052(zi)001:974: bi ni badz+ri na ste rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK052(zi)001:975: ha ni a ha ha ste mi shigs pa'i thig le'o //
NK052(zi)001:976: ya ni ya da na ste mi mngon pa'i dbyings nas byung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:977: khams kyi sgra ni snga ma bzhin te lus kyi khams so //
NK052(zi)001:978: de nyid sangs rgyas rnams su brtags shing shes par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:980: sangs rgyas khams las rnam par brtags //
NK052(zi)001:981: zhes bya ba la sogs pa rnams su sbyor shes kyang bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:982: de ltar sgyu ma dang mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya ba'i sgra dang don bshad nas /
NK052(zi)001:983: da ni bde mchog ces bya ba' sgra don bshad pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:984: sham zhes bya ba bde bar bshad //
NK052(zi)001:985: sangs rgyas kun gyi bde chen yin //
NK052(zi)001:986: sgyu ma thams cad rab sbyor bas //
NK052(zi)001:987: mchog tu bde bas bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:990: sham+ba ra zhes bya ba sham gyi sgra ni zhi
NK052(zi)001:991: ba dang bsil bar gyur pa la yang 'jug mod
NK052(zi)001:992: kyi / 'dir ni bde ba'i don du sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:993: de yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rnam par mi rtog pa'i bde ba chen po'i bdag nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:995: bdag ni mchog dang gtso bo'i don te 'dir mkha'
NK052(zi)001:996: 'gro ma sgyu ma rnam par rol pa'i bde ba
NK052(zi)001:997: dang ldan bzhin du thar pa'i mchog gi bde ba
NK052(zi)001:998: yang sbyor bas 'jig rten dang nyan thos dag gi
NK052(zi)001:999: bde ba las mchog dang gtsor gyur pa'i phyir bde
NK052(zi)001:1000: ba'i mchog go zhes bya ba'i tha tshigs go //
NK052(zi)001:1001: de ltar mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog bshad nas /
NK052(zi)001:1002: da ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba bshad pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1003: kun tu kun nas thams cad ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos so //
NK052(zi)001:1005: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK052(zi)001:1006: cad kyi dus dang dngos po rnam pa thams cad
NK052(zi)001:1007: kyang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin nyid dang
NK052(zi)001:1008: 'phrul pa yin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas ma yin pa'i
NK052(zi)001:1009: chos med de / sangs rgyas thams cad kyang de'i
NK052(zi)001:1010: bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas thams cad dang
NK052(zi)001:1014: kun tu kun nas thams cad ni //
NK052(zi)001:1015: zhes bya ba ni dus dang dngos po thams cad ston pa'i tshig go //
NK052(zi)001:1016: bdag nyid rtag tu rnam pa kun //
NK052(zi)001:1018: bdag nyid kyi sgra ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:1019: rtag tu ni dus rnam par ma phye ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1020: rnam pa kun tu ni dus dang dngos po rnams
NK052(zi)001:1021: kya rnam pa'i rab tu dbye ba thams cad do
NK052(zi)001:1022: // de dag mdor bsdus pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1023: sangs rgyas la sogs brtan g.yo kun //
NK052(zi)001:1025: de dag thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid du dpal rdo rje sems dpa' gyur pas /
NK052(zi)001:1026: kun gyi dngos por bdag gyur to //
NK052(zi)001:1028: de la bdag ces bya ba'i sgra ni /
NK052(zi)001:1029: 'dir ston pa dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yin pas thams cad nyid yin /
NK052(zi)001:1032: bdag ces bya ba'i tshig gi don rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK052(zi)001:1033: phyi rol pa'i rnam pa gang zag ces kun tu brtags pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1034: nyan thos rnams phung po la bdag ces kun tu brtags pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1035: theg pa chen po rnams phung po'i don blos rnam
NK052(zi)001:1036: par ma phyes pa tsam la bdag ces ming du
NK052(zi)001:1037: brtags dang / gzhan yang phung po'i don blos rnam
NK052(zi)001:1038: par gzhig na rang gi ngo bo gang yang mi
NK052(zi)001:1039: 'grub pa'i bdag nyid pas bdag nyid /
NK052(zi)001:1041: de bas na 'dir bdag gi don bzhi pa nyid
NK052(zi)001:1042: yongs su gzung ste chos rnams kyi bdag nyid ces
NK052(zi)001:1043: bya / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:1044: de bas na thams cad du bdag gyur to //
NK052(zi)001:1046: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba zhes bya ba'i bsdus pa'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:1047: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1048: sems dang sems dpa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK052(zi)001:1049: zhes bya la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1050: de la 'dir sems zhes bya ba ni 'di ltar
NK052(zi)001:1051: bcom ldan 'das de ni thams cad kyi sems nyid
NK052(zi)001:1052: yin no // zhes bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:1053: thams cad kyi sems dpa' nyid yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1055: thams cad kyi sems dpa'i ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1056: zhes bya ba la sogs pa kun la sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:1057: de la thams cad kyi sems nyid ji ltar yin na /
NK052(zi)001:1058: sems rnams kyi rang bzhin ni gdod ma nas dri
NK052(zi)001:1059: ma thams cad dang bral bas byang chub kyi sems
NK052(zi)001:1060: zhes bya ste / de nyid bsam pa'i yul las
NK052(zi)001:1061: 'das te zab cing rgya che ba la bde ba'i
NK052(zi)001:1062: dngos grub zad pa med pa'i gzhir gyur pas rdo
NK052(zi)001:1063: rje ltar brtan pa'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa'i yin
NK052(zi)001:1064: zhes bya ste / no // de nyid kyi phyir
NK052(zi)001:1065: sems dpa' nyid yin te sems nyid brtan pa nyid
NK052(zi)001:1066: zhes bya ste / no // kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1067: de ltar brtan par bsgom pa ni sems dpa'i ting
NK052(zi)001:1068: zhes bya ste / no // kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1069: nge 'dzin to // byang chub spyod pa sna tshogs
NK052(zi)001:1070: zhes bya ste / no // kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1071: nge 'dzin to // nyid // ces bya ba ni
NK052(zi)001:1072: zhes bya ste / no // kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1073: nge 'dzin to // nyid // / ji skad du
NK052(zi)001:1074: zhes bya ste / no // kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1077: gang phyir sems can don 'gyur ba //
NK052(zi)001:1078: de phyir kun tu bzang po yi //
NK052(zi)001:1079: byang chub spyod pa ji bzhin 'gro //
NK052(zi)001:1081: bltams pa dang dka' thub mdzad pa la sogs pa
NK052(zi)001:1082: 'ba' zhig kun tu bzang po'i byang chub kyi spyod
NK052(zi)001:1083: pa yin pa ma zad kyi /
NK052(zi)001:1084: tha na dug gsum dang bdud bzhi po nyid kyang kun tu bzang po'i byang chub kyi spyod pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1087: de bzhin bdud dang bdud las rgyal //
NK052(zi)001:1089: thams cad kyang kun tu bzang po'i byang chub kyi
NK052(zi)001:1090: sems nyid yin pa dang byang chub kyi spyod par
NK052(zi)001:1092: de ni byang chub sangs rgyas yin //
NK052(zi)001:1094: rang gi sems so sor rtog pa byang chub yin la /
NK052(zi)001:1095: rang byin gyis brlabs pa'i sbyor bas de thob pa ni sangs rgyas so //
NK052(zi)001:1096: rdo rje rdo rje 'dzin nyid dang //
NK052(zi)001:1098: rnam par shes pa nyid gdod ma nas dri ma med cing brtan pas rdo rje nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:1099: de so sor rtogs pas thob pa ni rdo rje 'dzin pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1100: de bzhin du pad ma dang nor bu yang sems
NK052(zi)001:1101: nyid ngo bo nyid kyis dri ma med pa dang
NK052(zi)001:1102: de nyid yon tan gyi gzhir gyur pa ste de
NK052(zi)001:1103: 'dzin pa yang snga ma bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:1104: de dag gi yang rigs yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1107: ma ni shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK052(zi)001:1108: pha ni thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:1109: 'dul phyir rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK052(zi)001:1110: skye ba dag ni rigs yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1115: gang du bzhugs pa'i tshig gi skabs su bstan par zad do //
NK052(zi)001:1116: da ni yongs su ma dag pa'i chos sna tshogs kyi bdag nyid yin par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1117: dus gsum srid gsum mchog gsum dang //
NK052(zi)001:1118: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1119: 'di ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1120: 'phrul pa thams cad du snang bar ston pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1122: 'jig rten gsum dag mtha' yas phyir //
NK052(zi)001:1123: gdul phyir srid gsum mchog gsum bdag /
NK052(zi)001:1124: thams cad nyid phyir dkon mchog gsum //
NK052(zi)001:1125: 'jig rten gsum dag khams gsum yin //
NK052(zi)001:1127: bcom ldan 'das de nyid snod bcud du snang ba yang /
NK052(zi)001:1128: sems can bsod nams cher 'phags phyir //
NK052(zi)001:1129: mi g.yo thams cad kho na bdag /
NK052(zi)001:1130: sems 'du byas phyir g.yo ba ste //
NK052(zi)001:1131: 'du byed thams cad kho na'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:1133: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyi phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1134: de dag la sogs pa'i don gyis na /
NK052(zi)001:1135: chos dbyings mnyam dang mi mnyam pa //
NK052(zi)001:1136: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:1137: dngos po thams cad de yin te //
NK052(zi)001:1138: nam mkha' kun gyi skabs na dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs /
NK052(zi)001:1139: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1140: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:1142: 'di ltar chos dbyings mtshan ma med kyang rung /
NK052(zi)001:1143: chos kyi mtshan nyid mtshan ma dang bcas pas bsdus kyang rung ste /
NK052(zi)001:1144: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi khyab pa'i go skabs thams cad na /
NK052(zi)001:1145: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sangs rgyas thams cad dang
NK052(zi)001:1146: mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde
NK052(zi)001:1147: ba'i mchog ces bya ba de'i rang bzhin du ma
NK052(zi)001:1148: gyur pa med cing de'i rnam par mi bzhugs pa
NK052(zi)001:1149: med do // zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:1150: da ni ji ltar sgrub pa'i cho ga bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:1151: de yang gang zhig ci 'dra ba bzhugs pa rnam pa gsum du bstan pa'i dbang gis /
NK052(zi)001:1152: de ji ltar bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya'i cho ga'ang rnam pa gsum du bstan par 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:1153: de las rtog pa dang po /
NK052(zi)001:1154: 'di ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin byang
NK052(zi)001:1155: chub kyi sems kyi mtshan nyid du bzhugs pa yin
NK052(zi)001:1156: pas / de ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs kyi phyag
NK052(zi)001:1157: rgya'ang de kho na nyid snang ba dam pa'i yul
NK052(zi)001:1158: la 'jug pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya yin par
NK052(zi)001:1159: pas / ston te / de nyid bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1160: bskal pa bye ba grangs med par //
NK052(zi)001:1161: sangs rgyas thams cad ma thob pa //
NK052(zi)001:1162: phyag rgya'i cho ga gang dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:1164: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:1165: 'dir phyag rgya'i cho ga ni mtshan ma med pa'i
NK052(zi)001:1166: ting nge 'dzin nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya ste
NK052(zi)001:1167: / 'dis 'debs shing rang gi rang bzhin du byin gyis rlabs par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1168: 'dir sangs rgyas kun bdag bde ba'i mchog ni /
NK052(zi)001:1169: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1170: bdag nyid shin tu sgrub pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1171: rang sems nyid byang chub kyi sems nyid byang chub
NK052(zi)001:1172: kyi sems rdo rje sems dpa' yin pas der sbyor
NK052(zi)001:1173: ba las de nyid 'grub bo zhe'o //
NK052(zi)001:1175: rang gi dam tshig bdag sbyor bas //
NK052(zi)001:1176: zhes bya ba 'di yang spyir dam tshig gi tshig
NK052(zi)001:1177: gi don gzhung lugs dang sdom pa dang lha dang
NK052(zi)001:1178: dkyil 'khor dang dam rdzas dam bud med dang chos
NK052(zi)001:1179: nyid dang ye shes la sogs la 'jug ste /
NK052(zi)001:1180: skabs 'dir ni rang gi dam tshig ni rang gi lha ste /
NK052(zi)001:1182: spyir sems so sor rtogs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1184: yi ge la sogs la 'jug pa las /
NK052(zi)001:1185: 'dir byang chub kyi sems so sor rtogs pa'i mtshan nyid mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK052(zi)001:1186: rang gi dam tshig bdag sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1189: byang chub sems la rab brtson na //
NK052(zi)001:1191: byang chub sems 'di rdo rje ste //
NK052(zi)001:1192: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK052(zi)001:1194: rang gis sems gdod ma nas rnam par dag pa gang yin pa de ni /
NK052(zi)001:1195: dus thams cad du bsten pa'i phyir rdo rje ste /
NK052(zi)001:1196: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyang de nyid yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1197: de bas na de nyid du sbyar na de nyid yin pa'i phyir de grub par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:1199: yin pa la sgrub ci dgos zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:1200: 'dir ma shes shing goms par ma gyur ba rnams
NK052(zi)001:1201: shes shing goms pa klong du gyur pa tsam la
NK052(zi)001:1202: dngos grub thob ces tha snyad du 'jug pa ma
NK052(zi)001:1203: gtogs par / ma thob pa thob par byar med do //
NK052(zi)001:1205: de kho na nyid snang ba dam pa'i yul la
NK052(zi)001:1206: 'jug pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya zhes bya ba
NK052(zi)001:1207: ni / byang chub sems ni de kho na bzhin
NK052(zi)001:1208: te 'gyur ba med pa'i de kho na nyid do
NK052(zi)001:1209: ni / // de blo phyin ci ma log pa
NK052(zi)001:1210: rnams kyi yul du de ltar snang ba ni yul
NK052(zi)001:1211: du snang ba rnams kyi dam pa yin pas de
NK052(zi)001:1212: ni / // skad ces bya'o // 'di ltar snang
NK052(zi)001:1213: ba thams cad las 'das pa ni snang ba rnams
NK052(zi)001:1214: kyi mchog tu gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1215: de la 'jug pa ni gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1216: de nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1217: rtog pa ni gzhung dang thabs dang dngos grub lha la sogs pa la 'jug ste /
NK052(zi)001:1218: 'dir ni gzhung de'i yul du gyur pa thabs kyi cho ga rnams la 'jug ste /
NK052(zi)001:1219: de'i skabs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1222: rnam par mi rtog chos dag las //
NK052(zi)001:1223: sems can don du yongs su rtog /
NK052(zi)001:1224: de phyir rtog pa zhes bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:1225: rtog pa yongs su dag phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1227: chos thams cad kyang rang bzhin spros pa dang bral
NK052(zi)001:1228: ba nyid kyis stong pa'i bdag nyid dang yul ma
NK052(zi)001:1229: yin zhing sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs kyang de bzhin
NK052(zi)001:1230: du rnam par mi rtog kyang sngon gyi smon lam
NK052(zi)001:1231: dang thugs rje'i dbang gis sems can mtshan ma sna
NK052(zi)001:1232: tshogs kyi rtog pas brlag cing rmongs par gyur pa
NK052(zi)001:1233: rnams la rtog pa de dag thams cad dbyer med
NK052(zi)001:1234: par dus gcig tu 'joms par byed pa'i thabs kyi
NK052(zi)001:1235: rtog pa sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer med mi
NK052(zi)001:1236: phyed pa'i mtshan nyid can rtog pa'i bdag nyid ston
NK052(zi)001:1237: pas de'i phyir rtog pa zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1239: da ni rtog pa gnyis pa /
NK052(zi)001:1240: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan nyid dam rnam pa
NK052(zi)001:1241: ci 'dra bar bzhugs pa gnyis pa yongs su dag
NK052(zi)001:1242: pa'i dbang gi sku'i mtshan nyid /
NK052(zi)001:1243: de sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:1244: sems dpar kun tu sbyor ba zhes bya ba'i phyag
NK052(zi)001:1245: rgya ston te / 'dir yang dpal rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:1246: dpa'i rang bzhin gyi sgo nas thabs kyi che ba
NK052(zi)001:1248: de'i rjes su thabs kyi cho ga 'bras bu dang
NK052(zi)001:1249: bcas pa ston kyang thabs kyi che ba dang 'bras
NK052(zi)001:1250: bu ni zhar la bshad pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1251: de sgrub pa'i mthu dang yon tan ci 'dra ba
NK052(zi)001:1252: zhig 'thob pa ni rtog pa bzhi par mgo dril
NK052(zi)001:1255: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK052(zi)001:1256: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1257: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:1259: gong du bstan pa ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK052(zi)001:1260: de gang zhig ci 'dra zhes dris pa khong nas
NK052(zi)001:1261: phyung ba de ston pa'i tshig ste /
NK052(zi)001:1262: rtog pa 'og ma thams cad la yang de bzhin du sbyar bar bya 'o //
NK052(zi)001:1264: gong du bstan pa bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:1265: rnal 'byor bcom ldan 'das zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1266: rnal 'byor gyi gtso bo dbang phyug chen po yang yin la /
NK052(zi)001:1267: bcom ldan 'das kyang yin pas de skad ces bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1268: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag sbyor bas //
NK052(zi)001:1269: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1270: sgrub thabs kyi che ba ston pa'i zhal la rdo
NK052(zi)001:1271: rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin dang rnam pa'ang ston par
NK052(zi)001:1272: byed do // de la 'dir rdo rje sems dpar sbyor ba ni de'i gzugs kyi skur sbyor ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1273: dbab pa thams cad ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK052(zi)001:1274: dpal rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa dngos grub thams
NK052(zi)001:1276: de la 'dir skabs kyi che ba'i don nam /
NK052(zi)001:1278: dngos grub kyi rgyu ni rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK052(zi)001:1279: dngos grub thob par 'gyur ba'i las skye ba gzhan
NK052(zi)001:1280: la bas gas pa rnam par smin pa ma phyung
NK052(zi)001:1282: dngos grub kyi gegs kyi rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems ma bskyed pa /
NK052(zi)001:1283: bka' bzhin ma byas pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1285: ma dad pa dang rnam pa bzhi spangs shing gtsang zhing bsdams pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1286: dad pa dang mos pa brtan pa thob pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1287: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig pa thob pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1288: de ltar yan lag bzhi dang ldan pa'i sgrub pa
NK052(zi)001:1289: pos yan lag de dag rab 'bring ji ltar thob
NK052(zi)001:1290: pa'i bye brag gis dngos grub rab 'bring du gyur
NK052(zi)001:1292: rnal 'byor gyi spyi'i rgyud kyi tshul las ni skyon gyi rtsa ba bzhi po de dag med na /
NK052(zi)001:1293: gtsang sbra dang sdom pa dag med kyang /
NK052(zi)001:1294: skal pa dang mos pa dang mnyam par bzhag pa
NK052(zi)001:1295: rab 'bring gi dbang gis dngos grub tu 'gyur ro
NK052(zi)001:1297: 'dir ni dad pa dang mnyam par bzhag pa yod
NK052(zi)001:1298: pa na skal ba med kyang 'grub par gsungs te
NK052(zi)001:1300: dkyil 'khor du yang ma zhugs pa'ang //
NK052(zi)001:1301: sgrib pa kun dang ldan pa'ang rung //
NK052(zi)001:1302: ngang gi lhar ni bdag sbyor na //
NK052(zi)001:1305: de bzhin du gnas la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1306: da ni thabs kyi cho ga nyid bstan pa /
NK052(zi)001:1307: bskal pa bye bar mi 'thob pa //
NK052(zi)001:1308: sangs rgyas dam pa thams cad de //
NK052(zi)001:1309: phyag rgya'i cho ga gang dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:1310: sgrub na kun tu thob 'gyur ba //
NK052(zi)001:1311: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1313: dpal rdo rje sems dpar kun tu sbyor ba'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:1315: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1316: cha lugs ji bzhin bsgyur ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:1318: 'dir cha lugs bzhin bsgyur ba ni thams cad 'byung
NK052(zi)001:1319: byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya la sogs pas de
NK052(zi)001:1321: rmi lam mig dang so dang mchu //
NK052(zi)001:1322: kha dang lus dang rkang lag gis //
NK052(zi)001:1323: cha lugs bzhin du gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:1324: zhes gsungs pa dang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:1325: dpal rdo rje sems dpar kun tu sbyor ba'i phyag rgya la bsgrub pa'i skabs su ni /
NK052(zi)001:1326: dam tshig gi lha mo yid la sprul pas mchod kyang rung /
NK052(zi)001:1327: phyi rol gyi phyag rgyas mchod kyang rung ste /
NK052(zi)001:1328: spros pa med pa la dga' ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:1329: spros pa dang bcas pa rnams kyi yang spyi'i thun mong gi phyag rgyar 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:1331: thams cad bdag nyid sbyor mchod dpal //
NK052(zi)001:1333: rnal 'byor kun la nyer sbyor bas //
NK052(zi)001:1336: de la rnal 'byor gyi bye brag 'di dag kyang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud phal las grags te /
NK052(zi)001:1337: grangs dang rang gi ngo bo dag kyang yul so sor sbyor ba byed do //
NK052(zi)001:1338: de la re zhig phyogs 'ga' las grags pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1344: de la thams cad sbyor ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1346: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK052(zi)001:1349: de yi nyer bar sbyor ba ni //
NK052(zi)001:1350: khams gsum ma lus thams cad do //
NK052(zi)001:1352: khams gsum gyi 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad dpal
NK052(zi)001:1353: rdo rje sems dpa'i nye ba'i longs spyod yin te
NK052(zi)001:1355: gzugs dang sgra dang de bzhin dri //
NK052(zi)001:1356: ro dang reg dang de bzhin yang //
NK052(zi)001:1357: rdo rje sems dpa' 'dra bas na //
NK052(zi)001:1358: de rnams de bzhin nyid kyis bsten //
NK052(zi)001:1359: chos kyi dbyings las byung ba yin //
NK052(zi)001:1360: rgyal chen dngos grub ster bar 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1362: nye bar sbyor ba'i yan lag tu gyur pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1365: shin tu sbyor rnams yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1366: de la rab tu sbyor ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1368: ting nge 'dzin rab tu sbyor bar bshad /
NK052(zi)001:1370: nye ba'i longs spyod gang la spyod kyang rang gi lha'i rnal 'byor du byas pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1372: rnal 'byor kun la longs spyod kyis //
NK052(zi)001:1373: ji ltar bde ba kun bstan cing //
NK052(zi)001:1374: rang gi lha yi rnal 'byor gyis //
NK052(zi)001:1375: bdag nyid rab tu mchod par bya //
NK052(zi)001:1376: zhes gsungs pa 'di dang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:1378: lha mo rnams dang sbyor ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:1380: rjes su sbyor bas mchod na ni //
NK052(zi)001:1381: sbyor ba kun gyi bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:1382: sangs rgyas brda' yi phyag rgya yis //
NK052(zi)001:1383: bde ba chen po yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:1385: rjes su sbyor ba rjes su sgrub //
NK052(zi)001:1386: skyes pa ltar byed dga' spyod pa //
NK052(zi)001:1387: slar yang rjes su sgrub par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:1388: ces gsungs pa nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1389: rnam pa gcig tu nye bar sbyor ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1390: dbang po drug gi spyod yul yin la /
NK052(zi)001:1391: yid kyi yul chos la sbyor ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1394: rnal 'byor kun gyis longs spyod kyis //
NK052(zi)001:1395: zhes bya ba la sogs pa tshig rkang ba bzhi gsungs pa 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1397: sangs rgyas brda' yi phyag rgya yis //
NK052(zi)001:1398: chos ni sbyor ba yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:1399: sbyor ba'i longs spyod thams cad kyis //
NK052(zi)001:1400: ji ltar bde bar bsten byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:1401: rang gi lhag pa'i lhar sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1402: rang gi mchod pa dam tshig yin //
NK052(zi)001:1404: sbyor ba zhes bya ba'i don yang /
NK052(zi)001:1406: ye shes tsam la mnyam 'jog pa //
NK052(zi)001:1407: rnal 'byor zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK052(zi)001:1410: bde ba chen po mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1411: sbyor ba'i bye brag gis rdo rje sems dpa' rnam pa bzhi 'grub pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1412: rdo rje sems dpa'i dpal tshe dang //
NK052(zi)001:1413: lang tsho nad med bde mchog 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:1415: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' kun tu sbyor ba'i rtogs pa zhes bya ba la /
NK052(zi)001:1416: dpal rdo rje sems dpar sbyor ba nyid kun tu sbyor ba yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1418: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1419: sbyor ba thams cad yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:1421: sbyor ba'i bye brag 'di dag dang sgrub pa'i bye
NK052(zi)001:1422: brag gsungs pa'ang skabs kha cig tu don 'dra bar
NK052(zi)001:1423: snang ste / gzhung 'di dang cha mthun par rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gzhan las kyang 'byung ste /
NK052(zi)001:1428: shin tu sgrub pa dang lnga gsungs la /
NK052(zi)001:1430: shin tu sbyor dang sbyor che ba //
NK052(zi)001:1431: sbyor ba rab sbyor sbyor skyes pa //
NK052(zi)001:1432: bde ba chen po nyid kyis gsungs //
NK052(zi)001:1433: zhes bya ba bstan pa'i skabs su /
NK052(zi)001:1434: sgrub pa lha yis sbyor ba ste //
NK052(zi)001:1435: rjes su sgrub pa lha mo'i don //
NK052(zi)001:1436: sgrub pa chen po gnyis ka'i rgya //
NK052(zi)001:1437: mnyam par sbyor ba rdo rje mchog /
NK052(zi)001:1438: nye bar sgrub pa gnyis ga'i gnas //
NK052(zi)001:1439: shin tu sgrub pa bde dam pa //
NK052(zi)001:1441: sgrub pa lnga pa 'di yang sbyor ba lnga dang rang bzhin tha dad pa med do //
NK052(zi)001:1443: bcom ldan rdo rje sbyor ba ste //
NK052(zi)001:1444: rab tu sbyor ba mkha' la 'gro //
NK052(zi)001:1445: phyag rgya de dang rab sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1446: sbyor ba chen por grags pa yin //
NK052(zi)001:1450: sbyor ba rab sbyor skal ldan pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:1451: rab dgyes ro myang bde dam pa //
NK052(zi)001:1452: lha dang lha nyid yang dag sbyor //
NK052(zi)001:1453: 'di ni gnyis su med ces bya //
NK052(zi)001:1456: de dag gi 'bras bu dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i go 'phang ngo zhe'o //
NK052(zi)001:1457: sgrub pa dang sbyor ba' don 'di dag kyang rnal
NK052(zi)001:1458: 'byor gyi rgyud zab mo rnams kyi thabs kyi cho
NK052(zi)001:1459: ga yin par shes par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:1460: 'di nyid kyi gzhung du'ang ji ltar rigs par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1462: da ni rtog pa gsum pa /
NK052(zi)001:1463: 'dir dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ci 'dra bar bzhugs
NK052(zi)001:1464: pa'i rnam pa gsum pa mchod pa' lha mo rnams
NK052(zi)001:1465: kyi bdag por bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1466: ji ltar sgrub pa'i cho ga gyur pa dpal rdo
NK052(zi)001:1467: rje dam tshig ces bya ba rjes su sbyor ba'i
NK052(zi)001:1469: de yang 'dir yang snga ma bzhin du rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:1470: sems dpa'i rang bzhin thabs kyi che ba dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:1472: de'i rjes su thabs kyi dngos po phyag rgya'i cho ga 'bras bu dang bcas pa ston to //
NK052(zi)001:1475: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni rang bzhin bstan pa snga ma bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:1477: rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK052(zi)001:1478: dpal ldan rang gi dam tshig bde //
NK052(zi)001:1479: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1480: 'dir rang gi dam tshig ni lha mo ste /
NK052(zi)001:1482: dam tshig mchog ni rig ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1484: de ltar rang gi dam tshig ma dang sbyor ba'i mthu yis ci zhig 'grub par 'gyur ce na /
NK052(zi)001:1485: phyag rgya bde ba chen po kun //
NK052(zi)001:1486: so sor rjes su rab grub 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1487: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1489: rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan btab la //
NK052(zi)001:1490: cung zad mi 'grub yong med do //
