NK052(zi)001:1491: phyag rgya kun gyi bde ba che //
NK052(zi)001:1492: bdag nyid sor sor rjes su 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:1493: ces gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK052(zi)001:1494: phyag rgya ma la brten pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes grub pa'am /
NK052(zi)001:1495: mtshan ma thams cad las 'das pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i bde ba nyid 'grub bo //
NK052(zi)001:1497: rnal 'byor bde ba mos pa kun //
NK052(zi)001:1499: bde ba mos pa ni 'dod pa'i yon tan te /
NK052(zi)001:1501: de yi gzugs dang sgra dang dri //
NK052(zi)001:1502: ro dang reg pa bde mos pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1504: rnal 'byor ni phyag rgya rnams la yid 'byor ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1505: de dang bcas par thob ces bya ba' tha tshig go //
NK052(zi)001:1506: bde ba mos pa'i dngos grub kun //
NK052(zi)001:1508: nam mkha' la sogs pa'i longs spyod do //
NK052(zi)001:1509: bde ba mos ma'i dbang phyug kun //
NK052(zi)001:1511: sa'i dbang phyug la sogs pa'i longs spyod do //
NK052(zi)001:1512: nam mkha'i dbyings nas mtha' klas pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:1513: bud med mchog rnams skye bar 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1515: ye shes kyi lha mo rnams dang lhan cig sbyor ba thob par 'gyur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1517: de yi dam tshig de byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:1518: sdug pa dam tshig bdag rjes 'brang //
NK052(zi)001:1519: shin tu sbyor dang sbyor chen po //
NK052(zi)001:1520: thams cad bdag nyid dam tshig mchog /
NK052(zi)001:1521: ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1522: de ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa' 'o //
NK052(zi)001:1523: de'i dam tshig ni lha mo rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:1524: de 'byung ba ni snang ba thob par gyur pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1525: sdug pa ni rang gi yid 'phrog par snang ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:1526: bdag la gus shing chags pas dga' bar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1527: dam tshig bdag rjes 'brang ba ni rjes su mthun par byed pa dang mi nyams pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1528: shin tu sbyor dang sbyor chen po ni de dag
NK052(zi)001:1529: dang gnyis su med par rol pa mtshan ma med
NK052(zi)001:1531: de dag kyang gang gi yin zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:1532: thams cad kyi bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dam tshig lha mo mchog rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:1534: da ni de sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1535: gcig bzhin du ni gcig spyod pa //
NK052(zi)001:1536: lhan cig spyod dang rjes spyod sdug /
NK052(zi)001:1537: ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1538: 'di dag ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i 'khor gyi lha mo spyi ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul dang /
NK052(zi)001:1539: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyag
NK052(zi)001:1540: rgya ma rnams dang ji ltar gnas shing spyad pa
NK052(zi)001:1541: thun mong du bstan pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1542: rgyud gzhan gyi skabs su ni /
NK052(zi)001:1543: rdo rje spun dang ming sring dam tshig ji ltar bsrung ba'i thabs su'ang 'chad do //
NK052(zi)001:1544: de la 'dir gcig bzhin du gcig spyod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1545: gtso bo nyid dang dbyer med par spyod pa'i gzungs
NK052(zi)001:1546: ma ste dpal rdo rje rab tu dga' ma lta
NK052(zi)001:1547: bu'o // lhan cig sbyod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1548: lhan cig gi steng du spyod pa ste dpal bde mchog ma la sogs pa bzhi rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:1550: de dang cung zad nye ba'i phyogs nas mnyes par byed pa rnams te /
NK052(zi)001:1551: rigs dang mchod pa'i lha mo gzhan rnams te de
NK052(zi)001:1552: lta bu'i lha rnams kyi mchod pa'i yon tan 'og
NK052(zi)001:1554: skyes bu'i tshul gyis dga' bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:1556: sa'i steng na gnas pa'i lha rnams dang mi'i tshul gyis so //
NK052(zi)001:1557: dbang po kun las byung ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:1558: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i mchod pa 'di ni /
NK052(zi)001:1559: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor pa la de dag gis mchod pa byed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1561: gang gis yang dag par mthong dang //
NK052(zi)001:1562: bdag po chen po mchod byed na //
NK052(zi)001:1563: de yis ston pa kun mthong ste //
NK052(zi)001:1564: rgyal ba mchog la mchod par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1565: de la lha kun mchod byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:1566: skad cig skad cig phyag kyang byed //
NK052(zi)001:1567: rab dgyes mtshan dang mdza' chen mo //
NK052(zi)001:1568: ro dang reg gis che ba'i che //
NK052(zi)001:1569: rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:1570: bde byed chen la mchod par byed //
NK052(zi)001:1571: skal ba chen mo'i sring mo yang //
NK052(zi)001:1572: bde byed bde bas rab rmongs ma //
NK052(zi)001:1573: mchod pa'i sprin phung bde ldan ma'i //
NK052(zi)001:1574: rgyal chen mchog gi mchod par byed //
NK052(zi)001:1575: ces bya ba la sogs pa lta bu ste /
NK052(zi)001:1577: rab tu rmongs pas dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1578: zhes bya ba'i don yang bshad pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1579: byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po'i lha'i chus
NK052(zi)001:1580: reg pas rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma'i dri ma
NK052(zi)001:1581: dag pa ste gsang ba dang ye shes kyi dbang
NK052(zi)001:1582: bskur ba thob par byas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1583: de nyid kyi dngos grub thob pa'ang yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1584: rnal 'byor thams cad bde ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:1585: rjes su sbyor bas mchod byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:1586: kun tu myong bar byed pa na //
NK052(zi)001:1587: shin tu sbyor ba rang grub 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:1589: 'dir yang rjes su sbyor ba ni gzungs dang sbyor ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1590: myang ba ni bde ba chen po'i ro myang ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1591: shin tu sbyor ba ni mtshan ma las 'das pa ste des rang bzhin gyis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:1593: kun tu myang ba ni dngos grub kyi rdzas byang chub kyi sems rtsa ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:1594: de zos pas 'og nas gsungs pa'i dngos grub tu 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:1596: skal pa bzang po dam tshig gi rtog pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1598: lha mo thams cad kun 'dus pas //
NK052(zi)001:1599: thams cad sna tshogs skal pa bzang //
NK052(zi)001:1601: de nyid dam tshig kyang yin no //
NK052(zi)001:1603: da ni dris tshig bzhi pa /
NK052(zi)001:1604: de yi mthu yang ci 'dra ste //
NK052(zi)001:1605: zhes smos pa de ston par byed de /
NK052(zi)001:1606: de ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin gang
NK052(zi)001:1607: zhig mtshan nyid rnam pa gsum du bzhugs par bstan
NK052(zi)001:1608: pa de rnams mnyes par bya ba'i thabs kyi cho
NK052(zi)001:1609: ga phyag rgya rnam pa gsum gyis sgrub pas de'i
NK052(zi)001:1610: mthu dang yon tan gyis phye ba'i rnam pa ji
NK052(zi)001:1611: lta bu zhig thob par 'gyur zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:1614: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1616: lha mo kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:1617: skal ba bzang mchog 'dod pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:1618: yang dag sbyor ba'i bde myong ba //
NK052(zi)001:1619: 'dod chags ther zug brtan pa can //
NK052(zi)001:1620: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1621: de la lha mo ni chos kyi dbyings te /
NK052(zi)001:1622: de ni 'dod pa'i yul gyi mchog go //
NK052(zi)001:1623: de la sbyor ba ni gnyis su med pa'i chos kyi sku ste /
NK052(zi)001:1624: dus gsum las 'das pa 'dod chags ther zug brtan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1625: de yi rtags kyi phyag rgya dpal rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:1626: dpa'i sku lha mo la rol pa' bde ba dang
NK052(zi)001:1627: rtag tu mi 'bral bar snang ste /
NK052(zi)001:1628: de lta bu'i dngos grub grub par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:1630: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzugs chen dang //
NK052(zi)001:1631: zhes bya ba la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ni /
NK052(zi)001:1632: chos kyi dbyings nas yul gyi lha mo la ye shes spyod yul du rol pa'i yum mo //
NK052(zi)001:1634: yul rnams ni spyad par bya ba yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1635: mo'i rtags kyis bstan pas yum rnams yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1637: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzugs chen ni sangs rgyas spyan no //
NK052(zi)001:1638: de bzhin du dbyangs ni gos dkar mo'o //
NK052(zi)001:1641: reg ni dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1644: dbyangs ni rdo rje dbyangs ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1645: dri ni rdo rje phreng ba ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1646: ro ni rdo rje gar byed ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1647: bde bar gshegs pa'i yum de dag thams cad la yang longs spyod par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:1649: sangs rgyas pha rol phyin grub pa //
NK052(zi)001:1651: sangs rgyas rnams kyi pha rol tu phyin ma rnams ni lam dang 'bras bu'i chos te /
NK052(zi)001:1652: bskyed pa dang yongs su spyad par bya ba'i phyir yum rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:1654: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu ni yongs su spyad par bya ba yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1655: mo'i rtags kyi bstan pas lha mo yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1656: thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyis lha mo'i skur bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1657: 'di ltar sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yum chen mo shes rab pha rol phyin ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:1658: de bzhin du yum chen mo bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin ma la sogs te /
NK052(zi)001:1659: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu'i lha mo dbyibs dang
NK052(zi)001:1660: kha dog dang mtshan ma dang bcas pas de bzhin
NK052(zi)001:1661: gshegs pa'i gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor chen por bzhugs pa
NK052(zi)001:1662: rnams so // gzungs dang sa rnams de bzhin du //
NK052(zi)001:1664: gzungs ni dran pa dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:1665: de nyid sangs rgyas rnams bskyed pa dang spyod pas yum mo //
NK052(zi)001:1667: de nyid dang mo'i rtags kyis bstan pas lha mo rnams yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1668: thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyis lha mo'i dbyibs dang
NK052(zi)001:1669: kha dog dang mtshan mas gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor na
NK052(zi)001:1672: yum chen mo tshig gi gzungs dang /
NK052(zi)001:1673: yum chen mo don gyi gzungs dang /
NK052(zi)001:1674: yum chen mo mi brjed pa za ma tog gi
NK052(zi)001:1675: gzungs la sogs pa ji skad du grags pa thams
NK052(zi)001:1676: cad do // sa rnams ni shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyi bdag nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:1677: de yang skyed pa dang spyad pas yum yin pa snga ma bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:1679: de nyid dang mo'i rtags kyis bstan pas lha mo yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1680: thabs mkhas pa nyid kyis bud med kyi dbyibs dang
NK052(zi)001:1681: kha dog dang mtshan mas gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK052(zi)001:1684: yum chen mo rab tu dga' ma dang yum chen mo dri ma med ma zhes bya ba nas /
NK052(zi)001:1685: yum chen mo chos kyi sprin ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:1686: yum chen mo kun tu 'od ma la sogs pa bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:1687: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud chen mo rnams las ji skad
NK052(zi)001:1688: du grags pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yum thams cad la
NK052(zi)001:1692: gzhan yang rdo rje can gyi grub mchog ni phyag na rdo rje'i yum mchog ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1693: sangs rgyas dag las bde ba dam pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum dam pa'i bde ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1694: phrogs nas nye bar spyad par byed //
NK052(zi)001:1696: dngos grub thams cad ma yin par len pa'i sgras bshad pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK052(zi)001:1697: de ltar ston pa'i byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1698: mthu chen las ni bkra shis brtan //
NK052(zi)001:1700: khyab 'jug gi chung ma bkra shis brtan no //
NK052(zi)001:1701: 'phrog las grub ces bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1702: dbang phyug chen po'i chung ma u ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1703: dran pas dga' zhes bya ba ni //
NK052(zi)001:1704: k+aa ma de ba'i chung ma dga' sdug mi'i dbang phyug ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:1705: gzhan ni snga ma bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:1706: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdzul 'phrul che /
NK052(zi)001:1707: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i /
NK052(zi)001:1708: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis par gyur nas sangs
NK052(zi)001:1709: rgyas kyi mdzad pa thams cad ston par byed pa'o
NK052(zi)001:1710: // skal ba bzang po mchog gi dngos grub ces bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1711: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi go 'phang dang
NK052(zi)001:1712: thun mong gi dngos grub chen po gnyis ka la
NK052(zi)001:1713: yang mchog gi dngos grub ces bya ba'i sgra 'jug
NK052(zi)001:1714: pa'i phyir ro // rtog pa bzhi pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1715: da ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i 'phrul ba'i dri ba rnam pa gsum ston te /
NK052(zi)001:1717: gzhan yang ci rigs rnam 'phrul pa'ang //
NK052(zi)001:1718: gang rnams ci 'dra de bzhin du //
NK052(zi)001:1719: rang don las rnams sgrub byed pa //
NK052(zi)001:1721: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de'i rnam par 'phrul pa ni gang dang gang rnams yin /
NK052(zi)001:1722: 'phrul pa de'i rnam pa ni ci 'dra bar 'byung /
NK052(zi)001:1723: de dag mnyes par bya ba'i thabs kyi cho ga
NK052(zi)001:1724: gang gis mnyes shing bsgrubs pas rang rang gi don
NK052(zi)001:1725: gyi las 'bras bu ni ci 'dra ba zhig 'grub
NK052(zi)001:1727: de la dang por dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid
NK052(zi)001:1728: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs kyis sems can ji ltar
NK052(zi)001:1729: 'dod pa bzhin du sna tshogs su 'phrul pa bstan
NK052(zi)001:1730: pa'i phyir / 'di ni rnal 'byor bcom ldan 'das //
NK052(zi)001:1731: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1733: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK052(zi)001:1734: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:1736: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni gdod ma nas sangs pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1737: rtag tu dri ma thams cad kyis ma bslad pa'i phyir dang /
NK052(zi)001:1738: dngos grub thams cad kyi mchog gi bdag nyid du grub pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1739: de'i bdag nyid las ma sprul pa'i sangs rgyas ni phyogs dang dus gzhan du mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1740: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:1741: de nyid 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs kyis rigs drug
NK052(zi)001:1742: gis bsdus pa'i sprul pa mtha' yas par bstan pas
NK052(zi)001:1745: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'phrul pa
NK052(zi)001:1746: de bzhin du sgrub pa po rnams kyis kyang de
NK052(zi)001:1747: bzhin du sgrub pas 'bras bu 'byung bar bstan pa'i
NK052(zi)001:1748: phyir / nyin re'am yang na zla re'am //
NK052(zi)001:1749: yang na de bzhin lo rer ni //
NK052(zi)001:1750: ji bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK052(zi)001:1751: sangs rgyas bde mchog gar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1752: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1753: de la ji skad du smos pa'i tshig 'di dag
NK052(zi)001:1754: gis ni sgrub pa po brtson 'grus rab 'bring gi
NK052(zi)001:1755: dbang gis ji ltar sgrub cing mchod pa'i dus dang
NK052(zi)001:1757: khams kyi ngo bo thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:1758: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:1759: sgrub pa'i phyag rgya bstan pa te /
NK052(zi)001:1760: 'di dag ni lha mo rnams dngos su ma tshogs na yang der byin gyis brlabs pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:1761: tshogs na'ang dmigs pa dang sgrub pa'i rten du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1763: dkyil 'khor gang dang gang brten pa //
NK052(zi)001:1764: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:1765: sgrub pa'i cho ga mdor bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1767: dkyil 'khor gang dang gang brten pa //
NK052(zi)001:1768: zhes bya ba 'i tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1769: rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor rnam pa drug le'u 'di nyid nas smos pa'i sku gzugs dgod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1770: le'u drug pa nas smos pa'i bud med du dgod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1771: le'u bdun pa nas smos pa'i thugs mtshan du dgod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1772: yig 'bru dgod pa'i phyag rgya nas smos pa'i ming gi phyag rgyar bris pa thams cad bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:1773: sna tshogs phyag rgya'i mchod pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:1775: le'u brgyad nas smos pa'i phyag dang gar gyi mchod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1776: le'u dgu pa nas smos pa'i sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK052(zi)001:1777: le'u bcu pa nas smos pa'i bsdus pa'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:1778: gnyis dang bcas pa sgrub mchod kyi phyag rgya ji
NK052(zi)001:1780: slob ma'i tshogs kun de dang der //
NK052(zi)001:1782: dkyil 'khor gyi lhar byin gyis brlabs pa'i slob ma'i tshogs dang /
NK052(zi)001:1783: dbang nod par bya ba'i phyir 'dus pa'i slob ma
NK052(zi)001:1784: dang dad pas mchod pa'i phyir 'dus pa dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:1786: mchod pa byas nas de sgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:1789: dkyil 'khor gang yin pa de dang de dag tu
NK052(zi)001:1790: 'dus par 'gyur ba'i rnal 'byor pa dang rnal 'byor
NK052(zi)001:1791: ma rnams kyis sna tshogs thams cad kyi phyag rgyas
NK052(zi)001:1792: byin gyis brlabs shing bsgyur te sgo gsum lha'i longs
NK052(zi)001:1793: spyod rnams las mi g.yeng par gnas pa nyid 'dir
NK052(zi)001:1794: sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho gar gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:1795: da ni ci rigs par 'phrul pa de dag rnam
NK052(zi)001:1796: pa ci 'dra bar 'byung bar gyur pa rgyas pa
NK052(zi)001:1797: bshad pa'i phyir / de las gzhan yang rtog kun gyi //
NK052(zi)001:1798: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:1799: de la sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:1800: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1801: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyis dbugs phyung ba bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1802: de la rgyud kyi mgo nyid du gsungs pa bzhin du /
NK052(zi)001:1803: 'dir yang bldabs nas ston pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1804: gong du dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyi skabs su /
NK052(zi)001:1805: gang zhig ci 'dra ji ltar sgrubs //
NK052(zi)001:1806: ces bya ba bstan pa bzhin du /
NK052(zi)001:1807: rnam par 'phrul pa bston pa'i skabs 'dir yang de
NK052(zi)001:1808: dag nyid ston par byed pas de'i phyir de lta
NK052(zi)001:1809: bur gsungs so // zhes sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:1810: de las dpal rdo rje sems dpas dbugs phyung ba'i skabs 'dir ni /
NK052(zi)001:1811: 'dul ba'i thabs ji snyed pas bsdus pas /
NK052(zi)001:1813: ma nges par snang ba thams cad yin pa'i phyir gdul bya spyir dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1814: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbugs phyung ba'i nyan
NK052(zi)001:1815: thos rnams thabs dang shes rab zung du ma 'brel
NK052(zi)001:1816: bas phyogs gcig par gyur pa'i mya ngan las 'das
NK052(zi)001:1817: pa rnams la sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi yon
NK052(zi)001:1818: tan zab cing rgya che ba thabs dang shes rab
NK052(zi)001:1819: kyis yongs su zin pa bstan cing snang bar mdzad
NK052(zi)001:1820: pas de dag theg pa chen po la sbyor bar
NK052(zi)001:1822: stong pa ma yin zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1823: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel bar ston pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1824: de la shes rab kyis chos thams cad dmigs pa
NK052(zi)001:1825: thams cad las 'das shing spros pa yongs su zhi
NK052(zi)001:1826: bar rtogs kyang thabs kyis snying rje'i bdag nyid mdzad
NK052(zi)001:1828: de bas na thabs de ni snying rje'i dbang du gyur pa'i thabs te /
NK052(zi)001:1830: thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:1831: shes rab pha rol phyin par gsal //
NK052(zi)001:1833: thabs de nyid la ni rtog pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:1835: rtog pa med pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:1836: thabs dang 'dir de'i mtshan nyid kyi chos ston pa yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1837: brag ca yi ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:1838: de la bstod pa'i glu 'di dag gi don ni /
NK052(zi)001:1839: spyir shes rab dang snying rje zung du 'brel bar ston kyang yon tan gyi bye brag gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1840: mnyam med mi g.yo la sogs pa'i tshig dang pos ni /
NK052(zi)001:1841: chos nyid dang thugs rje dang mdzad pa rnams mnga'
NK052(zi)001:1842: yang byang chub kyi sems la g.yo ba mi mnga'
NK052(zi)001:1843: bar ston to // yon tan shin tu phra ba'i tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1844: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i spyod yul la mnga' brnyes pa ston to //
NK052(zi)001:1845: rtag tu dri ma med pa'i tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1846: thugs rje lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang gis smon lam dang mdzad pa rgyun mi chad par ston to //
NK052(zi)001:1847: tshad med tshad dang bral ba'i tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1848: nyid kyi che ba la mi gnas par gdul bya'i ngor gzigs pa ston to //
NK052(zi)001:1849: shin tu bzang po'i tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1850: gdul bya mthar 'byin pa ston to //
NK052(zi)001:1851: mgon po dus gsum gyi tshig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1852: gsol ba 'debs par byed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1853: rigs kyi yon tan du'ang sbyar zhes kyang 'chad do //
NK052(zi)001:1854: glu 'di nyid kyi sgrub pa gud du gsungs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1855: tshig mang po la mi dga' ba rnams la phyag
NK052(zi)001:1856: rgya re re tsam gyi sgo nas sgrub pa bstan
NK052(zi)001:1857: pa'o // dpal rdo rje 'dzin pa he ru kas dbugs phyung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1860: rdo rje can la skyabs su dong ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1861: dpal phyag na rdo rje la'o //
NK052(zi)001:1862: des rdo rje sems dpa'i gzugs su mdzad nas sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu ba mdzad do //
NK052(zi)001:1863: thams cad kyis bka' glod pa mngon spyod kyis gdul par dgongs nas he ru ka sprul pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1864: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje sems dpa'i gzugs su mdzad pa des /
NK052(zi)001:1865: nyid kyi sna'i dbugs las rdo rje he ru ka
NK052(zi)001:1866: sprul pa mdzad de de gdug pa can 'dul bar
NK052(zi)001:1868: phyag na rdo rje dang rdo rje sems dpa' tha mi dad mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:1869: thun mong gi phrin las bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:1870: dbugs kyi drod las sprul pa yang /
NK052(zi)001:1871: sgrub pa po rnams kyi lam bstan pa mdzad par dgongs so //
NK052(zi)001:1872: de yi 'bar ba'i nyi ma las //
NK052(zi)001:1876: sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:1877: gong du 'tsho bar byed ces gsungs pa'i gso ba'i thabs bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1878: de bas na de dag dang /
NK052(zi)001:1879: lhan cig dur khrod rnam par rol //
NK052(zi)001:1880: zhes bya ba'i tshig 'di yang slar gsos pa'i lha
NK052(zi)001:1881: chen po de dag gdan dang bka' nyan du byas
NK052(zi)001:1882: te dur khrod chen por rol to //
NK052(zi)001:1886: thal pa bzhin du rab tu bshig /
NK052(zi)001:1887: ces smos pa'i ji ltar gshig pa'i tshul bshad pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1888: sku las sprul pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor gyi gdug
NK052(zi)001:1889: pa can rnams gsol nas gtso bo dang lhan cig
NK052(zi)001:1890: tu dur khrod chen po na rol to //
NK052(zi)001:1893: don gyi skabs dang tshig gi shugs kyis gdug pa
NK052(zi)001:1894: can slar gso ba'i cho ga bstan pa 'thad par
NK052(zi)001:1895: snang ngo // dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gis dbugs phyung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1896: log par lta ba la gnas pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1897: gang dag las dang las kyi 'bras bu la skur
NK052(zi)001:1898: pa 'debs pas mthong ba'i chos kyi spyod yul la
NK052(zi)001:1899: shin tu zhen pa rnams la /
NK052(zi)001:1900: rnam par dag pa dang thugs su chud pa'i bdag nyid rdo rje chos dang /
NK052(zi)001:1901: thugs rje chen pos sems can la gzigs pa'i bdag
NK052(zi)001:1902: nyid kun tu spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang po dang
NK052(zi)001:1903: / ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin ston pa'i bdag nyid
NK052(zi)001:1904: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ces bya ba rnams su
NK052(zi)001:1905: 'phrul nas de dag gi don mdzad pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1906: dpal rdo rje nyi mas dbugs phyung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1907: shin tu 'jungs shing brkam pa yis gzhan la ngan sems dang ldan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:1908: de dag yongs su gdul ba'i phyir dam pa'i nor la mnga' mdzad pa rdo rje nyi ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:1909: nam mkha' las yon tan 'byin pa nam mkha'i snying po lta bu'i bdag nyid kyis /
NK052(zi)001:1910: dpal dang gzi brjid dang sbyin pa phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi sgo nas /
NK052(zi)001:1911: rgyal po chen po'i mdzad spyod kyi don mdzad do //
NK052(zi)001:1912: dpal rta mchog gis dbugs dbyung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1913: le lo can rnams brtson 'grus kyi bdag nyid brtul phod pa mdzad pas /
NK052(zi)001:1914: byi dang chom rkun dang sring ba dang sgyu dang
NK052(zi)001:1915: ngo mthon gyi stobs rnams kyis brtul nas de dag
NK052(zi)001:1917: de ltar dbugs 'byin pa'i rnam pa de dag ni mdor bsdus pa tsam ste /
NK052(zi)001:1918: gtam gyi phyag rgya'ang mtha' yas pa ji snyed pa'ang rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1920: de ltar gtam gyi phyag rgya drug bstan pa de yang /
NK052(zi)001:1921: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa rab tu lci ba drug sbyang bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:1922: rigs drug gi 'phrul pa bstan pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1923: de la don dam pa byang chub sems gdod ma
NK052(zi)001:1924: nas dag pa ma rtogs pa ni nyes pa thams
NK052(zi)001:1926: de'i phyir yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi byang chub
NK052(zi)001:1927: sems kyi bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bstan
NK052(zi)001:1928: to // snying rje dang bral na 'dus ma byas
NK052(zi)001:1929: thob kyang byang chub chen por mi 'gyur zhing sems
NK052(zi)001:1930: can kun gyi don mi nus pas /
NK052(zi)001:1932: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid sangs rgyas kyi 'phrul pa bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:1933: khong khro ba dang gnod sems ni /
NK052(zi)001:1934: theg pa chen po dang 'gal ba'i mi dge ba'i rtsa ba chen po yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1935: de'i phyir snying rje chen po'i bdag nyid khro bo rdo rje rigs bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1937: nyes pa spyod pa kun gyi gzhi yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1938: de'i phyir dri ma med pa'i dam pa'i chos kyi bdag nyid pad+ma'i rigs bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:1939: ser sna dang brnab sems ni /
NK052(zi)001:1940: theg pa chen po'i thabs kun nas spong pa'i bdag nyid yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1941: de'i phyir sbyin pas kun la skyob pa'i bdag nyid rin po che'i rigs bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:1943: mi dge ba thams cad kyi grogs yin pa dang
NK052(zi)001:1944: dkar po'i phyogs yongs su bsdud par mi byed pas
NK052(zi)001:1945: / de'i phyir brtson 'grus kyi bdag nyid las kyi rigs bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:1946: de'i phyir theg pa chen po la gnas pa'i gang
NK052(zi)001:1947: zag gis rtsa ba'i sdom pa'ang yongs su gzung zhing
NK052(zi)001:1952: yongs su bsdam par bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:1956: 'di rnams kyi dbang gis rigs rnam pa drug ste /
NK052(zi)001:1957: de dag re re la yang bya ba ma yin pa ldog pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:1958: bya ba la 'jug pa'i dbang gis sdom pa gnyis gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1959: gtam gyi phyag rgya shes par /
NK052(zi)001:1961: sngon byung ba'i lo rgyus brjod pa ni gtam ste /
NK052(zi)001:1962: de nyid bcom ldan 'das kyi ting nge 'dzin las sprul pa'i phyir ye shes kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:1964: phyag rgya las ye shes 'byung bas phyag rgya shes pa zhes bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:1966: de ltar ci rigs pa rnam par 'phrul ba gang
NK052(zi)001:1967: zhig ci 'dra bar byung ba gtam rnam par 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:1968: pas bshad nas / da ni de dag ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga ston te /
NK052(zi)001:1969: de yang thabs kyi dngos gzhir gyur pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:1970: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul pa zhes
NK052(zi)001:1971: bya ba'i byin brlabs sgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i
NK052(zi)001:1973: dang por de bstan par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:1975: de nas gzhan yang thams cad du //
NK052(zi)001:1976: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1978: mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde mchog bshad /
NK052(zi)001:1980: bde bas bde ba bsgrub pa'i thabs tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:1981: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:1983: rdo rje sems dpa' bde 'byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:1984: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa na //
NK052(zi)001:1985: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:1987: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba 'byung ba'i gzhi'i gnas ni /
NK052(zi)001:1988: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:1989: rtag tu de na bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:1990: de bzhin du sgrub pa po rnams kyis kyang /
NK052(zi)001:1991: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor gyi gnas dang por bsham dgos pas /
NK052(zi)001:1992: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig dpal //
NK052(zi)001:1994: skyed mos tshal la sogs par bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:1995: ces bya ba'i bar dag gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:1997: 'dir dkyil 'khor te de nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:1998: snang ba bde zhes gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:2000: da ni gdan bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:2001: de ni dang po gdan bshams te //
NK052(zi)001:2003: sna tshogs pad mo rab kyis g.yog /
NK052(zi)001:2004: de ni thams cad dag pa'i gdan //
NK052(zi)001:2005: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:2006: 'di dag ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i rnal
NK052(zi)001:2007: 'byor pa rnams kyi rang rang gi go 'phang ji
NK052(zi)001:2008: ltar thob pa dang mthun pa'i mtshan ma dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:2009: pa'i gdan bshams par bya ba yin pa las /
NK052(zi)001:2010: thams cad la thun mong du 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK052(zi)001:2011: gyis ma chags shing dag pa'i rtags kyi gdan sna
NK052(zi)001:2012: tshogs pad mas mtshan pa'i ras gding bar bya ba
NK052(zi)001:2013: yin la / de la dkyil 'khor chen po'i tshul du bris te /
NK052(zi)001:2014: der gtso bo gzungs dang bcas pa'i phyag rgyar byin
NK052(zi)001:2015: gyis brlabs pa'i skye bo rnam pa bkod nas bsgrub
NK052(zi)001:2019: gzungs mtshan dang ldan pa nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:2020: de dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:2021: de las dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo rnams bskyed cing mchod nas sgrub pa po zhes kyang bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:2022: de ltar phyag rgya dgod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2023: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:2024: bud med dag ni legs sgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:2025: zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:2026: dngos grub kyi rten dam tshig gi rdzas ni /
NK052(zi)001:2027: mi yi mtshal ni grub pa la //
NK052(zi)001:2028: dmar chen po zhes bya bar bshad //
NK052(zi)001:2029: ces bya ba la sogs pa ste 'di ni 'og nas 'chad do //
NK052(zi)001:2030: rdo rje chu dang rdo rje bcas //
NK052(zi)001:2031: mtshal chen po dag sgrub pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:2033: rdo rje dri chen dri chu gnyis dang mtshal chen por sbyar ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:2034: de la mtshal chen po ni byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis las grub pa'i sha chen po'o //
NK052(zi)001:2036: de yi mtshal dang khu ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:2037: mtshal chen po ni sgrub pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:2039: pad ma rak+ta dang byang chub kyi sems dang sha
NK052(zi)001:2040: chen du sbyar ba ni dmar chen po zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:2041: bar bshad do // dmar chen dang ni ga bur bcas //
NK052(zi)001:2042: tsan dan dmar po sbyar ba dag /
NK052(zi)001:2044: ji skad du sbyar ba'i dmar chen dang /
NK052(zi)001:2045: yang byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis sbyar ba ni dam tshig gi rdzas so //
NK052(zi)001:2047: byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis gong du sbyar zin pas /
NK052(zi)001:2048: 'dir ga bur dang tsan dan dmar po gnyis ni phyi rol du grags pa'i gzung bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2049: 'di ltar dam tshig rdzas kyi 'phrad dang rkyen du sbyar ba yin no //
NK052(zi)001:2051: zhi ba'i btung ba bzhin zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2052: bram ze rnams kyi zla ba'i mchod sbyin byed pa'i btung ba myang ba bzhin du'o //
NK052(zi)001:2053: gzhan dag ni dam rdzas kyi yon tan no //
NK052(zi)001:2054: de ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du mchod pa la 'jug pa'i tshul bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:2055: de'i phyir de nas khrus byas de bzhin lus //
NK052(zi)001:2057: slong bas dal gyis dal gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2058: gos dgab pa yi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2059: bdag gi 'thung ba bskul par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2060: rdzogs par sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2061: shar ba dag ni mthong ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2062: zhes bya ba'i bar dag gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:2063: 'dir dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang mchod pa'i rim pa dag 'byung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2064: yongs su bzung ba dag bde bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:2065: 'og nas gud du bstan pa bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2066: 'dir tshig gi don gyi 'grel pa tsam bstan par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2068: slob bas dal gyis dal gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2070: lha mo rnams kyis bde ba chen po mi rtog
NK052(zi)001:2071: pa'i ngang las bzhengs par bskul zhing 'gro ba'i don
NK052(zi)001:2072: du byang chub kyi sems bskyed par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2074: gos dgab pa yi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2076: sgeg pa dang lta ba 'dzum pa dang glu dang
NK052(zi)001:2077: gar dang mkhyud pa dang sbyor ba la sogs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2078: sgo nas byang chub kyi sems bskyed par mdzad pa
NK052(zi)001:2079: ni / lus dang sems la mdzes pa bskyed pa'i sbyor ba yin pas de skad ces bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2080: sbyor ba des rang grub pa'i byang chub sems 'byung ba bskul bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2082: byang chub sems rnam pa gnyis 'byung ba'i dus de'i tshe dngos grub thob pa'i dus yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:2083: nyi zla shar ba mthong bas grub //
NK052(zi)001:2086: byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis gnyis su med
NK052(zi)001:2087: pa'i bde ba las skyed pa'i ting nge 'dzin mtshan
NK052(zi)001:2088: ma thams cad dang bral ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2089: nyi zla shar ba mthong ba zhes bya ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:2090: de'i tshe dngos grub kyi mchog thob pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:2093: slong bas zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2094: ye shes dang phyag rgya dbab pa la sogs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2095: sbyor bas bdag nyid sgrib pa thams cad dang bral
NK052(zi)001:2096: bar bya ste / stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du gnas pa las /
NK052(zi)001:2097: sngon gyi smon lam dang thugs rje'i dbang las gyur pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis /
NK052(zi)001:2098: stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor la sogs pa'i glus bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:2099: de'i dbang gis de las bzhengs nas rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:2100: dpa'i phyag rgyar byin gyis brlabs shing dkyil 'khor sprul
NK052(zi)001:2101: pa dang mchod pa chen po'i cho ga rgyas par
NK052(zi)001:2102: mdzad pa ni / gos dgab pa yi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2103: bdag gi 'byung ba bskul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2105: de nas dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor dang
NK052(zi)001:2106: bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bar
NK052(zi)001:2107: mthong ba ni / rdzogs par sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2108: shar ba dag ni mthong ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2110: slong ba'i glu nyid gang zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:2111: nges pa'i lam dang kun ldan pa //
NK052(zi)001:2112: rnam par 'das pas rnam par brgyan //
NK052(zi)001:2113: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:2114: glu 'di nyid thar pa'i lam du 'gyur zhing thar pa'i yon tan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2117: glu'i lam ni rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK052(zi)001:2118: de'u mtho dman dang ring thung gis phye ba drug 'gyur dang /
NK052(zi)001:2119: bzhi 'gyur la sogs pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2120: glu'i lam dang sgo de nyid kyis /
NK052(zi)001:2121: mya ngan las 'das pa'ang 'grub par byed /
NK052(zi)001:2123: 'dis phung po lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las
NK052(zi)001:2124: 'das pa'i dbyibs su brtan zhing grub par bzhugs pa
NK052(zi)001:2125: rnams kyang slong bar byed na gzhan lta ci smos
NK052(zi)001:2129: rdzogs par sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2132: lha mo kun dang bde mos pa //
NK052(zi)001:2133: rdo rje sems dpa' yang dag rdzogs //
NK052(zi)001:2134: nyi ma zla ba gsal bar 'char //
NK052(zi)001:2135: zhes bya ba 'di nyid kyis bshad par shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2136: yang slong ba'i glu gnyis pa gsungs pa /
NK052(zi)001:2137: rjes su chags pa rnam mang dga' ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2138: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:2139: 'di ni gsang ba'i lha mo bzhi yi sgo nas
NK052(zi)001:2140: dpal rdo rje sems dapa 'a la bde ba'i bde
NK052(zi)001:2141: ba sgrub pa'i phyir gnyis su med par rol pas
NK052(zi)001:2142: bskul ba dang / thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don la rol par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2143: gsum pa bskul ba'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:2144: ba hu bi bi ta rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK052(zi)001:2145: las rnam bzhi sprul pa spros pas sems can rnams
NK052(zi)001:2147: de lta bu'i dngos grub sgrub pa la stsol bar bskul ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:2148: de bas na rgyud 'di'i gzhung gi don ma lus pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2149: sngon byung ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam pa drug yin la /
NK052(zi)001:2150: de dag gi mdzad pa mdor bsdus pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2151: gsang ba yum bzhi'i bdag nyid glu rnam pa bzhi po 'di yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:2152: glu 'di dag re re'i sgo nas kyang las dang dngos grub thams cad la sbyar du rung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:2155: ba hu bi bi ta r+aa ga san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:2156: she sha ni sha sa t+wa bi na ya sarba
NK052(zi)001:2157: ta th+aa ga t+aa dza le pra dza le kurba
NK052(zi)001:2158: bi kurba sarba sham+ba re te na te te h'u
NK052(zi)001:2160: sems can chags pa can gdul ba'i don du rdo
NK052(zi)001:2161: rje sems dpa'i phrin las lha mo bde mchog ma'i
NK052(zi)001:2162: bdag nyid dbang gi sgo nas don mdzad par bskul
NK052(zi)001:2164: ba hu bi wi ta r+aa ti san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:2165: she sha ne she sha sa t+wa bi na ya
NK052(zi)001:2166: sarba ta th+aa ga t+wa dza le pra dza le
NK052(zi)001:2167: kurba bi kurba sarba sham pa re h+aum h+aum h+aum
NK052(zi)001:2169: sems can 'dod pa la sems dga' ba rnams la
NK052(zi)001:2170: rdo rje sems dpa'i phrin las lha mo rmongs byed
NK052(zi)001:2171: ma'i bdag nyid bud med la sogs pa'i longs spyod
NK052(zi)001:2172: rgyas pas don mdzad par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2174: ba hu bi wi ta roo drasan+ta ti a she
NK052(zi)001:2175: sha ni she sha sat+wa bi na ya sarba ta
NK052(zi)001:2176: th+aa ga t+aa dza le pra dza le kurba bi
NK052(zi)001:2177: kurba sarba sham+ba re ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo
NK052(zi)001:2179: sems can gdug pa can rnams la dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:2180: sems dpa'i phrin las lha mo za byed ma'i bdag
NK052(zi)001:2181: nyid drag po'i sgo nas don mdzad pa bskul ba'o
NK052(zi)001:2183: ba hu bi wi ta dz+ai bi san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:2184: she sha ni she sha sa t+aa bi na ya
NK052(zi)001:2185: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aah dza le pra dza le
NK052(zi)001:2186: kurba bi kurba sarba sham+ba re h+aum shi sh+ya bi
NK052(zi)001:2187: sha h+aum / zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2188: sems can srog gi phongs pa rnams la rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:2189: sems dpa'i phrin las lha mo tshe 'phel ma'i bdag
NK052(zi)001:2190: nyid zhi ba'i don mdzad par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2192: glu bzhi so so 'dis ni rgya chen po mi
NK052(zi)001:2193: nub pa'i gang zag rnams kyis gang la mos pa
NK052(zi)001:2194: bzhin du glu 'di dag re res dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK052(zi)001:2195: pa dang spyan drang ba mchod pa 'bul ba dang
NK052(zi)001:2196: bsnyen pa bya ba dang sgrub pa dang las la
NK052(zi)001:2197: sbyar ba thams cad byar rung ba'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:2198: las thams cad pas glu'i phyag rgyar bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:2199: gzhan ni de dag gi yon tan no //
NK052(zi)001:2201: de nas yang dag rab gsang bas //
NK052(zi)001:2202: bud med dag ni bzhi rnams dang //
NK052(zi)001:2203: zhes bya ba la sogs pas /
NK052(zi)001:2204: me tog dang bdug pa dang mar me dang dri
NK052(zi)001:2205: dang ldan pa'i bud med bzhis gar dang dbyangs kyis
NK052(zi)001:2206: phul na yang mchod pa kun nas bsdus par 'gyur
NK052(zi)001:2207: ro // da ni slob ma gzhugs pa'i cho ga bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:2209: mchod pa'i sbyor ba 'di dag dang //
NK052(zi)001:2210: lha mo bzhi po dag gis ni //
NK052(zi)001:2211: me tog la sogs mchod byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:2212: slob ma thams cad gzung bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2213: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:2214: de la 'dir me tog dor ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2215: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor nyid dor bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2217: gsang ba'i dbang gi rang bzhin ji skad du bstan pa'i dam tshig gi rdzas kyis bskur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2218: dbang gzhan ni dkyil 'khor gzhan nas ston to //
NK052(zi)001:2219: de nas dam tshig sbyin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2222: chos legs par ston pa rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:2223: sgrub pa po thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga yin la /
NK052(zi)001:2224: slob dpon rnams kyi bya ba'i las yin pas de
NK052(zi)001:2225: lta bas na ji skad du gsungs pa'i yan lag
NK052(zi)001:2226: lnga po de dag tshang bar sgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2227: de dag ni re zhig tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshig gi 'grel pa bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2228: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid ji ltar sgrub pa'i cho ga nyid bstan par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2229: de la 'dir sgrub pa po dpal rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:2230: dpa'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du dngos grub sgrub par
NK052(zi)001:2231: 'dod pas / thog mar rdo rje slob dpon la
NK052(zi)001:2232: bsnyen bkur bya la sogs pa sngon du bya ba'i
NK052(zi)001:2233: cho ga'i yan lag ji ltar bstan pa rdzogs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2234: 'dod pas / rnal 'byor pas / ji ltar dga'
NK052(zi)001:2235: ba dang ji ltar 'byor ba'i gzungs ma dang ldan
NK052(zi)001:2236: pa'i yo byad phun sum tshogs pa nyer bsdogs su
NK052(zi)001:2237: gnas pa rnams kyis tshogs kyi sgrub pa brtsam par
NK052(zi)001:2238: 'dod pas / rnal 'byor pas / bya ste / de la dus ni /
NK052(zi)001:2239: nyin re'am yang na zla re'am //
NK052(zi)001:2240: yang na de bzhin lo rer ni //
NK052(zi)001:2241: ji bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK052(zi)001:2242: sangs rgyas bde mchog gar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2244: mthong ba'i chos la dngos grub chen po bsgrub par
NK052(zi)001:2245: 'dod pa'i shin tu brtson pa rnams kyis nyi ma
NK052(zi)001:2246: re re rtag tu bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2247: de lta bu'i sbyor ba brtson pa dang mi ldan
NK052(zi)001:2248: pa rnams kyis ni zla ba re rer bsgrub par
NK052(zi)001:2249: bya'o // de las gzhan pa rnams kyis ni lo
NK052(zi)001:2250: re la sogs kyi mchod pa re re bya ste
NK052(zi)001:2251: bya'o // / de dag gi khyad par gyi dus kyang /
NK052(zi)001:2252: bcu bzhi dang ni bco lnga dang //
NK052(zi)001:2253: khyad par du ni tshes brgyad la'o //
NK052(zi)001:2254: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2255: gnas kyang dben pa'i gnas dag gam //
NK052(zi)001:2256: rang gi skyed pa'i tshal la sogs pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:2257: kun tu sna tshogs skal bzang po //
NK052(zi)001:2258: ci bde bar ni bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2261: rdo rje sems dpa' snang ba bde //
NK052(zi)001:2262: de bzhin gshegs pa'i lha rdzas mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2263: rin chen rgyan la sogs pas spras //
NK052(zi)001:2264: dril bu rgyal mtshan mchog ldan pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:2265: bla re dam pa bris pa na //
NK052(zi)001:2266: rdo rje'i tshig dang mchod la sogs //
NK052(zi)001:2267: glu dang sil snyan rnam par 'phrul //
NK052(zi)001:2268: me tog bdug spos sbyor ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:2269: mar me dri la sogs par ldan //
NK052(zi)001:2270: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyar ba //
NK052(zi)001:2271: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:2272: yang na bde ba'i gnas dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:2273: skyed mos tshal la sogs par bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:2280: yo byad kyi khang pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2281: kim ka ra'i khang pa rnams 'byor bar bshams te /
NK052(zi)001:2282: sngags kyi khang pa der sa gzhi legs par byi dor byas te /
NK052(zi)001:2283: li khri la sogs pa'i byi dor gyis phyogs thams cad du gzugs brnyan 'byung bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2284: de'i sa cha yang dkyil 'khor chen po'i tshul du rdo rje'i thig gis btab ste bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2285: dbyibs dkyil 'khor kun tu sna tshogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2286: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir dpal rnam par snang mdzad dang
NK052(zi)001:2287: he ru ka la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dbyibs gang
NK052(zi)001:2288: yang rung ba zhig blang bar 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:2289: sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig gi /
NK052(zi)001:2290: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor dbyibs gru bzhir bya bar bzhed do //
NK052(zi)001:2291: de la nang gi dkyil 'khor zlum po re'u mig dbu par bya la /
NK052(zi)001:2292: phyi rol gru bzhi sgo dang bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2293: de'i steng du rdul mtshon mi dgye bar stan gding bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2294: de la stan gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK052(zi)001:2295: der ni dang por stan bshams te //
NK052(zi)001:2297: sna tshogs pad mos ras kyis g.yog /
NK052(zi)001:2298: de ni thams cad dag pa'i stan //
NK052(zi)001:2299: stan de dag ni thams cad la //
NK052(zi)001:2300: ji ltar gnas pa bzhin du dgod //
NK052(zi)001:2301: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
NK052(zi)001:2302: rta babs bzhi yis mdzes par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2303: rdo rje rin chen pad mo sogs //
NK052(zi)001:2304: sgo bsrungs dang ni ldan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2306: rang rang gi lha'i bzhugs gnas rnams su sna tshogs
NK052(zi)001:2307: pad mas mdzes par byas pa'i ras kyi stan dang
NK052(zi)001:2308: tshang can re re gding bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2309: 'dod pa la longs spyod kyang mi gos pa'i phyag rgyas btab pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2311: sa gzhi la thig mi btab par sngags khang dang mnyam pa'i ras bzang pos gzhi byas la /
NK052(zi)001:2312: de la gong du smos pa bzhin du bris te /
NK052(zi)001:2313: de'i steng du rang rang gi stan rang rang gi
NK052(zi)001:2314: mtshan mas btab pa so sor gding bar yang bshad
NK052(zi)001:2315: do // de nas phyag rgya dgod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2317: gong du bstan pa'i lugs ma la sogs pa'i phyag rgya 'grub pa'i phyag rgya rnams dang /
NK052(zi)001:2318: byin gyis brlabs sgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i phyag rgya bud med rnams dgod pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2320: nyin gyi tha mar par bya /
NK052(zi)001:2321: zhes gsungs pa bzhin dgong ka'i dus su sku gzugs
NK052(zi)001:2322: dang rnal 'byor ma rnams gtso bo dang bcas par
NK052(zi)001:2323: byi dor dang khrus dang byug pa dang rgyan thams
NK052(zi)001:2325: ji ltar rang gi lha dang mthun pa'i gos bzang
NK052(zi)001:2326: po dang rang rang gi mtshan mas mtshan zhing bzhag
NK052(zi)001:2327: pa rnams phyogs gcig tu bzhugs nas /
NK052(zi)001:2328: des nas rdo rje lcam dral phal pa rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:2329: glu dang rol mo'i cha byad rnams kyis spyan drangs
NK052(zi)001:2330: te / sngags kyi khang pa so so'i stan stengs su gshegs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2331: sgo ba'i las byed rnams kyis phyi nas 'brang ba'i bgegs bskrad pa bgyi /
NK052(zi)001:2332: de nas brda' phyag bgyi ste /
NK052(zi)001:2333: rnal 'byor phal pa rnams dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo'i tshogs kyis lag pa spyi bor byugs te /
NK052(zi)001:2336: slob dpon gyis de bzhin dpral ba reg ste /
NK052(zi)001:2339: de bzhin du rnal 'byor ma mched lcam dral thams
NK052(zi)001:2340: cad kyang so so rang rang gis bkur rim bzhin
NK052(zi)001:2341: du phyag dang lan gyis phyag bgyi ste /
NK052(zi)001:2342: rang rang gi gnas su 'dod do //
NK052(zi)001:2343: bud med med pa'i gnas rnams su ni /
NK052(zi)001:2344: lugs ma la sogs pa rang rang gi sku gzugs bzhag go //
NK052(zi)001:2345: yod pa rnams ni sku gzugs dang 'brel bar bzhag ste /
NK052(zi)001:2347: khams kyi ngo bo thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:2348: de bzhin srog dang rtsa las byung //
NK052(zi)001:2349: rang gi lha yi cha lugs su //
NK052(zi)001:2350: bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya rab tu bya //
NK052(zi)001:2352: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2353: bud med dag ni legs sgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:2354: skal bzang rang gi phyag rgya mtshan //
NK052(zi)001:2355: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor brtag par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2356: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:2357: de la rnal 'byor pa rnams 'jug khar khrus dang
NK052(zi)001:2358: gtsang sbra dang gos dang rgyan gyis brgyan cing lha'i
NK052(zi)001:2360: de nas khrus byas dri zhim lus //
NK052(zi)001:2361: ci 'byor pa yi gos dang rgyan //
NK052(zi)001:2362: sna tshogs gos dag bgos nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:2363: me tog phreng ldan kha dri zhim //
NK052(zi)001:2366: kha dri zhim pa'i kha spos ni /
NK052(zi)001:2367: ka ko la dang sug smel dang //
NK052(zi)001:2368: gla sgang ga bur gla rtsi dang //
NK052(zi)001:2369: 'di rnams zhib tu btags pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:2370: seng ldeng bu ram dag dang sbyor //
NK052(zi)001:2371: shing tsha ba dra lo dra dang //
NK052(zi)001:2372: na le sham dang ga bur sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:2373: ha se ka ri'i shing mar gyis //
NK052(zi)001:2374: sbrus pa kha yi spos yin no //
NK052(zi)001:2375: zhes gsungs pa 'dis kha dri zhim por byas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2376: de ltar da kyil 'khor du 'khod nas bsgrub pa'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2377: sngon gyi slob dpon chen po sku gsung thugs kyi
NK052(zi)001:2378: dngos grub can rdo rje bzhad pa'i zhal snga nas
NK052(zi)001:2379: / 'di'i bsgrub pa'i cho ga de kho na nyid bcu'i cho nas bsgrub par gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:2380: de la de nyid bcu ni /
NK052(zi)001:2381: cho 'phrul bzhi sbyor ba rnam pa bzhi ste brgyad la /
NK052(zi)001:2384: snying po dang phyag rgya dang gsang sngags rigs sngags bzhi /
NK052(zi)001:2385: sbyor ba rnam pa bzhi ste brgyad /
NK052(zi)001:2386: byin gyis brlab pa dang dbang bskur ba gnyis te bcu /
NK052(zi)001:2387: ting nge 'dzin ni de dag thams cad kyi spyi'i chos su 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:2388: rdzas gud du bgrang med pas de kho na nyid bcu /
NK052(zi)001:2390: 'di yang rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i tshul gyis de kho na nyid bcu yin te /
NK052(zi)001:2391: dkyil 'khor gyi de kho na nyid la brten pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2392: de kho na nyid bcu ni dpal sgyu 'phrul dra
NK052(zi)001:2393: ba las gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK052(zi)001:2395: rdo rje byin brlabs tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2396: ting nge 'dzin ni bdag dbang bskur //
NK052(zi)001:2397: snying po phyag rgya sngags rig gis //
NK052(zi)001:2398: gsang ba'i mchod pa mchog gis bskul //
NK052(zi)001:2399: sbyor dang rab sbyor sbyor ba che //
NK052(zi)001:2400: rnal 'byor thams cad bsgrubs par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2401: de nyid bcu la sogs tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:2402: thams cad skye 'gyur bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2403: 'di yis sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:2404: de bzhin dpa' bo thams cad kyang //
NK052(zi)001:2405: ci bder yul la longs spyod pas //
NK052(zi)001:2409: dang por bdag nyid byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang
NK052(zi)001:2410: bskur ba'i tshul gyis dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal
NK052(zi)001:2412: de nas lha mo rnams kyang bdag dang mthun par
NK052(zi)001:2413: byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang bskur ba'i tshul gyis
NK052(zi)001:2414: rang rang gi lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgyar byin
NK052(zi)001:2415: gyis brlabs te / de nas gsang ba'i mchod pa bskul lo //
NK052(zi)001:2416: de nyid sbyor ba bzhi'i tshul gyis te /
NK052(zi)001:2420: lha mo rnams kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK052(zi)001:2422: de gnyis ka'i sgo nas gsang ba'i mchod pa bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2424: bde ba chen po nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin rnyed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:2425: 'di'i tshul gyis dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2426: de yang dang po nyid du stan byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2427: badz+ra pad+ma +aa sa na ma h+aa yo ga po tha ma h'u /
NK052(zi)001:2428: zhes bya bas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:2429: so so rang rang gi stan thams cad kyang byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2430: de nas yan lag bdun dang ldan pas byang chub kyi sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2431: dang por dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor bas dpung pa gnyis rdo rjer bciings te /
NK052(zi)001:2432: rdo rje'i se gol gtogs pas /
NK052(zi)001:2434: sangs rgyas thams cad nam mkha' la bsdu bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2435: de nas g.yon pas se gol brdabs la /
NK052(zi)001:2436: g.yas pa'i thal mo dal gyis brdabs te /
NK052(zi)001:2437: de bzhin thal mo lan gsum dal gyis brdabs pa
NK052(zi)001:2438: 'di ni mnyes par byed pa zhi ba'i thal mo'o
NK052(zi)001:2439: // de nas phyag gi phyag rgyas phyag bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2440: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:2441: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:2442: dpal ldan g.yon pa 'gying ba'i thabs //
NK052(zi)001:2443: g.yas pa ba dan gsum pa bya //
NK052(zi)001:2444: srid gzhung bcas shing stegs pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2445: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i dpal //
NK052(zi)001:2446: 'dzum dang bcas pa'i mig gis blta //
NK052(zi)001:2447: bsam pa g.yos pas phyag bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2448: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul 'di nyid kyis phyag 'tshal bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2451: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2452: dbang po kun las spro bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2453: dngos grub thams cad grub byed la //
NK052(zi)001:2454: zhi ba'i thal mo sbyar ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2455: shardza gan dar tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2456: rdo rje dbyings kyis bstod par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2457: mnyam med mi g.yo mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid can //
NK052(zi)001:2458: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:2459: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub thams cad sbyin mdzad pa //
NK052(zi)001:2460: dri med mi g.yo mnyam med dam pa'i chos mchog can //
NK052(zi)001:2461: yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la'ang tshad med de //
NK052(zi)001:2462: dpe ni nam mkha' dang yang bskrun du yod ma yin //
NK052(zi)001:2463: dngos grub mtha' yas mnyam med dpe dang bral ba rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2464: sems can khams la dngos grub mchog rnams nges pa stsol //
NK052(zi)001:2465: rtag tu dri ma med pa'i thugs rje shugs las 'byung //
NK052(zi)001:2466: smon lam grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
NK052(zi)001:2467: 'gro ba'i don sgrub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
NK052(zi)001:2468: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
NK052(zi)001:2469: tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:2470: bde bar gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes gyur kyang //
NK052(zi)001:2471: khams gsum rnams la dngos grub mchog rtsol mdzad pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:2472: thugs rje spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yong mi 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:2473: e ma'o shin tu zab pa'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NK052(zi)001:2474: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang na go 'phang dam pa mchog brnyes pas //
NK052(zi)001:2475: khams gsum kun la rtag tu dngos grub mchog rtsol mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:2476: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pas //
NK052(zi)001:2477: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la rtsol //
NK052(zi)001:2479: de dag mchod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK052(zi)001:2480: de nas sdig pa bshags pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2481: bsod nams kyi rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:2484: dge ba yongs su bsngo ba rnams ci dga' bar
NK052(zi)001:2485: byas la byang chub kyi sems bskyed par bya ste
NK052(zi)001:2487: brtson 'grus chen po go bsgos pa //
NK052(zi)001:2488: snying rjee chen pos brlan pa'i sems //
NK052(zi)001:2489: gzhan la phan pa gcig pu mthar gyur pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2490: ma lus lus pa med pa'i 'jig rten gnas pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2491: sems can rnams sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las bdag
NK052(zi)001:2492: gis bsgral bar bya'o snyam du bsam ste /
NK052(zi)001:2493: bdag byin brlabs pa la sogs pa sgrub pa'i cho ga la 'jug par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2494: de la byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshul yang 'di nyid las /
NK052(zi)001:2495: ting 'dzin la sogs rnam bzhi yis //
NK052(zi)001:2496: gang gis bskyed pa yongs bsgos nas //
NK052(zi)001:2497: bsgom na thams cad bdag nyid du //
NK052(zi)001:2499: sems gyi byin brlabs sbyor ba yang //
NK052(zi)001:2501: 'di nyid nyin re sgrub byed pa //
NK052(zi)001:2502: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid 'thob bo //
NK052(zi)001:2505: slong ba'i dal gyis dal gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2506: gos dgab pa yi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2507: bdag gi 'byung ba bskul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2508: rdzogs par sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
NK052(zi)001:2509: shar ba dag ni mthong ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2510: sdig pa kun las grol 'gyur zhing //
NK052(zi)001:2511: bsod nams thams cad grub par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:2512: zhes pa'i tshul de nyid bsgrub par bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:2513: dang por phyag rgya'i ye shes phab pas sgrib pa bral zhing ye shes phab ste /
NK052(zi)001:2514: bdag nyid shin tu rnam par dag par gnas pa la sangs rgyas kyis bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:2515: bdag byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho ga rim bzhin bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2516: de la phyag rgya'i ye shes dbab pa'i tshul ni 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:2517: bdag nyid dpal bde ba chen po rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:2518: dpa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du byas nas lag pa
NK052(zi)001:2519: g.yas g.yon gyi mthil la yi ge dang ta gnyis
NK052(zi)001:2520: las nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor cha thams
NK052(zi)001:2521: cad kyis rnam par mdzes pa mngon du brtags te
NK052(zi)001:2523: ma h+aa su kha sa man+ta b+ha dra h+au ah zhes brjod pas /
NK052(zi)001:2524: nyi ma dang zla ba'i steng du h+aum dang a
NK052(zi)001:2525: las spros pa dang bsdus pa'i sbyor bas rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:2527: g.yon pa'i sor mo thams cad la yi ge sa bon /
NK052(zi)001:2528: a +aa am a am lnga las gzungs mar bsam /
NK052(zi)001:2530: h+aum h+aum h+r+ai h+r+ai ahrnamasa las gtso bo lnga bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:2531: de nas snying po 'dis rdo rje thal mo bcings par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2532: badz+ra any+dza li zhes brjod pas /
NK052(zi)001:2533: gtso gzungs gzigs dang reg pas bde ba bskyed par bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:2534: de nas rdo rje khu tshur snying po 'di bsdam par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2535: badz+ra b+han+d+ha h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK052(zi)001:2536: de bzhin du ma khyud pa'i bde bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:2537: de nas rdo rje dbab par byin gyis brlab par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2538: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma yo ga a bi sha ma h+aa kha badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:2540: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes brjod cing /
NK052(zi)001:2541: bcings pa de babs par gyur gyi bar du bskyod par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2542: de nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa bral bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:2543: phyag rgya de rang gi snying gar yang dang yang du drag tu snying po 'dis dgrol bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2544: badz+ra b+han+d+ha ma h+aa kro d+ha ha na da ha
NK052(zi)001:2545: pa tsa b+han+d+ha ya sa sarba dush+ta pra dush+ta me
NK052(zi)001:2546: ma na sid+d+ha dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa ta mun+ta ka
NK052(zi)001:2547: r+pa ta / bi ka ra bi ki ra h+aum trata trata trata /
NK052(zi)001:2548: de nas rang gi lus mi shis pa'i dri ma dang bral nas /
NK052(zi)001:2549: zla ba ltar yongs su dag par bsgoms te /
NK052(zi)001:2550: mo sarba bi shud+d+ha d+harma ta sa ma ye h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:2552: de nas rdo rje khu tshur so sor bcings nas
NK052(zi)001:2553: mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba las lcags kyu ltar gcig
NK052(zi)001:2555: de bzhin du rang gi snying gar gsang sngags 'dis dgrol bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2556: badz+ra b+han+d+ha am ku sha ma h+aa kro d+ha dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum phata phata /
NK052(zi)001:2557: de nas yang bdag nyid sgrib pa gnyis dang bral nas shin tu rnam par dag par bsams te /
NK052(zi)001:2558: ye shes yongs su dag pa tsam las /
NK052(zi)001:2559: dmigs pa la yang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gis dge ba'i bshes gnyen mdzad de /
NK052(zi)001:2560: bdag la glu 'di blangs shig bskul bar bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:2561: stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor yod med mthus //
NK052(zi)001:2562: nam mkha' bzhin du dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK052(zi)001:2563: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhengs su gsol //
NK052(zi)001:2564: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK052(zi)001:2565: de nas de dag gis bdag bskul bar rig nas
NK052(zi)001:2566: bdag gi bde ba chen po rdo rje sems dpa'
NK052(zi)001:2567: rim pa 'di ltar bskyed pa bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2568: de yang phyag rgya dang bcas pa'i h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2569: de la phyag rgya ni rdo rje bsdams pa las rting pa gnyis phye ste /
NK052(zi)001:2570: mathe'u chung dang srin lag gi dbus su mthe bong rtse sprad nas dbab pa byas la /
NK052(zi)001:2571: ma h+aa su kha sa man+ta b+ha dra a bi sha h+aum +aahzhesa brjod nas /
NK052(zi)001:2572: dbab pa'i phyag rgya bskyed cing snying gar a las pad+mo bskyed la /
NK052(zi)001:2573: de'i steng du gung mo rdo rje rtse gcig tu byas te /
NK052(zi)001:2574: h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs pa bzhag go //
NK052(zi)001:2575: de nyid kyis bde ba chen po'i ye shes dbab ste /
NK052(zi)001:2576: sku phyag rgya chen por grub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2577: yang na a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du brtags te /
NK052(zi)001:2578: sa bon gyi rgyal po h+aum gi rang bzhin du
NK052(zi)001:2579: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa gyur par bsams la
NK052(zi)001:2580: / de yang h+aum lnga stan la 'khod pa las
NK052(zi)001:2581: a la sogs pa yi ge 'od zer gyis brgyan
NK052(zi)001:2582: / par bsam nas / h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK052(zi)001:2583: h+aum de las ye shes kyi rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur par bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:2584: de nas ye shes kyi rdo rje de las ye
NK052(zi)001:2585: shes rnam pa lnga'i gzugs dang kha dog sna tshogs
NK052(zi)001:2586: su byung nas / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK052(zi)001:2587: kyi dkyil 'khor chen po la sogs kun tu snang
NK052(zi)001:2588: su byung nas / bar byas te / slar rdo
NK052(zi)001:2589: rje la 'dus pa la phyag rgya chen po'i tshul
NK052(zi)001:2592: thams cad bde byed dag pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:2593: zla ba nya ltar rtsa dmar sku //
NK052(zi)001:2594: dngos grub kun la chags pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:2596: g.yas kyis 'dud pa snying ga ru //
NK052(zi)001:2597: 'dzum bcas rdo rje gsor bar mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:2599: sems dpa'i skyil krung dbyibs su gnas //
NK052(zi)001:2600: chu skyes spyan yang yud tsam rgyas //
NK052(zi)001:2601: sangs rgyas rin chen dbu rgyan mnabs //
NK052(zi)001:2602: sna tshogs rgyan gyis rnam par klubs //
NK052(zi)001:2604: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dri med mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2605: a las yang dag bskyed bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:2606: de nas kun tu sbyor bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2607: sangs rgyas rin chen khams gsum na //
NK052(zi)001:2608: rin chen gzhan dang mtshungs pa med //
NK052(zi)001:2609: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin po che //
NK052(zi)001:2610: de bas dbu rgyan mchog ces bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2611: de nas byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2612: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:2613: snying ga dang smin mtshams dang mgrin pa dang spyi bo rnams su byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK052(zi)001:2614: dga' ba'i snying rje nyid du byin gyis rlob par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:2616: rdo rje khu tshur bcings byas te //
NK052(zi)001:2617: mdzub mo mthe bo'i mnga' nyid du //
NK052(zi)001:2618: g.yas pas mthe bo mtshan ma yis //
NK052(zi)001:2619: kha ru bcug la bsdam par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2620: dga' chen dpal gyi rdo rje ste //
NK052(zi)001:2622: de yang rdo rje gar dang bcas pas phyag rgya bca' 'o //
NK052(zi)001:2623: de nas yang rdo rje'i phyag rgyas rdo rje 'dzin par byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:2625: dga' ba'i rdo rje rab bcings nas //
NK052(zi)001:2626: dbu ma bcings pa'i nang du gzhug /
NK052(zi)001:2627: mthe bong mathe'u chung mnyam bsnol ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:2628: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2629: bcings ba de yis byin brlabs na //
NK052(zi)001:2630: rdo rje 'dzin pa mchog tu gyur //
NK052(zi)001:2631: 'di yis ji ltar rigs pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:2632: blo dang ldan pa'i dbang bskur bya //
NK052(zi)001:2633: dar dpyangs bcing ba bcing bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:2634: 'gying dang bcas pa'i mtha' nas dgrol //
NK052(zi)001:2635: dar dpyangs 'dra ba'i tshul byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:2636: thal mo yis ni brtan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2637: h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa mi zhes brjod /
NK052(zi)001:2638: 'di ni rang gi rigs kyi dbang bskul ba'i byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2639: de nas rin po che rnam pa lnga'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:2640: chos kyi phyag rgyas rigs rnam pa lnga'i dbu rgyan
NK052(zi)001:2641: gyis dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2643: sangs rgyas rin chen phyag rgya ni //
NK052(zi)001:2644: mthe bong sems dpa'i skyil mo krung //
NK052(zi)001:2645: mdzub mo gnyis kyi rtse mo dgug /
NK052(zi)001:2646: gung mo gnyis ni mnyam par sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:2647: lhag ma rdo rje thal mo'o //
NK052(zi)001:2648: spyi bo dang ni dpral ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:2649: mdan pa gnyis pa lhag par ni //
NK052(zi)001:2650: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin chen mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2651: dbu rgyan kun tu brgyan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2652: dbu rgyan bcings pas bcing nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:2653: 'gying zhes mtha' nas dgrol bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:2654: dar gyi mtha' ma dpyangs pa ltar //
NK052(zi)001:2655: byas nas thal mos brtan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2656: bud+d+ha rat+na a b+hi sha ke ru ru spu ru
NK052(zi)001:2657: dz+wa la tish+tha bud+d+ha lo tsa ni sarba ar+tha s+aa
NK052(zi)001:2658: d+ha na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:2659: sangs rgyas rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2660: rdo rje rin chen gyi ni rab tu dga' ba'i phyag rgyas snga ma bzhin du dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:2661: badz+ra rat+na a b+hi she ke he ri mi ri
NK052(zi)001:2662: ti ni sh+ri ye a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+w+aa h+aa
NK052(zi)001:2663: / rdo rje rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2664: pad mo rin chen gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:2665: sangs rgyas rin chen las gung mo'i rtse mo phab pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2666: pad+ma rat+na a b+hi she ke t+aa re tut+t+aa re tu re a b+hi shiny+tsa mam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:2667: pad+mo rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2668: rin chen rin chen gyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:2669: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar te //
NK052(zi)001:2670: lag gnyis nor bu rin chen dang //
NK052(zi)001:2671: ji ltar rigs par sbyar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:2672: mthe bo mdzub mo rtse mo bzhi //
NK052(zi)001:2673: rat+na rat+na a b+hi she ke tram tram ba ba
NK052(zi)001:2674: ta ta ta ta tra ta a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam
NK052(zi)001:2675: s+w+aa h+aa / rin chen rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2676: las kyi rin chen gyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:2677: rdo rje thal mo rab bsdams te //
NK052(zi)001:2678: mdzub mo rtse mo yud tsam bkug /
NK052(zi)001:2679: mthe bo dpa' bo'i skyil mo krung //
NK052(zi)001:2680: lhag ma rnams ni 'od bzhin btang //
NK052(zi)001:2681: karma a b+hi she ke hi hi hi hi sh+ri
NK052(zi)001:2682: badz+ra pad+ma ba da ba mu khe a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK052(zi)001:2683: m+aam s+w+aa h+aa / las kyi rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2685: rdo rje phyag rgya dpral bar /
NK052(zi)001:2686: rin po che mdan pa g.yas su /
NK052(zi)001:2688: las kyi mdan pa g.yon du bzhag ste dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:2689: rang rang gi rigs phyag rgya gtsor byed pa'i tshe na ni /
NK052(zi)001:2690: rgyud las gsungs pa bzhin du rang rang gi gnas su bzhag ste dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2691: phyag rgya 'di dag kyang rnal 'byor spyi'i rgyud la /
NK052(zi)001:2692: gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsungs pa'i phyag rgya chen
NK052(zi)001:2693: po bca' ba'i mtshan nyid yin par shes par bya'o
NK052(zi)001:2694: // de ltar bdag nyid dbang bskur bar byas nas go bgo bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2695: rdo rje brgyad pa las mgrin par bzhag ste /
NK052(zi)001:2696: badz+ra ka ba tsa ya am ham bam am /
NK052(zi)001:2698: bcings pa de las gnyis su byas nas mdzub mo
NK052(zi)001:2699: brkyang ste so so nas gdong sprad pa mdud pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2700: tshul gyis snying ga nas brtsams nas spyi gtsug gi
NK052(zi)001:2702: h+aum ka ba tsa ya m+aam h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:2703: zhes sngags 'di lan gsum gsum byas na 'dis cis kyang mi phyed par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:2704: bdag phyag rgya chen po bsgrub pa'i rim pa rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:2705: de la yum rnams kyang bsgrub par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2706: gong du bstan pa bzhin tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK052(zi)001:2707: ji skad gsungs bzhin du rang rang gi gnas su
NK052(zi)001:2708: 'khod pa'i gzungs ma rnams rang rang gis byin gyis
NK052(zi)001:2710: gtso bo'i phyag rgya bsgrub pa dang tshul mthun par
NK052(zi)001:2711: bskyed cing byin gyis brlab pa dang dbang bskur ba
NK052(zi)001:2712: la sogs byas nas mchod pa brtsam par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2713: gal te mi nus na ni gtso bos bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2714: de dag gi cho ga ni 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:2715: ji ltar gong du bshad pa bzhin du yan lag
NK052(zi)001:2716: bdun dang ldan pa'i sgo nas byang chub tu sems
NK052(zi)001:2717: bskyed pa dang sgrub pa bral zhing ye shes dang
NK052(zi)001:2718: phyag rgya chen po dbab pa'i tshul ni mthun no
NK052(zi)001:2719: // cung zad mi mthun par dbab pa'i sngags la /
NK052(zi)001:2720: lha mo rang rang gi gsang sngags la /
NK052(zi)001:2723: rim gyis bskyed par byed na /
NK052(zi)001:2724: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan steng du
NK052(zi)001:2725: lha mo so so rang rang gi snying po bsam
NK052(zi)001:2726: pa las rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur te
NK052(zi)001:2727: / rang rang gi gsang sngags brjod pa las rang rang gi sku gyur par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2728: de nas byin gyis brlab pa dang dbang bskur ba
NK052(zi)001:2729: dang go bgo ba ni kun la mthun par sbyar
NK052(zi)001:2730: ro // de la so so'i snying po dang phyag
NK052(zi)001:2731: rgya dang gsang sngags rnams ni gzungs rnams rang rang
NK052(zi)001:2732: so so lhag pa'i lhar sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2733: de la gsang ba'i yum bzhi po /
NK052(zi)001:2737: tshe 'phel ma bzhi'i sa bon gyi snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:2743: sangs rgyas tshe dpag med kyi sku gzugs rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2745: dza badz+ra drish+ta sa ma ke ma ta /
NK052(zi)001:2746: h+aum badz+ra ki li ki li h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:2747: bam badz+re ni spa ra ra ta /
NK052(zi)001:2748: hohbadz+ra ka be shwa ri tram rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2750: zla ba'i kha dog 'dzum pa'i zhal //
NK052(zi)001:2751: dngos grub thams cad dag pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:2753: barla yi dbus ni dmar la dkar //
NK052(zi)001:2754: phyag rtse lo ma sngon po 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:2755: de bzhin bde ba'i dbang phyug dang //
NK052(zi)001:2756: bde bar reg pa'i dbang phyug pa //
NK052(zi)001:2757: dkar zhing ser ba'i barla dang ldan //
NK052(zi)001:2758: lha rdzas sna tshogs kha dog mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2760: pad+mo sna tshogs la gnas pa //
NK052(zi)001:2761: thams cad dag pa rab tu gnas //
NK052(zi)001:2762: sangs rgyas pad mo la sogs mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2763: rin chen sna tshogs rgyan dang gos //
NK052(zi)001:2764: zhes spyir bstan nas so so'i sku mdog dang phyag mtshan mdor bsdus nas bstan pa /
NK052(zi)001:2765: mdun du zla ba'i kha dog can //
NK052(zi)001:2766: chu skyes zhal ni mdzum dang bcas //
NK052(zi)001:2768: g.yas su sngo mthing phyag gnyis kyis //
NK052(zi)001:2769: rang gi phyag rgya bcas pa'i mkhyud //
NK052(zi)001:2770: sangs rgyas dbu rgyan phreng ba can //
NK052(zi)001:2771: sna tshogs rgyan gyis rnam pa klubs //
NK052(zi)001:2772: rgyab tu lha mo chu srin can //
NK052(zi)001:2774: dbal byed dran pa sna tshogs kyi //
NK052(zi)001:2776: bdud bcas g.yon na sngo bsangs te //
NK052(zi)001:2777: sangs rgyas tshe yi rin chen can //
NK052(zi)001:2778: sangs rgyas gtsug gis rnam par spras //
NK052(zi)001:2779: rnal 'byor ldan pas bsam par bya //
NK052(zi)001:2780: lha mo de dag ni mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde mchog gi rtsa ba'i phyag rgya'i tshogs so //
NK052(zi)001:2781: de nas phyogs bzhi'i re cha bzhi la rigs kyi yum bzhi po //
NK052(zi)001:2782: sangs rgyas byang chub ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:2784: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:2785: 'dod pa'i dbang mo dang bzhi ste /
NK052(zi)001:2786: de dag gi sa bon gyi snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:2789: tshangs pa'i mgo bzhi mda' bzhis phug pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2792: dpag bsam gyi shing gi lcug ma rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2795: badz+ra me g+he gu mu gu mu b+h+rum /
NK052(zi)001:2796: ha sha ra d+ha badz+ri im im /
NK052(zi)001:2797: kham badz+ra she shi ri h+aum h+aum rnams so /
NK052(zi)001:2798: lha mo de dag gi sku mdog dang dbu rgyan
NK052(zi)001:2799: dang gdan dang rgyan rnams ni gsang ba'i yum gyi
NK052(zi)001:2801: gong du thugs mtshan bsgom pa'i skabs su smos pa las cung zad du na /
NK052(zi)001:2802: khams gsum rnam rgyal ma'i phyag g.yon tri shul bsnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2803: de'i mtshams gyi re cha bzhi la nang gi mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi bzhugs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2804: dpal rdo rje gling bu dbang byed ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:2805: de bzhin du pi wang bde bas rmongs byed ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:2806: cang te'u sdug bsngal sel ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:2807: rdza rnga myos byed ma rnams te /
NK052(zi)001:2808: 'di bzhi yang gzhung spyi las grags pa'i sgeg mo la sogs pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2809: de dag gi snying po'i sa bon ni /
NK052(zi)001:2811: thugs mtshan ni ming gis shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2813: badz+ra he ra ti badz+rim bi l+aa s+ya ni trata /
NK052(zi)001:2814: he ra ti badz+ra g+ai ti te tim /
NK052(zi)001:2815: he ra ti badz+ra h+aa se ha ha wem /
NK052(zi)001:2816: he ra ti badz+ra n+ri t+ya be sa be sa dz+hi rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2817: sku'i tshul ni snga ma bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2818: gra bzhir phyir lha mo bzhi po me tog bdug
NK052(zi)001:2819: pa mar me dri chab ma rnams kyi sa bon
NK052(zi)001:2821: thugs mtshan ni ming gis bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:2827: sku'i tshul snga ma bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:2828: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhir dgod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:2832: pad+ma b+han+d+ha'i nang nas rta mgrin gu byung ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:2835: rin po che'i snod na sangs rgyas tshe mtha' yas kyi sku phyung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2837: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra pra she h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:2841: kun kyang khros pa'i cha byad la 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa /
NK052(zi)001:2842: g.yon brkyang pa'i stabs su bzhugs pa /
NK052(zi)001:2844: g.yas na rdo rje lcags kyu thogs /
NK052(zi)001:2845: g.yon na pad+ma b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang ba'i nang nas
NK052(zi)001:2846: mgo ljang gu 'phangs bstod pa de skad 'byin pa
NK052(zi)001:2847: bsnams so // rdo rjee zhags pa'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:2848: g.yas rdo rje zhags pa g.yon na phag gi mche ba can bsnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2850: phyag g.yas g.yon na rdo rje lcags sgrog bsdams pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2851: yang mig gi steng na nyi ma dang zla ba
NK052(zi)001:2855: g.yon na b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i kha rdo rje rgya
NK052(zi)001:2856: gram gyis bkab pa'i steng na sangs rgyas snang ba
NK052(zi)001:2857: mtha' yas kyi sku phyung ba bsnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2858: 'di ltar las lhag pa'i gzungs kyi tshogs yod na
NK052(zi)001:2859: yang mchod pa'i lha mo'i tshogs gyur pa rigs kyi
NK052(zi)001:2860: byin gyis brlabs kyis mchod par byin gyis brlabs so
NK052(zi)001:2861: // gal te dkyil 'khor du dgod pa'i gzungs ma rnams ma tshang na /
NK052(zi)001:2862: sku gzugs la sogs dgod pa'am de dag med na bsam par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2863: 'di dag ni lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgya bsgrub pa'i cho ga'o //
NK052(zi)001:2864: de nas mchod pa brtsam par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2865: gtso gzungs kyi rdo rje pad+ma'i dbyibs can du byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2866: gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis brtsam pa ni lung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:2868: de nas gsang ba'i phyag rgya bzhis dgyes pa bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2869: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes brjod cing rdo rje bcings pa
NK052(zi)001:2870: las dbu la gnyis nang du lcags kyur bcas te
NK052(zi)001:2871: / snying gar drangs pa ni lcags kyu ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:2872: de nyid gdong reg pa ni zhags pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2873: de nyid lu gu rgyud ltar bya ba ni bcings pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2874: de nyid rtse mo bsdams pa ni dgyes pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2875: 'di ni gsang ba'i phyag rgya ste phyi'i phyag rgya rnams kyis kyang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2876: de la phyi'i phyag rgya ni 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:2877: rdo rje bcings pa gnyis su byas te /
NK052(zi)001:2878: g.yon gyi steng du bzhag nas rgyab sprad la mathe'u chung bsnol /
NK052(zi)001:2879: g.yas kyi mdzub mo sgreng ba'i tshigs bcag nas g.yas
NK052(zi)001:2880: kyi mdzub mo bkug pa ni rdo rje 'bod pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2881: phyag rgya ste / badz+ra k+aa ma ang+ku sha ad+d+ha
NK052(zi)001:2882: +aa gad+d+ha h+aum dzah zhes bya ba'i snying po dang
NK052(zi)001:2883: bcas pas spyan drangs par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2884: de nyid las phan tshun mdzub mo gnyis zhags pa ltar bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:2885: badz+ra p+aa sha pra be sh+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:2886: zhes bya ba'i snying po dang bcas par bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:2887: de nyid las phan tshun shin tu bskum ste /
NK052(zi)001:2888: badz+ra k+da ma b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha bam /
NK052(zi)001:2890: de nyid las mathe'u chung gnyis lu gu rgyud ltar gzung ste /
NK052(zi)001:2891: rgyab sbyar nas bskyod pa ni dgyes pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:2892: badz+ra tush+tam k+aa ma bu kha to sha ya to sha ya ho /
NK052(zi)001:2893: zhes brjod nas phyag rgya de dgyes pa bskyed de /
NK052(zi)001:2895: zhi ba'i thal mo gsum gyis dgyes pa bskyed nas dbyangs kyis bskul bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2896: de nas sangs rgyas rnams mchod pa'i phyir rang gi snying gar bcug ste /
NK052(zi)001:2897: sbyor ba bzhi'i tshul gyis rang nyid lha'i ngo bo la lha mo rnams kyis mchod par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:2898: brdung ba rnams dang gar dang glu dang mchod pa'i
NK052(zi)001:2899: gtor ma la sogs pa ji ltar 'byor pas mchod
NK052(zi)001:2900: de sbyor ba bzhi'i tshul gyis mnyam par bzhag ste
NK052(zi)001:2901: bsgrub par bya'o // gal te sgrub pa po la
NK052(zi)001:2902: la dag 'byor pa chung ngam shin tu spros dang
NK052(zi)001:2903: bcas pa la mi dga' ba rnams gzungs ma gcig
NK052(zi)001:2904: tsam la brten par 'dod na yang de nyid rdo
NK052(zi)001:2905: rje shin tu dga' mar byin gyis brlabs la snga
NK052(zi)001:2906: ma bzhin du sgrub cing mchod par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2907: gal te phyi rol gyi phyag rgya med na ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK052(zi)001:2908: mdun du yi ge a las bcom ldan 'das ma
NK052(zi)001:2909: rdo rje shin tu dga' ma bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK052(zi)001:2910: cha lugs dang kha dog dang dbyibs su ldan pa
NK052(zi)001:2911: bskyed de / snga ma bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:2912: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa byas nas mchod pa brtsam par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2913: de la'ang mchod pa'i cho ga dang mchod pa'i rdzas rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:2914: mchod pa dang mchod pa'i gtor ma ye shes kyi phyag rgya nas gsungs pa bzhin du byas te /
NK052(zi)001:2915: dam tshig gi rdzas ji skad du gsungs pa dang yang ldan par byas la /
NK052(zi)001:2916: gong du bstan pa bzhin du gsang ba'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:2917: dang phyi'i phyag rgyas dgug pa la sogs nas zhi
NK052(zi)001:2918: ba'i thal mo gsum gyis dgyes pa bskyed pa'i bar
NK052(zi)001:2919: du byas nas / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la
NK052(zi)001:2920: sogs pa mchod pa'i don du mdun gyi nam mkha'
NK052(zi)001:2921: la mngon du blta bar bya ba'i phyir dbyangs 'dis
NK052(zi)001:2922: du byas nas / bskul bar bya'o // rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:2923: sems dpa' bde chen skal bzang dpal khyod bdag lags
NK052(zi)001:2924: du byas nas / bskul bar bya'o // so // sgrub la rtogs pa mdzad du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:2925: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag nyid bde ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:2926: 'gro ba'i rgyud rnams rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul mchog grub par bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:2928: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyor ba sna tshogs gar rnams bstan du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:2929: dzahh+aum bam hoh kye bde mchog bde ba zung /
NK052(zi)001:2930: rnam par sprul snang bar mdzad du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:2931: a la la hoh de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi
NK052(zi)001:2932: sna tshogs sgyu ma mkha' 'gro slob ma gzung du
NK052(zi)001:2933: gsol / ma dang ta las gyur pa'i mig gis
NK052(zi)001:2934: nam mkha'i ngos la de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:2935: til gyi gang bu bzhin gang bar brtags te /
NK052(zi)001:2936: rdo rje lcags kyu bcings nas /
NK052(zi)001:2937: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes brjod cing rang gi lha la
NK052(zi)001:2938: mchod pa'i phyir de rnams rang gi snying gar gzhug
NK052(zi)001:2939: par bya'o // de nas ji ltar sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2940: sbyor dgyes pa yii rol bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:2941: sbyor ba bzhi yi tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:2942: mnyam par bzhag nas rab tu bya //
NK052(zi)001:2943: mchod pa thams cad ma sbyor na //
NK052(zi)001:2944: phyag rgya bcing zhing mchod bya ma //
NK052(zi)001:2945: rang nyid lha yi ngo bo la //
NK052(zi)001:2946: de dag gis mchod dmigs pa bya //
NK052(zi)001:2947: brdung dang gar du bcas pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:2948: stegs bcas dga' la bde ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:2949: glu la sogs pa'i ro ldan pas //
NK052(zi)001:2950: bde ba chen po skal bzang khyod //
NK052(zi)001:2951: thams cad 'dod pa bzhin du 'dod chags pas //
NK052(zi)001:2952: dzahh+aum bam hoh bcon ldan 'das bdag bzhes shing mchod
NK052(zi)001:2953: pa thams cad kyi cho ga la sogs pa sbyor
NK052(zi)001:2954: ba dang ldan pas dbul bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:2955: dzahh+aum bam hohru ta sma ra ta ra ta hu
NK052(zi)001:2956: lu hu lu pra sid+d+ha ka ni du nam h+aum
NK052(zi)001:2957: d+ham tak+ki h+aum / dz+dza hu lu hu lu a
NK052(zi)001:2958: la la la hoh shud+d+ha s+ya d+ha da ri sha
NK052(zi)001:2959: ya sarba ta ke ta g+he ta g+he ta g+he
NK052(zi)001:2960: ta ta g+he ta g+he g+he ta g+he ta g+he
NK052(zi)001:2961: ta ho ta k+ki h+aum dz+dza hu lu hu lu
NK052(zi)001:2962: a la la la hoh ru ta ma ta thal
NK052(zi)001:2964: bcom ldan 'das bde ba chen po rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:2965: dpa' la 'di mchod pa thams cad dbul bar bya'o
NK052(zi)001:2966: // ta g+he g+he ta g+he g+he ta g+he g+he
NK052(zi)001:2967: ta g+he g+he ta g+he g+he ta g+he g+he ta
NK052(zi)001:2968: // g+he g+he ta / rgyud kyis brdung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2973: dam tshig gsum gyis brdung ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:2974: bcom ldan 'das kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs bskul
NK052(zi)001:2975: ba'i dam tshig gsum gyi gsang ba'i sbyor ba ste
NK052(zi)001:2976: / de rnams kyi brdung ba phyag rgya dbyangs su blang zhing /
NK052(zi)001:2977: shardza dang d+he ba da'i dbyangs 'dis kyang sbyor ba'i
NK052(zi)001:2978: bdag nyid kyis h+aum la sogs pa'i dbyangs kyis bskul
NK052(zi)001:2979: bar bya'o // rjes su chags pa rnams mang dga' ba'i pad+ma rnam dag pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:2980: mchod pa gsal bas rjes su mchod byas pas //
