NK052(zi)001:2981: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor ba bde ba grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:2982: kye mchog tu bde ba'i dam tshig ngo bo nyid //
NK052(zi)001:2983: mchog tu bde ba'i rnal 'byor shin tu rnal 'byor skal bzang mchog brnyes pa //
NK052(zi)001:2984: rang gi dam tshig skyon med rtag la rol cig
NK052(zi)001:2985: rol cig hoh kye mchog tu gsang ba'i bdag po
NK052(zi)001:2986: rang gi dam tshig yin pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:2987: rab tu gsang ba'i lha mo mchog rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:2988: 'gro ba'i rgyud ni rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul ba gsal bar mkhyen //
NK052(zi)001:2989: dam tshig thams cad dngos po brtan sgros kun gyi
NK052(zi)001:2990: bdag nyid rnal 'byor bde ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma
NK052(zi)001:2991: ho // kye dam pa rtag pa dngos grub chen po rab tu bsgrubs la ston /
NK052(zi)001:2992: dzahh+aum bam hoh kye ma mchog bde ba 'drongs rnam par sprul /
NK052(zi)001:2993: sna ba mdzad la a la la hoh de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK052(zi)001:2994: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma sna tshogs kyi //
NK052(zi)001:2995: slob ma dag ni gzung du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:2996: 'di ni bcom ldan 'das kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs bde ba bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:2997: g.yas g.yon gyi lag pa yis /
NK052(zi)001:2998: 'gying ba'i tshul gyis gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:2999: g.yon gyi srin lag mthe bo sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:3000: g.yas kyi ba dan gsum pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3001: phyag rgya 'di yis btab pa na //
NK052(zi)001:3002: sangs rgyas kun dang yang dag 'grogs //
NK052(zi)001:3003: thams cad mchog gi dngos grub che //
NK052(zi)001:3004: dbang phyug chen po rab tu grub //
NK052(zi)001:3005: de nyid dor ba'i tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:3006: sla ru sdud pa cher byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3007: bsgyur nas g.yas kyi 'gram pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:3008: spyi gtsug mtshams su bzhag pa las //
NK052(zi)001:3009: sla ru gar gyi dbab tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:3010: cha lugs kun gyis rab bsgyur zhing //
NK052(zi)001:3011: mchod pa thams cad dbul bar byas //
NK052(zi)001:3012: la lar zla ba dri med stong pas mdzes pa'i gzugs su rnam pa snang //
NK052(zi)001:3013: la lar rab tu 'jigs pa'i nyi ma bye bas phrag dgu'i 'od zer mchog pas 'jigs //
NK052(zi)001:3014: la lar mdangs bzang gzi chen bde zhing zhi bar ldan pa rgyal ba'i gzugs su snang //
NK052(zi)001:3015: la lar 'gro ba thams cad mnyam par 'jog pa'i gzugs ldan gsung mchog ldan par ston //
NK052(zi)001:3016: rdo rje sems dpa' grub phyir 'dul mkhas ma lus bde ba'i mchog rnams las //
NK052(zi)001:3017: a ral thams cad mnyam sbyor grub par mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:3018: ru ta ma ta a la la la hoh rnam
NK052(zi)001:3019: pa mang po 'dul ba'i tshul gar mkhas mchog gis
NK052(zi)001:3020: gar mdzad pa // dam tshig gar gyi dbang phyug sangs rgyas gar mkhan mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3021: a la la la hoh rnam mang bde mchog rab
NK052(zi)001:3022: tu gar mdzad pa yis thar pa'i bde ba grub
NK052(zi)001:3023: par mdzod // 'di yis ba dan gsum dang ldan pas gar du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3024: rab tu dga' dang rjes su chags par dga' ba'i mda' gzhu rab tu phra bas rgyas btab pas //
NK052(zi)001:3025: rab tu dga' ba sbyor ba'i bde bas myos pa'i bde ba thams cad bdag la grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3026: rab tu bde ba rnam pa sna tshogs rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba'i longs spyod dang //
NK052(zi)001:3027: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug che mchog grub pa de bzhin gshegs pa bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:3028: ho rta mchog hoh kye rab tu bde ba'i rnam
NK052(zi)001:3029: pa sna tshogs rol cig hoh de bas slong rnam
NK052(zi)001:3030: par rol / h+aum snang bar mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:3031: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi mkha' 'gro sgyu ma
NK052(zi)001:3032: rnam pa sna tshogs kyis slob ma gzung du gsol
NK052(zi)001:3033: // kye bde ba'i mchog grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3034: kye ma'o bde bas bde ba gsol //
NK052(zi)001:3035: dam pa rab tu bzhugs par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3036: bdag la rab tu bde bar gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3037: a la la la hoh e ma'o shi shi zhugs shig mkha' 'gro bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3040: de nas gar dang ldan pa yis /
NK052(zi)001:3041: dbyangs 'di rnams kyis glu blangs shing //
NK052(zi)001:3042: dpal ldan g.yon du 'dud pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3043: g.yas kyi ba dan gsum du bya //
NK052(zi)001:3044: de ltar g.yas dang g.yon tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:3045: sems dpa'i skyil krung bsnyems byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3046: rnal 'byor bde byed bdag nyid kyis //
NK052(zi)001:3047: bde ba rnams ni yang dag dbul //
NK052(zi)001:3048: de nas 'di yis mchod bya ba //
NK052(zi)001:3049: g.yas dang g.yon gyi lag pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3050: 'gying ba'i mchog gi gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3051: steng du dor dang 'od du dor //
NK052(zi)001:3052: bskor dang de bzhin byug bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:3053: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3054: dri yi mchog pas bskor ba yin //
NK052(zi)001:3055: lhag ma gar gyi tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:3056: gling pu pi wang rdza rnga mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3057: de bzhin cang te'u rnam dag kyang //
NK052(zi)001:3058: g.yon gyi khu tshur rab bsdams te //
NK052(zi)001:3059: lag pa g.yas pas brdung byas shing //
NK052(zi)001:3060: rang gi mig gis bskul bcas pas //
NK052(zi)001:3061: sngags pas mchod pa 'bul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3062: zhi ba'i thal mo bde mchog gis //
NK052(zi)001:3063: thal mo sbyar bas dgyes pa bskyed //
NK052(zi)001:3064: g.yon du 'dud pas phyag bya zhing //
NK052(zi)001:3065: 'dzum dang bcas pa'i lta ba'i mig /
NK052(zi)001:3066: smin ma mig dang mchu gdong ba //
NK052(zi)001:3067: kha dang lus kyi gdon pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3068: cha lugs ji bzhin gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3069: phyag rgya thams cad dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3070: na mo stu sarba bud+d+he b+h+yoh zhes bya ba'i phyag rgyar rab gnas te /
NK052(zi)001:3071: mchod pa mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK052(zi)001:3072: ma lus lus med grub par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3073: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aahdzah h'u bam hohsu ra ta s+t+wam /
NK052(zi)001:3074: phyag rgya 'di rnams kyis btab na //
NK052(zi)001:3075: bdag nyid dang ni yang na gzhan //
NK052(zi)001:3076: sgrub pa po ni myur 'grub ste //
NK052(zi)001:3078: langs pa'i tshe yang de bzhin du dbang bskur ba dang bsrung ba la sogs pa byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3079: bde bas thal mos dgyes bskyed nas ci dga' bar gnas par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3080: gal te tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'di lta bur slob ma 'jug par 'dod na yang /
NK052(zi)001:3081: 'di nyid las gsungs pa bzhin du dbang bskur ba dang dam tshig byin par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3082: 'di lta bu'i cho gas ji ltar dam bcas pa bzhin bsgrub nas /
NK052(zi)001:3083: tha mar dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams grub mtshan ma
NK052(zi)001:3084: thob bam ma thob kyang rung ste dngos grub blang
NK052(zi)001:3085: bar bya'o // dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:3086: chen po'i tshul gyis tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgrub
NK052(zi)001:3088: gang yang dkyil 'khor chen po la spro ba med
NK052(zi)001:3089: cing cho ga mang po la mi dga' ba rnams
NK052(zi)001:3090: spros pa med pa'i spyod pa med le'u gnyis las
NK052(zi)001:3091: gsungs bzhin du / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' 'ba'
NK052(zi)001:3092: zhig gi phyag rgya bsgrub par 'dod pa rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:3094: dang por rdo rje slob dpon las /
NK052(zi)001:3095: gsang ba'i dbang dang lung thob par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3096: ji ltar bde ba'i gnas su phyi nang gi mchod pa ci 'byor pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3097: me tog la sogs pa'i rgyan gyis bkram zhing brgyan nas /
NK052(zi)001:3098: lus sems bsrang ste ting nge 'dzin la 'jug par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3099: de la dang por srid pa gsum po thams cad
NK052(zi)001:3100: mi dmigs pa'i ye shes kyis rnam par dag pa
NK052(zi)001:3103: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas su rim pa bzhin bsgoms pas snod du rung bar byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK052(zi)001:3105: snying gar yi ge a dkar po bsgoms te /
NK052(zi)001:3106: de'i 'od zer gyis 'phro 'du thams cad byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3107: sangs rgyas rnams la bskul ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:3108: sems can gyi don byas te slar 'dus pa las
NK052(zi)001:3109: ston ka'i zla ba ltar gsal ba'i dri ma med
NK052(zi)001:3110: pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom mo //
NK052(zi)001:3111: de'i steng du dug gsum sku gsung thugs su dag pa'i bdag nyid yi ge h+aum bsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:3112: de las 'phro 'du snga ma bzhin du byas pas
NK052(zi)001:3113: sems nyid ye nas rdo rje'i rang bzhin gyi ye
NK052(zi)001:3114: shes kyi rdo rje bsgom mo //
NK052(zi)001:3115: de las sngags kyi sku rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK052(zi)001:3116: yi ge gsum gyis snga bzhin du byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3117: de nas rdo rje rab tu dga' ba'i phyag rgya snying gar bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:3118: su ra ta stum zhes brjod pas /
NK052(zi)001:3119: phyag rgya'i rtse mo las rdo rje rab tu dga' ba bcom ldan 'das dang mthun par bskyed de /
NK052(zi)001:3120: +aahh+aum zhes pas snga ma dang 'dra bar byin gyis brlab bo //
NK052(zi)001:3121: de nas yi ge h+aum dang d+h+ri yis gnas rnam pa gnyis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK052(zi)001:3122: mchod pa dam pa dbul bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3123: phyogs bcu sangs rgyas thams cad mngon sum du spyan drangs te /
NK052(zi)001:3124: phyi nang gi mchod pa ci 'byor pa yang bstab bo //
NK052(zi)001:3125: de nas dzab bsgom ci nus tshad du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3127: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aahdzahh+aum bam hoh su ra stam /
NK052(zi)001:3131: sku'i des pa zla ba nya ba'i kha dog ltar
NK052(zi)001:3132: cung zad tsam dmar ba sna tshogs pad+ma'i stan la
NK052(zi)001:3133: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK052(zi)001:3134: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rgyab rten can /
NK052(zi)001:3135: sangs rgyas lnga yis dbu brgyan pa /
NK052(zi)001:3136: rdo rje dril bu cung zad bsgyings pa /
NK052(zi)001:3137: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3138: de'i thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' dang h+aum gis brgyan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3139: de ltar ci nus su bsgom ste gtong bar 'dod pa na yang ye shes sems dpar bsdu /
NK052(zi)001:3141: de nas h+aum h+aum gi zhabs skyed ha la thim /
NK052(zi)001:3142: ha las 'dod chags zla tshes te /
NK052(zi)001:3143: zla tshes nyid kyang thig le'o //
NK052(zi)001:3144: thig le nyid kyang de bzhin nyid //
NK052(zi)001:3145: de ltar bsdus nas ldad pa na //
NK052(zi)001:3146: lus kyang sku gsung thugs kyi bsrung //
NK052(zi)001:3147: sems la rtag tu gnas par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3148: 'di ltar rtag tu yi dam byed pa'i tshe /
NK052(zi)001:3149: dam bcas pa rdzogs nas bsgrub pa las /
NK052(zi)001:3150: dngos grub len pa'i tshe yum dang gnyis su med pa las dngos grub blang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:3151: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' kun tu sbyor ba'i phyag rgya nyi tshe ba rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:3152: de ni bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:3155: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin nyid //
NK052(zi)001:3156: thar pa thams cad rnam sbyang phyir //
NK052(zi)001:3158: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:3159: rang gi byin brlabs bsgrub pa'i rgyas //
NK052(zi)001:3160: phyag rgya ji bzhin rjes mthun pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:3161: sangs rgyas sprul pa bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3165: rten dang dgon pa gtsug lag khang //
NK052(zi)001:3166: ri yi rtse rnams thams cad du //
NK052(zi)001:3167: rnam pa du ma sna tshogs pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:3168: sangs rgyas dgongs pa bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3169: zhes gsungs pa dag tu bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3171: khyad par du me tog dmar po dang /
NK052(zi)001:3173: mar me gsum lnga yan chad kyi phreng ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:3174: tsan dan gyi byug pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3176: sangs rgyas rnams la bshos 'bul ba //
NK052(zi)001:3177: sha dang chang ni rnam par spangs //
NK052(zi)001:3178: zhes gsungs pa lta bu khyad par gyi rdzas dang /
NK052(zi)001:3179: spyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la mi 'gal ba'i rdzas rnams bsog /
NK052(zi)001:3180: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbyibs ni /
NK052(zi)001:3181: zlum po la re mig dgu pa sgo dang ldan par bya /
NK052(zi)001:3182: phyag rgya ni rang gi rigs kyi lha'i sku gzugs la sogs pa dgod pa'am /
NK052(zi)001:3183: snga ma bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshom bu ma'i dkyil 'khor 'god do //
NK052(zi)001:3184: sgrub pa po rnams kyi rgyan dang gos rang gi
NK052(zi)001:3185: lha'i kha dog dang cha lugs su byas te 'jug
NK052(zi)001:3186: par bya'o // de la 'dir yang phyag rgya chen po bsgrub pa'i rim pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3187: rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su gsungs
NK052(zi)001:3188: pa dang rjes su mthun par yan lag bdun pa
NK052(zi)001:3189: dang ldan pa'i sgo nas byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK052(zi)001:3190: pa dang / sgrib pa bral zhing ye shes dang
NK052(zi)001:3191: phyag rgya chen po dbab pa rnams de bzhin du
NK052(zi)001:3192: pa dang / bya'o // cung zad mi 'dra ba
NK052(zi)001:3193: ni sku rim gyis bskyed nas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:3194: gyi steng du yi ge kham bsams te /
NK052(zi)001:3195: de 'phro ba dang 'du ba'i sbyor bas dam pa chos kyi 'khor lo'am /
NK052(zi)001:3196: glegs bam du gyur par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3197: de las bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi skur gyur par bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:3198: don dam rnam par dag pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:3199: btso ma gser gyi kha dog bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:3200: chags med la sogs chags can phyir //
NK052(zi)001:3201: dkar zhing sna tshogs gsal ba'i mdangs //
NK052(zi)001:3202: chos kyi rgyal srid rab bsgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:3203: rin chen chos las lhag pa med //
NK052(zi)001:3204: de bas theg chen byang chub sems //
NK052(zi)001:3205: rgyal ba rdo rje rin chen can //
NK052(zi)001:3206: g.yas pa'i mthe bo gung mo gnyis //
NK052(zi)001:3207: g.yon pa'i khu tshur bcang ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:3208: sor mo kun la reg pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:3209: rtsa ba'i phyag rgya yin par grags //
NK052(zi)001:3210: g.yas pa'i yan lag gnon pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3211: g.yon pa'i yan lag kun las rgyal //
NK052(zi)001:3212: sems dpa' skyil mo krung bcas na //
NK052(zi)001:3213: bdud rnams thams cad rab tu 'joms //
NK052(zi)001:3214: zhes gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:3215: de nas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3216: thog ma nyid du rang gi rigs kyi phyag rgyas byin gyis brlab par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3217: rdo rje phyag rgya bcings pa las //
NK052(zi)001:3218: sbyor ldan thal mo khong stong sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:3219: khams gsum dag ni ma lus pa //
NK052(zi)001:3220: de ma thag tu 'bebs par byed //
NK052(zi)001:3222: dang por rang gi gnas byin gyis brlabs so //
NK052(zi)001:3223: dga' chen dpal gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:3224: rdo rje'i phyag rgyas kyang byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3225: dbang bskur ba'i dang po nyid du rang gi rigs
NK052(zi)001:3226: kyi phyag rgya chen pos dbang bskur bar bya ste
NK052(zi)001:3227: / rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar te //
NK052(zi)001:3228: lag gnyis nor bu rin chen du //
NK052(zi)001:3229: ji ltar rigs par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK052(zi)001:3230: mdzub mo mthe bo rtse mo bzhi //
NK052(zi)001:3231: yongs su bsgyur te btegs nas su //
NK052(zi)001:3232: dpral bar legs par bzhag pa na //
NK052(zi)001:3233: khams gsum bdag po rgyal ba bdag /
NK052(zi)001:3234: ma lus lus pa med par 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:3235: ru ru s+phu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa
NK052(zi)001:3236: na sarba ar+tha s+aa d+ha ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aa
NK052(zi)001:3238: rigs gzhan gyi sngags dang phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3239: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i skabs su gsungs pa bzhin 'dir yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:3240: lha mo rnams byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3241: spyir gtso bo dang mthun pa'i rim pa las cung
NK052(zi)001:3242: zad mi 'dra bar rang rang gi sa bon gyi
NK052(zi)001:3243: snying po dang thugs mtshan dang gsang sngags dang sku'i
NK052(zi)001:3244: tshul rnams so sor bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3245: de nas gsang ba'i yum bzhin la shar phyogs kyi
NK052(zi)001:3246: re cha la sangs rgyas kun brjod ma zla ba'i
NK052(zi)001:3247: dkyil 'khor gyi steng du yi ge sham las lce'i
NK052(zi)001:3248: phyag rgyar gyur / de las skur gyur pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3249: sku mdog dkar mo rgyan rnams thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK052(zi)001:3252: badz+ra sa t+wa sham zhes bya ba sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:3253: de bzhin lho phyogs su shin tu rgyal mo /
NK052(zi)001:3254: nub phyogs su kun tu bzang mo /
NK052(zi)001:3255: byang du mi bzad pa'i za ma tog go //
NK052(zi)001:3256: de rnams kyi sa bon ni /
NK052(zi)001:3263: kha phyogs dang mthun pa la /
NK052(zi)001:3264: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK052(zi)001:3265: phyag mtshan gong du smos pa rnams rim pa bzhin bsnams pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3270: phyogs bzhi'i re'u cha bzhi la rigs kyi yum bzhi /
NK052(zi)001:3271: shar phyogs kyi re cha la /
NK052(zi)001:3272: sangs rgyas kun gyi yan lag dang ldan ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:3273: lho'i re'u cha la zhal bzang mo /
NK052(zi)001:3274: nub kyi re'u cha la sprin chen mo'o //
NK052(zi)001:3275: byang gi re'u cha la nam mkha'i spyan no //
NK052(zi)001:3276: de rnams kyi snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:3277: ham tshem tram d+ham rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:3279: sangs rgyas sku'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK052(zi)001:3281: ser ba sprin dang bcas pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3282: mig gi phyag rgya dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:3284: kha dog phyogs dang mthun pa la /
NK052(zi)001:3285: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK052(zi)001:3286: ji skad du smos pa'i mtshan ma phyag na bsnams pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3291: d+ham bi shwa badz+ra rnams kyis sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3292: phyi nang gi mchod pa'i lha mo rnams dang sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3293: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du gsungs pa ltar 'dir yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:3294: spros pa med pa la dga' ba rnams kyis ni
NK052(zi)001:3295: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma 'ba' zhig gtso
NK052(zi)001:3296: bo dang mthun par bskyed de bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3297: de nas phyi nang gi phyag rgya bzhis bsgrub par bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:3298: gong du gsungs pa bzhin 'dir yang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3299: de nas sangs rgyas thams cad bdag la bcug ste lha mo'i tshogs kyi mchod par bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:3301: me tog la sogs pa'i mchod pa dang glu dang
NK052(zi)001:3302: gar dang rol mo'i phyag rgya rnams dbul bar bya
NK052(zi)001:3303: ste / lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:3304: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3305: dpal ldan g.yon pa 'gying ba'i thabs //
NK052(zi)001:3306: g.yas pa ba dan gsum par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3307: rdo rje dpal gyi thal mo bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3308: bsam pa g.yas pas phyag byas pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:3309: sangs rgyas mchod pa legs byas na //
NK052(zi)001:3310: ma lus lus pa med pa 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:3311: phyag btsal ba'i phyag rgya shes pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3312: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:3313: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes bsgyur ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:3314: rdo rje thal mo sbyar nas su //
NK052(zi)001:3315: de bzhin g.yon du bsgyur bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3316: de ni sbyor ba btegs nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3317: spyi bo'i mtshams su bzhag par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3318: skal bzang zhes bya ba'i glus //
NK052(zi)001:3319: mchod pa thams cad dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3320: gyen du mthor zhing thur du 'bebs //
NK052(zi)001:3321: skor zhing de bzhin nyug pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:3322: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3323: dri yi mchod pa dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3324: gang ngam 'on te stong yang rung //
NK052(zi)001:3325: yang ni ci 'byor ba yis kyang //
NK052(zi)001:3326: dam tshig mnyam par bsgrub pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3328: gyi glu yi phyag rgya ni //
NK052(zi)001:3329: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis ci dgar blang //
NK052(zi)001:3330: ma lus lus pa med pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3331: sems can thams cad thar bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:3332: gling bu dang ni rgyud gcig dang //
NK052(zi)001:3333: de bzhin rgyud mang rgyud stug dang //
NK052(zi)001:3334: sil snyin phyag rgyar bshad pa rnams //
NK052(zi)001:3335: las rnams thams cad rab bsgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:3336: cha lugs ji bzhin gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:3337: ma brdung bar yang rab tu grub //
NK052(zi)001:3338: las rnams kun la mchog tu ni //
NK052(zi)001:3340: dzahh+aum bam hohru ta ma ta sma ra ra ta /
NK052(zi)001:3342: pra sid+d+h+ya tak+ki h+aum dzah a la la la ho /
NK052(zi)001:3343: shud+d+h+ya sid+d+ha da ri sha ya sarba /
NK052(zi)001:3346: ta g+he na ta g+he na g+he na g+he na g+he na to //
NK052(zi)001:3348: tak+ki h+aum dzah g+he na de g+he do //
NK052(zi)001:3351: a la la la hoh ru rgya ma te /
NK052(zi)001:3352: thal mo brdab pa brtag pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3354: ta g+hen ta g+hen g+he ta g+hen g+he ta g+he /
NK052(zi)001:3359: d+ha nga d+ha nga d+ha nga /
NK052(zi)001:3361: de ltar rol mo dang gar dang glu'i mchod pa dbul te /
NK052(zi)001:3362: 'jig rten khams mang rdul phran grangs med khyab par spros pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:3363: rgyal ba'i don rnams rab tu phra ba'i rdul gyi grangs rnyed pa //
NK052(zi)001:3364: sprul pa'i sku rnams rab tu phra ba'i grangs snyed kyi //
NK052(zi)001:3365: srid pa bde chen de bzhin gshegs kun rnam 'phrul sna tshogs kyis //
NK052(zi)001:3366: rdul phran grangs snyed de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par 'phrul ba mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3367: de nas gar gyi glus mchod de /
NK052(zi)001:3368: gar gyi phyag rgya thams cad bsgyur zhing /
NK052(zi)001:3369: la lar dri med zla ba'i dkyil 'khor stong pas mdzes pa'i gzugs su rnam par snang //
NK052(zi)001:3370: la lar rab tu 'jigs pa'i nyi ma bye ba phrag dgu'i 'od zer mchog pas 'jigs //
NK052(zi)001:3371: la lar mdangs bzang gzi chen bde dang zhi bar ldan pa rgyal ba'i gzugs su snang //
NK052(zi)001:3372: la lar 'gro ba thams cad mnyam par 'jog pa'i gzugs ldan par ston //
NK052(zi)001:3373: rdo rje sems dpa' grub phyir 'dul la mkhas pa ma lus bde ba'i mchog rnams las //
NK052(zi)001:3374: a ral thams cad mnyam sbyor grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3375: ru ta ma ta a la la la hoh rnam
NK052(zi)001:3376: pa mang po 'dul bar mdzad pa'i tshul la gar
NK052(zi)001:3377: mkhan mchog gis gar mdzad pa //
NK052(zi)001:3378: dam tshig gar gyi dbang phyug sangs rgyas gar mkhan
NK052(zi)001:3379: gar mdzod a la la la hoh rnam mang bde
NK052(zi)001:3380: mchog rab tu gar mdzad pa yis thar pa'i bde
NK052(zi)001:3382: 'di yis ba dan gsum dang ldan pas gar du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3383: rab tu dga' dang rjes su chags par dga' ba'i mda' gzhu rab tu phra bas rgyas btab pas //
NK052(zi)001:3384: rab tu dga' bar sbyor ba'i bde bas myos pa bde ba thams cad bdag la grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3385: rab tu bde ba rnam pa sna tshogs rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba'i longs spyod dang //
NK052(zi)001:3386: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug che mchog grub pa de bzhin gshegs pa bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:3387: he rta mchog hoh kye rab tu bde ba'i rnam pa sna tshogs rol gcig ho /
NK052(zi)001:3391: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi mkha' 'gro sgyu ma rnam pa sna tshogs kyi /
NK052(zi)001:3393: kye bde ba'i mchog grub par mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:3394: kye ma'o bde bas bde ba gsol //
NK052(zi)001:3395: dam pa rab tu bzhugs par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3396: bdag la rab tu bde bar 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3397: a la la la hoh e ma'o shi shi zhugs shig zhugs shig /
NK052(zi)001:3401: de nas gar dang ldan pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3402: dbyangs 'di rnams kyi klu blangs shing //
NK052(zi)001:3403: dpal ldan g.yon du 'dud pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3404: g.yas kyi ba dan gsum du bya //
NK052(zi)001:3405: de ltar g.yas dang g.yon tshul gyi //
NK052(zi)001:3406: sems dpa'i skyil krung bsnyems byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3407: rnal 'byor bde byed bdag nyid kyis //
NK052(zi)001:3408: bde ba rnams ni yang dag dbul //
NK052(zi)001:3409: de nas 'di yis mchod bya ba //
NK052(zi)001:3410: g.yas dang g.yon gyi lag pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3411: 'gying ba'i mchog gi gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3412: steng du dor dang 'og tu dor //
NK052(zi)001:3413: bskor dang de bzhin byug bya ste //
NK052(zi)001:3414: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3415: dri yis mchod pas bskor ba yin //
NK052(zi)001:3416: lhag ma gar gyi tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:3417: gling bu'i pi wang rdza rnga mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3418: de bzhin cang te'u rnam dag kyang //
NK052(zi)001:3419: g.yon gyi khu tshur rab bsdams te //
NK052(zi)001:3420: lag pa g.yas pas brdung byas shing //
NK052(zi)001:3421: rang gi ming gi bskul byas pas //
NK052(zi)001:3422: sngags pas mchod pa dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3423: zhi ba'i thal mo bde mchog gis //
NK052(zi)001:3424: thal mo sbyar bas dgyes pa bskyed //
NK052(zi)001:3425: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:3426: lta ba rab zhi bde bar gnas //
NK052(zi)001:3427: sbyor ba kun gyi bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3428: mdzes pa'i ma mchu g.yo bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:3429: sangs rgyas byang chub mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:3430: rab tu dga' bar lta zhing 'dzum //
NK052(zi)001:3431: shin tu srid pa yang dag bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:3432: smin ma mig dang so dang mchu //
NK052(zi)001:3433: kha dang lus dang rkang lag gis //
NK052(zi)001:3434: cha lugs bzhin du gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3435: phyag rgya kun gyi mchod pa dbul //
NK052(zi)001:3436: ru ru s+phu ru dz+wa la ti sh+tha sid+d+ha lo tsa ni sarba ar+tha s+aa d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:3437: chos kyi phyag rgya mchog 'di ni //
NK052(zi)001:3438: sems can thams cad dbang byed pa //
NK052(zi)001:3439: stobs kyis myur du bkug nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3440: rang bzhin du ni byed du 'jug /
NK052(zi)001:3441: de la dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi gsang sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:3443: 'dis rang gi las la sbyar te bzlas pa dang bsgom pa ci nus pa byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3445: de'i tshe'ang dbang bskur ba dang bsrung ba la sogs pa byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3446: rdo rje thal mos dgyes pa bskyed nas ci dga' bar gnas par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3447: gal te tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'di lta bur slob
NK052(zi)001:3448: ma 'jug par 'dod na yang 'di nyid las gsungs
NK052(zi)001:3449: bzhin du dbang bskur ba dang dam tshig sbyin par
NK052(zi)001:3450: bya'o // 'di lta bu'i tshogs ji ltar dam bcas
NK052(zi)001:3451: pa bzhin bsgrubs nas thal mar dngos grub kyi rdzas
NK052(zi)001:3452: rnams grub pa'i mtshan ma thob bam ma thob kyang
NK052(zi)001:3453: bya'o // rung ste / dngos grub blang bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3454: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i
NK052(zi)001:3455: tshul gyis tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa'i cho
NK052(zi)001:3456: ga rdzogs so // da ni dpal he ru k+aa'i
NK052(zi)001:3457: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa'i cho ga bshad
NK052(zi)001:3458: ga rdzogs so // de / de'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:3460: dam tshigs la sdang rnam sbyang phyir //
NK052(zi)001:3461: thams cad rnal 'byor dbang phyug mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3462: rdo rje mkha' 'gro byang bar gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3464: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:3465: rang gi byin rlabs bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:3466: gzugs brnyan ngo bor sbyor ba yi //
NK052(zi)001:3467: phyag rgya'i sbyor bas gar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3469: de la dpal he ru ka'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du dngos grub sgrub par 'dod pas /
NK052(zi)001:3470: thog mar rdo rje slob dpon yongs su bzung ba
NK052(zi)001:3471: la sogs pa sngon du bya ba'i cho ga yan
NK052(zi)001:3472: lag ji skad bstan pa rdzogs par byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3473: sgrub pa rtsom par byed pa na gzungs ma dang
NK052(zi)001:3474: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa nyer bsdogs su gnas
NK052(zi)001:3476: nyin re'am yang na zla re'am //
NK052(zi)001:3477: yang na de bzhin lo rer ni //
NK052(zi)001:3478: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du bsgrubs par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3480: bcu bzhi dang bco lnga dang /
NK052(zi)001:3481: khyad par du ni tshes brgyad la'o //
NK052(zi)001:3484: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang //
NK052(zi)001:3485: ma mo'i gnas la sogs 'dug na //
NK052(zi)001:3486: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dgos pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:3490: gong du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin ji ltar 'byor ba byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3491: de thun mong gi yo byad rnams dang /
NK052(zi)001:3492: khyad par gyi yo byad kyang /
NK052(zi)001:3494: rdo rje can la sna tshogs pa //
NK052(zi)001:3497: rdo rje can la ru ru ke //
NK052(zi)001:3500: rdo rje can la mar me bdun //
NK052(zi)001:3503: bdag gis phyur chen skal bzang po //
NK052(zi)001:3504: rdo rje las ni dpal 'grub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3505: phyi'i mchod pa dang gtor ma'i yo byad ni /
NK052(zi)001:3507: sgeg mo dang ni na chung dang //
NK052(zi)001:3508: myos dang de bzhin bdud rtsi dang //
NK052(zi)001:3509: gcig pu kha dang 'dod chags sdang //
NK052(zi)001:3510: g.yon can bran mo de bzhin te //
NK052(zi)001:3511: lan tsha la sogs ro kun dang //
NK052(zi)001:3512: kha ra la sogs bdud rtsi bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:3514: sha dang chang du ldan pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:3515: bza' ba sna tshogs grub pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:3516: dga' ba'i longs spyod skal mchog ste //
NK052(zi)001:3517: tshe yi dam pa grub par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3518: a mra smrin dang rgun 'bru dang //
NK052(zi)001:3519: pa na se dang na le ker //
NK052(zi)001:3520: a ru ka la sogs pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:3524: btung ba dang bza' ba dang bca' ba'i yo byad ji lhar 'byor pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3525: bla re la sogs pa'i rgyan gyi khyad par ji ltar 'byor ba bzhin byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3526: sa'i cha yang dkyil 'khor chen po'i tshul du rdo rje'i thig gis btab ste byas /
NK052(zi)001:3528: rdo rje can gyi zla khams bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:3530: zla kham la re mig dgu par byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3531: phyi rol khyams dang sgor ldan pa bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3532: sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig /
NK052(zi)001:3533: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor gud du byed na pho
NK052(zi)001:3534: brang zlum po shar nub tu zla kham du bcad
NK052(zi)001:3535: de / nub phyogs ri'u mig dgu par byas /
NK052(zi)001:3536: shar phyogs su dngos grub kyi rdzas dang dngos grub kyi rtsol ba bzhag /
NK052(zi)001:3537: bar du sgo kha sprod bar bzhed do //
NK052(zi)001:3538: spyir ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su rdul
NK052(zi)001:3539: tshon mi dgye bar sa'i cha rdo rje'i thig gis
NK052(zi)001:3540: btab ste / der rang rang gi lha'i stan bting ste /
NK052(zi)001:3541: der phyag rgya rnam pa gnyis dgod par bzhed de /
NK052(zi)001:3542: de la phyag rgya gnyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:3543: lugs ma la sogs pa'i phyag rgya bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya rnams dang /
NK052(zi)001:3544: byin gyis brlabs bsgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i phyag rgya bud med rnams dgod pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3545: de la bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3547: khams kyi ngo bo thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:3548: de bzhin srog dang rtsa las byung //
NK052(zi)001:3549: rang gi lha'i cha lugs su //
NK052(zi)001:3550: bsgrub pa'i phyag rgya rab tu bya //
NK052(zi)001:3552: byin gyis brlabs sgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3554: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yin //
NK052(zi)001:3555: bud med dag ni legs bsgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:3556: skal bzang rang gi phyag mtshan //
NK052(zi)001:3557: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor brtags par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3559: ji bzhin byin gyis brlabs byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:3560: sangs rgyas bde mchog gar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3562: phyag rgya 'di rnams dgod pa'i dus dang tshul yang /
NK052(zi)001:3563: nyin gyi tha mar bzhag par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3564: zhes gsungs pa bzhin dgong ka'i dus su sku gzugs
NK052(zi)001:3565: dang rnal 'byor ma rnams gtso bo dang bcas par
NK052(zi)001:3566: byi dor dang khrus dang byug pa dang rgyan thams
NK052(zi)001:3568: ji ltar rang gi lha dang mthun pa'i gos bzang po dang /
NK052(zi)001:3569: rang rang gi mtshan mas mtshan cing bzhag pa rnams /
NK052(zi)001:3570: phyi rol gyis phyogs gcig tu bzhugs nas /
NK052(zi)001:3571: de nas rdo rje lcam dral phab pa rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:3572: glu dang rol mo'i cha byad rnams kyis spyan drangs
NK052(zi)001:3573: te / sngags kyis khang par so so'i gdan stengs su gshegs shing bzhugs su gsol /
NK052(zi)001:3574: de nas sgo ba'am las byed rnams kyis phyi nas 'brengs pa'i bgegs bskrad par bgyi /
NK052(zi)001:3575: de nas brda phyag bgyi ste /
NK052(zi)001:3576: rnal 'byor phal pa rnams dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo'i tshogs kyis lag pa spyi bor byug ste /
NK052(zi)001:3579: slob dpon gyis de bzhin du dpral bar reg ste /
NK052(zi)001:3582: de bzhin du rnal 'byor mched lcam dral thams cad
NK052(zi)001:3583: kyang so so rang rang gis bkur rim bzhin du
NK052(zi)001:3584: phyag dang lan gyis brda phyag bgyi ste /
NK052(zi)001:3585: rang rang gi gnas su 'khod do //
NK052(zi)001:3586: bud med tshang bar med na de'i gnas su lugs
NK052(zi)001:3587: ma sogs pa rang rang gi sku gzugs bzhag go
NK052(zi)001:3588: // yod pa rnams ni sku gzugs dang 'brel bar bzhag go //
NK052(zi)001:3589: de nas rang byin gyis brlab pa bsgrub pa'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:3590: man ngag gi tshul rnam pa gnyis su 'chad de /
NK052(zi)001:3592: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i zhal snga nas /
NK052(zi)001:3593: sgrub pa'i cho ga de nyid bcu'i sgo nas bsgrub par gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:3595: slob dpon h+aum ka'i zhal snga nas /
NK052(zi)001:3596: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa mchod pa'i cho ga
NK052(zi)001:3597: yan lag bcu dang bcas pas bsgrub par gsungs pa'o
NK052(zi)001:3598: // de la slob dpon rdo rje zhal snga nas /
NK052(zi)001:3599: bsgrub pa'i cho ga de kho na nyid bcu gsungs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3600: cho 'phrul bzhi'i sbyor ba rnam pa bzhi ste brgyad la rdzas bcu ste /
NK052(zi)001:3607: dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul gnyis te drug /
NK052(zi)001:3608: ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul spyi'i chos dang ldan pa bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3609: rdzas gud du bgrang du med pas /
NK052(zi)001:3610: de ltar drug gi steng du sbyor ba rnam pa bzhi ste bcu'i tshul gyis bsgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:3612: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i zhal snga nas /
NK052(zi)001:3613: phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi gzhir gyur pa /
NK052(zi)001:3614: thams cad 'byung byed ye shes phyag rgya bsgrub pa'i
NK052(zi)001:3615: cho ga'ang de nyid bcu'i tshul gyis bsgrub par gsungs
NK052(zi)001:3617: rdo rje'i byin rlabs tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:3618: ting nge 'dzin ni bdag dbang bskur //
NK052(zi)001:3619: snying po phyag rgya sngags rig gis //
NK052(zi)001:3620: gsang ba'i mchod pa mchog gis bskul //
NK052(zi)001:3621: sbyor dang rab sbyor sbyor che ba //
NK052(zi)001:3622: rnal 'byor thams cad bsgrub bya ba //
NK052(zi)001:3623: de nyid bcu la sogs tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:3624: thams cad skye 'gyur bsgrub par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3625: 'di yis sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:3626: de bzhin dpa' bo thams cad dag /
NK052(zi)001:3627: ci bder yul la longs spyod pas //
NK052(zi)001:3631: dang por bdag nyid byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3632: dbang bskur ba'i tshul gyis dpal he ru ka'i rnal 'byor bsgrub par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3633: de yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la brten nas bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3634: de nas lha mo rnams kyang bdag dang mthun par byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3635: dbang bskur ba'i tshul gyis rang rang gi lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgyar byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:3636: de nas gsang ba'i mchod pa bskul lo //
NK052(zi)001:3637: de nyid sbyor ba bzhi'i tshul gyis te /
NK052(zi)001:3642: lha mo rnams kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK052(zi)001:3644: de gnyis ka'i sgo nas gsang ba'i mchod pa bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3646: bde ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin rnyed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:3648: de yang dang po nyid du stan byin gyis brlab par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3649: badz+ra pad+ma +aa ba na ma h+aa yo ga bi tham h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:3650: zhes bya bar byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:3651: so so rang rang gi stan thams cad kyang byin gyis brlabs par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3652: de nas yan lag bdun dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3653: dang por dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor bas dpung pa gnyis rdo rje bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:3654: rdo rje se gol gtogs pas /
NK052(zi)001:3655: dzahh+aum bam ho zhes brjod cing /
NK052(zi)001:3656: sangs rgyas thams cad nam mkha' la bsdu bar bya /
NK052(zi)001:3657: de nas g.yon pas se gol btabs pa /
NK052(zi)001:3658: g.yas pa'i thal mo dal gyis brdabs te /
NK052(zi)001:3659: de bzhin du thal mo lan gsum dal gyis brdabs
NK052(zi)001:3660: pa 'di ni mnyes par byed pa bzhi'i thal mo'o
NK052(zi)001:3662: phyag gi phyag rgyas phyag byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3663: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:3664: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3665: dpal ldan g.yon pa 'gying ba'i thabs //
NK052(zi)001:3666: g.yas pa ba dan gsum pa byas //
NK052(zi)001:3667: smin ma g.yon pa 'degs tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:3668: ru lu ru lur bcas brgad na //
NK052(zi)001:3669: tshangs pa nye dbang drag por bcas //
NK052(zi)001:3670: khams gsum pa rnams phyag byed 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3671: tshul 'di nyid kyis phyag btsal bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3674: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga po rnams //
NK052(zi)001:3675: dbang po kun las spro sa ste //
NK052(zi)001:3676: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:3677: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3678: rdo rje thal mo gyen du dgrol //
NK052(zi)001:3679: mchod pa'i gtor ma kun gyi tshul //
NK052(zi)001:3680: dur khrod cha lugs gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:3681: phyag rgya 'di yis gar byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:3682: skal bzang rdo rje drag por rgod //
NK052(zi)001:3683: mchod pa thams cad dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3684: zhi ba'i thal mo sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:3685: sha rdza gan rdar tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:3686: rdo rje dbyangs kyis bstod par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3687: rdo rje dbyangs kyi tshig kyang /
NK052(zi)001:3689: zhes bya ba la sogs pa dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bstod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3690: ba hu bi bi ta'i sgo nas bstod de /
NK052(zi)001:3692: de nas sdig pa bshags pa bya /
NK052(zi)001:3693: bsod nams kyi rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:3696: dge ba yongs su bsngo ba rnams ci dga' ba byas la /
NK052(zi)001:3697: byang chub kyi sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3698: 'di ltar brtson 'grus chen pos go bgos pa /
NK052(zi)001:3699: snying rje chen pos brlan pa'i sems gzhan la phan pa gcig pu mthar gyur pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3700: ma lus lus pa med pa'i 'jig rten na gnas
NK052(zi)001:3701: pa'i sems can rnams sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las
NK052(zi)001:3702: bdag gis bsgral bar bya ba'i phyir dpal he ru
NK052(zi)001:3705: bdag byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa bsgrub pa'i cho ga la 'jug par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3706: 'di'i tshul dang rim pa yang 'di nyid kyi gtam gyi phyag rgya las /
NK052(zi)001:3707: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:3708: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:3709: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK052(zi)001:3710: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:3711: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK052(zi)001:3712: shin tu khro gtum gdug par gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3713: de nas bcom ldan rdo rje can //
NK052(zi)001:3714: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:3715: rdo rje se gol phyag rgyas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3716: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu bar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:3717: de yi bka' tsam gyis bsgrags nas //
NK052(zi)001:3718: 'jig rten khams ni ma lus par //
NK052(zi)001:3719: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin bcas pa //
NK052(zi)001:3720: kun gyis til 'bru bzhin du rgyas //
NK052(zi)001:3721: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK052(zi)001:3722: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK052(zi)001:3723: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo yi //
NK052(zi)001:3724: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:3725: de nas sna yi rtse mo la //
NK052(zi)001:3726: yid ni brtan par yang dag gzung //
NK052(zi)001:3727: sna yi dbugs ring drong ba las //
NK052(zi)001:3728: rgyal ba'i phyag rgya'i sbyor ba phyung //
NK052(zi)001:3729: bcom ldan 'das de nyid rnal 'byor pa //
NK052(zi)001:3730: rdo rje khro bor gyur nas phyung //
NK052(zi)001:3732: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor las /
NK052(zi)001:3733: dpal he tu ka'i rnal 'byor du bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3734: de'i rim pa'ang dang por phyag rgya'i ye shes phab pas sgrib pa bral zhing ye shes te /
NK052(zi)001:3735: bdag nyid shin tu rnam par dag par gnas pa las sangs rgyas rnams kyis bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:3736: bdag nyid byin gyis brlab pa'i cho ga rim pa bzhin bsgrub ste /
NK052(zi)001:3737: rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor du gnas pa las
NK052(zi)001:3738: thugs rje chen po'i dbang gis sngon gyi smon lam
NK052(zi)001:3740: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas pa na gnas pa'i gdug pa can thams cad 'dul bar dgongs te /
NK052(zi)001:3741: de yang sangs rgyas thams cad dang bka' blod cing byin gyis brlabs pa sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:3742: rdo rje se gol gyi phyag rgyas bskul zhing /
NK052(zi)001:3744: dam tshig bka'i phyag rgyas dam las 'da' ba bsgrags te /
NK052(zi)001:3745: sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'jig rten ma lus pa thams cad til 'bru bzhin du rgyas par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3746: de nas bka' blod na zhi bas 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab ste /
NK052(zi)001:3748: de nas dpal rdo rje sems dpa' rnal 'byor de
NK052(zi)001:3749: nyid kyis sangs rgyas thams cad dang dbyer med pa'i
NK052(zi)001:3751: yang na dbyer med par gyur pa nyid kyis kyang rung ste /
NK052(zi)001:3752: de'i rnal 'byor gyis rang gi shangs kyi rlung sgrom
NK052(zi)001:3753: nas h+aum gi dbugs ring las dpal he ru ka'i
NK052(zi)001:3755: de ltar phyung ba'i tshe dper na lus mi snang
NK052(zi)001:3756: bar nus shing sprul pa'i rdzu 'phrul thob pa rnams
NK052(zi)001:3757: lus gzhan du 'phrul par byas pa'i phyir rang gi
NK052(zi)001:3759: rang gi sems lus gzhan du sprul pa byung na /
NK052(zi)001:3760: rang gi lus snga ma mi snang bar sprul pa'i lus su gyur pa bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:3761: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rnal 'byor gyi h+aum gi
NK052(zi)001:3762: dbugs ring las dpal he ru ka phyung ba'i tshe
NK052(zi)001:3763: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid rdo rje khro bor gyur nas byung bar shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3764: cho ga mang po la sbyor ba mi nus pa rnams kyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:3765: ji skad bstan pa'i sgrib pa bral ba la sogs
NK052(zi)001:3766: pa med par skad cig tsam gyis rdo rje sems
NK052(zi)001:3767: dpa'i ting nge 'dzin du gnas te /
NK052(zi)001:3769: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:3770: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i dmigs pas bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:3771: snga ma bzhin du dpa' he ru ka bskyed par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3773: dpal chen rdo rje he ru ka /
NK052(zi)001:3775: sems dpa' sngon po 'bar ba'i mdangs //
NK052(zi)001:3777: 'jigs pa chen po'i dus ltar grags //
NK052(zi)001:3778: dur khrod kyi ni me dang 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:3780: thod pa mang po'i dbu rgyan can //
NK052(zi)001:3781: dur khrod bzhin du rab tu 'jigs //
NK052(zi)001:3782: khro la sogs pa'i tshul ldan pa //
NK052(zi)001:3783: zhabs rnams sna tshogs 'gyur ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:3784: smin ma khro gnyer bcas par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3787: rdo rje 'bar dang kha tam ga /
NK052(zi)001:3788: thod pa kham phor de bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:3789: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa ltar bskyed par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3790: de nas byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3791: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:3792: snying ga dang smin mtshams dang mgrin pa dang spyi bo rnams su byin gyis rlob par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:3795: rdo rje bsdams par byas nas su //
NK052(zi)001:3796: mdzub mo mthe bo'i mdal dag tu //
NK052(zi)001:3797: g.yas pa'i mthe bo mtshan ma yi //
NK052(zi)001:3798: rtse mo btsug la bsdam par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3799: dga' chen dpal gyi rdo rje ste //
NK052(zi)001:3801: phyag rgya de yang rdo rje gar dang bcas pas bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3802: de nas yang rdo rje'i phyag rgyas rdo rje 'dzin par byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:3804: dga' ba'i rdo rje rab bcings nas //
NK052(zi)001:3805: gung mo bcings pa'i nang du gzhug /
NK052(zi)001:3806: mthe bong mathe'u chung rtse mo can //
NK052(zi)001:3807: rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs su bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3809: 'di ni rigs kyi spyi'i phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3811: rdo rje phyag rgya de'i gung mo nam mkha' la bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:3813: dpal he ru ka nyid du byin gyis rlob par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:3814: de nas phyag rgya de 'gying ba dang bcas pas
NK052(zi)001:3815: mtha' nas bkrol te spyi bo'i mtshams su bzhag nas
NK052(zi)001:3816: dar dpyangs 'dra ba'i tshul du byas te /
NK052(zi)001:3818: zhes brjod de thal mos brtan par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3819: 'di ni byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3820: de nas rin po che rnam pa lnga'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:3821: dang chos kyi phyag rgyas rigs rnam pa lnga'i dbu
NK052(zi)001:3822: brgyan gyis dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3823: de la sangs rgyas rin chen gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3824: mthe bo sems dpa' skyil mo krung //
NK052(zi)001:3825: mdzub mo gnyis ni rtse mo dgug /
NK052(zi)001:3826: gung mo gnyis ni mnyam par sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:3827: lhag ma rdo rje thal mo 'o //
NK052(zi)001:3828: spyi bo dang ni dpral ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:3829: mdan pa gnyis dang ltag pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:3830: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin chen mchog /
NK052(zi)001:3831: dbu rgyan kun tu brgyan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3832: dbu rgyan bcings pas bcings nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3833: 'gying zhing mtha' nas dgrol bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3834: dar gyi mtha' ma dpyangs pa ltar //
NK052(zi)001:3835: byas nas thal mo brtan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3836: bud+d+ha rat+na a b+hi sha ke ru ru s+phu ru dz+wa la tish+tha /
NK052(zi)001:3837: bud+d+ha lo tsa na sarba a r+tha s+aa d+h+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam swa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:3838: sangs rgyas rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3839: rdo rje rin chen rigs kyi ni rdo rje rab
NK052(zi)001:3840: tu dga' ba'i phyag rgyas snga ma bzhin du dbang
NK052(zi)001:3841: bskur ro // badz+ra rat+na a b+hi shi ke t+aa
NK052(zi)001:3842: re tut+ta re a b+hi she ke he bi mi
NK052(zi)001:3843: ri ti ri na sh+ri ye a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam
NK052(zi)001:3844: bskur ro // s+w+aa h+aa / rdo rje rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3845: pad mo rin gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:3846: sangs rgyas rin chen las gung mo'i rtse mo phab pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3847: pad+ma rat+na a b+hi she ke t+aa re tut+t+aa re a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK052(zi)001:3848: pad+mo rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3849: rin chen rin chen gyi ni /
NK052(zi)001:3850: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar te //
NK052(zi)001:3851: lag gnyis nor bu rin chen du //
NK052(zi)001:3852: ji ltar rigs par sbyar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:3853: mthe bo mdzub mo rtse mo bzhi //
NK052(zi)001:3854: rat+na rat+na a b+hi she ke tram tram ba ba
NK052(zi)001:3855: ta ta ta ta ta ta a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam
NK052(zi)001:3856: s+w+aa h+aa / rin chen rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3857: las kyi rin chen gyi ni /
NK052(zi)001:3858: rdo rje thal mo rab bsdams te /
NK052(zi)001:3859: mdzub mo'i rtse mo yid tsam dgug /
NK052(zi)001:3860: mthe bo dpa' bo'i skyil mo krung //
NK052(zi)001:3861: lhag ma rnams ni 'od bzhin btang //
NK052(zi)001:3862: karma rat+na a b+hi she ke hi hi hi hi
NK052(zi)001:3863: sh+r+ai badz+ra pad+ma ba da ba mu she a b+hi
NK052(zi)001:3865: las kyi rin chen gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:3867: rdo rje'i phyag rgya dpral bar /
NK052(zi)001:3868: rin po che mdan pa g.yas su /
NK052(zi)001:3870: las kyi mdan pa g.yon du bzhag ste dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:3871: de nas thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:3872: thod phreng gi phyag rgya mgo'i gnas lngar gtug la /
NK052(zi)001:3873: thod pa'i dbu rgyan du bsam ste /
NK052(zi)001:3875: sor mo thams cad nang du bsnol //
NK052(zi)001:3876: sor mo'i rtse mo kun sprad nas //
NK052(zi)001:3877: mthe bong rdo rje mnan pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:3878: sna dang mig sbugs lta bu ste //
NK052(zi)001:3879: pad mo rin chen phyag rgya 'di //
NK052(zi)001:3880: bdag nyid chen po dbang bskur ba //
NK052(zi)001:3881: rgyal srid thams cad ma lus pa //
NK052(zi)001:3882: lus pa med pa myur du 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:3883: spyi bo dang dpral ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:3884: mdan pa gnyis dang ltag par sbyar //
NK052(zi)001:3885: thod pa'i phreng bas dbu rgyan te //
NK052(zi)001:3886: sangs rgyas gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK052(zi)001:3887: dbu rgyan bcings bcings nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3888: 'gyings bas mtha' nas dgrol bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:3889: dar gyi mtha' ma dpyangs pa ltar //
NK052(zi)001:3890: byas nas thal mo brdab par bya //
NK052(zi)001:3891: zhes bya ba dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3892: de nas dpal he ru ka'i rang gi rigs kyi phyag rgya smin mtshams su bzhag ste /
NK052(zi)001:3893: dbang bskur zhing bsrung ba dang mkha' 'gro ma dang
NK052(zi)001:3894: dur khrod kyi bdag po thams cad dbang du bsdu
NK052(zi)001:3895: bar bya ste / phyag rgya ni 'di skad du /
NK052(zi)001:3896: lag pa shin tu brkyang ba ni //
NK052(zi)001:3897: mdzub mo gnyis ni mdud par bcing //
NK052(zi)001:3898: gung mo mthe bong rtse mo nas //
NK052(zi)001:3899: rdo rje phyag rgya yongs su bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:3900: yongs su bsgyur te btegs nas kyang //
NK052(zi)001:3901: khro gnyer du ni legs bzhag na //
NK052(zi)001:3902: rgyal srid thams cad rab grub pa //
NK052(zi)001:3903: ma lus lus pa med par 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:3904: 'di yis bsrung bar byas nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:3905: rdo rje las ni dpal dang 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:3906: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rab grub pa //
NK052(zi)001:3907: ma lus lus pa med pa 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:3908: ma mo dang ni byang ma dang //
NK052(zi)001:3910: dur khrod dngos grub thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:3911: las rnams thams cad byed par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:3912: zhes gsungs pas sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3913: de ltar bdag nyid dbang bskur ba byas nas go bgo bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3914: rdo rje bsdams pa brkyang ba mgrin par bzhag ste /
NK052(zi)001:3915: badz+ra ki ba tsa ya am ham bam +aam /
NK052(zi)001:3917: bcings pa de las gnyis su byas nas mdzub mo brkyang ste /
NK052(zi)001:3918: so so nas gdong sprad pa mdud pa'i tshul gyis
NK052(zi)001:3919: snying ga nas brtsams nas spyi gtsug gi bar du
NK052(zi)001:3920: 'dor zhing / h+aum ka pa tsa ya mam tum /
NK052(zi)001:3921: zhes sngags 'di lan gsum gsum byas na 'dis cis kyang mi phyed par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:3922: de la dpal he ru ka'i sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gyi tshul ni /
NK052(zi)001:3923: zhal gcig phyag bzhir bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:3924: gong du dkyus las gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:3926: phyag na rdo rje 'bar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:3927: rdo rje kha t+w+ai ka dril bu 'khrol ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:3929: snying chen la sogs pa sha chen gyi kham phor thogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3930: zhal bzhi phyag brgyad zhabs bzhi 'phrul pa'i tshe /
NK052(zi)001:3935: phyag g.yas g.yon dang po snga ma dang 'dra /
NK052(zi)001:3936: 'og gnyis kyis gos chen po gsol lo //
NK052(zi)001:3937: phyag tha ltag gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'gengs /
NK052(zi)001:3938: tha ma gnyis snga ma dang 'dra /
NK052(zi)001:3939: zhabs bzhis dregs pa chen po khyo shugs brkyang bskum gyi tshul gyis bardzisa par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3941: dur khrod kun gyi 'byung po yi //
NK052(zi)001:3942: phyag rgya dpal ldan phun sum tshogs //
NK052(zi)001:3943: zhes gsungs pas dur khrod kyi rgyan spyir grags pa rnams kyis brgyan kyang nyes pa med do //
NK052(zi)001:3944: bdag byin gyis brlab pa bsgrub pa'i rim pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:3945: gzhan yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK052(zi)001:3946: las dpal he ru ka 'byung ba mi byed par
NK052(zi)001:3947: / rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin byang chub kyi
NK052(zi)001:3948: sems las dpal he ru ka bskyed par 'dod na
NK052(zi)001:3949: / ni / chos dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ngang
NK052(zi)001:3950: las snying rje byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin nyi
NK052(zi)001:3952: de'i steng du kun gzhi rnam par shes pa sa bon h+r+aihzhesa bya bar gyur par bsams la /
NK052(zi)001:3953: de las 'od zer 'phro ba dang 'du ba'i sbyor ba'i rdo rje gyu ra par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3954: ye shes kyi rdo rje de las ye shes kyi
NK052(zi)001:3955: 'od zer sna tshogs byung nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK052(zi)001:3956: thams cad snang bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3957: slar rdo rje la 'dus pa las dpal he ru
NK052(zi)001:3958: ka'i phyag rgya chen po'i tshul du gyur par bsams
NK052(zi)001:3959: shing / gsang sngags 'dis kyang byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3960: he ru kahbadz+ra sa ma ya h+r+aihsarba dush+ta sa ma ya mu dra b+ham dza ka h+aum phata /
NK052(zi)001:3962: de ltar sku bskyed nas byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:3964: go bgo ba snga ma bzhin du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3965: 'di ni bdag phyag rgya chen por bsgrub pa'i rim pa gzhan yin te /
NK052(zi)001:3966: cho ga bsdus pa'i tshul yin no //
NK052(zi)001:3967: da ni yul rnams kyi phyag rgya chen po bsgrub pa bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:3968: de yang gzungs ma rnams rang rang gis byin gyis brlab par nus na ni /
NK052(zi)001:3969: gong du rang rang gi gnas su 'khod pa bzhin
NK052(zi)001:3970: du lha so so rang rang gi skur bskyed cing
NK052(zi)001:3971: bsgrub par bya'o // rang rang gis byin gyis brlab
NK052(zi)001:3972: par mi nus na ni gtso bos byin gyis brlab
NK052(zi)001:3973: bsgrub par bya'o // par bya'o // de la dpal he ru ka'i 'khor gyi lha mo ni /
NK052(zi)001:3974: ke'u ri la sogs pa brgyad khyad par du bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:3975: mchod pa'i lha mo dang sgo ma rnams dpal rdo
NK052(zi)001:3976: rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor dang mthun par spyir grags
NK052(zi)001:3977: so // sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig gis ni /
NK052(zi)001:3978: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams phra men mar bsgyur zhes bshad /
NK052(zi)001:3979: 'di nyid kyi rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma las lha mo bcu gnyis su bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:3980: ke'u ri la sogs pa brgyad dang /
NK052(zi)001:3981: dpal rdo rje mda' 'dzin ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:3982: de bzhin du kha t+ai 'dzin ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:3984: sna tshogs 'dzin ma rnams su gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:3985: 'di bzhi ni phyi'i grwa la dgod pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:3986: de la lha rnams rang rang gis byin gyis rlob
NK052(zi)001:3987: na ni rang rang gi gnas su rang rang gi
NK052(zi)001:3988: sa bon rang rang gi skur bskyed par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3989: de yang cho ga gsum gyi tshul gyis bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3990: 'di ltar sa bon las thugs mtshan du bskyed de /
NK052(zi)001:3991: de la rang rang gi sngags kyis phyag rgya chen po bsgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:3992: gal te gtso bos byin gyis rlob par byed na ni /
NK052(zi)001:3993: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas lha mo rnams kyi sa bon sprul te /
NK052(zi)001:3994: de las so so'i sngags kyis bskul bas /
NK052(zi)001:3995: lha mo rnams kyi sku bskyed de dkyil 'khor du dgod par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:3996: de ltar gang yang rung bas phyag rgya chen po bsgrub bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:3998: de la lha mo rnams kyi sa bon ni /
NK052(zi)001:3999: ke ri la sogs gsang ba'i yum bzhi'i ni /
NK052(zi)001:4001: puk+ka si la sogs pa rigs kyi yum bzhi'i sa bon ni /
NK052(zi)001:4002: h+aum mat+ta zhes bya ba lan bzhi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4003: rdo rje mda' 'dzin ma la sogs pa bzhi'i sa bon ni /
NK052(zi)001:4004: k+sham bam yam ram rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:4006: rnon po mda' dang de bzhin 'dren //
NK052(zi)001:4007: chang dang chu dang lcug ma dang //
NK052(zi)001:4008: ras dang de bzhin med dag ni //
NK052(zi)001:4009: zhes gsungs pa'i ma mo bdun dang /
NK052(zi)001:4010: brgyad pa las kyi phyag rgyar gsungs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4011: rdo rje mda' 'dzin ma la sogs pa ni ming nyid las shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4012: lha mo 'di rnams kyi sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:4013: h+aum badz+ra gu h+ya sid+d+hi sa ra ma yo g+ai
NK052(zi)001:4014: shwa ri h+aihh+aum h+aum badz+ra tsan+da de shwa ri kha
NK052(zi)001:4015: t+wam gi ma h+aa badz+ra ka p+aa la mu ku
NK052(zi)001:4017: h+aum badz+ra na ya ni dz+himrah&a&a&a h+aum badz+ra p+aa ti ke dzi /
NK052(zi)001:4021: 'degs byed ma bzhi'i gsang sngags te /
NK052(zi)001:4022: ke ri la sogs pa'i gsang ba'i yum bzhi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4023: h'u badz+ra pra ha na ni /
NK052(zi)001:4024: h'u badz+ra shu l+aa gri b+hin+da mata /
NK052(zi)001:4025: h'u badz+ra ko she tigatsha&a&a&a ma ta /
NK052(zi)001:4026: h+aum badz+ra m+aa l+aa p+aa she ma ta /
NK052(zi)001:4028: gar byed ma dang gsod ma dang /
NK052(zi)001:4030: rdo rje las ma rnams kyi gsang sngags te /
NK052(zi)001:4031: puk+ka si la sogs pa rigs kyi yum bzhi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4032: gzhan yang lha mo bcu gnyis su sgrub par byed pa na /
NK052(zi)001:4033: dpal rdo rje mda' 'dzin ma la sogs pa bzhi'i gsang sngags te /
NK052(zi)001:4035: bam ma h+aa ra ta badz+re ho /
NK052(zi)001:4036: mo badz+ra lo tsa ne yam /
NK052(zi)001:4038: 'di bzhi ni rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma'i dbang du gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:4039: rtog pa 'dir lhag par ma gsungs pas ma bkod kyang nyes pa med do //
NK052(zi)001:4041: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du smos pa bzhin du 'dir yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:4042: lha mo mang po sgrub par mi nus na /
NK052(zi)001:4043: bud med gcig lha mo sma sha ni'i rang bzhin
NK052(zi)001:4044: yum kro d+h+ai shwa rir byin gyis brlabs la bsgrub
NK052(zi)001:4045: par bya'o // gal te mos pa dang nus pa'i
NK052(zi)001:4046: dbang gis phyi rol gyi phyag rgya med na gtso
NK052(zi)001:4047: bo'i thugs ka nas lha mo sma sha ni g.yas
NK052(zi)001:4048: pa gtso bo la mkhyud pa g.yon pa b+han+d+ha bsnams
NK052(zi)001:4049: pa kha t+aam ga la rgyab rten bcas pa bskyed
NK052(zi)001:4050: par bya'o // de / de dang rol pa las lha mo bdun bskyed pa bzhed do //
NK052(zi)001:4051: lha mo 'di rnams kyi sku mdog dang phyag mtshan
NK052(zi)001:4052: dang tshul ni go sla ba'i phyir spyir grags pa'i
NK052(zi)001:4055: zhi ba'i zhal te gzigs thabs kyang zhi bar gzigs /
NK052(zi)001:4057: mda' bzhi dus gcig tu 'phangs pas tshangs pa chen
NK052(zi)001:4058: po'i mgo bzhi bcad nas mda' rtse la 'phyang ba
NK052(zi)001:4059: / zhing gi stan brkyang ba'i steng na sna tshogs
NK052(zi)001:4060: pad+ma dang nyi ma'i stan la g.yon brkyang gis bzhugs
NK052(zi)001:4063: gzigs thabs khro bag tu gzigs /
NK052(zi)001:4065: g.yas g.yon gyi dpung pa la kha t+wam ga se
NK052(zi)001:4066: ral khar bkal nas khros pa'i tshul gyis snying gar
NK052(zi)001:4068: g.yas pa'i gung mos rtsibs brgyad pa'i 'khor lo 'phangs bstod nas 'dzin pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4069: rkang pa g.yas pa gyen du btegs nas gnon pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4071: zhal gnyis la gong ma ni phag chen po'i dbu /
NK052(zi)001:4072: 'og ma ni sku mdog dmar ba'i zhal /
NK052(zi)001:4074: phyag bzhi'i g.yas dang po rdo rje rtse gsum pa /
NK052(zi)001:4075: g.yon dang po kham phor chang gis bkang ba /
NK052(zi)001:4076: g.yas g.yon gnyis na khu tshur so sor bcings nas g.yas pas 'khor lo gzung ba /
NK052(zi)001:4077: g.yon pas brten nas 'degs pa'i tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK052(zi)001:4078: g.yas brkyang ba'i tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4080: dga' ba rtog pa'i tshul du ldan pa /
NK052(zi)001:4081: shi ba slong ba'i tshul du gzigs pa /
NK052(zi)001:4083: phyag g.yas pa kham phor zla ba lta bu 'od
NK052(zi)001:4084: dang ldan pa sha chen po dang khrag dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:4086: g.yon pa rdo rje ba dan 'dzin pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:4087: 'di'i phyag rgya ni lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong mdzub mo la bcar te /
NK052(zi)001:4088: srin lag mthur du bkug la /
NK052(zi)001:4089: sor mo lhag ma gsum rkyang pa ni ba dan gsum pa'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4090: ji ltar 'dod pa'i stobs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4092: drag po gar byed pa'i zhal la /
NK052(zi)001:4093: rnam pa 'gyur ba'i tshul du gzigs pa /
NK052(zi)001:4097: zhal dang lnga ni dkar la /
NK052(zi)001:4098: sku lus dngos ni dmar ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:4099: nya bzhi ni dmar ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:4100: phyag mchog lo ma sngon po 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:4102: lag pa g.yas rdo rje khu tshur gyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'bar ba 'dzin pa /
NK052(zi)001:4103: g.yon pa dpag bsam gyi shing gi lcug ma rlung gis bskyod pa 'dzin pa /
NK052(zi)001:4104: thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan zhing /
NK052(zi)001:4105: gar gyi gzigs thabs 'gyur ba dang bcas pas dur khrod kyi dbus su gar byed cing bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4107: gyen du dbugs 'byin pa lta bur gzigs pas gzhan
NK052(zi)001:4108: gyi srog 'phrog par byed pa'i sbyor ba la gnas
NK052(zi)001:4110: g.yas pa rdo rje khu tshur gyis dar dkar gyi
NK052(zi)001:4111: sgye'u rlung gis bkang ste rdo rjes mtshan pa gzung
NK052(zi)001:4112: nas rlung gi dkyil 'khor 'thor bas bsgrub bya'i srog
NK052(zi)001:4114: g.yon pa tri shul bsnams nas dur khrod kyi nang na gar byed cing bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4116: shi ba'i ro ldang ba'i sbyor ba dang ldan pas gzigs pa /
NK052(zi)001:4118: lag pa g.yon pas rdo rje khu tshur gyis rdo rje ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK052(zi)001:4119: g.yon pa 'bar ba'i me snod 'dzin pa /
NK052(zi)001:4122: mkha' 'gro ma bdun gyi phrin las kun byed pa'i ngo bo ste dpal khrag 'thung dang 'dra'o //
NK052(zi)001:4124: dpal chen po nyid ltar rdo rje dang bcas pas khrag gsol ba /
NK052(zi)001:4125: lag pa g.yon pas thod pa dang zhags pa bzungs
NK052(zi)001:4126: nas dpung pa la kha t+w+aam ga se ral kha'i
NK052(zi)001:4128: lha mo 'di dag kyang stan zhing brkyang ba'i steng na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la bzhugs shing /
NK052(zi)001:4129: zhing ras dang sbrul dang thod pa rkyang ba'i dbu rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4131: de nas mchod pa brtsam par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4132: lha mo'i tshogs de dag gis /
NK052(zi)001:4133: dpal he ru ka la glu 'di dag gis bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:4134: lha mo dang ni gnyis su med par rol pa'i
NK052(zi)001:4135: bde ba chen po'i mchod pa rnam par dag pas
NK052(zi)001:4136: / sangs rgyas thams cad mchod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4137: dkyil 'khor rnam par 'phrul cing sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4138: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi rdzas la brten nas
NK052(zi)001:4139: rdo rje rnal 'byor lcam dral rnams la dngos grub
NK052(zi)001:4141: slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing dbang bskur ba' phyir lha mos glu 'di dag gis bskul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4142: rjes su chags pa rnam mang dga' ba'i pad mo rnam dag pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:4143: mchod pas gsal bar rjes su mchod byas pa //
NK052(zi)001:4144: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor bde bas bde ba grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4145: kye mchog tu bde ba'i dam tshig rang gi ngo bo nyid //
NK052(zi)001:4146: mchog tu bde ba'i shin tu rnal 'byor skal bzang mchog brnyes pa //
NK052(zi)001:4147: rang gi dam tshig skyon med dag la rol cig rol cig ho /
NK052(zi)001:4148: kye ma'o mchog tu gsang ba'i bdag po rang gi
NK052(zi)001:4149: dam tshig yin pa'i phyir rab tu gsang ba'i lha
NK052(zi)001:4151: 'gro ba'i rgyud ni rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul ba gsal bar mkhyen //
NK052(zi)001:4152: dam tshig thams cad dngos po brtan g.yo kun gyi ngo bor 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4153: rgyal ba kun gyi bdag nyid rnal 'byor sgyu ma mkha' 'gro sgyu ma ho //
NK052(zi)001:4154: kye rtag pa pad ma'i dngos grub chen po rab tu bsgrub la ston //
NK052(zi)001:4155: dzahh+aum bam hoh e ma'o bde mchog bde ba drongs /
NK052(zi)001:4158: a la la la hoh zhes bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:4159: 'di ni dpal he ru ka la bde bas bde
NK052(zi)001:4160: ba bsgrub pa'i phyir gnyis su med pa rol par
NK052(zi)001:4161: bskul ba dang thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don
NK052(zi)001:4164: ba hu bi bi ta rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK052(zi)001:4165: las rnam pa bzhi sprul pa spro bas sems can
NK052(zi)001:4166: rnams gdul bar bskul ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4167: de lta bu'i dngos grub sgrub pa po la gsol cig par bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:4168: ba hu bi bi ta r+aa ga san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:4169: she sha ni sha sa t+wa bi na ya sarba
NK052(zi)001:4171: dza le pra dza le kurba bi kurba sarba sham+ba re te na te te h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4172: ba hu bi bi ta ra ti san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:4173: she sha ni she sha sa t+wa bi na ya
NK052(zi)001:4175: dza le pra dza le kurba bi kurba sarba sham ba re h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4176: ba hu bi bi ta ro du tra san+ta ti
NK052(zi)001:4177: a she sha ni she sha sarba bi na sarba
NK052(zi)001:4179: dza le pra dza le kurba bi kurba sarba sham ba re ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4180: ba hu bi bi ta dz+ai bi san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:4181: she sha ni she sha sat+wa bi na ya sarba
NK052(zi)001:4183: dza le pra dza le kurba bi kurba sarba sham pa ri h+aum shi sh+ya bi sha h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4185: glu dag dag re'i sgo nas kyang /
NK052(zi)001:4186: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang spyan drangs pa dang mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4187: bsnyen pa bya ba dang bsgrub dang las la sbyar
NK052(zi)001:4188: ba thams cad du rung ba'i phyir las thams cad
NK052(zi)001:4189: pa'i glu'i phyag rgyar bshad pas na /
NK052(zi)001:4190: de bas na skabs 'dir dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:4191: ba hu bi bi ta ro'u dra san+ta ti /
NK052(zi)001:4192: zhes bya ba gsum pa 'di nyid kyis bya ba thams cad la sbyar ba yin pas na /
NK052(zi)001:4193: rgya chen po mi nus pa'i gang zag rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:4194: 'di tsam gyi bya ba thams cad bsgrub pa yin
NK052(zi)001:4195: no // de nas yang mchod pa kun nas bsdus
NK052(zi)001:4196: pas gtso bo mnyes pas bya zhing mchod pa' phyir
NK052(zi)001:4197: no // / me tog dang bdug pa dang mar
NK052(zi)001:4198: me dang dri dang ldan pa'i bud med bzhis gar
NK052(zi)001:4200: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4201: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam par mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:4203: dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzad gsol /
NK052(zi)001:4204: mchod pa chen po thams cad dag par mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:4206: mchod pa chen po thams cad grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4207: de nas de dag gis bar rig nas /
NK052(zi)001:4208: bdag gi mig gnyis yi ge ma dang ta las
NK052(zi)001:4209: nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pas
NK052(zi)001:4210: nam mkha'i ngos la bltas pas bde bar gshegs pa
NK052(zi)001:4211: rnams kyis nam mkha'i khams til gyi gong bu bzhin
NK052(zi)001:4213: rdo rje lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcings nas /
NK052(zi)001:4214: ba hu bi bi ta ro'u dra san+ta t+ai /
NK052(zi)001:4215: a she sha ni she sha sa t+wa bi na ya sarba ta th+aa ga ta /
NK052(zi)001:4216: dza le pra dza le kurba bi kurba sarba sham+ba re ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4217: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes brjod cing rang gi lha la
NK052(zi)001:4218: mchod pa'i phyir de nas rang gi snying khar zhugs
NK052(zi)001:4219: pa'o // 'khor gyi lha mo'i tshogs rnams ni lha mo la zhugs par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4220: de nas mchod pa brtsam pa'i phyir thabs dang shes
NK052(zi)001:4221: rab kyi rang bzhin rdo rje dang pad+ma byin gyis
NK052(zi)001:4222: brlab pa la sogs pa byas te /
NK052(zi)001:4223: gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya bzhi dang sbyar zhing mchod pa brtsam par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4224: byang chub kyi sems bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga dang
NK052(zi)001:4225: sbyar te pad+ma b+han+d+ha'i nang du tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:4227: dngos grub kyi rdzas dang gsang ba'i dbang gi rdzas su bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4228: de ltar sbyor ba bzhi dang ldan pa'i ting nge
NK052(zi)001:4229: 'dzin gyis bsgrub pa'i tshe'ang rgyud 'dir sna tshogs thams
NK052(zi)001:4230: cad kyi phyag rgya'i mchod pa'i sgo nas bsgrub par
NK052(zi)001:4231: gsungs pa yin pas de la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4232: de la sna tshogs thams cad kyi phyag rgya'i mchod pa rnams dbul ba'i go rim ni /
NK052(zi)001:4233: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i zhal snga nas /
NK052(zi)001:4234: gsang ba'i mchod pa dang po byas la /
NK052(zi)001:4235: de nas glu dang gar dang ldan pas rol mo'i
NK052(zi)001:4236: phyag rgya rnams dbul zhing lta bas dang 'dzum pa
NK052(zi)001:4237: dang la sogs pa lus kyi 'gyur ba thams cad
NK052(zi)001:4238: kya sgo nas lha'i phyag rgyar ldan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4239: chos kyi phyag rgya la gnas pas bsgrub par gsungs pas de bzhin du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4241: mchod pa thams cad ni dbang po drug gi mchod pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:4242: dbang po drug yul la spyod pa ni 'jig rten
NK052(zi)001:4243: gyi chos lugs dang mthun par bstan bcos las kyang
NK052(zi)001:4244: grags la / de bzhin du gsang sngags kyi gzhung
NK052(zi)001:4245: du tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchod pa chen po byed
NK052(zi)001:4246: pa'i tshe'ang go rim de bzhin du dbul bar bya
NK052(zi)001:4247: grags la / ste / de bas na dang nyid
NK052(zi)001:4248: du mig gi yul gzugs kyi mchod pa dgram ste
NK052(zi)001:4249: grags la / ste / / sa gzhi la byi dor bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4250: bla re la sogs pa'i rgyan dgram pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4252: me tog la sogs pa nye ba'i mchod pa rnams dang /
NK052(zi)001:4253: gzhan yang phyi nang gi mchod par gyur pa thams
NK052(zi)001:4254: cad mig gi yul du snang bar bkod de dbul
NK052(zi)001:4255: lo // de nas rdo rje gar dang ldan pas
NK052(zi)001:4256: rdo rje glu dang rol mo sna tshogs kyi sgo
NK052(zi)001:4257: nas gzugs dang sgra ru ldan pa'i mchod pa dbul
NK052(zi)001:4258: lo // lo // de nas tshogs kyi zhal zas
NK052(zi)001:4259: sna tshogs kyi kha gong du bcad pa rnams phye
NK052(zi)001:4260: ste dri sna tshogs ldang bar byas la /
NK052(zi)001:4261: bdug pa las dri zhim po rnams kyi bdug pa sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4262: rnal 'byor ba rnams la kha spos rnams kyang phul te dri'i mchod pa rnams dbul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4263: de nas zhal zas sna tshogs la rol te ro'i mchod pa dbul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4264: de nas rjes chad pa dang lhag ma'i mchod sbyin bagyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4265: de ltar ro'i mchod pa zin nas sku khrus gsol
NK052(zi)001:4266: te byug spos phul la na bza' rnams dbul lo
NK052(zi)001:4267: // de nas rab tu reg pa'i mchod pa dbul te /
NK052(zi)001:4268: lha mo rnams kyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:4269: phyag rgya bzhi'i tshul gyis gzung ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4273: mthar sbyar ba la sogs pa'i sgo nas reg pa'i
NK052(zi)001:4274: bde ba nyams su myong ba'i tshul gyis rab tu
NK052(zi)001:4275: reg pa'i mchod pa dbul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4276: de nas chos kyi mchod pa dbul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4277: byang chub kyi sems skye ba nas sprul pa mang po sprul zhing las rnam pa bzhi brtsam /
NK052(zi)001:4278: bde ba nyams su myong ba'i dus na ma skyes
NK052(zi)001:4279: pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom zhing byang chub kyi sems
NK052(zi)001:4280: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang la lhun gyis gnas
NK052(zi)001:4281: par bsgom mo // de ltar mchod pa zin nas
NK052(zi)001:4282: dkyil 'khor bsdus te lus bsrungs nas spyod lam ci
NK052(zi)001:4283: par bsgom mo // rigs su bya'o // de ltar sgrub pa'i rigs pa gang yang rung mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:4284: re zhig 'dir man ngag gi tshul gong gi dkyil
NK052(zi)001:4285: 'khor rnams dang mthun par cung zad dgod par bya
NK052(zi)001:4286: ste / bud med bzhi'am brgyad kyis me tog la
NK052(zi)001:4287: sogs pa'i mchod pa dang glu dang gar dang rol
NK052(zi)001:4288: mo'i phyag rgya rnams dbul te /
NK052(zi)001:4289: de yang dang por phyag rgya dang gar gyis drangs la glu dang rol mo dang sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:4290: rdo rje gar bsgyur zhing rdo rje'i tshig gis bskur te phyag rgya'i mchod pa thams cad dbul lo //
NK052(zi)001:4291: de la phyag gi phyag rgya ni 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:4292: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:4293: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:4294: dpal ldan g.yon pa 'gying ba'i thabs //
NK052(zi)001:4295: g.yas pa ba dan gsum par bya //
NK052(zi)001:4296: smin la g.yon pa 'degs tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:4297: ru lu ru lur bcas brgad na //
NK052(zi)001:4298: tshangs pa nye dbang drag por bcas //
NK052(zi)001:4299: khams gsum pa rnams phyag byed 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4300: dpal he ru ka'i phyag btsal ba'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4301: mchod pa dbul ba'i gar gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4302: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:4303: mdzub mo mthe chung mdzes bsgyur te //
NK052(zi)001:4304: rdo rje thal mo gyen du dgrol //
NK052(zi)001:4305: mchod pa'i gtor ma kun gyi tshul //
NK052(zi)001:4306: dur khrod cha lugs gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:4307: phyag rgya 'di yis gar byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:4308: bskal bzang rdo rje drag po dgod //
NK052(zi)001:4309: mchod pa thams cad dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4310: dpal he ru ka'i thod pa'i thal mo ste //
NK052(zi)001:4311: mchod pa gtor ma thams cad kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4312: 'di dang ldan pas 'bar ba'i gar dgu bsgyur zhing /
NK052(zi)001:4313: ha ha ru lu ru lu zhes stab bo //
NK052(zi)001:4315: skor zhing de bzhin nyug pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:4316: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:4317: dri yi mchod pa dbyung bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4318: gang ngam 'on te stong yang rung //
NK052(zi)001:4319: yang na ci 'byor pa yis kyang //
NK052(zi)001:4320: dam tshig mnyam par bsgrub pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:4321: mchod pa thams cad grub par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4322: de ltar phyag dang gar du ldan pas dpal he
NK052(zi)001:4323: ru ka'i phyag rgya dang ldan pa'i sil snyan la
NK052(zi)001:4324: sogs pas mchod pa dbul te /
NK052(zi)001:4325: de la glu'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4326: rdo rje drag po gad mo che //
NK052(zi)001:4327: mkhur ba'i dbugs kyi rlung 'byin zhing //
NK052(zi)001:4328: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yin //
NK052(zi)001:4329: ru lu ru lu'i sgra phyung ni //
NK052(zi)001:4331: khams gsum dag kyang rgyas 'debs shing //
NK052(zi)001:4332: thar par byed cing gsod par byed //
NK052(zi)001:4333: shi ba'am mod la 'tsho bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:4334: sil snyan gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4335: gling bu dang ni rgyud gcig dang //
NK052(zi)001:4336: de bzhin rgyud mngas rgyud stug dang //
NK052(zi)001:4337: sil snyan phyag rgyar bshad pa rnams //
NK052(zi)001:4338: las rnams thams cad rab bsgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:4339: cha lugs ji bzhin gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:4340: ma brdungs par yang rang bzhin 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:4341: las rnams kun la mchog tu ni //
NK052(zi)001:4343: dzahh+aum bam hoh ru ta pa /
NK052(zi)001:4344: ta sma ra ra hu lu hu lu pra sid+h+ya /
NK052(zi)001:4345: t+aak+ki h+aum dzah ka ni du ni h+aum /
NK052(zi)001:4346: ga ru t+aak+ki h+aum dza hu lu hu lu a
NK052(zi)001:4347: la la la hoh shud+d+h+ya sid+d+h+ya da ri ya sar+b+aa
NK052(zi)001:4353: t+aak+ki h+aum dzahg+hena te g+hen to //
NK052(zi)001:4355: ga ru a la la la hoh ru d+ya ma ti /
NK052(zi)001:4356: thal mo brdabs pa rtags pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4357: d+he ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u /
NK052(zi)001:4359: d+heng ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u /
NK052(zi)001:4360: d+he h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK052(zi)001:4361: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo /
NK052(zi)001:4363: d+heng ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u ko'u /
NK052(zi)001:4364: dpal he ru ka'i rnga'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4365: de ltar rol mo dang gar dang ldan pas glu'i mchod pa dbul /
NK052(zi)001:4366: gzigs pa rnam pa sna tshogs 'gyur ba'i rgyas thob la //
NK052(zi)001:4367: rnam pa sna tshogs 'o byed mkhyud par rmongs mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4368: rnam pa sna tshogs bde ba'i mchod ston kun gsol ba //
NK052(zi)001:4369: rnam pa sna tshogs bde mchog ngo mtshar bstan du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4370: rgyas btab rmongs byas mnabs su gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4371: bde mchog ngo mtshar bde la bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:4372: h+aum a la la la hoh snang bar mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:4373: rnal 'byor bde mchog sgyu ma'i sprul //
NK052(zi)001:4374: dam tshig dag la 'jug tu gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4375: nyon mongs kun las rgyas par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4376: ma lus pa mnabs su gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4377: nyon mongs thams cad bsal bar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4378: de nas gar gyi glus mchod de /
NK052(zi)001:4379: gar gyi phyag rgya thams cad bsgyur zhing /
NK052(zi)001:4380: la lar dri med zla ba'i dkyil 'khor stong pas mdzes pa'i gzugs su rnam par snang //
NK052(zi)001:4381: la lar rab tu 'jigs pa'i nyi ma bye ba phrag dgu'i 'od zer mchog pas 'jigs //
NK052(zi)001:4382: la lar mdangs bzang gzi chen bde dang zhi bar ldan pa rgyal ba'i gzugs su snang //
NK052(zi)001:4383: la lar 'gro ba thams cad mnyam par 'jogs pa'i gzugs ldan gsung mchog ldan par ston //
NK052(zi)001:4384: rdo rje sems dpa' 'grub phyir 'dul la mkhas pa ma lus bde ba'i mchog rnams la //
NK052(zi)001:4385: a ral thams cad mnyam sbyor grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4386: ru ta ma ta a la la la hoh rnam
NK052(zi)001:4387: pa mang pos 'dul ba mdzad pa'i tshul la mkhan
NK052(zi)001:4389: dam tshig gar gyi dbang phyug sangs rgyas gar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4390: a la la la hoh rnam mang bde mchog rab
NK052(zi)001:4391: tu gar mdzad pa'i thar pa'i bde ba thob par
NK052(zi)001:4392: mdzod // 'di yis ba dan gsum dang ldan pas gar du bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4393: rab tu dga' dang rjes su chags par dga' ba'i mda' gzhu rab tu phra ba'i rgyas btab pas //
NK052(zi)001:4394: rab tu dga' bar sbyor ba'i bde bas myos pa bde ba thams cad bdag la grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4395: rab tu bde mchog rnam pa sna tshogs rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba'i longs spyod dang //
NK052(zi)001:4396: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug che mchog grub pa
NK052(zi)001:4397: de bzhin gshegs pa ho rta mchog hoh rab tu
NK052(zi)001:4398: sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog la rol cig hoh bde
NK052(zi)001:4399: bas slong ba rnam par rol /
NK052(zi)001:4401: a la la la hoh de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi mkha' 'gro sgyu ma sna tshogs kyis /
NK052(zi)001:4402: slob ma thams cad bzung du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4403: kye bde ba'i mchog grub par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4404: e ma'o bde ba bde ba gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4405: dam pa rab tu bzhugs par mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4406: bdag la rab tu bde bar 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4407: a la la la hoh e ma'o shi shi zhugs shig zhugs shig /
NK052(zi)001:4411: rdo rje sems dpa' sdud pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:4412: rdo rje rin chen bla med pa //
NK052(zi)001:4413: rdo rje chos ni gsung ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:4414: rdo rje las ni byed par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4416: rdo rje las kyi mda' gzhu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4417: dpal rdo rje chags pa'i dam tshig la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4418: rdo rje kha t+w+aam ga rab tu 'jigs pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4419: rdo rje dril bu dkrol ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4420: la la rab tu drag cing skye bo drag pa'i bud med sku ltar rab tu snang /
NK052(zi)001:4421: 'gro ba thams cad 'dul phyir la lar rab tu rno ba'i 'khor lo phyag na bsnams pa'i sku /
NK052(zi)001:4422: la lar rab tu des shing zhi ba mi 'gyur sbyin pa tshangs pa'i sku yang ston par mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:4423: la lar rab tu 'bar ba'i chags pa pad+ma'i rgyal po'i dam tshig bdag la grub par mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:4424: thams cad dbang bskur dbang phyug pa mi zad gter mchog bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:4425: kun mchog rgyal mtshan rnam rgyal bsgreng ba rdo rje rin chen shin tu che ba bdag la mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:4426: la lar mkhas pa'i gzugs kyang 'dzin //
NK052(zi)001:4427: la lar dus mtha'i dus ltar drag /
NK052(zi)001:4428: la lar rgyal ba'i dbang po bzhin du zhi //
NK052(zi)001:4429: la lar rta mchog 'dod sbyor 'dod pa sgrub //
NK052(zi)001:4430: de nas gar dang ldan pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:4431: dbyangs 'di rnams kyi glu blangs shing //
NK052(zi)001:4432: dpal ldan g.yon du 'dud pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:4433: g.yas kyi ba dan gsum du bya //
NK052(zi)001:4434: g.yas dang g.yon gyi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:4435: bde ba dbab ba'i gar byed pas //
NK052(zi)001:4436: skyil mo krung ni phyed bcas la //
NK052(zi)001:4437: rkang pa rang gi sarba mnan nas //
NK052(zi)001:4438: de nyid kyi ni sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:4439: de nas bde bar blangs bsdams nas //
NK052(zi)001:4440: legs par bsdams te phyir btags nas //
NK052(zi)001:4441: rab tu bkram ste btung bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4442: bde ba reg par mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:4443: mchod pa rnams ni yang dag dbul //
NK052(zi)001:4444: de nas 'di yis mchod bya ba //
NK052(zi)001:4445: g.yas dang g.yon gyi lag pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:4446: 'gying ba mchog gi gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:4447: steng du dor dang 'og tu dor //
NK052(zi)001:4448: bskor dang de bzhin byug byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:4449: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:4450: dri yi mchod pa dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4451: lhag ma gar gyi tshul gyis su //
NK052(zi)001:4452: gling bu pi wang rdza rnga mchog /
NK052(zi)001:4453: de bzhin cang te'u rnam dag kyang //
NK052(zi)001:4454: g.yon gyi khu tshur rab bsdams te //
NK052(zi)001:4455: lag pa g.yas pas brdung bya zhing //
NK052(zi)001:4456: rang gi ming gis bskul byas pas //
NK052(zi)001:4457: sngags pas mchod pa dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4458: zhi ba'i thal mo dgyes pa bskyed //
NK052(zi)001:4459: smin mtshams khro gnyer 'gyur ba bcas //
NK052(zi)001:4461: lta ba'i phyag rgya mchog 'di ni //
NK052(zi)001:4462: khams gsum dag kyang 'bar bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:4463: sha chen gyis ni ro myong zhing //
NK052(zi)001:4464: ma mchu so yis mnan pa yi //
