NK052(zi)001:4466: khams gsum dag kyang za bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:4467: stegs la sogs pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK052(zi)001:4468: mdzes pa'i bzhin ni rnam bsgyur zhing //
NK052(zi)001:4469: rim gror bcas shing stegs pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:4470: stegs pa'i lta ba'i gar byed cing //
NK052(zi)001:4471: mdzes pa'i tshul dang gar thabs kyis //
NK052(zi)001:4472: bzhin gyi phyag rgya ldan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:4473: smin ma mig dang so dang chu //
NK052(zi)001:4474: kha dang lus dang rkang lag gis //
NK052(zi)001:4475: cha lugs bzhin du gar byas te //
NK052(zi)001:4476: phyag rgya kun gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK052(zi)001:4477: su b+ha ga s+t+wam ma h+aa de bi hi ri mi dir ni sh+r+ai ye /
NK052(zi)001:4478: chos kyi phyag rgya dam pa 'di //
NK052(zi)001:4479: 'dod pa'i bde ba kun sbyin pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4480: he ru ka badz+ra sa ma hi /
NK052(zi)001:4481: sarba dush+ta sa ma ya mu dra pra b+ham dza ka h+aum phata /
NK052(zi)001:4482: 'di yang dpal he ru ka'i gsung gi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4483: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo zhes bya ba'i yi ge
NK052(zi)001:4484: gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs pa 'di yang dpal he
NK052(zi)001:4485: ru ka'i gsung gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4486: las dang dngos grub sna tshogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4487: ba hu bi bi ta ro'u dra san+ta ti a
NK052(zi)001:4488: she sha ni she sha sat+wa bin ya sarba ta
NK052(zi)001:4489: th+aa ga ta / dza le pra dza le kurba
NK052(zi)001:4490: bi kurba sarba sham+ba re ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK052(zi)001:4491: th+aa ga ta / b+h+yo h+aum / 'di yang dpal he ru ka'i gsung gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4492: las dang dngos grub sna tshogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4493: de nas bzlas pa dang bsgom pa ci nus pa byas te dkyil 'khor bsdu bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4494: de nas dpal he ru ka'i phyag rgyas bsrung ba byas te /
NK052(zi)001:4495: ci dga' bar gnas par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4496: de la bsrung ba'i phyag rgya ni 'di yin te /
NK052(zi)001:4497: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:4498: he ru dpal gyi rnam 'phrul bas //
NK052(zi)001:4499: ji lta'i tshul bzhin byed pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:4500: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings nas //
NK052(zi)001:4501: go cha bgo ba'i thabs su bya //
NK052(zi)001:4502: spyi bo dang ni dpral ba gnyis //
NK052(zi)001:4503: glo ru gnyis dang rgyab tu gnyis //
NK052(zi)001:4504: rdo rje phreng bas bcings pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:4505: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu dag /
NK052(zi)001:4506: dar bcings thabs su bcings nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:4507: 'gying dang bcas pa'i mtha' nas dgrol //
NK052(zi)001:4508: dar dpyangs pa yi thabs byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:4509: thal mo brdab pas brtan par bya //
NK052(zi)001:4510: 'di yis bsrung ba byas na ni //
NK052(zi)001:4511: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal dang 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:4512: mi chod pa dang mi phyed pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:4513: rdo rje sku ni rab tu 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:4514: rims dang dug dang dbyig dug nad //
NK052(zi)001:4515: mkha' 'gros gtsos dang gdon rnams dang //
NK052(zi)001:4516: yan lag ma rung byed pa kun //
NK052(zi)001:4517: 'di yis bsrung na yong mi tshug /
NK052(zi)001:4518: dpal rdo rje go cha zhes bya ba'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4519: de la dpal he ru ka'i dngos grub thams cad kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4520: g.yon pa dril bu sgra sgrogs shing //
NK052(zi)001:4521: g.yas pa yi ni lag pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:4522: rdo rje gyen du gsor zhing bskor //
NK052(zi)001:4523: sgyu ma thams cad 'byung bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:4524: zhes pa 'di dngos grub la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4525: de la dpal rdo rje he ru ka'i las thams cad pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4526: rdo rje khu tshur bcings pa las //
NK052(zi)001:4527: mathe'u gnyis ni rab brkyang na //
NK052(zi)001:4528: mkha' 'gro las rnams thams cad ni //
NK052(zi)001:4529: ma lus lus pa med pa 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:4530: ces bya'i dpal rdo rje he ru ka'i khu tshur
NK052(zi)001:4531: gyi phyag rgya 'dis he ru ka'i las thams cad
NK052(zi)001:4532: la sbyar ro // gal te slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhugs par 'dod na ni /
NK052(zi)001:4533: 'di nyid las gsungs pa bzhin dbang dang dam tshig sbyin par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4534: 'di ltar bu'i cho gas ji ltar dam bcas pa bzhin bsgrubs nas /
NK052(zi)001:4535: tha mar dngos grub len pa'i tshe gnyis su med
NK052(zi)001:4536: par rol pa las byang chub kyi sems blangs te
NK052(zi)001:4537: / sngar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bzhag
NK052(zi)001:4538: pa'i bdud rtsi dang sbyar ba'i dngos grub blang bar
NK052(zi)001:4539: / bya'o // 'di ni dpal he ru ka'i dkyil
NK052(zi)001:4540: 'khor chen po'i tshul gyis tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK052(zi)001:4541: bsgrub pa'i cho ga ste man ngag gi phyogs gcig
NK052(zi)001:4543: man ngag gi phyogs gnyis pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4545: mchod pa'i cho ga yan lag bcu dang bcas pas bsgrub par gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:4546: de yang tshul snga ma ni /
NK052(zi)001:4547: tshom bu mi'i dkyil 'khor du dngos grub chen bsgrub pa gtsor gsungs la /
NK052(zi)001:4549: gdug pa can gdul ba'i las grub pa gtsor gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:4551: dang por dpal he ru ka'i 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i rim gyis sam /
NK052(zi)001:4552: cig car ci dga' bar bskyed par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4553: de la rim gyis bskyed par 'dod na ni cho ga snga ma'i tshul tu 'dir yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:4554: cig car bskyed par 'dod na ni dang po rnam
NK052(zi)001:4555: par mi rtog pa las dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK052(zi)001:4558: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:4559: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:4560: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsungs rab la //
NK052(zi)001:4561: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK052(zi)001:4562: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK052(zi)001:4563: shin tu khro gtum gdug par gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4564: zhes brjod pas dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba de nyid kyis gdug pa can gdul ba'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:4565: sangs rgyas thams cad bka' glod par dgongs nas /
NK052(zi)001:4566: dpung pa g.yas g.yon rdo rje bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:4567: rdo rje se gol gyi sgras sangs rgyas thams cad
NK052(zi)001:4568: bsdu ba mdzad pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK052(zi)001:4569: til 'bru bzhin du rgyas par btags te /
NK052(zi)001:4570: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bka' glod pa //
NK052(zi)001:4571: shin tu gdug cing gtum po la //
NK052(zi)001:4572: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK052(zi)001:4573: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo yi //
NK052(zi)001:4574: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK052(zi)001:4575: ces glod de drag pos gdul bar dgongs nas /
NK052(zi)001:4577: b+h+r+au smug nag las 'od zer gyi 'phro 'dus sangs
NK052(zi)001:4578: rgyas kyi zhing thams cad dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal
NK052(zi)001:4579: yas khang du byin gyis brlab bo //
NK052(zi)001:4580: de nas 'bar ba'i sku bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:4581: de nas sna yi rtse mo la //
NK052(zi)001:4582: yid ni brtan pa yang dag gzung //
NK052(zi)001:4583: sna yi dbugs ring dro ba las //
NK052(zi)001:4584: rgyal bas phyag rgya'i sbyor ba phyung //
NK052(zi)001:4585: bcom ldan rnal 'byor de nyid ni //
NK052(zi)001:4586: rdo rje khro bor gyur nas byung //
NK052(zi)001:4587: thod phreng gi phyag rgya smin mtshams su bcas te /
NK052(zi)001:4588: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra sa ma ya hi sarba
NK052(zi)001:4589: dush+ta sa ma ya mu dra pra b+han+dza ka h+aum
NK052(zi)001:4591: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas dpal he ru ka byung bas /
NK052(zi)001:4592: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid he ru kar gyur par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4593: de nas byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho ga tshul snga ma ltar 'dir byas kyang rung /
NK052(zi)001:4594: phrin las gtsor gnyer bsam byas kyang rung ste /
NK052(zi)001:4595: de la mkha' 'gro ma'i dkyil 'khor gdon par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:4597: lha mo smra sha ni yum kroo d+h+ai sh+aa rir byin gyis brlabs te /
NK052(zi)001:4598: de dang rol pa las mkha' 'gro ma'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'am /
NK052(zi)001:4600: gtso bo nyid kyi sku'i 'od zer las so so'i snying po brjod pa tsam gyis bskyed par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4601: sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig ni /
NK052(zi)001:4602: snying po re re la yang lan bzhi bzhi brjod par gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:4605: rdzogs pa dang mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:4607: de ltar sku bskyed nas mchod pa'i cho ga yan lag bcu'i sgo nas gsungs pa yang /
NK052(zi)001:4608: slob dpon h+aum ka ra'i zhal snga nas dpal yang dag grub pa las /
NK052(zi)001:4610: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te //
NK052(zi)001:4611: gzhug dang brtan dang mi g.yo dang //
NK052(zi)001:4612: dam tshig zil gnon phyag byed dang //
NK052(zi)001:4613: mchod dang stob dang bza' ba dag /
NK052(zi)001:4614: tshul rigs goms pa'i blo dag gis //
NK052(zi)001:4615: ci rigs su ni las rnams bya //
NK052(zi)001:4617: de yang dang por snyan gsan dbab /
NK052(zi)001:4619: de nas dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gzhug cing bstim /
NK052(zi)001:4620: de nas bzhugs pa rnams brtan par bya /
NK052(zi)001:4621: de nas brtan pa rnams mi g.yo zhing dbang du bya /
NK052(zi)001:4623: de nas gdug pa zil gyis mnan /
NK052(zi)001:4628: de ltar yan lag de dag gis drag po'i phrin las sgrub bo //
NK052(zi)001:4629: de yang bsdu na rnam pa bzhi yin te /
NK052(zi)001:4634: de yang dang por snyan gsan phab /
NK052(zi)001:4635: de nas spyan drang ba ni lcags kyu'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:4636: gzhug pa ni zhags pa'i don /
NK052(zi)001:4637: brtan pa ni lcags sgrog gi don /
NK052(zi)001:4638: mi g.yo ba ni dril bu'i don /
NK052(zi)001:4639: de ltar phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa'i dam tshig bskul ba'i don /
NK052(zi)001:4640: zil gnon ni phrin las bskul ba'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:4641: de bas na thams cad spyan drang ba'i cho ga'i yan lag tsam mo //
NK052(zi)001:4644: bstab pa dang bza' ba ni gdug pa can 'dul ba'i las grub pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:4645: mdor bsdu na spyan drang ba dang phyag btsal ba yang mchod pa'i cho ga yin te /
NK052(zi)001:4646: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor mchod nas las bsgrub pa tsam du zad do //
NK052(zi)001:4647: de la snyan gsan gsol ba nas phyag bya ba
NK052(zi)001:4648: las thug gi bar ni mchod pa'i yi ge gzhan
NK052(zi)001:4649: nas gsal bar 'byung ba ltar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4651: man ngag gi tshul snga ma nas 'byung ba lta bur ci tsam 'byor bas bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4652: bstab pa dang bza' ba yang gzhan bzhin bya /
NK052(zi)001:4653: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba la sogs pa spyi'i yan lag rnams kyang spyi dang mthun par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4654: dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa'i cho ga rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:4655: da ni dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi
NK052(zi)001:4656: dkyil 'khor la sogs par bsgrub pa'i cho ga bshad
NK052(zi)001:4658: gzhan yang shin tu rnal 'byor pa /
NK052(zi)001:4659: ma lus pad mo rnam sbyang phyir //
NK052(zi)001:4660: skal bzang dam pa mi 'gyur ba //
NK052(zi)001:4661: pad mo sgyu ma dbang phyug gyur //
NK052(zi)001:4662: zhes bya ba la sogs pa rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:4663: de la dkyil 'khor 'di rnams kyi cho ga yang
NK052(zi)001:4664: gong du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK052(zi)001:4665: spyi'i cho ga rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4666: dpal rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK052(zi)001:4667: he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor du bye brag gi cho
NK052(zi)001:4668: ga bstan pas de bzhin du rigs gzhan la yang
NK052(zi)001:4669: rang rang gi rigs kyi phyag rgya rgyud las so
NK052(zi)001:4670: sor gsungs pa rnams de bzhin du sbyar te shes
NK052(zi)001:4671: par bya'o // de la rigs so so'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:4672: gang yin ngo mi shes pa rnams kyang 'og nas
NK052(zi)001:4673: phyag rgya so so'i skabs su bab pa'i dus su
NK052(zi)001:4674: par bya'o // / rigs gang gi phyag rgya yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4675: rang gi ngo bo gang yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4676: dgos pa gang du sbyar ba rnams kyis ston par 'gyur bas shes par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:4677: de bas na 'dir rgyud 'di nyid du gsal bar gsungs pa'i snying po gsang sngags lta bu dang /
NK052(zi)001:4678: phyag rgya'i tshul shes tsam brjod par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4679: de la dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK052(zi)001:4680: snying po pad ma'i dbyibs la phyi rol snga ma dang mthun par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4682: h+r+aihzhesa bya ba mdog dkar po zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa las bskyed de /
NK052(zi)001:4683: sku mdog shel sgong ltar dkar po 'od zer dmar
NK052(zi)001:4684: po la sogs pa 'bar ba sna tshogs kyi phreng
NK052(zi)001:4685: ba 'khrigs pas sangs rgyas tshe dpag med kyis dbu
NK052(zi)001:4686: brgyan pa / rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK052(zi)001:4687: phyag grangs nges pa med de ni /
NK052(zi)001:4688: rgyan la sogs pas gar thabs kyi tshul gyis sna
NK052(zi)001:4689: tshogs pad ma bsnams shing pad ma'i phyag rgya can
NK052(zi)001:4690: / sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4692: s+w+aa b+h+aa ba bi shud+d+ha pad+ma na rte shwa ra h+r+aih zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4695: shar phyogs su rnam par gzigs /
NK052(zi)001:4696: phyag g.yon pas pad+ma dmar po 'dzin /
NK052(zi)001:4697: g.yas mtheb mdzub sbyar te snying gar 'dren pa'i tshul gyis kha 'byed pa sa bon dzahls bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4699: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+mi dzah zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4700: lhor sgrol ma byang chub ma /
NK052(zi)001:4701: g.yon na pad ma ljang gu g.yas khu tshur snying gar bcings pa h+aum las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4704: nub phyogs su rgya can ma /
NK052(zi)001:4705: g.yas pad ma dkar po g.yas 'khor lo bsnams pa snying po bam las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4709: g.yon pad ma mthing g.yas gsal shing bsnams pa ho las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4713: shar phyogs su khro mo dbang phyug ma /
NK052(zi)001:4714: phyag mtshan rnams gzigs dang 'dra ba h+aum las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4715: h+aum pad+ma tsan+di shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK052(zi)001:4718: phyag mtshan sgrol ma byang chub ma dang mthun pa hi las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4719: he ma ma h+aa bi shwa pad+ma mu dre d+ye h+aum phata /
NK052(zi)001:4721: nub tu pad+ma dpal chen ma /
NK052(zi)001:4722: g.yas pad+ma ser po chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan bsnams pa sa bon a las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4726: g.yon pad+ma le brgan g.yas rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams pa hohls bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4727: ho pad+mi bi shwa kra ma h+aum h+aum dzah gsang sngags so //
NK052(zi)001:4728: mchod pa'i lha mo sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4729: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor las shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4730: dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la ni /
NK052(zi)001:4731: dkyil 'khor gyi snying po rin po che zur brgyad kyi dbyibs su bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4732: de la dpal rdo rje nyi ma sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi mdangs 'dra ba /
NK052(zi)001:4733: phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis kyi mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK052(zi)001:4734: 'og ma gnyis na ral gri dang me ltar 'bar ba'i rdo rje nyi ma bsnams te /
NK052(zi)001:4735: rdo rje skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa snying po tram las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4738: sid+d+h+aa sa ma ya sid+d+h+aa ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na b+aa ba ta ta tri /
NK052(zi)001:4741: shar phyogs su dbang bskur ldan /
NK052(zi)001:4742: dbang bskur ba'i bum pa bsnams pa dzahls bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4743: badz+ra sat+wa dzah gsang sngags so //
NK052(zi)001:4746: yang na gser gyi gzhong pa rin po che sna tshogs kyis bkang ba 'dzin pa h+aum las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4749: nub phyogs su rgyal mtshan mchog ldan ma /
NK052(zi)001:4750: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i rgyal mtshan bsnams pa bam las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4753: byang phyogs su mchod pa chen mo /
NK052(zi)001:4754: rin po che me tog gi gzhong pa bsnams pa hohls bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4755: badz+ra karma hoh gsang sngags so //
NK052(zi)001:4758: phyag na mda' gzhu 'gengs pa a las bskyed de /
NK052(zi)001:4761: lho phyogs su ral gri 'dzin ma /
NK052(zi)001:4762: ral gri bsnams pa h+r+aihls bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4763: pra ti h+r+aih gsang sngags so //
NK052(zi)001:4764: nub phyogs su rdo rje gzi brjid ma /
NK052(zi)001:4765: phyag na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK052(zi)001:4766: nyi ma'i snying po can bsnams pa ho las bskyed
NK052(zi)001:4769: byang phyogs su bsreg za ma /
NK052(zi)001:4770: phyag na me 'bar ba ba snams pa ha las bskyed /
NK052(zi)001:4773: gzhan yang snga ma bzhin du sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:4774: dpal rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK052(zi)001:4775: dkyil 'khor gyi dbyibs dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo la gcig tu chad pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:4776: gong gi dkyil 'khor gang yang rung bar sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:4778: zhal bzhi phyag bzhi zhabs bzhi'i rmig pa bzhi sku mdog dmar po /
NK052(zi)001:4779: zhal dbus dmar po chags pa'i zhal /
NK052(zi)001:4780: g.yas mthing ga khros pa'i zhal /
NK052(zi)001:4781: g.yon dkar po zhi ba'i zhal /
NK052(zi)001:4782: spyi bo rta mgo ljang gu drag shul gyi zhal lo //
NK052(zi)001:4784: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na rdo rje rgya gram dang sna tshogs pad ma bsnams pa /
NK052(zi)001:4785: g.yas 'og ma ba dan rtse gsum 'phyar /
NK052(zi)001:4786: g.yon 'og ma mtha' rnam pa gnyis su shi ba slong ba'i tshul du bzhugs /
NK052(zi)001:4787: zhabs bzhi rmig pa bzhi gyad kyi dor stabs kyis /
NK052(zi)001:4788: ma h+aa de ba dang gshin rje dang tshangs pa
NK052(zi)001:4789: khyab 'jug rnams bardzisa nas de'i chung ma rnams 'phrog
NK052(zi)001:4790: nas sbyar ro // snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:4796: bi shwa badz+ra sa t+wa ha /
NK052(zi)001:4797: zhes bya ba'i sngags kyi sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:4799: slob ma dbang bskur ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4803: chos legs par bstan pa rnams kyi cho ga rnams
NK052(zi)001:4804: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i skabs nas gsungs pa dang
NK052(zi)001:4805: / rigs so so'i phyag rgya so so las gsungs pa bzhin tshang bar bsgrub par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4806: dam tshig rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK052(zi)001:4807: de ltar rnam pa spyad na ni //
NK052(zi)001:4808: zhes bya ba la sogs pa man chad ni dkyil
NK052(zi)001:4809: 'khor so so'i yon tan gyi bye brag ston par
NK052(zi)001:4810: byed pa'o // le'u 'di ni sgrub thabs kyi cho
NK052(zi)001:4811: ga thams cad kyi dngos gzhir gyur pa mkha' 'gro
NK052(zi)001:4812: ma sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba
NK052(zi)001:4813: byin brlabs bsgrub pa rjes su mthun pa'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:4814: bstan pa yin pas mkha' 'gro ma'i phyag rgya'i rtog
NK052(zi)001:4815: pa zhes bya ba ste rtog pa drug pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4816: ci rigs rnam par 'phrul pa de dag ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga la /
NK052(zi)001:4817: thabs kyi dngos gzhir gyur pa mkha' 'gro ma'i sgyu ma rnam par 'phrul pa bshad nas /
NK052(zi)001:4818: da ni de'i yan lag dang grogs su gyur pa rnam par 'phrul pa bzhi ston pa la /
NK052(zi)001:4819: 'di ltar 'khor lo rnam par 'phrul ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4820: de bzhin du mchod pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:4822: phyag rgya kun nas bsdus pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4823: de las 'dir 'khor lo rnam par 'phrul pa zhes
NK052(zi)001:4824: bya ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi phyag rgya mtshan
NK052(zi)001:4825: ston pa ste / de yang 'khor lor 'jug pa'i
NK052(zi)001:4826: yan lag cho ga rnam pa lngas bsdus pa bstan
NK052(zi)001:4827: ston pa ste / pa'i phyir / de nas gzhan yang bshad bya ba //
NK052(zi)001:4828: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi lha'i //
NK052(zi)001:4829: rnam pa sna tshogs kun gyi mchog /
NK052(zi)001:4830: 'khor lo thams cad rnam sprul pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4831: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:4832: de la 'dir dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rgyu dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:4833: du 'jug pa'i yan lag cho ga lnga gsungs pa
NK052(zi)001:4834: ni / 'dir dgag pa'i sgo nas bshad pa /
NK052(zi)001:4835: dkyil 'khor kun tu ma zhugs shing //
NK052(zi)001:4836: dam tshig rnam pa spangs pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:4837: gsang ba yang dag mi shes pas //
NK052(zi)001:4838: sgrub pa ci yang mi 'grub bo //
NK052(zi)001:4840: de las bzlog nas bsgrub pa'i tshul nas bshad pa /
NK052(zi)001:4841: de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas //
NK052(zi)001:4842: de bzhin du ni yon phul te //
NK052(zi)001:4843: gsang ba'i cho ga nyid shes pas //
NK052(zi)001:4844: mi 'gyur ba'i cho ga kyang 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:4846: de la cho ga lnga ni /
NK052(zi)001:4847: dang po theg pa chen po'i dam tshig gi sdom
NK052(zi)001:4848: pa ma nor bar ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK052(zi)001:4850: des bstan pa'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs te dbang thob par bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4851: de nas kyang brtson pas bka' bzhin du sgrub pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:4852: de ltar lnga'i sgo nas dngos grub 'grub par bshad pa las /
NK052(zi)001:4853: dang po dkyil 'khor bri ba'i gnas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:4854: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes par ni //
NK052(zi)001:4855: thams cad bdag nyid rjes su bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:4857: 'di ni sngon du bstan pa bzhin du gnas kyi rang bzhin du gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:4858: rigs so so'i gnas pa la /
NK052(zi)001:4859: dben pa yi ni gnas dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:4860: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4861: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas so //
NK052(zi)001:4864: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4865: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4867: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4870: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4871: dpal pad ma gar dbang gi'o //
NK052(zi)001:4873: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4875: mkhar ni rnam pa sna tshogs /
NK052(zi)001:4876: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4877: dpal rta mchog gi gnas so //
NK052(zi)001:4878: cha lugs rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK052(zi)001:4879: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:4880: rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang sngags pa
NK052(zi)001:4881: dang mchod pa'i yo byad rnams kyi cha lugs sam
NK052(zi)001:4884: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:4885: gdul bya'i 'gro ba ji ltar 'du ba ci 'dra
NK052(zi)001:4886: bar de ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:4888: 'phrul pa de ci 'dra bar ba sgrub pa po
NK052(zi)001:4889: rnams kyis 'dris kyi dkyil 'khor bya bar bstan pa'o
NK052(zi)001:4890: // dpal rdo rje sems dpa' lha rnams kyi /
NK052(zi)001:4891: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:4892: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:4893: dkyil 'khor thig gdab shes rab can //
NK052(zi)001:4894: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4895: dkyil 'khor spyi'i thig gdab pa'i tshul bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:4896: dkyil 'khor yang dag ji ltar bar //
NK052(zi)001:4897: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:4898: dkyil 'khor bri ba' cho ga bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:4899: kun tu sna tshogs skal bzang po //
NK052(zi)001:4900: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:4901: rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbyibs bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:4902: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:4903: dkyil 'khor kun tu ma zhugs shing //
NK052(zi)001:4904: dam tshig rnam pa spang ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:4905: gsang ba yang dag mi shes pas //
NK052(zi)001:4906: bsgrub pa ci yang mi 'grub bo //
NK052(zi)001:4908: dngos grub mi thob pa'i rgyu bstan pa'i sgo nas
NK052(zi)001:4909: dngos grub kyi rgyu sngon du bya ba'i cho ga
NK052(zi)001:4910: yan lag lnga dang ldan pas bsgrub par gsungs te
NK052(zi)001:4911: / le'u 'di'i don yang tshig 'dis bsdus so //
NK052(zi)001:4912: de la dang por dam tshig bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:4913: srog chags bsad par mi bya zhing //
NK052(zi)001:4914: dkon mchog gsum ni yong mi spang //
NK052(zi)001:4915: byang chub sems kyang mi btang ste //
NK052(zi)001:4916: slob dpon skal bzang yong mi btang //
NK052(zi)001:4918: dam tshig gi sdom pa 'di bzhi ni gsang ba'i
NK052(zi)001:4919: theg pa spyi dang khyad par gyi rtsa ba'i sdom
NK052(zi)001:4921: de yang gsang ba'i theg pa la gnas pa rnams kyis /
NK052(zi)001:4922: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa dang byang chub sems
NK052(zi)001:4923: dpa'i sdom pa spyir byas nas rang gi sdom pa
NK052(zi)001:4924: khyad par du bsrung bar bya ba yin pa las
NK052(zi)001:4925: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa'i skabs rtsa ba'i ltung
NK052(zi)001:4926: ba pas pham pa bzhi yin pa las /
NK052(zi)001:4927: de las shin tu lci ba ni srog gcod pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:4928: de bas na 'di theg pa thun mong gi bslab
NK052(zi)001:4929: pa'i gzhi rnams kyi snying po yin pas de bstan
NK052(zi)001:4930: to // dkon mchog gsum mi spang ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:4931: byang chub kyi sems mi btang ba gnyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:4932: theg pa chen po thams cad kyi thun mong du
NK052(zi)001:4933: rtsa ba'i ltung bar gsungs pa thams cad kyi snying
NK052(zi)001:4934: po yin pas de bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:4935: slob dpon skal bzang mi btang ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:4936: gsang sngags kyi khyad par gyi dam tshig tu rtsa
NK052(zi)001:4937: ba'i ltung ba gsungs pa rnams kyi nang na'ang snying
NK052(zi)001:4938: po yin te / de bas na spyi dang khyad
NK052(zi)001:4939: par gyi dam tshig rnams kyi rtsa ba rnams kyi
NK052(zi)001:4941: kun tu sna tshogs skal bzang por //
NK052(zi)001:4942: zhes bya ba la sogs pas rigs so so'i skal pa bzang ngan bye brag bstan pa /
NK052(zi)001:4943: gsang sngags kyi mthu'i che ba ston pa 'di dag ni /
NK052(zi)001:4944: gsang ba yang dag mi shes pas mi 'grub cing de gsal bar shes pas bsgrub pa gsungs ste /
NK052(zi)001:4945: ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs kyi cho ga'i man ngag
NK052(zi)001:4946: shes pa zhes bya ba cho ga yan lag gcig
NK052(zi)001:4947: go // de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni /
NK052(zi)001:4948: byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid kyi chags pa mi gtong bas skal pa bzang po /
NK052(zi)001:4949: byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid spangs pas dam tshig la sdang ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:4950: de lta bu'i 'gro ba thams cad skal pa ngan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:4951: dpal rnam par snang mdzad ni /
NK052(zi)001:4952: 'gro ba thams cad bskyabs pa'i phyir srid pa'i myu gur mngon par bsgrub pas skal bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:4954: srid pa'i myu gu bkag pas skal pa ngan no //
NK052(zi)001:4956: thams cad la sbyor bas skal ba bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:4958: tshig gi don med par rtogs te yul thams cad stong pa nyid du mthong ste /
NK052(zi)001:4959: ngag shin du 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin tsam la gnas pas skal pa ngan no //
NK052(zi)001:4960: dpal pad ma gar dbang ni /
NK052(zi)001:4961: rnam par dag pa'i chos gzigs pas skal pa bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:4963: log par lta ba dang ldan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:4964: dag pa'i chos ma mthong bas skal pa ngan no //
NK052(zi)001:4965: dpal rdo rje nyi ma ni /
NK052(zi)001:4966: sangs rgyas kyi rgyal srid bsgrub ste sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su sbyong bas skal pa bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:4967: dka' thub spyod pa rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:4968: bdag gi bu yongs su bskyang ba'i snying rje'ang med
NK052(zi)001:4969: na gzhan lta ci smos te skal pa ngan no
NK052(zi)001:4971: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rgyal srid thams cad bsdus te /
NK052(zi)001:4972: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par byed pas skal pa bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:4973: thub pa drang srong rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:4974: 'dod pa'i longs spyod tha na rtsa bcud can yang 'dzin par mi byed de /
NK052(zi)001:4975: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i skal pa thams cad dman pas bskal pa ngan no //
NK052(zi)001:4976: de ltar rigs so so'i skal pa bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:4977: byang chub sems kyi sgo nas spyir gsungs pa /
NK052(zi)001:4978: bde ba thams cad bdag sgrub phyir //
NK052(zi)001:4979: kun gyi slob dpon skal ba bzang //
NK052(zi)001:4980: lta ngan dam tshig la sdang ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:4981: slob ma thams cad skal ba ngan //
NK052(zi)001:4982: zhes gsungs te de ltar skal ba bzang ngan gyi
NK052(zi)001:4983: bye brag gsang ba'i don 'di nyid shes na dngos
NK052(zi)001:4986: de bas na gang zhig dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i dus na yang /
NK052(zi)001:4991: bdag skal ba bzang po la dga' /
NK052(zi)001:4992: zhes gsol nas 'jug par gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:4993: de ltar gsang ba'i don 'di dag mi shes pa rnams ni /
NK052(zi)001:4994: g.yas pa yis ni gzhug par bya //
NK052(zi)001:4996: de la g.yas pa zhes bya ni /
NK052(zi)001:4997: dak+shi na zhes bya ba'i don rnam pa gsum la 'jug te /
NK052(zi)001:5000: pra dak+shi na zhes bya ste phyi rol nas bskor ba la 'jug go //
NK052(zi)001:5001: de lta bu'i sgra'i don dang sbyar nas sngon gyi
NK052(zi)001:5002: mkhan po rnams kyis bshad pa 'di ni phyogs kyi
NK052(zi)001:5003: don yin te / phyogs g.yas pa ni thabs kyi brdar brtags pas thabs kyis drang ba' don te /
NK052(zi)001:5004: theg pa chen po'i sdom pa dang dbang dag mi
NK052(zi)001:5005: sbyin par gzhug pa tsam 'ba' zhig bya ba'i don
NK052(zi)001:5006: du bshad do // kha cig gis /
NK052(zi)001:5007: yon dbul ba'i don du bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:5008: gdul bya skal ba dang ldan pa legs par bya ba rnams ni brdas bsre ba yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5009: ma byang ba rnams ni yon gyis bsre ba yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:5010: 'dir gsang ba'i brdar ma shes na yon gyis bsre ba yin no //
NK052(zi)001:5013: phyi rol nas bskor ba'i don bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:5014: skal ba bzang po la dga' ba ma shes na thog mar phyi'i sdom pa dang dbang bskur te /
NK052(zi)001:5015: de nas rim gyis sbyangs nas skal ba bzang po la sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5017: tshul rnam pa gsum po de dag kun kyang sgra
NK052(zi)001:5018: dang don gnyis kas zin par 'dra bas gzhung bzang
NK052(zi)001:5019: ngan gyi bye brag ni med do //
NK052(zi)001:5020: de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas //
NK052(zi)001:5021: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni gzhug pa bsdus pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5022: kun tu sna tshogs bla ma la //
NK052(zi)001:5023: yon mchog dag ni dbul bar nges //
NK052(zi)001:5024: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi yon dbul ba ba stan to //
NK052(zi)001:5025: khams kyi rang bzhin thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:5026: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni dbang bskur ba bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:5027: de yang rgyud 'di las dbang rnam pa bzhi gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5028: de la gsang ba'i dbang ni /
NK052(zi)001:5029: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5031: yig 'bru dgod pa'i phyag rgya las gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5033: dbang bskur ba'i phyag rgya las gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5034: 'dir ni dbu rgyan dbang gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5036: dbu rgyan byas te mgo'i gnas lngar bzhag go //
NK052(zi)001:5038: de yang rdo rje slob dpon du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5039: rdo rje slob mar dbang bskur ba gnyis te /
NK052(zi)001:5040: de la chos kyi rgyal po nyid du dbang bskur ba la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5041: rgyud 'di rnams las byas pa'i thod pa rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur 'am /
NK052(zi)001:5042: yang na de las byas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:5043: slob dpon chen po'i go 'phang bsgo ba yin pa rnams la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5044: rin chen las byas pa'i dbu rgyan cig gis dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:5045: rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa ni ji ltar smos pa bzhin du dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5046: da ni gong du smos pa'i dkyil 'khor du dgod pa'i mtshan ma'i phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5048: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:5049: rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang lha
NK052(zi)001:5050: mo rnams kyi phyag mtshan 'di rnams lha gang dang
NK052(zi)001:5051: gang gi yin pa so so ngo sprad pa ni
NK052(zi)001:5052: gong du tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du legs par gyis
NK052(zi)001:5053: bshad pa 'di ni phyogs kyi don yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5054: phyogs g.yas pa ni thabs kyi brdar btags pas thabs kyis drang ba'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5055: theg pa chen po'i sdom pa dang dbang dag mi
NK052(zi)001:5056: sbyin par gzhug pa tsam 'ba' zhig bya ba'i don
NK052(zi)001:5057: du bshad do // kha cig gis /
NK052(zi)001:5058: yon dbul ba'i don du bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:5059: gdul bya skal ba dang ldan pa legs par bya ba rnams ni brdas bsre ba yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5060: ma byang ba rnams ni yon gyis bsre ba yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:5061: 'dir gsang ba'i brdar ma shes na yon gyis bsre ba yin no //
NK052(zi)001:5064: phyi rol nas bskor ba'i don du bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:5065: skal pa bzang po la dga' ma shes na thog mar phyi'i sdom pa dang dbang bskur te /
NK052(zi)001:5066: de nas blo rim gyis sbyangs nas skal ba bzang po la sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5068: tshul rnam pa gsum po de dag kun kyang sgra
NK052(zi)001:5069: dang don gnyis kas zin par 'dra bas gzhung bzang
NK052(zi)001:5070: ngan gyi bye brag ni med do //
NK052(zi)001:5071: de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas //
NK052(zi)001:5072: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni gzhug pa'i bsdus pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5073: kun tu sna tshogs bla ma la //
NK052(zi)001:5074: yon mchog ni dbul bar nges //
NK052(zi)001:5075: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi yon dbul ba ba stan to //
NK052(zi)001:5076: khams kyi rang bzhin thams cad dang //
NK052(zi)001:5077: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni dbang bskur ba bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:5078: de yang rgyud 'di las dbang rnam pa bzhi gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5079: de la gsang ba'i dbang ni /
NK052(zi)001:5080: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5082: yig 'bru dgod pa'i phyag rgya las gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5084: dbang bskur ba'i phyag rgya las gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5085: 'dir ni dbu rgyan gyi dbang gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5087: dbu rgyan byas te mgo'i gnas lngar bzhag go //
NK052(zi)001:5089: de yang rdo rje slob dpon du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5090: rdo rje slob mar dbang bskur ba gnyis te /
NK052(zi)001:5091: de la chos kyi rgyal po nyid du dbang bskur ba la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5092: rgyud 'di rnams las byas pa'i thod pa rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur ba'am /
NK052(zi)001:5093: yang na de las byas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:5094: slob dpon chen po'i go 'phang bsgo ba ma yin pa rnams la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5095: rin po che las byas pa'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:5096: rnam par sna tshogs la sogs pa ni ji ltar smos pa bzhin du dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5097: da ni gong du smos pa'i dkyil 'khor du dgod pa'i mtshan ma'i phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5099: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:5100: rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang lha
NK052(zi)001:5101: mo rnams phyag mtshan 'di rnams lha gang dang gang
NK052(zi)001:5102: gi yin pa so so'i ngo sprad pa ni gong
NK052(zi)001:5103: du tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du legs par bstan pas
NK052(zi)001:5104: des go la / 'dir yang bstan na zlos bur
NK052(zi)001:5105: 'gyur zhing yi ge mang bas 'jigs pas ma bshad
NK052(zi)001:5106: des go la / do // cung zad mi gsal ba shas tsam bshad pa /
NK052(zi)001:5107: dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK052(zi)001:5108: rdo rje 'bar ba kha t+wam ga /
NK052(zi)001:5109: thod pa kham phor de bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:5110: dmar chen dang ni snying chen dang //
NK052(zi)001:5111: sha chen po'ang de bzhin te //
NK052(zi)001:5113: dpal he ru ka'i phyag rgya phyag bzhir bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5114: de la rdo rje 'bar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5115: rdo rje kha t+w+aam ga gnyis ni /
NK052(zi)001:5116: he ru ka'i phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis so //
NK052(zi)001:5117: thod pa dmar gyis bkang ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5118: kham phor snying chen dang sha chen bkang ba ni phyag 'og ma gnyis so //
NK052(zi)001:5119: yum kro d+h+ai sh+aa ri yang g.yon thod pa thogs /
NK052(zi)001:5120: kha t+w+aam ga la rgyab rten bcas te lag pa
NK052(zi)001:5121: g.yas ba dan gyi phyag rgya bcas te gtso bo
NK052(zi)001:5122: la mkhyud pa'o // lha mo sma sha ni yum
NK052(zi)001:5123: kro d+h+ai shwa rir bstan pa'ang der 'dus par bzhed
NK052(zi)001:5124: la mkhyud pa'o // do // lhag mo lha ma
NK052(zi)001:5125: bdun gyi phyag rgya las ma gsungs pa'ang dgongs pa
NK052(zi)001:5127: dpal pad ma gar dbang gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK052(zi)001:5128: khro mo dbang phyug ma dang pad ma mthu chen
NK052(zi)001:5129: ma'i phyag rgya ma smos pa gsang ba'i yum la
NK052(zi)001:5130: ltos so // yul gzhan gyi dpe las phyag rgya tshang bar smos pa dag kyang yod do //
NK052(zi)001:5131: rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la rigs kyi yum gyi phyag rgya ma smos pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5132: gtso bo' phyag rgya la ltos so //
NK052(zi)001:5134: 'bar ba dang me 'bar ba zhes phyogs gcig 'dra ba las 'dus par sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:5135: dpal rta mchog gi phyag rgya la /
NK052(zi)001:5136: mtshan ma'i phyag rgya grub pa gnyis //
NK052(zi)001:5138: gong du smos pa gnyis sam yang na ma smos pa'i slong ba dang ba dan gnyis so //
NK052(zi)001:5140: da ni mchod pa rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba /
NK052(zi)001:5141: phyag btsal ba dang gar gyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5142: de nas gzhan yang bshad pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5143: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi lha'i /
NK052(zi)001:5144: rnam pa kun tu sna tshogs mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5145: mchod pa thams cad rnam 'phrul pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5146: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5148: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:5149: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes par bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:5150: zhes bya ba la sogs pa phyag btsal ba'i phyag rgya gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5151: de la tshigs su bcad pa dang po 'di ni
NK052(zi)001:5152: rigs so so'i phyag thams cad la dang sbyar bar
NK052(zi)001:5153: bya ba ste / 'di ltar rdo rje khur tshur
NK052(zi)001:5154: g.yon gyi steng du g.yas bzhag ste dku g.yon du
NK052(zi)001:5155: bya ba ste / brten nas / de nas g.yas
NK052(zi)001:5156: kyi mdzub mo dang g.yon gyi mathe'u chung nas dkrol
NK052(zi)001:5157: nas rdo rje gar du bsgyur ba las /
NK052(zi)001:5158: g.yon phab ste dkur dril bu 'dzin pa ltar bya /
NK052(zi)001:5159: g.yas bteg ste mthe bo dang srin lag rtse sprad
NK052(zi)001:5160: nas ba dan gyi thabs su bsgreng ba spyir bya
NK052(zi)001:5161: nas / de nas rigs so so'i phyag rgya ji skad smos pa de las /
NK052(zi)001:5162: srid zhu bcas shing stegs pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5163: ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa' 'o //
NK052(zi)001:5164: rdo rje dpal gyi thal mo bsgyur //
NK052(zi)001:5165: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:5166: smin ma g.yon pa 'degs tshul gyis //
NK052(zi)001:5167: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal he ru ka'i 'o //
NK052(zi)001:5168: thal mo pad mo kha 'bus bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:5169: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi'o //
NK052(zi)001:5170: lus kyi yan lag thams cad ni /
NK052(zi)001:5171: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i 'o //
NK052(zi)001:5172: dpal ldan rdo rje'i 'gying ba'i thabs //
NK052(zi)001:5173: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal rta mchog gi'o //
NK052(zi)001:5174: phyag rgya de dag gang du sbyar bar bya zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:5175: ji skad du bstan pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams su mchod pa sna tshogs 'bul bar byed pa na /
NK052(zi)001:5176: dang por phyag 'tshal ba'i phyag rgya sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5177: de'i rjes su gar gyi phyag rgya sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5178: gar gyi rgyud rnams ji snyed dang //
NK052(zi)001:5179: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:5180: 'di dag kyang rang gi ngo bo gang zhig yin pa ming 'di nyid kyis shes so //
NK052(zi)001:5181: gang gi yin pa ni rigs rnam pa drug gi ste /
NK052(zi)001:5182: 'di ltar ji skad smos pa nyid nas //
NK052(zi)001:5183: skal bzang h+aum zhes bya ba'i glus //
NK052(zi)001:5184: mchod pa thams cad dbul bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:5185: zhes bya ba la thug gi bar du dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i 'o //
NK052(zi)001:5186: lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:5187: mdzub mo mathe'u chung mdzes bsgyur ba'i //
NK052(zi)001:5188: rdo rje thal mo sbyar nas su //
NK052(zi)001:5189: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:5192: he ru ka'i thod pa'i thal mo zhes pa'i bar du he ru ka'i 'o //
NK052(zi)001:5193: de bzhin du dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi thal mo dang /
NK052(zi)001:5194: dpal rdo rje rin chen gyi thal mo yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5195: dpal rta mchog gi gar ni gud du ma gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5198: zhes bya ba la sogs pa me tog la sogs
NK052(zi)001:5199: pa'i mchod pa dbul ba'i gar 'di dag kyang rigs
NK052(zi)001:5201: gar gyi phyag rgya 'di dag gang du sbyar bar bya zhes na /
NK052(zi)001:5202: ji skad du smos pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams su /
NK052(zi)001:5203: me tog la sogs pa'i mchod pa sna tshogs 'bul ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5204: dang por phyag btsal ba'i phyag rgyas sbyar nas /
NK052(zi)001:5205: de'i rjes su gar gyi phyag rgya dang ldan pas mchod pa dbul bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5206: de la 'di skad du le'u dgu pa las gsungs
NK052(zi)001:5207: pa'i sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK052(zi)001:5208: po thams cad kyang mchod pa'i yang yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5209: le'u brgyad pa 'dir gsungs pa'i phyag rgya dang gar gyi phyag rgya'ang phyag rgya yin na /
NK052(zi)001:5210: 'di dag tsam gang gi phyir mchod pa rnam par 'phrul bar bzhag ce na /
NK052(zi)001:5211: 'di star 'di gnyis ni mchod pa tsam du gsungs pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5212: phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5214: rnam pa gcig tu phyag nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni rgyud phyi ma'i tshul te /
NK052(zi)001:5215: phyag rgya rnam par spros pa'i tshul gyis rgyud snga ma'i kha skong yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5216: le'u bcu pa las gsungs pa'i phyag rgya dgrol ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5217: dpal rdo rje spyan gyi phyag rgya gnyis na rgyud
NK052(zi)001:5218: phyi ma'i yang phyi ma'i tshul gyis phyag rgya spros
NK052(zi)001:5219: pa de dag thams cad kyang bsdus par gsungs te
NK052(zi)001:5220: / de'i phyir ji skad du gsungs pa de dag kyang dgos pa 'dra ba yin no //
NK052(zi)001:5221: dpal skal pa bzang po dam tshig gi rtog pa
NK052(zi)001:5222: zhes bya ba ni 'dir dam tshig gi sgra ni
NK052(zi)001:5223: bsten pa'i don ste de bas na mchod pa nyid
NK052(zi)001:5224: dam tshig gi sgrar bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:5226: da ni phyag rgya rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba /
NK052(zi)001:5227: rnam par sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5228: de nas gzhan yang bshad pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5229: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi lha //
NK052(zi)001:5230: kun tu sna tshogs mchog rnams kyi //
NK052(zi)001:5231: phyag rgya thams cad rnam sprul pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5232: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5233: de la sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa
NK052(zi)001:5234: brgyad 'di dag ni thabs kyi dngos po yin te
NK052(zi)001:5235: / 'debs byed kyi phyag rgya yin pas de bas
NK052(zi)001:5236: sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya zhes ming lhag par gdags
NK052(zi)001:5238: de la phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK052(zi)001:5239: thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5240: dam tshig ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5241: sbyor ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5242: sbyor ba thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5243: zhal ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5244: 'dzum pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5245: lta ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5246: chos ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5247: glu ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5248: rol mo ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5249: glu'i mchod pa rgyan gyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5250: mchod pa thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5251: mchod pa'i gtor ma ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5252: phyag rgyas dbang bskur ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5253: rdo rje'i phyag rgya thams cad kyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5254: bstod pa bcas pa'i ming gi phyag rgya zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:5255: ba 'bru dgod pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang
NK052(zi)001:5256: / brda' ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5257: ngag brda ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5258: ye shes ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5259: rnam par shes pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5260: bsrung ba thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5261: gso ba thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5262: dgra cha ye shes phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5263: las thams cad kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5264: dpal rdo rje rnon po'i las kyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5265: dngos grub thams cad kyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:5266: de la grangs nyi shu rtsa brgyad du kha skong ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5267: rdo rje'i phyag rgya thams cad shes pa las mchog
NK052(zi)001:5268: dang bcas pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:5269: ba gud du byas nas nyi shu rtsa brgyad du
NK052(zi)001:5271: brda'i skabs su'ang khrag ni me tog yin par bshad /
NK052(zi)001:5272: ces bya ba la sogs pa sbas pa'i brda zhes gud du grags so //
NK052(zi)001:5274: rang gi ngo bo gang yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5275: bdag po lha dang gang yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5276: dgos pa gang la sbyar bar zhes bya ba yin
NK052(zi)001:5277: pa rnams ni rang rang gi skabs bstan par bya'o
NK052(zi)001:5278: // de la phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dang po /
NK052(zi)001:5279: thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:5280: phyag rgya thams cad kya gzhir gyur pas de skad ces bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5281: de yang rang gi ngo bo ni rigs so so'i sku'i don gyi tshul dang /
NK052(zi)001:5283: skyil mo krung gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK052(zi)001:5284: dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:5285: rigs so so'i glu rnams ston to //
NK052(zi)001:5286: phyag rgya 'di rnams gang gi yin pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5287: rigs kyi gtso bo drug lha mo so so dang bcas pa rnams kyi phyag rgya yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5288: de la lha mo rang rang gi phyag rgya'ang rang rang gi skabs su sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5289: dgos pa gang du sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5290: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du dngos grub sgrub par byed
NK052(zi)001:5291: pa'i tshe tshul 'di lta bur sgo gsum nas bsgyur
NK052(zi)001:5292: te phyag rgyas btab la bsgrub pa'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:5293: de la dang por dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil
NK052(zi)001:5294: 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi thams cad 'byung byed kyi
NK052(zi)001:5296: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK052(zi)001:5297: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5298: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:5299: thams cad bad ga nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:5300: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5301: de la 'di dag dang po nyid du yang smos
NK052(zi)001:5302: pa bzhin du 'dir yang smos pa'i dgos pa ni
NK052(zi)001:5303: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya ston pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK052(zi)001:5304: de nyid gang zhig ji ltar bzhugs par bstan pa dgos pa nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:5305: de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya zla
NK052(zi)001:5306: ba nya ltar dag cing brtsan dmar ba bzhugs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:5308: bde ba kun la zhen pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:5309: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5310: sku las 'od mdangs dmar ba las 'od zer gyi
NK052(zi)001:5311: d+r+wa ba kha dog sna tshogs pa 'phro ba'i don
NK052(zi)001:5312: no // 'dod chags kun la chags pa'i phyir //
NK052(zi)001:5313: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5314: dbu rgyan sangs rgyas rin po che byang chub sems
NK052(zi)001:5315: kyi chus dag pas rang bzhin gyis grub pa 'di
NK052(zi)001:5316: ltar thod phreng ba la sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan
NK052(zi)001:5317: gyis brgyan pa mnga' ba'i don bstan pa /
NK052(zi)001:5318: khams gsum dag ni rin chen gzhan //
NK052(zi)001:5320: skyil mo krung gi mtshan nyid bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5321: g.yas dang g.yon gyi sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:5323: 'khor gyi lha mo rnams phyag rgya ston pa la /
NK052(zi)001:5324: lha mo thams cad kyi phyag rgya spyir ston pa'ang yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5325: gtso bo lha mo bde mchog ma ste rgyas 'debs ma'i phyag rgyas ston pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5326: zla ba'i kha dog 'dzum pa'i zhal //
NK052(zi)001:5328: dpal rdo rje mda' bde ba'i mchog rol pa'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:5331: barla yi dbus ni dmar la dkar //
NK052(zi)001:5333: dkar zhing ser ba'i barla dang ldan //
NK052(zi)001:5334: zhes gsungs pa ni mdangs dang ldan pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5335: spyir sku mdog zla ba dang 'dra ba las /
NK052(zi)001:5336: dmar la dkar zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5337: na chung smug rtsis brgyan pa lta bu'o //
NK052(zi)001:5338: dkar zhes ser ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5340: phyag mchog lo ma sngon po 'dra //
NK052(zi)001:5342: a gra zhes bya ba'i sgra dam pa dang rtse mo la 'jug ste /
NK052(zi)001:5343: 'dir rtse mo'i don du sbyar te phyag gi rtse
NK052(zi)001:5344: mo dkar ba las kyang cung zad ser la de
NK052(zi)001:5345: las kyang cung zad ljang ba'i mdangs dang ldan te
NK052(zi)001:5346: / dper na 'bras kyi ljang ba la 'ja' tshon gyi mdangs 'phrog pa lta bu'o //
NK052(zi)001:5348: sku'i mtshan nyid thams cad mi smos par /
NK052(zi)001:5349: zhal dang barla dang phyag rtse tsam zhig smos pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK052(zi)001:5350: de ni 'di ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni chags pa chen por bstan pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5351: chags pa'i longs spyod kyi gzhi 'ang bud med kyi lus yin pas de ltar bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:5352: bud med lus yin lag las kyang bzhag rgyas shing mdzes pa mdzum pa'i mdangs dang ldan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5353: barla rgyas shing mdangs dang ldan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5354: phyag rgyas shing mdangs dang ldan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5355: 'di rnams la chags pa'i gzhir 'gyur ba de rnams bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:5357: barla zhes bya ba ni u ru zhes bya ba'i sgra'i mdo las bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5358: smad kyi cha thams cad u ru'i sgras khyab pas /
NK052(zi)001:5359: lte ba'i dkyil 'khor man chad nas pus mo yan
NK052(zi)001:5360: chad sha rgyas shing mdangs dang ldan pas shin tu
NK052(zi)001:5361: mdzes pas chags pa'i gzhir 'gyur te /
NK052(zi)001:5362: de bas na 'dir yang de nas bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:5364: gang du thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan yod pa gtsor smos dgos te /
NK052(zi)001:5365: de bas na ji skad du bstan pa de dag ni thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan nyid te /
NK052(zi)001:5366: mtshan de dag kyang chags pa chen po'i gnas su gyur pa'i phyir de dag bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:5368: lha rdzas sna tshogs 'khrigs pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5371: mi'i rdzas kyi kha dog las ni lha rdzas kyi
NK052(zi)001:5372: kha dog khyad par du 'phags pa de las kyang
NK052(zi)001:5373: lha'i lha sangs rgyas kyi 'od zer khyad par du
NK052(zi)001:5374: 'phags pas de lta bu'i 'od zer sna tshogs kyi
NK052(zi)001:5376: pad+ma sna tshogs la gnas pa //
NK052(zi)001:5377: thams cad dag pa rab tu gnas //
NK052(zi)001:5379: stan sna tshogs pad ma la bzhugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5380: sangs rgyas pad+mo la sogs mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5381: rin chen sna tshogs rgyan dang gos //
NK052(zi)001:5382: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:5383: mi mjed la sogs brgyan pa bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:5385: sku'i rgyan dpe dang bcas par bstan pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5387: sangs rgyas pad+mo zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5388: rgyan thams cad kyi mchog me tog gi rgyan yin
NK052(zi)001:5389: te thams cad kyi steng du 'byin pa'i phyir ro
NK052(zi)001:5390: // zhes 'jig rten gyi gtsug lag las grags pa bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:5391: 'dir pad ma dang ut+pala la sogs te me tog gi rgyan dang /
NK052(zi)001:5392: rdo rje rin po che dang /
NK052(zi)001:5393: gser dang dngul dang shel dang bee d+aur+ya la sogs pa rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i /
NK052(zi)001:5394: dbu rgyan dang snyan cha dang mgur chu dang do shal dang se mo do dang dpung dang /
NK052(zi)001:5395: phyag dang zhabs kyi sor mo'i gdu bu dang /
NK052(zi)001:5396: lha rdzas kyi gos rnams brgyan cing bzhag pa'ang lha dang mi'i rgyan ltar /
NK052(zi)001:5397: las las grub rgyan ma yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5398: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po nyid rgyan du
NK052(zi)001:5399: 'phrul par mdzad pas de bas na sangs rgyas kyis
NK052(zi)001:5402: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:5403: mi mjed la sogs brgyan pa bzhin //
NK052(zi)001:5405: dper na sangs rgyas kyi zhing mi mjed 'di /
NK052(zi)001:5406: bcom ldan 'das sh+aa kya thub pa byang chub sems
NK052(zi)001:5407: dpa' dang 'phags pa nyan thos kyi 'khor dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:5408: pas sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di brgyan cing mdzes te
NK052(zi)001:5410: dbang phyug thams cad zil gyis mnan te lhan ne lhang nger gsal ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5412: mngon par dga' ba dang bde ba can gyi zhing
NK052(zi)001:5413: khams dag nas sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa rnams
NK052(zi)001:5414: kyi sku'i bkod pas sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgyan pa
NK052(zi)001:5415: dang / 'dir lha mo rnams kyi sku'i rin che'i rgyan dang gos kyis brgyan pa ni 'dra'o //
NK052(zi)001:5417: mchog tu dga' ba la rab tu sbyor ba /
NK052(zi)001:5419: thabs dang shes rab kyi bde ba'i sgo nas mi gnyis pa'i ye shes sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5422: rgyud dang 'bras bu gnyis kar bde bas yon tan gyi gnas gong na smon du med pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5423: dpal rdo rje mda' bde ba'i mchog rol pa //
NK052(zi)001:5425: dpal rdo rje ni thams cad kyang dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya yin pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5428: lha mo rgyas 'debs ma ni chags pa bskul ba'i
NK052(zi)001:5429: bde ba'i yul te cha lugs snga ma lta bus
NK052(zi)001:5430: shar phyogs na bzhugs shing me tog gi mda' gzhu
NK052(zi)001:5431: bsnams te bskul bas rtsen par mdzad pas rol pa
NK052(zi)001:5432: zhes bya ste de'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5433: sngon gyi slob dpon kha cig ni /
NK052(zi)001:5434: bde ba bskul ba'i phyag rgya 'di ni gtso bo'i g.yas nas skul bar byed la /
NK052(zi)001:5435: rtag tu sbyor zhing byang chub sems 'bebs pa'i bde
NK052(zi)001:5436: ba dang mi 'bral ba ni mdun na pang nas
NK052(zi)001:5437: mkhyud nas bzhugs / zhes kyang 'dod na /
NK052(zi)001:5438: 'dir mda' sngon la smos pa ni chags pa bskul
NK052(zi)001:5439: ba las chags pa'i dam tshig 'byung ba'i phyir rim
NK052(zi)001:5442: de ni lha mo rmongs byed ma'i phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5443: rnam pa sna tshogs dam tshig chags //
NK052(zi)001:5445: dpal rdo rje dam tshig bde ba'i mchog rol pa /
NK052(zi)001:5446: zhes bya ba'i bar dag ste /
NK052(zi)001:5447: de ni lha mo 'di la chags pa'i dam tshig gtsor smos pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5448: 'di ltar lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:5449: sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal ba'i glu bstan pa'i skabs
NK052(zi)001:5450: nas / dpal rdo rje las kyi mda' gzhu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:5451: dpal rdo rje chags pa'i dam tshig la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:5452: dpal rdo rje kha t+w+aam ga rab tu 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:5453: dpal rdo rje dril bu rab tu 'khrol ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:5454: zhes gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK052(zi)001:5455: lha mo 'di ni gtsor chags pa'i dam tshig la gnas te /
NK052(zi)001:5456: dran pa gzhan nyams pas rmongs byed ma zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5457: dbus kyi lha mchog chen po'o //
NK052(zi)001:5459: bdag dbus kyi lha mchog chen po'i phyag rgyar gnas pa las mkhyud pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5462: lha mo'i dang phyag rgya dbus kyi gtso bo dang mthun pas tshig 'di smos so //
NK052(zi)001:5464: phyag rgya dbus kyi gtso bo dang mthun pas de la ltos pa ni bden mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:5465: tshig 'di dag ni 'og nas phyag rgya mi mthun pa'i lha mo la yang 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:5466: lha mo za byed ma'i phyag bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5467: se ral kha yi tshul dag tu //
NK052(zi)001:5469: rnal 'byor bde ba'i mchog rol pa //
NK052(zi)001:5470: zhes bya ba'i bar dag ste /
NK052(zi)001:5474: bde ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin brnyes pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5475: mtshan ma'i rnam rtog zad pa'i phyir za byed ma zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5477: dang por chags pa'i bde ba bskul ba las bde
NK052(zi)001:5478: ba babs pa'i bdag nyid la gnas pa 'byung ngo
NK052(zi)001:5479: // lus dang sems kyi bde ba rnyed pa de
NK052(zi)001:5480: las mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnal 'byor
NK052(zi)001:5482: de las 'bras bu'i chos kyi sku skye shi med pa thob pas /
NK052(zi)001:5483: 'og nas ston pa'i lha tshe 'phel ma'i don yin no //
NK052(zi)001:5484: de la lha mo za byed ma'i rdo rje kha
NK052(zi)001:5485: t+w+aam ga dang ba dan dang rdo rje rgya gram
NK052(zi)001:5486: gyis bkab pa bsnams pa ni mtshan ma 'joms pa'i
NK052(zi)001:5487: phyag rgya drag po'i tshul du bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5488: lha mo tshe 'phel ma'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:5489: rdzogs sangs rgyas pa'i khams phor grub //
NK052(zi)001:5491: tshe bde ba'i mchog ces pa'i bar dag ste /
NK052(zi)001:5492: phyag rgya ni pad+ma b+han+d+ha'i dang nas tshe dpag med kyi sku gzugs byung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5493: tshe bde ba zhes bya ba'i don gang du ni sbyar ba nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:5494: rtsa ba'i phyag rgya'i tshogs so //
NK052(zi)001:5496: snying po'i phyag rgya'o zhes bya ba'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:5497: 'di ltar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ni mi gnyis
NK052(zi)001:5498: pa'i ye shes chen po gdod ma nas dag pa'i
NK052(zi)001:5499: byang chub kyi sems yin pas bde ba chen po
NK052(zi)001:5500: zhes bya la / bde ba'i ye shes de ni cha rnam pa bzhi rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:5501: cha bzhi ni gsang ba'i lha mo bzhi'i bde ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5502: de bas na thams cad kyi snying po'i rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyag rgya'i tshogs zhes gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5503: da ni rigs kyi yum rnams kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:5504: de la sangs rgyas byang chub ma'i phyag rgya bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5505: gtsug lag ji lta'i rjes mthun par //
NK052(zi)001:5507: dpal rdo rje mda' zhes bya ba'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5509: 'di ni shar phyogs kyi re'u cha la bzhugs shing
NK052(zi)001:5510: tshangs pa'i zhal bzhi la mda' bzhis phug pa bsnams
NK052(zi)001:5512: mda' 'phang ba'i gtsug lag dang mda' bzhi 'phen pa ltar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5513: rkang pa bteg cing phab pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:5515: dpal mthu bo che'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:5517: chos kyi 'khor ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5518: 'di ni lho phyogs kyi re'u cha la bzhugs shing 'khor lo bsnabs /
NK052(zi)001:5520: rkang pa g.yas g.yon gyen du 'degs shing sa la rtob pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5521: gshibs nas kyang mchong zhing lag pas 'khor lo bstod nas 'dzin pa ltar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5522: bya ba dang ni zlog pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:5524: dpal rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug /
NK052(zi)001:5526: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5527: 'di ni nub phyogs kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te /
NK052(zi)001:5529: 'di'i gar ni mdun du gyur pa dang phyir 'gyed
NK052(zi)001:5530: pa la sogs pa'i stobs kyis g.yul 'gyed pa ltar
NK052(zi)001:5531: byed pa'o // lcug ma gang yang rung gzung nas //
NK052(zi)001:5533: dpal rdo rje 'dod pa'i lha mo //
NK052(zi)001:5535: 'dod pa'i dbang mo'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5536: 'di ni byang phyogs kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te /
NK052(zi)001:5537: dpag bsam shing gi lcug ma bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5539: bud med gang yang rung pa gzung nas mkhyud cing brtson par byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5540: da ni sgo bzhi'i phyag rgya 'chad de /
NK052(zi)001:5542: myang ba rngub pa ltar byas nas //
NK052(zi)001:5546: rta gdong gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5547: 'di ni shar phyogs kyi sgo na bzhugs shing g.yas na rdo rje lcags kyu thogs /
NK052(zi)001:5548: g.yon na pad+ma b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i nang nas rta
NK052(zi)001:5549: mgo ljang gu byung ba 'phangs bstod de rta skad
NK052(zi)001:5551: bdud rtsi'i zas la sogs pa la gdug pa can
NK052(zi)001:5552: gyi tshogs su brtags te ro bcud rngub pa ltar
NK052(zi)001:5553: byas pas gdug pa can rnams skems par byed pa'o
NK052(zi)001:5554: // sna yi myang zhing rngub pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:5558: phag gdong gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5559: 'di ni lho sgo na bzhugs te g.yas na zhags pa g.yon na phag gi mche ba bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5561: snga ma bzhin du dri rnams myang zhing rngub pa
NK052(zi)001:5562: ltar byas pa khams gsum dbang du sdud par byed
NK052(zi)001:5563: pa'o // mig tshugs zhen par blta ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:5565: dpal rdo rje can nyi zla ma /
NK052(zi)001:5567: nyi zla'i spyan gyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5569: phyag na lcags sgrog gi yang mig nyi zla 'od 'bar ba bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5571: mig g.yas g.yon nyi ma dang zla ba'i 'od 'bar
NK052(zi)001:5572: bas mig tshugs kyis gdug pa can la zhen par
NK052(zi)001:5573: blta bas sreg cing za bar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5574: thams cad bdag nyid myang ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:5578: ro langs ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5579: 'di ni byang phyogs kyi sgo na bzhugs pa phyag g.yas na dril bu /
NK052(zi)001:5580: g.yon na b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i kha t+w+aam rdo rje rgya gram gyis bkab ste /
NK052(zi)001:5581: de'i steng na sangs rgyas tshe dpag med kyi sku phyung ba bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5583: dbang po drug gi yul thams cad la ro myong
NK052(zi)001:5584: ba ltar byed pas thams cad thal bar brlag pa
NK052(zi)001:5585: ste / slar gsos nas byang chub sems dang ldan par byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5586: da ni dpal gling bu dbang byed la sogs pa mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi'i phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:5588: gling bu len pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK052(zi)001:5589: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5590: gling bu dbang byed ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5591: 'di ni shar lho mtshams kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te phyag na gling bu bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5592: rgyud gzhan las rdo rje sgeg mo zhes stan pa'i go yin par shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5594: gling bu len pa ltar byed cing bde ba dbab
NK052(zi)001:5595: pa'i gar byed pas 'gro ba dbang du byed pa'o
NK052(zi)001:5596: // pi wang len pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK052(zi)001:5597: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5598: pi wang rmongs byed ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5599: 'di ni lho nub mtshams kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te pi wang bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5600: gzhan las phreng ba ma zhes bya ba'i gor sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:5602: pi wang len pa ltar byed cing bde bas rmongs par byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5603: cang te'u tshul ston rnal 'byor pa //
NK052(zi)001:5604: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5605: cang te'u sdug bsngal sel ba'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5606: nub byang mtshams kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te cang te'u bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5607: rdo rje dbyangs ma zhes pa'i gor sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:5609: cang te'u 'khrol pa ltar byed pas sdug bsngal sel ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5610: rdza rnga'i tshul ston rnal 'byor pa //
NK052(zi)001:5611: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5612: rdza rnga myos byed ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5613: 'di ni byang shar mtshams kyi re'u cha la bzhugs te rdza rnga bsnams /
NK052(zi)001:5614: rdo rje gang zhes 'byung ba'i gor sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:5615: rdza rnga brdung ba ltar byed pas 'bebs shing myos pa ltar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5616: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:5617: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5619: skabs 'dir me tog la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi'i gar 'byung ba las /
NK052(zi)001:5620: 'dir ma smos pa'i dgongs pa ni 'di rnams gling
NK052(zi)001:5621: bu la sogs pa dag 'brel bar bstan pas ni
NK052(zi)001:5622: / gong du mtshan ma'i phyag rgya dgod pa'i skabs nas /
NK052(zi)001:5624: gling bu dang ni pi wang kun //
NK052(zi)001:5625: ku mu da dang many+dza ra //
NK052(zi)001:5626: me tog bdug pa mar me dang //
NK052(zi)001:5627: sna tshogs dri rnams de bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:5628: zhes bya ba la sogs pa lta bu gsal bar
NK052(zi)001:5629: gsungs pa 'di rnams kyi gar gyi phyag rgya spyi'i
NK052(zi)001:5630: gar gyi mchod pa'i skabs nas /
NK052(zi)001:5632: skor zhing de bzhin nyug pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:5633: me tog bdug pa mar me mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5635: zhes pa lta bu gong du gsal bar gsungs pas
NK052(zi)001:5636: de bas na de lta bu la dgongs par mngon
NK052(zi)001:5637: no // de ni gar gyi phyag rgya de'i glu ston te /
NK052(zi)001:5639: de nas phyag rgya ye shes 'di //
NK052(zi)001:5640: dpal ldan rdo rje mchog gi glu //
NK052(zi)001:5641: las rnams thams cad rab grub cing //
NK052(zi)001:5642: srid pa shin tu bsgrub pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:5643: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5644: de la ye shes nyid phyag rgyar byin gyis brlabs
NK052(zi)001:5645: pas phyag rgya ye shes te de yang rdo rje'i
NK052(zi)001:5646: glu nyid do // de las thams cad grub cing
NK052(zi)001:5647: rtag tu mya ngan las mi 'da' bar srid pa
NK052(zi)001:5648: ji srid pa de srid du srid pa'i myu gu'i
NK052(zi)001:5649: 'phrul pa ston cing don sgrub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5651: rdo rje sems dpa' bde chen skal bzang dpal khyod bdag lags bsgrub la rtogs par mdzad du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:5652: zhes pa la sogs pa'i glu 'di dag ni tshogs
NK052(zi)001:5653: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su mdun gyi nam mkha'
NK052(zi)001:5654: la ye shes kyi lha mo mngon du blta bar
NK052(zi)001:5655: bya ba'i phyir lha rnams bskur ba'i glu'o //
NK052(zi)001:5656: zhes gong du bstan pa ltar sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:5657: gar gyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya'ii skabs su ni /
NK052(zi)001:5658: lha mo 'di rnams kyis gar bsgyur ba'i rjes su glu 'di dag kyang blang bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5659: glu 'di'i don ni rnal 'byor pa dang rnal 'byor ma gang gis blangs kyang rung ste /
NK052(zi)001:5660: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la rang bzhin mi gnyis
NK052(zi)001:5661: pa'i sgo nas dngos grub gsol bar bskul zhing 'gro
NK052(zi)001:5662: ba'i don mdzad par bskul ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:5664: bde chen rdo rje sems dpa' ni /
NK052(zi)001:5665: gsang ba'i lha mo bzhi'i rang bzhin yin pas de'i sgo nas bskul te /
NK052(zi)001:5667: rdo rje sems dpa' bde chen skal bzang dpal khyod /
NK052(zi)001:5670: bdag lags zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5671: rang bzhin mi gnyis pas snod du rung bar bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5672: bsgrub la rtogs par mdzad du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:5674: de ltar lags kyang bdag cag gis ma rtogs shing
NK052(zi)001:5675: ma grub pas de rtogs shing grub par mdzad du
NK052(zi)001:5677: kye de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bde ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5680: 'gro ba'i rgyud rnams rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul ba mchog 'grub pa //
NK052(zi)001:5683: de bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:5687: dngos grub blangs pa'i dbyangs te /
NK052(zi)001:5689: e ma'o bde mchog ngo mtshar ni /
NK052(zi)001:5690: a la la la hoh zhes bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:5692: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyor ba rnam pa sna tshogs gar rnams bstan du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:5694: 'gro ba'i don mdzad par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5695: dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5696: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid gsang ba'i yum bzhi'i
NK052(zi)001:5697: rang bzhin pas de'i sgo nas dngos bskul ba ste
NK052(zi)001:5699: drangs te bcug nas bcings pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:5700: zhugs nas dbang du gyur pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:5705: rgyas 'debs ma'i sgo nas bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5706: bde bas gzung rnam par sprul //
NK052(zi)001:5709: h+aum snang ba mdzad du gsol /
NK052(zi)001:5715: tshe 'phel ma'i sgo nas bskul ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:5716: mdor na lha mo bzhi'i yon tan smos pa'i sgo
NK052(zi)001:5717: nas dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nyid la bskul ba'o
NK052(zi)001:5719: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:5720: da ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi thams cad
NK052(zi)001:5721: 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir
NK052(zi)001:5723: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5724: 'di yang gong du bstan pa bzhin du sku'i tshul gyi don dang /
NK052(zi)001:5726: skyil mo krung gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK052(zi)001:5727: 'khor rnams kyi lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgya'i gar dang /
NK052(zi)001:5728: rang gi rigs kyi glu rnams ston te /
NK052(zi)001:5729: dkyil 'khor gzhan la yang de bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5730: de la dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku gser btso ma'i kha dog 'dra ba'i don ni /
NK052(zi)001:5731: don dam pa rnam par dag pa mtshan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5732: 'od zer dkar zhing dmar mdangs can byung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:5733: shes rab dang thabs kyi sgo nas ma chags pa'i thugs rjes mnga' ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5734: dbu rgyan gyi don gsungs pa /
NK052(zi)001:5735: chos kyi rgyal srid rab bsgrub pa //
NK052(zi)001:5736: rin chen chos las lhag pa med //
NK052(zi)001:5737: de bas theg chen byang chub sems //
NK052(zi)001:5738: rgyal ba rin chen rdo rje can //
NK052(zi)001:5740: 'dir rgyal srid kyi mchog kyang chos kyi rgyal srid yin la /
NK052(zi)001:5741: rin po che 'i mchog kyang chos rin po che yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5742: de bas na theg pa chen po'i chos bla na
NK052(zi)001:5743: med pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyis brgyan pa la
NK052(zi)001:5744: mnga' brnyes pa'i phyir rin po che'i dbu rgyan rdo
NK052(zi)001:5745: rje phyed pas mtshan pas dbu rgyan to //
NK052(zi)001:5748: g.yas pas mthe bong gung mo gnyis //
NK052(zi)001:5749: zhes pa la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:5750: 'di ni chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5751: 'dis byang chub kyi sems bskyed par byed pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5752: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mtshan nyid
NK052(zi)001:5753: mtha' gnyis las mi gnas pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK052(zi)001:5754: bskor ba ste / de'i phyir rtsa ba'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:5755: 'dis btab pa'i yon tan smos pa rnams kyang de
NK052(zi)001:5757: g.yas kyi yan lag gnon pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:5758: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5759: skyil mo krung gi bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5760: da ni lha mo rnams kyi gar gyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:5761: de yang lha mo 'di brgyad kyi phyag rgya'i tshul ni /
NK052(zi)001:5762: sangs rgyas kun brjod ma la sogs pa gsang ba'i yum bzhi ni /
NK052(zi)001:5763: dbus kyi re'u cha la phyogs bzhi nas gtso la mkhyud pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs /
NK052(zi)001:5765: sangs rgyas kun brjod ma'i lce'o //
NK052(zi)001:5766: shin tu rgyal mo'am dpa' mo'i cha lang dang rnga'o //
NK052(zi)001:5767: kun tu bzang mo'i rdo rje'o //
NK052(zi)001:5768: mi bzad ma'i za ma tog gi rin po che'i snod do //
NK052(zi)001:5770: phyogs bzhi'i re re'u cha la bzhugs te /
NK052(zi)001:5772: sangs rgyas kun gyi yan lag dang ldan ma ni sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs so //
NK052(zi)001:5773: zhal bzang ma'i me long dang rlung g.yab bo //
NK052(zi)001:5774: sprin chen mo'i sprin rdo rje ser ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5775: nam mkha'i spyan gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5776: lha mo 'di rnams kyi gar ni /
NK052(zi)001:5777: lag pa g.yas pa rnams kyis ji skad du smos pa'i rang rang gi khu tshur rnams bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:5778: lag pa g.yon pa rnams kyi khu tshur rnams 'gebs par byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5779: de la khu tshur 'di rnams kyi ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5780: rigs so so'i khu tshur drug ni /
NK052(zi)001:5781: las thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya las 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:5783: tha ma dngos grub thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya las 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:5784: dpal 'grub spyan gyi khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5785: gnyis pa dam tshig ye shes kyi phyag rgya las 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:5786: de la rdo rje khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5787: khu tshur thams cad kyi gzhi yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5788: de bca' ba yang 'di skad du /
NK052(zi)001:5789: srin lag mathe'u chung yan lag dbus //
NK052(zi)001:5790: mthe bo legs par bzhag par bya //
NK052(zi)001:5791: de nas khu tshur bcas nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:5792: mdzub mo legs par dgug par bya //
NK052(zi)001:5793: rdo rje dpal rdo rje khu tshur gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:5795: srin lag dang mathe'u chung gi bar du mthe bo'i rtse mos sleb par bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:5796: khu tshur bcangs nas mdzub mo bkug ste cung zad bkyed nas bzhag pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5797: dpal he ru ka'i khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5798: rdo rje khu tshur bcangs pa las //
NK052(zi)001:5799: mathe'u chung gnyis ni rab brkyang nas //
NK052(zi)001:5801: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis las mathe'u chung brkyang ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5802: pad mo bud med khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5803: bteg pa'i khu tshur bcangs pa las /
NK052(zi)001:5804: mthe bong dag la gung mo bzhag /
NK052(zi)001:5805: pad mo khu tshur grub pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:5807: de la bteg pa'i khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5808: mdzub mo'i sen mo mthe bong gi tshigs kyis cung zad mnan pa grags so //
NK052(zi)001:5809: de la cung zad mthe bong sen mo'i steng du gung mo rtse mo btsugs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5811: rin chen 'dzin pa'i khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5812: khu tshur rdo rje rin chen mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5814: ji ltar bca' ba ma gsungs pas khu tshur gong
NK052(zi)001:5815: ma nyid las mthe bong dang gung mo rtse sprad
NK052(zi)001:5818: rdo rje khu tshur nyid las gnyis pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5819: zhes slob dpon dag gis bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:5822: rdo rje khu tshur legs bcangs la //
NK052(zi)001:5823: bdag gi mthe bong nang du gzhug /
NK052(zi)001:5824: de gzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi khu tshur ro //
NK052(zi)001:5826: rdo rje khu tshur nyid las mthe bo cung zad bsnur te /
NK052(zi)001:5827: rtse mo nang du chud pa tsam du byas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5830: khu tshur snying gar bcangs pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:5831: bud med phyag rgya de bshad de //
NK052(zi)001:5833: khu tshur 'di la mtheb mos mdzub mo'i tshigs dbu ma mnan no //
NK052(zi)001:5835: rta mchog dpal gyi khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5837: rdo rje khu tshur dpal bcangs la //
NK052(zi)001:5838: sor mo thams cad yongs su bzung //
NK052(zi)001:5839: brtul phod las rnams thams cad ni //
NK052(zi)001:5840: ma lus lus pa med pa 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:5842: 'di la mthe bos sor mo thams cad gzung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:5844: dpal 'grub spyan gyi khu tshur ni /
NK052(zi)001:5846: mdzub mos mthe bo mnan nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:5847: rang gi mthe bo mdzub mos mnan //
NK052(zi)001:5848: dpal 'grub spyan gyi phyag rgya de //
NK052(zi)001:5849: mdzub mo mig gi 'bras bur bya //
NK052(zi)001:5851: lag pa g.yas pa khu tshur bcas te mdzub mos
NK052(zi)001:5852: mthe bo mnan nas g.yas pa' mthe bong de nyid
NK052(zi)001:5853: kyis phyir mdzub mo'i rtsa ba mnan te /
NK052(zi)001:5854: mdzub mo'i rtse mo mig gi 'bras bu ltar byas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5855: de ltar lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgya'i gar bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:5856: da ni grub pa'i glu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5857: phyag rgya shes pa 'di dag gi //
NK052(zi)001:5858: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i glu mchog ni //
NK052(zi)001:5859: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5860: slong bar byed pa brtan grub pa //
NK052(zi)001:5862: brtan pa grub pa mya ngan las 'das pa rnams kyang slong bar byed pa //
NK052(zi)001:5863: zhes bya ba yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:5864: glu'i yan lag sha rdza ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:5866: de'u phra sbom gyi bye brag go //
NK052(zi)001:5867: 'jig rten khams mang rdul phran grangs med khyab par spros pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:5868: zhes pa la sogs pa'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:5869: rgyal ba rnams mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' las
NK052(zi)001:5870: bslangs nas sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa zhing gi rdul
NK052(zi)001:5871: rnyed 'phrul pas sems can gyi don mdzod cig /
NK052(zi)001:5873: de lta bu'i sbyor bas bdag la grub par mdzod cig /
NK052(zi)001:5875: nam mkha' thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5876: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5878: rigs so so'i khyad par gyi mtshan yin te /
NK052(zi)001:5880: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5881: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5883: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5884: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5885: nam mkha' thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5887: spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5888: de bzhin nyid rtogs pa phun sum tshogs pa gtsor bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5890: rdo rje thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5892: byang chub kyi sems thog ma dang tha mar 'gyur ba med pa'i gtsor bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5894: sna tshogs pad+mo mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5896: rnam par dag pa'i chos dang de khong du chud pa gtsor bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5897: rin po che'i rigs la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5898: rgyal srid thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:5900: yon tan rin po che la mnga' brnyes pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5901: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa sbyin pa gtsor bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5903: rta mchog mnyam sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5905: brtul phod kyi las gtso bo bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5907: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5909: bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi bde ba dang bde ba chen po la mnga' brnyes pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5910: de nas bud med gzhi rnams dang //
NK052(zi)001:5911: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5912: rang gi dkyil 'khor du de lta bu gar dang
NK052(zi)001:5913: glu dang ldan pas me tog la sogs pa'i mchod
NK052(zi)001:5916: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:5917: da ni dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:5919: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5921: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK052(zi)001:5922: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK052(zi)001:5923: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:5924: gzhan gyi ma yin mi 'phrog pa //
NK052(zi)001:5925: lha rdzas chu yis dag pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:5926: de bzhin rang bzhin nyid dag dang //
NK052(zi)001:5927: mthu dang ngo bo nyid kyis grub //
NK052(zi)001:5929: dbu rgyan gyi don gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:5930: de yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5931: sangs rgyas rin po che'i dbu rgyan gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5932: dpal rnam par snang mdzad la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5933: chos rin po che'i dbu rgyan gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:5934: dpal he ru ka la ni /
NK052(zi)001:5935: byang chub sems kyi dbu rgyan gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5936: de bas na tshig 'di dag kyang 'og nas ston
NK052(zi)001:5937: pa'i dbu rgyan don gyi byang chub sems kyi rang
NK052(zi)001:5938: bzhin bstan pa'o // gos chen po dang klubs pa che //
NK052(zi)001:5939: sha chen po dang sbrang rtsi che //
NK052(zi)001:5940: dur khrod kun gyi 'byung po yi //
NK052(zi)001:5941: phyag rgya dpal ldan dbang phyug mchog /
NK052(zi)001:5943: dpal he ru ka'i phyag rgya'i tshul ni /
NK052(zi)001:5944: 'byung po thams cad kyi gtso bo dur khrod kyi
NK052(zi)001:5945: bdag po dang mthun par gos chen po mnabs shing
NK052(zi)001:5946: snod chen po dang sbrang rtsi chen pos bkang ste
NK052(zi)001:5947: rol pa'o // phyag rgya gzhan yang gsungs pa /
NK052(zi)001:5948: rdo rje kha t+aam rdo rje bcas //
NK052(zi)001:5949: dril bu dkrol ba'i sgrar bcas pa //
NK052(zi)001:5950: dpal ldan he ru ka 'babs pa'i //
NK052(zi)001:5951: phyag rgya sna tshogs rnam 'phrul pas //
NK052(zi)001:5953: dpal he ru ka phyag gzhir bstan pa'i tshe /
NK052(zi)001:5955: rdo rje kha t+aam ka dril bus brgyan pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:5956: phyag gnyis ni snod chen por btung ba chen po dang /
NK052(zi)001:5957: bza' ba chen pos bkang ba bsnams te rol to //
NK052(zi)001:5958: phyag brgyad du bstan pa'i tshe /
NK052(zi)001:5959: gos chen po phyag gnyis kyis gzung ste rlung gi dkyil 'khor ltar bskor nas gsol lo //
NK052(zi)001:5960: gnyis pa mda' gzhu 'gengs zhes bshad /
NK052(zi)001:5961: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan can //
NK052(zi)001:5962: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu dang //
NK052(zi)001:5964: dpal he ru ka'i dbu rgyan dang rdo rje sems dpa'i dbu rgyan 'dra ste /
NK052(zi)001:5965: thod pa dang sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bus brgyan to //
NK052(zi)001:5966: de la thod pa'i dbu rgyan ni /
NK052(zi)001:5967: byang chub kyi sems gtso bor bstan pa'i phyir te /
NK052(zi)001:5968: dbu rgyan kun kyang byang chub kyi sems kyi rtags
NK052(zi)001:5969: yin mod kyi gang du gang gtsor gsungs pa de
NK052(zi)001:5970: khyad par du sbyar bar rigs so //
NK052(zi)001:5971: se ral kha yi tshul dag tu //
NK052(zi)001:5972: kha t+aam ka la rgyab rten byas //
NK052(zi)001:5973: lag pa g.yon pa thod pa thogs //
NK052(zi)001:5974: g.yas pa ba dan gsum par bya //
NK052(zi)001:5975: nam mkha'i phyag rgya rnal 'byor pa //
NK052(zi)001:5976: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:5977: dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor 'dir rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma brgyad gsungs pa las /
NK052(zi)001:5978: lha mo sman sha na ni rigs thams cad 'byung
NK052(zi)001:5979: ba'i gzhi thams cad las kyi bdag nyid yin pas
NK052(zi)001:5980: de bas na 'dir yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai bstan
NK052(zi)001:5981: te / kha t+aam ka se ral khar btsugs te
NK052(zi)001:5982: rgyab brten nas lag pa g.yon thod pa thogs te
NK052(zi)001:5983: g.yas pa ba dan gsum pas gtso la mkhyud pa'i
NK052(zi)001:5984: tshul gyis rtag tu sbyor ba dang mi bral ba
NK052(zi)001:5985: te / bstan pa'o // de yang gang gi phyir dpal he ru ka ni /
NK052(zi)001:5986: dur khrod chen po na tan dang ga na'i phrin
NK052(zi)001:5987: las la rtag tu rol par bstan pa'i phyir ro
NK052(zi)001:5988: // nam mkha' thams cad mnyam sbyor bskal pa bzang
