NK052(zi)001:5989: po dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma bde ba'i mchog
NK052(zi)001:5994: da ni dpal he ru ka'i skyil mo krung bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:5995: g.yas dang g.yon pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:5996: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:5997: 'dir skyil mo krung yang gzungs dang rol pa las
NK052(zi)001:5998: byang chub kyi sems len pas 'dul bar mdzad pa'o
NK052(zi)001:5999: // de ni 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6000: de nas gzhan yang rab bshad pa //
NK052(zi)001:6002: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6003: de la mkha' 'gro ma 'di rnams kyi phyag rgya'i
NK052(zi)001:6004: gar gyi mtshan nyid kyang 'dir rim pa bdun du
NK052(zi)001:6005: ston to // de la dang po ni /
NK052(zi)001:6008: lta stangs kyi gar ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6010: dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i sgo nas rgyas 'debs shing dbang du byed pa'i gar ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6012: gar gyi las dang yon tan ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6014: gar gyi thabs tshul ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6016: las kyi sgo nas las kyi phyag rgya ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6018: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi ming dang grangs rim ston to //
NK052(zi)001:6019: de la dang por gnas tshul gyi gar bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6020: zhi dang drag po rmongs pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6021: dga' ba'i gar byed 'gyur ba bcas //
NK052(zi)001:6022: shi ba ldang ba'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:6023: bde ba'i phyag rgya rab tu gnas //
NK052(zi)001:6025: de la zhi ba ni rgyas 'debs ma'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6026: ke ri ni zhi ba'i tshul du gnas shing bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6027: de bzhin du snying 'dren ma ste tso'u ni drag po'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6028: rmongs byed ma ste pra mo ha ni rmongs pa'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6029: 'degs byed ma ste bee ta li ni dga' ba'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6030: gar byed ma ste puska s+ai ni gar byed pa'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6031: gsod byed ma ste tsan+da l+ai ni g.yeng zhing 'gyur ba'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6032: zab mo ste g+hasma r+ai ni shi ba ldang ba'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:6033: bde ba'i phyag rgya rab tu gnas //
NK052(zi)001:6036: 'di rnams ni mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi bde bar gnas pa'i phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6038: lha mo sma sha ni ma smos pa ni kun
NK052(zi)001:6039: gyi spyir bstan pas lhag par ni smos kyang mi
NK052(zi)001:6040: dgos la / gong du yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai
NK052(zi)001:6041: nyid du bstan pas gtso bo dang sbyor ba'i tshul
NK052(zi)001:6042: du bzhugs pa nyid du zad do //
NK052(zi)001:6043: 'on kyang lha mo 'di dag kun kyang ji skad
NK052(zi)001:6044: du bstan pa'i rang rang gi tshul 'di dag dang
NK052(zi)001:6045: ldan pa'i dpal chen po'i sku la sbyar te bde
NK052(zi)001:6046: ba gnas pa'i phyag rgya can no //
NK052(zi)001:6048: de ni gnas tshul gyi gar bstan pas sbyor ba'i
NK052(zi)001:6049: bde ba la gnas pa'i gar du gsungs par shes
NK052(zi)001:6050: par bya'o // de ni gnyis pa lta stangs kyi gar ston pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6051: zhi ba drag po rmongs byed dang //
NK052(zi)001:6052: gyen du dbugs 'byin gar byed lus //
NK052(zi)001:6053: lta ba'i phyag rgya grub pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6055: de la go'u ri ni zhi bar gzigs te zam zim du blta ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6056: tso'u ri ni drag por gzigs te rnam par bzlog ste blta ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6057: pra mo ha ni rmongs par gzigs te 'bru tshugs su blta ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6058: be te li ni shi ba sos pa'i tshul du
NK052(zi)001:6059: gzigs te dal bus cung zad gyen du blta ba'o
NK052(zi)001:6060: // puska s+ai ni gar byed pa'i tshul du gzigs te sna tshogs su blta ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6061: tsan+da l+ai ni rnam par g.yengs par gzigs te dbugs 'thor ba'i tshul gyis so //
NK052(zi)001:6062: g+hasma r+ai ni ro za ba'i tshul du gzigs te 'dir yang lus zhes gsungs pa dang sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:6063: blta ba'i phyag rgya grub pa'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6066: lta stangs kyi gar gyi phyag rgya rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i mthun can no //
NK052(zi)001:6068: de ni gsum pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i sgo
NK052(zi)001:6069: nas rgyas 'debs shing dbang du byed pa'i gar bstan
NK052(zi)001:6070: pa'i phyir / gsang ba sbyor ba bde mchog gis //
NK052(zi)001:6071: me tog bdug pa sbyar ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6072: chang dang chu dang lcug ma dang //
NK052(zi)001:6073: ras dang me gtor grub pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:6074: khyad par du yang rgyas 'debs so //
NK052(zi)001:6077: gsang ba'i sbyor ba bde mchog gis //
NK052(zi)001:6079: lha mo thams cad kyang dpal chen po dang sbyor
NK052(zi)001:6080: ba'i sgo nas rgyas 'debs par byed pa las mi
NK052(zi)001:6081: 'da' bas dam tshig gi phyag rgyar 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:6083: dang por chags pas dbang du byed pas rgyas 'debs par byed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6085: me tog dang mda' yang don gcig ste dbang du
NK052(zi)001:6086: byed pa'i mda' thams cad ni me tog gi mda'
NK052(zi)001:6087: zhes grags te / 'jig rten na bdud k+aa ma
NK052(zi)001:6088: de ba me tog mda' can zhes bya bas kyang
NK052(zi)001:6089: zhes grags te / / 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i
NK052(zi)001:6090: phyag rgya me tog gi mda' lnga ga nga la
NK052(zi)001:6091: 'phangs pa de rang dbang med par chags pa skyes
NK052(zi)001:6093: ye shes kyi lha dag kyang lha mo sgrol ma
NK052(zi)001:6094: lta bu dbang gi phrin las mdzad pa na me
NK052(zi)001:6095: tog gi mdas byed pa lta bu'o //
NK052(zi)001:6096: bdug pa sbyar ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6098: de bas bdug pa lcags kyu'ang don gcig ste /
NK052(zi)001:6099: sdud par byed pa'i tshul gyis rgyas 'debs par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6102: phyag na thod pa chang gis bkang ba thogs te /
NK052(zi)001:6103: rmongs par byed pa'i tshul gyis rgyas 'debs so //
NK052(zi)001:6106: phyag na bdud rtsi'i chu bsnams te gso ba'i tshul gyis rgyas 'debs so //
NK052(zi)001:6108: gar byed ma'i phyag rgya ste dpag bsam shing gi
NK052(zi)001:6109: lcug ma bsnams te gar byed pa'i tshul gyis rgyas
NK052(zi)001:6110: 'debs so // zhing gi sgal tshigs thod pa lcang
NK052(zi)001:6111: lo dang ma bral ba yang dpag bsam shing gi
NK052(zi)001:6113: ras dang zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6115: phyag na ras kyi rlung sgye'u bsnams pas 'jig rten 'khor bar byed pas rgyas 'debs ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:6116: me gtor zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6117: zab mo'i phyag rgya ste phyag na me 'bar bas 'jig rten sreg par byed pas rgyas 'debs ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:6118: grub pa'i sa zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6119: phyag rgya de dag thams cad kyang rang grub pa'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6120: de lta bu rnams kyis khyad par du yang rgyas 'debs so //
NK052(zi)001:6122: skabs 'dir yang lha mo sma sha ni rgyas 'debs pa'i phyag rgya spyir sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:6123: da ni bzhi pa phyag rgya gar gyi las dang
NK052(zi)001:6124: yon tan gyi 'bras bu ji lta bu zhig sbyin
NK052(zi)001:6125: par byed pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6126: rtse gcig mnyam par sbyar ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:6127: sbyor ba'i gnyer ba bde ba sbyin //
NK052(zi)001:6130: goo r+ai'i phyag rgya rtse gcig tu mnyam par sbyor
NK052(zi)001:6131: bas sbyor ba'i las kyis don du gnyer ba dngos
NK052(zi)001:6132: grub zhi zhing rgyas 'debs pa sbyin par byed do
NK052(zi)001:6133: // de bzhin du gzhan la yang sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:6134: 'dren byed pa tsoo r+ais drag pos snying nas 'byin par nus pa sbyin par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6135: rmongs byed ma ste pra mo has rmongs par byed pa sbyin pa byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6136: 'degs byed ma ste bee ta lis gso bar nus pa sbyin par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6137: gar byed ma ste puska s+ais drag shul gyi las dang dbang gis grub pa sbyin par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6138: gsod ma ste tsan+ta l+ais g.yeng ba dang gsod pa'i grub pa sbyin par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6139: zab mo ste g+hasma r+ais sreg cing gdug pa za ba'i grub pa sbyin par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6140: sma sha ni dngos grub thams cad pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6141: de ni lnga pa ltabs tshul gyi gar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6142: mngon par 'thor zhing se gol rdob //
NK052(zi)001:6144: zas dang gsang ba'i lus dag dang //
NK052(zi)001:6145: zhes bya ba'i bar dag gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6146: de la mngon par 'thor zhing se gol brdob //
NK052(zi)001:6149: dal bur gyen du dbugs 'byin pas //
NK052(zi)001:6157: tsoo'u ri snying 'dren pa'i gar stabs so //
NK052(zi)001:6158: 'o byed mkhyud pa de bzhin te //
NK052(zi)001:6160: pra mo ha chags pas rmongs par byed pa'i gar stabs so //
NK052(zi)001:6161: gar byed rab tu rmongs pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:6163: puska s+ai'i gar gyis rmongs pa byed pa'i gar stabs so //
NK052(zi)001:6166: g+hasma ri ro yi ba'i gar stabs so //
NK052(zi)001:6168: zhes bya ba ro nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6169: ro za ba'i skabs zhes sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:6172: lha mo sma sha na'i phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6173: zhes slob dpon kha gcig gis bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:6175: da ni drug pa las kyi phyag rgya'i sgo nas gar gyis mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6176: tshangs pa chen po'i mgo dang /
NK052(zi)001:6177: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos te /
NK052(zi)001:6178: de la tshangs pa chen po'i mgo ni go'u ri
NK052(zi)001:6179: ste mda' bzhi dus gcig 'phangs nas tshangs pa'i mgo
NK052(zi)001:6181: de bzhin 'jig rten gsum las rgyal //
NK052(zi)001:6184: 'jig rten gsum las rgyal bar byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6187: tshig 'di gnyis rim par bsnol te /
NK052(zi)001:6189: 'dren byed tsoo ri ma'i phyag rgya yin la /
NK052(zi)001:6190: 'jig rten gsum las rgyal ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6191: rgyal byed pra mo ha'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6193: rang gi phyag rgya'i tshul ston no //
NK052(zi)001:6194: shugs kyis bstan pa'i tshig ste bee ta l+ai dang sbyar /
NK052(zi)001:6195: dur khrod dag gis gar byed ni /
NK052(zi)001:6197: de bzhin rlung gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK052(zi)001:6199: rab tu 'jigs par sreg pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6201: las kyi phyag rgyar rab tu gnas //
NK052(zi)001:6203: sma sha ni yang las kyi phyag rgya yin la /
NK052(zi)001:6204: mjug bsdu ba'i tshul yang las kyi phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6206: dang po rgyas 'debs ma'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:6207: zhes bya ba la sogs rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:6208: de la dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor 'dir mkha'
NK052(zi)001:6209: 'gro ma rnams kyi gar lhag par rgyas par bstan
NK052(zi)001:6210: cing / dkyil 'khor gzhan du de ltar ma bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6211: dpal he ru ka ni dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6212: dur khrod chen po na 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgus so //
NK052(zi)001:6213: de dang lhan cig rol pa'i mkha' 'gro ma rnams
NK052(zi)001:6214: kyang 'bar ba'i gar sna tshogs kyis rol te tha
NK052(zi)001:6215: mal pa'i tshul gcig tu mi gnas pas de bas
NK052(zi)001:6216: na rang gzhin gyis gar sna tshogs bstan dgos pa
NK052(zi)001:6217: nyid do // de nas phyag rgya 'di kun gyi //
NK052(zi)001:6218: phyag rgya'i lan rnams bla na med //
NK052(zi)001:6219: phyag rgya'i bdag nyid kun 'joms pa //
NK052(zi)001:6221: gar gyi phyag rgya de dag gi yon tan te /
NK052(zi)001:6222: 'di dag ni las kyi phyag rgya dang 'joms pa'i phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6223: gzhan gyi phyag rgya thams cad zlog cing 'joms par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6225: dpal rdo rje pad mo slong //
NK052(zi)001:6227: sbyor ba'i gar gyi sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:6229: de nas phyag rgya shes pa 'di //
NK052(zi)001:6230: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sbyor ba glu //
NK052(zi)001:6231: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6232: rdo rje pad mo slong ba'i glu yang 'di nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6234: gzigs pa rnam pa sna tshogs 'gyur ba'i rgyas thob la //
NK052(zi)001:6236: rgyas 'debs ma'i sgo nas te gzigs thabs kyi gar gyis so //
NK052(zi)001:6237: rnam pa sna tshogs 'o byed ma khyud pas rmongs mdzad de //
NK052(zi)001:6239: rmongs byed ma'i sgo nas te /
NK052(zi)001:6241: rnam pa sna tshogs bde ba'i mchod ston kun gsol la //
NK052(zi)001:6243: za byed ma'i sgo nas te rol pa'i gar gyis so //
NK052(zi)001:6244: rnam pa sna tshogs bde mchog ngo mtshar bstan tu gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6246: tshe 'phel ma'i sgo nas te bde ba chen po dngos grub la gnas pa'i gar gyis so //
NK052(zi)001:6247: phyag rgya bzhi po 'di dag mdor bsdus pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6248: rgyas btab rmongs byed mnabs su gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6249: bde mchog ngo mtshar bde la bzhugs //
NK052(zi)001:6250: zhes pa dang rim pa bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:6251: h+aum a la la la hoh snang bar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:6253: dngos grub gsol bar bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6254: rnal 'byor bde mchog sgyu mas sprul //
NK052(zi)001:6257: dam tshig dag la 'jug tu gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6259: rang gi dam tshig gi lha mo dang dam tshig gi rdzas la rol bar bsku la ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6260: nyon mongs kun las rgyal bar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:6262: thabs de'i sgo nas khams gsum las rgyal bar mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:6264: ma lus pa dag mnabs su gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6266: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mtshan ma thams
NK052(zi)001:6267: cad zad par mdzad pa'i phyir thams cad gsol cig
NK052(zi)001:6269: nyon mongs pa thams cad bsal bar mdzod //
NK052(zi)001:6272: dpal he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya rdzogs /
NK052(zi)001:6273: de ni dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6275: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6277: shel gong bzhin du dag pa la 'dod chags bsreg pa'i 'od zer gyis 'khrigs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6279: sangs rgyas tshe yi rin chen spras //
NK052(zi)001:6280: gos dang sna tshogs rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK052(zi)001:6281: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:6282: bde ba can bzhin dam par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:6284: dbu rgyan tshe dpag med kyis brgyan cing ye shes
NK052(zi)001:6285: las 'phrul pa'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pas shin
NK052(zi)001:6287: dper na sangs rgyas tshe dpag med kyi zhing khams
NK052(zi)001:6288: bde ba can na sangs rgyas sras bcas mdzes par
NK052(zi)001:6289: byas shing dam par basngagasa pa thob pa bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:6290: 'dir dbu rgyan sna tshogs yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rang bzhin yin pas de 'dra'o //
NK052(zi)001:6293: gar thabs rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK052(zi)001:6294: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6295: pad ma'i phyag rgyas pad ma'i mtshan ma bsnams pa
NK052(zi)001:6296: brgya rnyed la sogs pas sprul pa'i gar mdzad cing
NK052(zi)001:6297: thams cad sbyor bar mdzad do //
NK052(zi)001:6299: skyil mo krung bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6300: g.yas dang g.yon pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:6301: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6302: de la rgyal po'i skyil mo krung ni /
NK052(zi)001:6303: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung nyid las rkang pa g.yas pa phab ste bag glod pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6304: de ni 'khor gyi lha mo rnams kyi phyag rgya'i gar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6305: bsnyems pa'i lag pa g.yon pa yis //
NK052(zi)001:6306: pad mo dmar po ci bder bzung //
NK052(zi)001:6307: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6308: lha mo 'di rnams kyang phyag g.yon pa rnams kyis
NK052(zi)001:6309: 'gying bag gi pad ma rnams bag yangs su 'dzin
NK052(zi)001:6310: / g.yas pa rnams kyis so so'i phyag rgya'i gar dang ldan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6311: de la rnam par gzigs ma ni /
NK052(zi)001:6312: g.yon pad mo dmar po bag yangs 'dzin /
NK052(zi)001:6313: g.yas mtheb mdzub rtse sprod de pad ma smyung po'i
NK052(zi)001:6314: phyag rgya bcas nas pad ma kha 'byed pa'i tshul
NK052(zi)001:6315: gyis snying kha 'dren pa ltar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6316: sgrol ma byang chub ma ni /
NK052(zi)001:6317: g.yon pa pad ma sngon po 'dzin /
NK052(zi)001:6318: g.yas bud med kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6319: khu tshur snying gar 'dren pa'i tshul gyis 'ching ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6322: g.yas 'khor lo'i phyag rgya bstod de 'ching ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6325: g.yas gar byed cing ba dan gsum pa'i phyag rgya 'ching ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6328: g.yas pa gar byed cing chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan gyi phyag rgya 'ching ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6331: g.yas gar byed cing rdo rje rtse gsum gyi phyag rgya 'ching ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6332: 'dir lha mo drug las ma bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:6333: yul kha cig gi yi ge las ni /
NK052(zi)001:6334: lha mo brgyad tshang bar bskangs ba dag kyang yod do //
NK052(zi)001:6335: lha mo 'di dag gi grangs ston pa las /
NK052(zi)001:6336: rnam par gzigs ma rna ma dag dpal //
NK052(zi)001:6338: rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya'i don to //
NK052(zi)001:6339: sgrol ma byang chub mchog yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6341: khu tshur snying gar bcas pa nyid byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6342: rgya can ma ni 'khor lo bskor zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6343: chos kyi 'khor lo skor bar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6344: khro gnyer ma yi phyag rgya len //
NK052(zi)001:6346: ba dan gsum pa'i phyag rgya gzhan gyi phyag rgya slar bzlog pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6347: pad mo gnas pa dpal chen yin /
NK052(zi)001:6349: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan nyid dpal bskyed kyi phyag rgya yin pas so //
NK052(zi)001:6352: rdo rje rtse gsum gyi phyag rgya 'gro ba gsum dbang du byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6353: da ni de'i glu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6354: de nas phyag rgya shes pa 'di //
NK052(zi)001:6355: pad+ma'i rgyal po dpal gyi glu //
NK052(zi)001:6356: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6357: glu 'di'i don yang pad mo sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs
NK052(zi)001:6358: kyis sems can gyi don mdzad par bskul ba dang
NK052(zi)001:6359: / de lta bu dag bdag la yang bstan du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6362: bod pa bskul ba gnyis kyi tshul lo //
NK052(zi)001:6364: nyid kyi yon tan can du bos nas de lta bu'i tshul de bstan du gsol mdzad du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6367: 'di ltar de bzhin gshegs pa kun //
NK052(zi)001:6368: zhes bya ba nas kye sems dpa' pad mo dag pa mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6370: de lta bu'i sgyu ma'i dga' ba gdul bya la bstan du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:6376: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag /
NK052(zi)001:6377: ces bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6378: sangs rgyas la sogs pa 'phrul pa cir snang ba
NK052(zi)001:6379: thams cad khyod kyi bdag nyid lags pas de lta
NK052(zi)001:6382: pad mo 'dzin pa de'i spyan sngar gar mkhan gar mdzod cig /
NK052(zi)001:6384: dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi bdag po ni rdo rje chos yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6385: 'di ltar rdo rje chos las spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK052(zi)001:6386: dbang po sprul te de las dpal pad ma gar
NK052(zi)001:6387: gyi dbang phyug sprul nas des pad ma'i sgyu 'phrul
NK052(zi)001:6388: sna tshogs kyi 'phrul pa'i gar thabs 'gyed par mdzad
NK052(zi)001:6389: do // de bas na pad+mo 'dzin pa rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:6390: chos rigs kyi bdag po des dpang po mdzad de
NK052(zi)001:6391: de'i spyan sngar gar mkhan gyis sprul pa'i gar mdzod
NK052(zi)001:6393: dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:6394: da ni dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6396: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6398: rgyal po'i cha byad de khro zhing 'dzum pa dang
NK052(zi)001:6399: bcas pa'i tshul nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ltar kun gyis
NK052(zi)001:6401: 'dir dbu rgyan gyi don gsal bar ma gsungs kyang /
NK052(zi)001:6402: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i dbu rgyan
NK052(zi)001:6403: mdzad de nam mkha' las ni rin po che thams
NK052(zi)001:6404: cad phab nas thams cad kyi re ba rdzogs par
NK052(zi)001:6406: rdo rje gzhu dang mda' mchog dag /
NK052(zi)001:6408: phyag mtshan te phyag bzhi la gzhu dang mda' dang
NK052(zi)001:6409: ral gri dang me nyi ma bsnams te rgyal po'i
NK052(zi)001:6410: mtshan ma'o // skyil mo krung bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6411: rdo rje pus mo gnyis bcings te /
NK052(zi)001:6412: bdag gi stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:6414: rkang pa gnyis mkhriig ma bsnol nas pus mo gnyis
NK052(zi)001:6415: bkug la rdo rje ltar bcings te gnas pa 'di
NK052(zi)001:6416: ni rdo rje skyil mo krung ste de nyid /
NK052(zi)001:6417: bad ga gi stan zhes kyang bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6418: rang gi rkang pa rdo rje gdan gyi phyag rgyar gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK052(zi)001:6419: lha mo rnams kyi gar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6420: dbang bskur ba dang gter dag dang //
NK052(zi)001:6421: rgyal mtshan mchog ldan mchod pa che //
NK052(zi)001:6422: ji lta'i tshul dag ston pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:6423: rang gi don rnams rab bsgrub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6425: 'dir gar ji ltar bya ba ma gsungs par /
NK052(zi)001:6426: ji lta'i tshul dag ston pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:6428: dbang bskur ltar bya ba'i gar dang /
NK052(zi)001:6429: gter 'byin pa ltar byas pa'i gar dang /
NK052(zi)001:6430: rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba ltar byas pa'i gar dang /
NK052(zi)001:6431: me tog 'thor ba ltar byas pa'i gar rnams dang sbyor ro //
NK052(zi)001:6432: de la dbang bskur ba dang gter 'byin pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6433: bum pa'i phyag rgya spyi bo nas gtugs pa ltar byed pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:6434: sa las 'byin pa ltar byed pa dang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6435: de la bum pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6436: thal mo sbyar ba la mdzub mo gnyis kyi rtse mo gung mo'i tshigs dang por btsugs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6437: de nas gar de'i glu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6438: de nas phyag rgya shes pa 'di //
NK052(zi)001:6439: rgyal po'i sgyu ma mchog gi glu //
NK052(zi)001:6440: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6441: glu 'di'i don yang dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i yon
NK052(zi)001:6442: tan rin po che'i khyad par de bdag la gsol
NK052(zi)001:6445: bud med rin chen rnams kyi phyir //
NK052(zi)001:6446: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6447: rin po che thams cad kyi nang na bud med rin chen basngagasa pa'i tshig ste /
NK052(zi)001:6449: rin po che rigs yin pas yon tan gyi che ba basngagasa shing gsol ba 'debs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6450: de bas na 'dir rin po che'i dam pa bud
NK052(zi)001:6451: med kyi dam pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya ma
NK052(zi)001:6452: / phyag rgya'i dam pa chos kyi sku ste /
NK052(zi)001:6453: de bas na rin po che'i dam pa bdag la gsol cig /
NK052(zi)001:6455: dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya rdzogs so //
NK052(zi)001:6456: da ni dpal rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6458: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6459: de la 'dir dpal rta mchog sku mdog dmar po
NK052(zi)001:6460: zhal bzhi phyag bzhi zhabs bzhi rta'i rmig pa bzhis
NK052(zi)001:6461: lha chen po thams cad ngo mthon stobs kyis gnon
NK052(zi)001:6462: pa ste / de la zhal bzhi ni /
NK052(zi)001:6463: 'dod chags can la g.yem pa ston //
NK052(zi)001:6465: ma h+aa de ba la sogs pa 'dod chags can
NK052(zi)001:6466: gdul ba'i phyir zhal dbu ma dmar po chags pa'i
NK052(zi)001:6468: gdug pa rnams la gdug par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:6470: gshin rje la sogs pa gdug pa can gdul pa'i
NK052(zi)001:6471: phyir zhal g.yas mthing ga shin tu 'khrug pa'i zhal
NK052(zi)001:6472: du bstan pa'o // zhi ba rnams la zhi bar 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:6474: tshangs pa la sogs pa'i zhi ba rnams gdul ba'i
NK052(zi)001:6475: phyir zhal g.yon dkar po shin tu gzi mdangs che
NK052(zi)001:6476: bar ston pa'o // drag shul can la drag shul sbyor //
NK052(zi)001:6478: khyab 'jug la sogs pa drag shul can gdul ba'i phyir dbu la rta mgo ljang gu byung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6480: g.yon pa'i khu tshur mdzub mo yis //
NK052(zi)001:6481: dpal ldan pad mo sna tshogs 'dzin //
NK052(zi)001:6482: rdo rjer bcas shing slong ba bsgrub //
NK052(zi)001:6483: g.yas pa ba dan gsum par bya //
NK052(zi)001:6485: phyag g.yon dang po rdo rje khu tshur gyi mdzub mos sna tshogs pad+ma 'dzin /
NK052(zi)001:6486: g.yas dang po rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin /
NK052(zi)001:6487: g.yon 'og ma mtha' rnam gnyis su shi ba slong bar mdzad /
NK052(zi)001:6488: g.yas 'og ma ba dan lce gsum pa bsnams te khams kyi bya spron mdzad do //
NK052(zi)001:6490: zhabs bzhi'i rmig pa bzhis gang gnon pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6494: lha mo gang gi dkyil 'khor na bzhugs pa de'i
NK052(zi)001:6495: tshe de'i rigs kyi dbu rgyan dang ldan par sbyar
NK052(zi)001:6497: khro bo'i skyil mo krung zhes bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6498: zhabs g.yas gnyis brkyang bskum pa'i tshul gyis lha chen po rnams gnon to //
NK052(zi)001:6499: 'khor gyi lha mo rnams ma smos pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6500: las thams cad pa yin pa las gang dang 'tshams
NK052(zi)001:6501: pa'i gong du smos pa'i lha mo rnams ci rigs
NK052(zi)001:6503: de ni glu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6504: de nas phyag rgya shes pa 'di /
NK052(zi)001:6505: rta mchog dpal ldan gnas pa'i glu //
NK052(zi)001:6506: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6508: zhal bzhi dang zhabs bzhi'i sgo nas dngos grub gsol ba bskul ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:6509: de lta bu'i dngos grub gsol mi gsol gyi the
NK052(zi)001:6510: tshom ma mdzad par thugs gnad nas bskul bar ston
NK052(zi)001:6512: myos byed stong bas lhag par bde ba'i gzugs ston pa //
NK052(zi)001:6514: 'dod chags can la g.yem pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:6515: zhal dbu ma'i sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:6516: de bzhin du gzhan la yang sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:6517: gshin rje stong bas 'jigs pa ni zhal g.yas kyi sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:6518: tshangs pa stong pas lhag par zhi zhing gzi mdangs che ba ni zhal g.yas kyi sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:6519: de yang dug gsum sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid 'dir /
NK052(zi)001:6521: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog tu de bzhin gshegs pa kun grub mdzod /
NK052(zi)001:6523: sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las ni rta'i zhal yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6524: de'i sgo nas bskul ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6525: thams cad dag par mos pas //
NK052(zi)001:6526: zhes bya ba'i tshig gnyis yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6527: drag shul gyi rtsal gyis thul cig /
NK052(zi)001:6532: da ni zhabs kyi sgo nas bskul ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6533: rab kyi rtsal gyis gnon pa'i stobs kyis ngo mthon dbang phyug ga non /
NK052(zi)001:6534: sbyor che hu lu hu lu mig gsum pa las gsum grub drongs /
NK052(zi)001:6535: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6536: 'dir lha chen po bzhi zhabs bzhis gnon la de'i chung ma bzhi phrogs shing zhes pa'i don te /
NK052(zi)001:6539: zhes te dbang phyug chen po ma h+aa de ni gnon cig pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6542: bod pa ste dpal rta mchog kyang thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin pas so //
NK052(zi)001:6545: bskul ba ste srin skad do //
NK052(zi)001:6547: ma h+aa de ba'i ming gi bye brag go //
NK052(zi)001:6549: de'i chung ma ste u ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:6551: ces thams cad du yang sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6555: de la mthu che ba ni ra yan ste khyab 'jug go //
NK052(zi)001:6559: bskul ba ste srin skad do //
NK052(zi)001:6561: de'i chung ma ste bkra shis brtan no //
NK052(zi)001:6571: bskul ba ste srin skad do //
NK052(zi)001:6577: chung ma dga' sdug mi'i dbang phyug ma ste drongs shig pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6578: a la la la hoh zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6579: dngos grub blang ba'i tshig go //
NK052(zi)001:6580: de la srin skadakyi yi ge /
NK052(zi)001:6581: ru ta ma ta sma ra ra ta /
NK052(zi)001:6582: zhes bya ba yi ge brgyad po 'di'i lo rgyus ni /
NK052(zi)001:6583: sngon las kyi srin po chen po /
NK052(zi)001:6584: mat+tam ka ru dra zhes bya ba 'jig rten du
NK052(zi)001:6585: byung ste 'jig rten dbang du bsdus pa'i tshe srin
NK052(zi)001:6586: po de'i nga rgyal gyi gtum skad phyung ba grub
NK052(zi)001:6587: pa'i snying por gyur pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6588: de nas srin po des dur khrod chen po'i gnas
NK052(zi)001:6589: brgyad du ma mo chen mo brgyad yi ge 'bru
NK052(zi)001:6590: 'di brgyad las sprul te bzhag pas de phyin chad
NK052(zi)001:6591: ma mo brgyad kyi srog gi snying por gyur to
NK052(zi)001:6592: // de nas dpal he ru kas ru dra brtul
NK052(zi)001:6593: te ru dra'i ngag gi bden pa phrogs nas rgyal
NK052(zi)001:6594: ba'i gsang sngags su byin gyis brlabs /
NK052(zi)001:6595: ye shes kyi ma mo brgyad sprul te /
NK052(zi)001:6596: dur khrod brgyad kyi srung mar bzhag nas /
NK052(zi)001:6597: las kyi ma mo brgyad de'i bran mor byas so //
NK052(zi)001:6600: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6602: mo sum+b+ha ni sum+b+ha h+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK052(zi)001:6605: de yang sum+b+ha ni mnan pa'i tshig ni /
NK052(zi)001:6607: nges par gnon pa'i tshig ste /
NK052(zi)001:6608: ni zhes bya ba nges pa la sbyor ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6609: da ni lha la dngos grub mi g.yo bar blang
NK052(zi)001:6610: ba' phyir lha gnad la bskul ba' glu ston pa'i
NK052(zi)001:6611: phyir / mdza' bo mi la bya'am mi bya'i yongs rtog de dag med kyang bla /
NK052(zi)001:6612: de 'dra'i mdza' bo sgyu ma yin pas de la mdza' zhes su zhig zer /
NK052(zi)001:6613: zhes bya ba'i tshig rkang bzhi smos te /
NK052(zi)001:6614: de la glu thams cad kyang a ba b+h+ram sha ta'i skad kyis ston mod kyi /
NK052(zi)001:6617: bi shi tsi'i skad bsres pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6620: sngon las kyi srin po ma t+aam ka ru dra
NK052(zi)001:6621: gzhan la bskul ba'i tshe srin skad 'dis bskul bas
NK052(zi)001:6622: las g.yo ba med pa grub pa las /
NK052(zi)001:6623: de la dpal he ru kas brtul ba'i tshe kho'i
NK052(zi)001:6624: ngag gi bden pa yang phrogs te las grub pa
NK052(zi)001:6626: dpal chen po'i grub pa'i glur bsgyur ba yin pas lha gnad la bskul ba'i glu 'di bzang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:6628: glu 'di'i don ni dpe dang zur gyi sgo nas bskul ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:6629: 'di ltar lha mi mdza' bo rnams la phan gdags
NK052(zi)001:6630: par bya'am mi bya zhes pa'i yongs su rtog pa'i
NK052(zi)001:6631: the tshom ni gzhi nas med na sla ba yin
NK052(zi)001:6632: te / gar te mdza' bor khas mches pa zhig
NK052(zi)001:6633: la phan gdags par bya ba'am mi bya'i the tshom
NK052(zi)001:6634: yod na de 'dra ba'i mdza' bo ni sgyu ma'i
NK052(zi)001:6636: mdza' bo'i gzugs brnyan yin pas de 'dra ba la
NK052(zi)001:6637: mdza' bo'i ming yang gdags par mi rigs te su
NK052(zi)001:6638: zhig mdza' bo zhes mi brjod do //
NK052(zi)001:6640: tshig 'di'i zur gyis 'dod pa'i don 'di ltar smra ba yin te /
NK052(zi)001:6641: lha khyod ni bdag gi lha lags pas bdag la
NK052(zi)001:6642: dngos grub gsol mi gsol the tshom mi mda' grags
NK052(zi)001:6643: / gal te mnga' srid na lha ltar snang ba
NK052(zi)001:6644: khyod lta bu zhes zhes su zhig 'dogs par byed
NK052(zi)001:6646: rgol ba gang la bya'am mi bya ba'i tshig 'di
NK052(zi)001:6647: yang tshig snga ma'i zla'i sgo nas bskul ba yin
NK052(zi)001:6648: te / 'di ltar dpa' bo zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6649: rgol ba byung nas de la phyir rgol ba la
NK052(zi)001:6650: yid mi zhum zhing the tshom mi za yin na
NK052(zi)001:6651: / gal te dpa' bo khas mches pa zhig la
NK052(zi)001:6652: rgol ba la slar brgal mi brgal gyi the tshom
NK052(zi)001:6653: / yod na / de 'dra'i rgol ba sgyu ma
NK052(zi)001:6654: dang gzugs brnyan lta bu'i don gyis dgos pa mi
NK052(zi)001:6655: 'grub pa de lta bu la dpa' bo zhes su
NK052(zi)001:6658: dpal rta mchog gi thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6659: thams cad 'byung byed ye shes phyag rgya zhes bya ba /
NK052(zi)001:6660: sgyur byed kyi phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi
NK052(zi)001:6661: thog mar bstan pa de nyid rang gi ngo bo
NK052(zi)001:6663: lha gang dang gang gi phyag rgya yin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:6664: dgos pa'i skabs su sbyar ba yin pa dang bcas te bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:6665: da ni gnyis pa dam tshig ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6666: de la phyag rgya 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6667: lha rnams kyi thugs dam tshig gi mtshan mar gyur pa lag gis bcas pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6668: lha gang dang gang yin pa ni rigs kyi gtso bo drug gi rang rang gi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6669: dgos pa gang gi skabs su sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6670: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du sgrub pa'i skabs su'ang dam
NK052(zi)001:6671: tshig gi phyag rgya 'di dag gis btab nas lha
NK052(zi)001:6672: rnams dam tshig las mi 'da' bar 'gyur ba dang
NK052(zi)001:6673: / gzhan yang gdul bya'i dbang gis las so sor
NK052(zi)001:6674: bsgrub par bya ba las ji ltar gsungs pa bzhin
NK052(zi)001:6676: gar ye shes kyi phyag rgya bsgyur ba'i tshe /
NK052(zi)001:6677: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gcig tu rnal 'byor pa gnyis
NK052(zi)001:6678: kyis rgol ba'i tshul gyis rigs so so'i phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:6679: kun kyang phyag rgya dang phyag rgya'i lan gyis sgyur
NK052(zi)001:6680: bar byed pa'i tshe sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:6681: 'di dag kyang phyag rgya rang rang gi bya ba ma gtogs par /
NK052(zi)001:6682: spyir tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:6683: gar ye shes kyi phyag rgyar sbyar ba ni phal cher mthun par sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6684: de la dam tshig ye shes kyi phyag rgya 'di'i
NK052(zi)001:6685: rigs dang gang yin pa so sor bstan pa ni
NK052(zi)001:6686: / mdzub mo mthe bong mnan nas ni //
NK052(zi)001:6687: zhes bya ba la sogs pa dpal grub spyan gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6688: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6689: de'i khyad par gyi bya ba gang la sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6690: las dang dngos grub thams cad pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6691: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar ba //
NK052(zi)001:6692: zhes bya ba la sogs pa sems dpa'i gtsug tor gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6693: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6695: chos kyi dbyings kyi rtags gtsug tor gyi phyag rgyas bsrung ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6696: rdo rje thal mo gyen du dbye //
NK052(zi)001:6697: zhes bya ba la sogs pa dpal rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6698: dpal he ru ka'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6700: gdug pa 'dul ba dang nor la sogs pa'i bya ba bsgrub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6701: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyor nas //
NK052(zi)001:6702: zhes bya ba la sogs dpal pad+ma'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6703: dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6706: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar la //
NK052(zi)001:6707: zhes bya ba la sogs pa dpal nor bu'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6708: dpal rdo rje nyi ma'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6709: rgyal srid kyi bya ba la sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6711: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyar nas //
NK052(zi)001:6712: zhes bya ba la sogs pa /
NK052(zi)001:6713: dpal rta mchog gi dam tshig gi phyag rgyas kyang dngos grub la sbyor ba byed do //
NK052(zi)001:6714: dam tshig ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6715: da ni dam tshig chen po ye shes kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6716: lus dang ngag sems rdo rje yi //
NK052(zi)001:6717: mtshan ma'i phyag rgya ldan byas te //
NK052(zi)001:6718: thams cad 'byung ba'i sbyor ba yis //
NK052(zi)001:6719: bdag gi lha ni bdag nyid bya //
NK052(zi)001:6720: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6721: phyag rgya 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6722: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum rang gi lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyas btab ste /
NK052(zi)001:6723: thams cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya nas
NK052(zi)001:6724: 'byung ba bzhin sku'i tshul dang phyag rgya dang bzhugs
NK052(zi)001:6725: thabs dang / dbu rgyan la sogs pa ji ltar bsgom zhing bcas pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6726: 'di lta bu la gzhung gzhan las phyag rgya chen po /
NK052(zi)001:6729: rigs rnam pa drug gi phyir sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6730: de'i bya ba gang la sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6731: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la sogs pa'i skabs 'ga' zhig tu sbyar ba ma zad /
NK052(zi)001:6732: ji ltar nus pa bzhin du rtag tu sbyar bar bya ba yang yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6733: dam tshig chen po'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6734: sbyor ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6735: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba /
NK052(zi)001:6736: ji ltar gzugs dang dbyibs su ldan //
NK052(zi)001:6737: bde ba nyid kyis kun tu bdag /
NK052(zi)001:6738: kun gyis bdag la gzhug par bya //
NK052(zi)001:6739: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6740: phyag rgya 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6741: dam tshig chen po'i phyag rgya lta bur ldan pa de la /
NK052(zi)001:6742: ye shes kyi lha bkug cing bcug ste /
NK052(zi)001:6743: dbyer med pa byas pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6744: 'di lha gang gi yin pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6745: rigs drug lha mo dang bdun gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6746: dgos pa gang du sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6747: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshe ni lha spyan drangs pa'i skabs su sbyar ba yin la /
NK052(zi)001:6749: go rim bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6750: rigs so so'i ngo bstan na /
NK052(zi)001:6751: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor /
NK052(zi)001:6753: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:6758: lha mo'i phyag rgya shes pa /
NK052(zi)001:6762: yod pa ma yin med pa min //
NK052(zi)001:6763: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6764: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:6765: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
NK052(zi)001:6766: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6768: bud med la sogs rin chen mchog /
NK052(zi)001:6769: ces bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6772: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6774: shin tu gdug cing drag po la //
NK052(zi)001:6775: zhes bya ba la sogs ni /
NK052(zi)001:6777: sbyor ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6778: de ni thams cad sbyor ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:6779: sbyor ba ji snyed yod kun dang /
NK052(zi)001:6780: byed pa rnam pa sna tshogs la //
NK052(zi)001:6781: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6782: de la 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6783: lus ngag gi bya ba sna tshogs dang ji snyed
NK052(zi)001:6784: sna tshogs la rang gi lha'i phyag rgyas btab ste
NK052(zi)001:6785: byas nas rang gi dngos grub la sbyor bar 'gyur
NK052(zi)001:6787: 'on kyang rigs so so rang rang gi byed pa so so yang yod pa shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6790: bye ba gang la sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6794: khyad par du rigs so so'i rang gi las dang
NK052(zi)001:6795: dngos grub la rang gi lus la sogs pa byed
NK052(zi)001:6796: pa'i spyod pa so sos sbyar ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:6797: de la sbyor ba ci snyed /
NK052(zi)001:6799: dpal dam tshig ces bya ba'i phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6801: spyod pa sna tshogs kyi sgo nas /
NK052(zi)001:6803: bya ba ni bzlog pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:6804: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6805: rgyal po'i byed spyod de dpal rdo rje nyi ma'o //
NK052(zi)001:6806: 'o byed mkhyud pa la sogs pa ni 'dod chags
NK052(zi)001:6807: kyi byed spyod de dpal pad ma gar gyi dbang
NK052(zi)001:6808: phyug gi'o // thar bar byed cing gsod par byed //
NK052(zi)001:6810: gar byas nas ni za bar byed //
NK052(zi)001:6811: ces pa'i tshig 'di gnyis ka drag po'i byed spyod du snang ste /
NK052(zi)001:6812: de bzhin gshegs pa'i byed spyod du lhag par gsal ba med pas /
NK052(zi)001:6813: sngon chad kyang rigs kyi sbyor ba cung zad mi mthun par smra na /
NK052(zi)001:6814: yang don dang sbyar na de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs ni /
NK052(zi)001:6815: shes rab pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul gyis rtag
NK052(zi)001:6816: chad kyi mtha' las grol zhing thar pa'i gnyi ga'i
NK052(zi)001:6819: thar par byed gsod par byed //
NK052(zi)001:6820: shi ba'ang mod la sogs par byed /
NK052(zi)001:6821: ces bya ba 'di gnyis de bzhin gshegs pas mdzad pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6822: sems can 'khor ba las ma thal bar byas dang /
NK052(zi)001:6823: mya ngan las 'das mthar shi ba rnams slar srid
NK052(zi)001:6824: pa'i myu gu bskyed de gso ba yang snying rje'i
NK052(zi)001:6826: thar pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i gegs su gyur pa
NK052(zi)001:6827: bdag tu lta ba'i rtog pa dang gzung ba 'dzin
NK052(zi)001:6828: pa'i mtshan nyid kyi chos kya rtog pa 'joms par
NK052(zi)001:6829: byed / gsod par byed pa'ang shes rab kyi spyod
NK052(zi)001:6830: pa yin pas de bas na 'di ni sangs rgyas
NK052(zi)001:6831: kyi byed spyod du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6833: thams cad la bkag pa med par longs spyod pa'i
NK052(zi)001:6834: mtshan nyid 'bar ba chen po gar gyis rol pa
NK052(zi)001:6835: thams cad za bar byed pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6837: sbyor ba'i longs thams cad kyis //
NK052(zi)001:6838: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:6839: dpal rdo rje 'dzin pa he ru ka'i byed spyod do //
NK052(zi)001:6840: dpal rta mchog ni las thams cad kyi bdag nyid pas /
NK052(zi)001:6841: sbyor ba kun gyis bde myong ba //
NK052(zi)001:6842: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6843: dpal rta mchog gi bde spyod do //
NK052(zi)001:6844: thams cad sbyor ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6845: da ni zhal ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6846: de la phyag rgya 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6847: lha rnams kyi bzhin gyi mtshan nyid /
NK052(zi)001:6849: rigs rnam pa drug lha mo rnams dang bdun gyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:6850: dgos pa gang du sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6851: ji srid du sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyas 'debs par byed pa de srid 'di sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6852: de lha mo kun gyi bde ba'i mchog ni /
NK052(zi)001:6853: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK052(zi)001:6855: ji ltar mdzes pa'i 'gyur bag go //
NK052(zi)001:6856: lha mo rnams kyi zhal gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6857: bud med mkhas pa sgyu ma che //
NK052(zi)001:6858: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6859: 'di ltar bud med kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi tshul 'jo ba dang sgeg pa dang 'gying ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:6860: stegs pa dang 'dzum pa dang zur gyis blta ba
NK052(zi)001:6861: dang srid zhur chas pa la sogs pa bzhin gyi
NK052(zi)001:6862: phyag rgya'o // dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi bzhin gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:6863: sangs rgyas byang chub mnyam sbyor ba //
NK052(zi)001:6864: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6865: rab tu dga' ba'i bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:6866: gsang bar blta la gnas na ni //
NK052(zi)001:6868: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs byang chub thugs su chud pa'i mtshan nyid pas zhi bar blta ste /
NK052(zi)001:6869: mdor na chos nyid la gzigs pa'i bzhin zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK052(zi)001:6871: stegs la sogs pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK052(zi)001:6872: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6873: 'bar ba'i gar dgu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6874: dpal rdo rje nyi ma ni /
NK052(zi)001:6875: mche ba cung zad gtsigs pa'i zhal //
NK052(zi)001:6876: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6877: rgyal po'i bzhin gyi mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6878: dpal pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi ni /
NK052(zi)001:6880: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6881: chags pas mdzes pa'i bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:6883: drag po mche ba rnon po gtsigs //
NK052(zi)001:6884: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6885: 'dir dpal rta mchog gi zhal gsum gyi phyag rgya bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:6886: rtsa ba'i zhal gyi bzhin gyi phyag rgyas bstan pa
NK052(zi)001:6887: ni las thams cad pa yin pas las gang la
NK052(zi)001:6888: sbyor ba'i tshe rigs so so'i bzhin gyii phyag rgya
NK052(zi)001:6890: zhal ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6891: da ni 'dzum pa'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6893: lha rnams kyi spyi'i zhal gyi phyag rgya las kyang 'dzum pa'i khyad par du byas pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:6895: mchu dang mig yin mod kyi de yang gtso bo ra mchu'i sgros g.yo ba'i tshul yin la /
NK052(zi)001:6896: lta ba ni gud du yang bstan pas de bstan
NK052(zi)001:6897: 'dir mchu g.yo ba'i mtshan nyid 'dzum pa'i phyir bstan
NK052(zi)001:6898: to // de la 'dir gang gi yin pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6899: spyir rigs drug po thams cad kyi yin yang dpal
NK052(zi)001:6900: rta mchog ni zhal gsum gyi mchu g.yo ba ni
NK052(zi)001:6901: gong du zhal gyi skabs su bstan zin la /
NK052(zi)001:6902: zhal dbu ma ni rigs ma nges pas 'dir ma bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:6903: de bas na 'dir lha lnga'i phyag rgya bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:6905: zhal ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang 'dra'o //
NK052(zi)001:6906: de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yin ni /
NK052(zi)001:6907: lha mo kun gyi zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6910: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ni /
NK052(zi)001:6913: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6916: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6919: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6921: 'dzum pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6922: da ni lta ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston to /
NK052(zi)001:6923: de la 'di'i rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:6924: spyi'i bzhin gyi phyag rgya las gzigs thabs khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:6926: spyir rigs kun gyi yin yang rta mchog snga ma bzhin sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:6927: gzhan rigs lnga dang lha mo rnams gcig tu byas
NK052(zi)001:6928: te lha rnam pa drug gi phyag rgya yin no
NK052(zi)001:6933: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6936: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6939: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6942: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6944: khro zhing 'gyur dang zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:6946: stegs la sogs pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni pad+ma rigs kyi'o //
NK052(zi)001:6947: lta ba ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6948: da ni chos kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6950: gsang sngags 'di dag nyid chos te lung gi bdag nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:6951: de nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya yin pas de skad ces bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:6952: gong gi phyag rgya rnams dang tshul mthun par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:6954: gzhung gzhan las grags pa mtshungs mthun par /
NK052(zi)001:6955: chos ni phan pa dang bde ba ston pa'i bdag nyid lung gi chos rnams yin la /
NK052(zi)001:6956: de'i phyag rgyar gyur pa ni gsang sngags 'di dag ces sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:6957: de ni 'di'i rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK052(zi)001:6959: rigs rnam pa drug gi ste /
NK052(zi)001:6960: de la sangs rgyas kun la ston pa'i sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:6962: grub pa spyan gyi sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:6964: skal pa bzang po bdag nyid ma'i sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:6967: gzhung la la las las kyi rigs su ston /
NK052(zi)001:6968: bya ba'i rgyud la sogs pa spyi'i gzhung las pad+ma'i rigs kyi yum du ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6970: tram ba ba zhes bya ba' sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:6971: rin po che'i rigs kyi lha mo bzhi'i snying po ste /
NK052(zi)001:6974: rta mchog gi pad+mo rgod pa'i zhal gyi sngags te /
NK052(zi)001:6975: 'di yang spyi'i rgyud las pad+ma'i rigs su gsungs /
NK052(zi)001:6976: rgyud 'dir las kyi rigs su gsungs so //
NK052(zi)001:6977: 'di dag gang du sbyar bar bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:6978: las dang mchod pa thams cad kyi skabs su sbyar ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:6979: rgyud 'dir lha so so'i gsang sngags mang po ma gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6980: de'i tshul ni gong du bsgrub pa'i kun nas bsdus pa las thams cad yin par shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6981: de bas na rgyud phyi ma las /
NK052(zi)001:6982: lha thams cad kyi yig 'bru dang gsang sngags rgyas par gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:6983: de'i tshul ni gong du bsgrub pa'i skabs su ji ltar sbyar ba bshad pa rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:6984: chos kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:6985: da ni glu ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:6987: glu nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:6991: glu'i mchod pa'i tshe sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6992: de la h+aum gis drang ba'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:6993: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ste /
NK052(zi)001:6994: de la glu dang glu'i mkhan po dang glu'i dbyangs
NK052(zi)001:6995: dang glu'i tshig dang glu'i rgyan dang glu byin gyis
NK052(zi)001:6996: rlob par byed pa rnams kyis shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:6997: de la glu'i mkhan po ni /
NK052(zi)001:6999: de la lha dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor pa'ang yin no //
NK052(zi)001:7001: skad kyi gsang mtho dman dang drag dal dang di'u khug la sogs pas phye bas bshad pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7003: de ba ta zhes bya ba la sogs pa glu'i
NK052(zi)001:7004: lam bzhi 'gyur dang drug 'gyur la sogs pa rnams
NK052(zi)001:7006: don dang ldan pa'i tshig 'bru rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:7008: don lhag por ston pa med kyang glu mdzes pa'i yig 'bru'i gdangs 'byung ba rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:7009: glu byin gyis rlobs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7010: dmigs pa dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK052(zi)001:7011: grub pa'i sngags kyi yig 'bru rnams yin no //
NK052(zi)001:7012: de la yi ge h+aum ni /
NK052(zi)001:7013: don de dag kun dang ldan pa ste 'di ltar
NK052(zi)001:7014: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin yin pas glu'i
NK052(zi)001:7015: mkhan po'o // h+aum rings sna glu'i sgra dbyangs yin pas glu'i dbyangs so //
NK052(zi)001:7016: don chen po dang ldan pa'i tshig 'bru yin pas glu'i tshig go //
NK052(zi)001:7017: glu'i de'u khugs gsal zhing rgyas par byed pas glu'i rgyan no //
NK052(zi)001:7018: h+aum gis byin gyis brlab pa'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:7019: thams cad chos kyi phyag rgyar gyur te don dang
NK052(zi)001:7020: byin rlabs dang dgos pa la sogs pa thun mong
NK052(zi)001:7021: ma yin pa'i gnas su gyur pas glu byin gyis
NK052(zi)001:7024: la sogs pa de bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7025: de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i glu'i dbyangs ni /
NK052(zi)001:7026: ka ka la sha da ba la sogs zhes gsungs pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7029: pha rol gyi gdangs skad de ltangs ltangs len zhing 'don pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7031: glu'i ring thung cha mnyam pa ste de la sogs pa glu thams cad la sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7033: gyi glu yi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7034: tshangs pa dbyangs kyis ci gar blang //
NK052(zi)001:7036: de la +aam gi don ni h+aum ba zhin no //
NK052(zi)001:7038: tshangs pa dbyangs nyid yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7039: 'jig rten dang por byung ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7040: tshangs pa dbang phyug khyab 'jug ste //
NK052(zi)001:7042: de gsum gyis 'jig rten thams cad bsdus par rig byed kyi gtsug lag las 'byung ste /
NK052(zi)001:7043: de gsum gyi snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:7045: de gsum gcig tu sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7047: de ni dang por tshangs pas smras so //
NK052(zi)001:7048: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byung nas ni rgyal ba
NK052(zi)001:7049: rnams kyi snying por byin gyis brlab pa mdzad de
NK052(zi)001:7050: / de bas na 'di ni sngags thams cad dang mthun par phyag 'tshal ba'i phyag rgyar bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7051: spyir tshangs pa'i dbyangs zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7052: tshangs pa ni ngag la dbang thob par dbyangs kyi
NK052(zi)001:7053: yan lag bcu la sogs pa rnams la dbang bsgyur
NK052(zi)001:7054: te 'jig rten na mchog tu gyur to //
NK052(zi)001:7055: de bzhin du snyan par blang zhing gyis drang ngo //
NK052(zi)001:7057: dpal he ru ka'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:7058: rdo rje drag po gar mo che //
NK052(zi)001:7059: khur ba'i dbugs kyi rlung 'byin zhing //
NK052(zi)001:7060: 'brug gi sgras ltar zab pa yi //
NK052(zi)001:7061: ru lu ru lu'i sgra byung na //
NK052(zi)001:7063: de la ru lu ru lu zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7064: srin po ma rangs khros pa'i gad mo ste 'dis thams cad rlag par byed do //
NK052(zi)001:7065: de nyid dpal he ru kas 'dul bar mdzad de /
NK052(zi)001:7066: srin skad 'di yang he ru ka'i gsang sngags su byin gyis brlabs so //
NK052(zi)001:7067: dbyangs 'di gsum yang srin skad dang dpal gyi glu thun mong du gyur pa yin no //
NK052(zi)001:7069: te zhes bya ba dag pa chos kyi sgra'o //
NK052(zi)001:7070: rdo rje nyi ma'i glu ni /
NK052(zi)001:7071: hi zhes bya ba rnam par rgyal ba'i sgra'o //
NK052(zi)001:7073: ka ka la la dang tso ra'i dbyangs zhes te /
NK052(zi)001:7075: chom rkun gyi dbyangs te spyugs glu phra mos sems can du mi ston pa'i sgra'o //
NK052(zi)001:7079: kha gdangs nas de'u bstod pa thams cad kyang gzhan gyi phru ma 'joms pa'i glu'o //
NK052(zi)001:7080: glu ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7081: da ni rol mo ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7083: gling bu la sogs pa sil snyan gyi sgra dang /
NK052(zi)001:7084: de dag brdung ba'i stobs dang /
NK052(zi)001:7085: snying po dang phyag rgya dang gsang sngags rigs sngags
NK052(zi)001:7086: la sogs pa rnams kyi bya ba so so dang
NK052(zi)001:7087: thabs kyi sgra rnams ci rigs su sbyar zhing bya'o
NK052(zi)001:7094: sngon gyi slob dpon dag gis rol mo'i sgra ni mtshan ma dang bral ba /
NK052(zi)001:7096: de la snying po dang phyag rgya dang gsang sngags dang rigs sngags ni /
NK052(zi)001:7097: sku la sogs pa'i bye brag gis rigs rnam pa bzhir grags pa'i lha dag go //
NK052(zi)001:7098: dzahh+aum ba hohl sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7099: rol mo'i thabs dang sbyar ba'i tshig dang /
NK052(zi)001:7102: thal mo brdab pa brtag pa de /
NK052(zi)001:7104: rgyun gyi rnga dang dam tshig gsum gyi rnga ni /
NK052(zi)001:7105: sangs rgyas dang thun mong du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7107: ji skad smos pa bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:7108: rol mo ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7109: da ni gar ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7111: rdo rje se gol gyi sgra dang /
NK052(zi)001:7112: rdo rje thal mo'i sgra 'dis sangs rgyas thams cad
NK052(zi)001:7113: bsdus pa glu dang rol mo dang sbyar zhing gar
NK052(zi)001:7116: g.yon pa'i se gol brdab pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:7117: thal mo dal bus brdabs pas 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:7118: gnyis ga'ang kun tu sdud pa yin //
NK052(zi)001:7120: se gol dang thal mo gnyis ka'ang sangs rgyas thams cad sdud pa 'dra ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7121: se gol yang lan gsum du brdab cing thal mo
NK052(zi)001:7122: yang lan gsum du dal bus brdab par bya ba
NK052(zi)001:7123: yin pa las / se gol ni /
NK052(zi)001:7127: ta la to zhes bya ste thabs kyi rang bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:7128: thabs dang shes rab kyi sgra ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK052(zi)001:7134: gar dgu'i rang bzhin lha dgur bshad pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7136: chags pa chen po'i rang bzhin pas stegs pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7138: spang dka' ba'i 'dod pa spangs shing thub par dka' ba'i bdud bzhi bcom par ston pas dpa' bo'o /
NK052(zi)001:7140: thugs rje lhun gyis grub pas gdul bya rmu rgod
NK052(zi)001:7141: rnams la yang btang snyoms mi mdzad de myur du
NK052(zi)001:7144: chos zab mo ston pas rgod pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7146: rgyal po'i tshul bas thams cad kyi re ba skongs shing yi rang bar byed pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7147: khro bo rdo rje rta mchog ni /
NK052(zi)001:7150: dka' thub la gnas te rgyan spangs pas mi thub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7152: ci yang 'gyur zhing 'phrul ba'i bdag nyid pas ngo mtshar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7154: dus gsum du 'gyur ba dang spros pa'i mtshan ma med pas zhi ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7155: lha dgu rigs drug tu bsdu ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7157: rnam par snang mdzad dang 'dra ste de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK052(zi)001:7159: zhing dag ma dag gi bye brag dang /
NK052(zi)001:7160: mi dang lha gdul ba'i bye brag dang /
NK052(zi)001:7162: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor du theg
NK052(zi)001:7163: pa sna tshogs dang theg pa chen po'i chos ston
NK052(zi)001:7164: pa'i bye brag gi phye ba tsam du zad pas
NK052(zi)001:7165: rigs la tha dad med do //
NK052(zi)001:7166: spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang ye shes phun
NK052(zi)001:7167: sum tshogs pa gtsor bstan pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:7168: rigs so // byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK052(zi)001:7169: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:7170: 'di yang rang bzhin dang sku'i tshul tsam gyis phye bar zad do //
NK052(zi)001:7172: rigs thams cad kyi 'khor gyi lha mo rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:7173: 'di ni gar gyi spyi'i don bshad pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7174: gar 'di ji ltar bsgyur ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7175: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du len par bslabs pa'i rnal
NK052(zi)001:7176: 'byor pa gnyis kyis rdo rje slob dpon dang rdo
NK052(zi)001:7177: rje mched rnams kyi spyan sngar phyag rgya dang phyag
NK052(zi)001:7178: rgya'i don gyis gar byas te /
NK052(zi)001:7180: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gar thams
NK052(zi)001:7181: cad 'byung byed ye shes kyi phyag rgya nas mgo
NK052(zi)001:7183: de rdzogs par gyur pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7184: de nas rgol bas dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi phyag rgya thams cad kyi gar bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7185: de nas phyir rgol bas dpal he ru ka'i gar bsgyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7186: de nas rgol bas pad ma gar dbang gi gar bsgyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7187: de nas phyir rgol bas rdo rje nyi mar bsgyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7188: de nas rgol bas dpal rta mchog tu bsgyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7189: de nas yang rgol bas dpal rdo rje sems dpar bsgyur te /
NK052(zi)001:7190: snga ma bzhin du phyag rgya dang phyag rgya'i lan gyis sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7193: de las gang zhig 'pham par gyur pa des tshogs
NK052(zi)001:7194: kyi dkyil 'khor de tshogs kyi zas yon dang bcas
NK052(zi)001:7197: dkyil 'khor chen po drug gi phyag rgya thams cad
NK052(zi)001:7198: tshogs kyi mchod pa gcig tu sbyar ba yin no
NK052(zi)001:7199: // gang ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7200: da ni glu rgyan gyi phyag rgya zhes grags pa rdo rje glu'i mchod pa'i phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7201: gang la rdo rje theg pa'i don gyis brgyan pa'i glu de ni de skad ces bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7203: gsang ba'i lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas lan gsum du bldabs te byung ba las /
NK052(zi)001:7205: lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas bstod de dngos grub gsol bar spyir bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7207: lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don la rol cing sprul par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7209: lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas de lta bu dngos grub bdag la gsol cig par bskul ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7210: de la don dang po'i tshig dang po /
NK052(zi)001:7211: rab tu dga' ba rjes su chags pa /
NK052(zi)001:7215: rab tu dga' bar sbyor ba /
NK052(zi)001:7217: rmongs byed ma'i sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:7221: za byed ma'i sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:7223: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug /
NK052(zi)001:7227: rol pa thams cad kyi phyag barda'o //
NK052(zi)001:7228: rta mchog ho zhes pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7229: sna tshogs su rol pa'i barda'o //
NK052(zi)001:7230: don gnyis pa 'i tshig dang po /
NK052(zi)001:7231: rab tu sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:7241: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi slob ma gzung du gsol //
NK052(zi)001:7250: dam pa rab tu zhugs pa /
NK052(zi)001:7254: de ltar gsungs pa'i yum bzhi'i sgo nas don gsum gyi tshul du sbyar ba 'i glu bstan nas /
NK052(zi)001:7255: da ni rigs bzhi'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'i glu ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7257: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:7258: rdo rje rin chen bla med pa //
NK052(zi)001:7259: rdo rje chos ni gsung ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:7260: rdo rje las ni byed par 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:7262: sat+wa'i sgra don du ma la 'jug pa las 'dir sdud pa la bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7263: mtshan nyid dbyer med par sdud pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7265: bla na med pas rdo rje rin chen zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7267: bstan pa'i chos gsungs pas rdo rje chos zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7269: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mdzad pa thams cad byed par 'gyur bas rdo rje las zhes bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7270: tshig phyi ma 'di rnams rgyu'am gtan tshigs su 'gyur ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7271: don gyis mngon pa tsam du ma zad kyi /
NK052(zi)001:7272: sgra'i sgo nas kyang bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:7274: badz+ra sat+wa sam gra h+aa da zhes bya ba ni lnga pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:7275: badz+ra rat+na ma nut+ta ri zhes bya ba ni gsum pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7277: da ni gsang ba yum bzhi'i sgo nas dkyil 'khor
NK052(zi)001:7278: gyi lha thams cad la phyag 'tshal ba' glu ston
NK052(zi)001:7279: te / h+aum rdo rje las kyi mda' gzhu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK052(zi)001:7283: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i lha rnams chags pa chen pos zhen pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK052(zi)001:7284: de lta bu la phyag 'tshal ba nyid rgyas 'debs
NK052(zi)001:7285: ma'i sgo nas btsal zhes sbyar te 'og ma rnams
NK052(zi)001:7286: la yang de bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7287: de la chags pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK052(zi)001:7288: bde ba chen po las rtag tu mi 'da' ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7289: kha t+aam ka rab tu 'jig pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7294: dbang phyug che mchog grub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7295: de bas na lha thams cad rtag tu don 'di bzhi'i rang du bzhugs so //
NK052(zi)001:7296: de mtshon pa'i sgo ni gsang ba' lha mo bzhi'i sgo nas so //
NK052(zi)001:7297: da ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i tshul gyis rigs drug gi sgo nas bstod de /
NK052(zi)001:7298: de la 'jig rten pa'i rigs gsum ni /
NK052(zi)001:7299: drag po chen po ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7302: de la 'jig rten las 'das pa'i skabs su ni /
NK052(zi)001:7303: 'dod chags kyi bdag po dbang phyug chen po de ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rigs so //
NK052(zi)001:7304: zhe sdang gi bdag po gsod byed rkyen zhes bya
NK052(zi)001:7305: ba khyab 'jug ni rdo rje he ru ka'i rigs
NK052(zi)001:7306: so // gti mug gi bdag po gti mug sel
NK052(zi)001:7307: bar byed pa rig byed thams cad kyi slob dpon
NK052(zi)001:7308: tshangs pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK052(zi)001:7309: de ltar rigs gsum po de ni 'jig dang 'jig
NK052(zi)001:7310: rten las 'das pa'i rigs kyi tshul thun mong du
NK052(zi)001:7312: rab tu 'bar ba'i chags pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7314: thams cad dbang bskur zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7316: la lar mkhas pa'i zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7318: glu rgyan gyi ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7319: da ni mchod pa thams cad ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7321: me tog dang bdug pa dang mar me dang byug
NK052(zi)001:7322: spos rnams kyi phyag rgya tshoms gcig tu bstan la
NK052(zi)001:7323: / bshos dang gtor ma'i bye brag kha zas kyi mchod pa ni tshom gcig tu bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7324: rigs so so ni gsal bar ston pas smos mi dgos so //
NK052(zi)001:7325: sgegs ma dang ni na chung la sogs pa ni brda'i skabs nas bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7327: gtsang rme lhag par dbye ba mi bzhed pa las /
NK052(zi)001:7329: sangs rgyas rnams la bshos dbul ba //
NK052(zi)001:7330: sha dang chang ni rnam par spangs //
NK052(zi)001:7333: spyir gsang sngags kyi rgyud las gtsang rme'i spang blang gi sgo nas pa gnyis gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:7335: rigs sngags dang gsang sngags rnams mchod pa gang la dgyes pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7336: de la gsang sngags pa'i spyod pa la ni /
NK052(zi)001:7337: bya ba'i rgyud du gtsang bar bstan la /
NK052(zi)001:7338: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du de ltar ma bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7340: rdo rje khro bo'i rigs lta bu smi ba'i rdzas kyis phal cher dgyes par bshad la /
NK052(zi)001:7341: dpal sh+aakya thub pa lta bu de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK052(zi)001:7342: rigs la ni rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud du'ang gtsang
NK052(zi)001:7345: da na phyag rgya dbang bskur ba'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7346: 'di dag ji ltar gang du sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7347: gong du tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i skabs su
NK052(zi)001:7348: dbang bskur ba'i skabs su rin po che rnam pa
NK052(zi)001:7349: lnga'i phyag rgyas sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7350: de la cung zad ma smos pa rnams bstan pa na /
NK052(zi)001:7351: sangs rgyas rin chen gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:7352: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7354: lhag ma rnams ni go rim bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:7355: thams cad rdo rje'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7356: byin gyis brlabs pa la sbyar ba ste /
NK052(zi)001:7357: de la dga' chen dpal gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK052(zi)001:7358: sna tshogs rdo rje'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7359: rigs thams cad la spyir byin gyis brlab par shes par bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7360: rdo rje lcags kyu'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7361: lhag par byin gyis brlab par smos pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:7362: dgug pa la sogs pa las sna tshogs la sbyar bar bya'o /
NK052(zi)001:7363: lhag ma rdo rje'i phyag rgya rnams so //
NK052(zi)001:7364: rigs so so'i byin gyis brlab pa la sbyar bar bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7365: de la dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i rdo rje'i phyag rgya ni /
NK052(zi)001:7366: gong gi rdo rje'i phyag rgya nyid dang 'dra'o //
NK052(zi)001:7368: ji skad smos pa'i rim pa bzhin no //
NK052(zi)001:7369: rdo rje'i phyag rgya 'di rnams las spyi'i phyag rgya gsum ni mchog dang bcas pa'i phyag rgya /
NK052(zi)001:7371: de la rdo rje'i phyag rgya 'di /
NK052(zi)001:7372: dag gi rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK052(zi)001:7373: sangs rgyas lnga po thams cad kyang dpal rdo rje
NK052(zi)001:7374: sems dpa'i rigs yin pas thams cad kyang rdo rje'i
NK052(zi)001:7375: phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs par bya ba yin no
NK052(zi)001:7376: // da ni yig 'bru dgongs pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya bstan pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:7377: +aa li k+aa li mnyam sbyar nas //
NK052(zi)001:7378: kha yig thad khar 'dud par bya //
NK052(zi)001:7379: zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:7380: 'di ni rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du lha rnams
NK052(zi)001:7381: kyi yi ge'i phyag rgya bkod nas der slob ma
NK052(zi)001:7382: bcug ste / rdo rje'i ming gis dbang bskur na sangs rgyas su lung bstan par 'gyur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7384: 'on kyang bri ba gcig pur ma zad kyi brjod par yang bstan te /
NK052(zi)001:7385: de la gang brjod par bstan pa de ni /
NK052(zi)001:7386: gar ye shes kyi phyag rgya'i skabs su sbyar bar bya ba yin no //
NK052(zi)001:7387: de la yig 'bru ji ltar dgod ce na /
NK052(zi)001:7388: 'di nyid kyi phyi ma phyi ma'i rgyud las /
NK052(zi)001:7389: yi ge ka sogs da yig mtha' //
NK052(zi)001:7390: da nya bsal nas dgod par bya //
NK052(zi)001:7391: yi ge d+h+aa sogs k+sha yig mthar //
NK052(zi)001:7392: de yi rjes su bri bar bya //
NK052(zi)001:7393: dbugs gnas pa ni a yi phreng //
NK052(zi)001:7394: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK052(zi)001:7395: 'dir le'u bdun pa las gsungs pa'i dkyil 'khor ba'i lta ba bzhin du thig btab nas /
NK052(zi)001:7396: dbus kyi re cha la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bcas te /
NK052(zi)001:7397: de'i steng du +aa li bcu drug dang /
NK052(zi)001:7398: k+aa li sum cu rtsa bzhi la da nya bsal
NK052(zi)001:7399: ba sum cu rtsa gnyis bcu drug rim gnyis su
NK052(zi)001:7400: phye ste / de ltar bcu drug phrag gsum yi
NK052(zi)001:7401: ge grangs mnyam par byas nas kha'i thad kar gdud
NK052(zi)001:7402: phye ste / par bya / zhes te /
NK052(zi)001:7403: shar phyogs su 'go gzugs te phreng ba'i tshul du gdud cing bskor //
NK052(zi)001:7405: de yi 'og tu ri mo rnams //
NK052(zi)001:7406: yi ge thams cad dgod par bya //
NK052(zi)001:7408: de nas phyi nang gi yi ge thams cad legs par dgod do //
NK052(zi)001:7410: de la dbus kyi yi ge dgod pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7411: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor zhes //
NK052(zi)001:7412: rab tu chags pa'i mtshan bris na //
NK052(zi)001:7417: badz+ra sat+wa yo gi zhes bya bas bskor ro //
NK052(zi)001:7418: de la dbus kyi dpal gyi yi ge ji ltar bri ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7419: gug sgyed dag gi lcug mar bya //
NK052(zi)001:7420: zhes bya ba ma dra zhes bya ba spyi dang
NK052(zi)001:7421: yan lag gnyis ka'i ming yin pas dpal gyi gu
NK052(zi)001:7422: gu lcug ma ltar drang ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7425: dpal gyir myu gu ltar rtse mo can du bya ba'o //
NK052(zi)001:7426: glang skor zla ba kham pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:7428: 'dir sgra la dgos pa med kyang sa bon gyi
NK052(zi)001:7429: yi ge yi ge pas thig le zla tshes kyis
NK052(zi)001:7430: brgyan de zla kham du gyur pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7431: tshes gnyis zla ba gnyis su bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7433: dbang phyug chen po'i mig 'dra bas brgyan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7434: dpal gyi ri mo 'di yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phyag rgya yin pa'i phyir /
NK052(zi)001:7435: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK052(zi)001:7436: phyag rgya mi 'gyur dam pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:7437: sangs rgyas dpal gyi ri mor bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7439: yi ge de dag mi 'gyur mchog /
NK052(zi)001:7441: yi ge thams cad a yig mi 'gyur ba'i rang bzhin pas chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7443: ji ltar gtso bo la sbyar ba de ltar lha mo thams cad la yang /
NK052(zi)001:7444: dbus su dpal gyi ri mo bris te /
NK052(zi)001:7445: de'i khor yug tu rang gi ming gi phreng bas
NK052(zi)001:7446: bskor te +aa li dang k+aa li snga ma bzhin
NK052(zi)001:7447: du byas nas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la bkod de
NK052(zi)001:7450: lhag ma rigs so so'i dkyil 'khor rnams kyang 'di bzhin du sbyar te /
NK052(zi)001:7451: de las rang rang gi ming gi phyag rgya cung
NK052(zi)001:7452: zad mi mthun pa ni dkyus las gsal bar gsungs
NK052(zi)001:7453: par zad do // yig 'bru dgod par ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7454: da ni brda' ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston te /
NK052(zi)001:7455: de yang 'di gang du sbyar bar bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7456: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su rnal 'byor pa
NK052(zi)001:7457: rnams brda 'di lta bu'i sgo nas brda sprad dgos
NK052(zi)001:7458: pas der sbyar ba'i phyir dang /
NK052(zi)001:7459: spyir yang gong du rgyud kyi gzhung bstan pa'i skabs
NK052(zi)001:7460: su brda bstan pa rnams rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK052(zi)001:7461: bstan to // de la rigs so so gang gi yin pa sbyar ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7462: rigs kyi spyir sbyar ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7463: rigs so sor sbyar ba gnyis nyid las gsal bar 'byung ngo //
NK052(zi)001:7464: de la lus kyi brda rnams ni spyir bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7465: ngag gi brda rnams ni spyi dang bye brag tu ston to //
NK052(zi)001:7466: de la brda 'di dag las dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i
NK052(zi)001:7467: brda la sogs pa gzhung gi yi ge de nyid
NK052(zi)001:7468: las shes su rung ba rnams ni ma bshad do
NK052(zi)001:7469: // cung zad mi gsal ba rnams bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7471: sangs rgyas thams cad rin chen mchog /
NK052(zi)001:7472: dbu rgyan mi 'gyur dam pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:7473: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid mchog /
NK052(zi)001:7474: yin par rang byung rnams kyis gsungs //
NK052(zi)001:7475: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan dang //
NK052(zi)001:7476: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu dag /
NK052(zi)001:7477: sangs rgyas brda yi phyag rgya yin //
NK052(zi)001:7478: dpal gyi pad+mo'i tshul du bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7480: rigs kyi spyi dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba la /
NK052(zi)001:7481: gang gi tshe rdo rje slob dpon gyi go 'phang
NK052(zi)001:7482: la sbyor ba'i dbang bskur ba de'i tshe thod pa'i
NK052(zi)001:7483: phreng ba dang / sangs rgyas gtsug tor gyi nor bu gnyis sbyar bya ba yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7484: ji skad rtog pa bdun pa'i dbang bskur ba'i skabs nas /
NK052(zi)001:7485: thod pa rin chen dbu rgyan nam //
NK052(zi)001:7486: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu dag /
NK052(zi)001:7487: kun tu sna tshogs bla mar ni //
NK052(zi)001:7488: kun gyi slob dpon kun la bya //
NK052(zi)001:7489: rgyal srid thams cad rnam dag pa //
NK052(zi)001:7490: ma lus lus pa med pa 'grub //
NK052(zi)001:7491: ces gsungs pa 'di'i don dang brda bstan par sbyar ro //
NK052(zi)001:7492: sangs rgyas rang bzhin grub gcig dang //
NK052(zi)001:7493: de bzhin pad+mo rang bzhin gcig /
NK052(zi)001:7494: thams cad dbang bskur dbang bskur che //
NK052(zi)001:7495: yin par don kun grub par gsungs //
NK052(zi)001:7497: gang gi tshe chos kyi rgyal po rgyal srid thams
NK052(zi)001:7498: cad la mnga' brnyes pa nyid du dbang bskur bar
NK052(zi)001:7500: slob ma gzhan mchog dang 'bring dang tha ma gang rung ba thams cad dbang bskur ba la /
NK052(zi)001:7501: sangs rgyas kyi phyag rgya dang pad+ma'i phyag rgyas dbang bskur bar bya ba yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7502: ji skad du rtog pa bdun par slob ma tha
NK052(zi)001:7503: mal pa thams cad dbang bskur bar bstan pa'i skabs
NK052(zi)001:7504: nas / rin chen ngo mtshar ci la bya //
NK052(zi)001:7505: de bzhin sna tshogs rgyan gyis spras //
NK052(zi)001:7506: sangs rgyas pad+mo'i dbang bskur bas //
NK052(zi)001:7507: slob ma thams cad dbang bskur ro //
NK052(zi)001:7508: zhes gsungs pa 'di nyid kyis brda sbyar bar bya'o //
NK052(zi)001:7512: de bzhin zhes bya ba ni /
NK052(zi)001:7514: gang gi phyir 'di dag gi don de nyid kyi
NK052(zi)001:7515: rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya gcig pu yin
NK052(zi)001:7518: phyag rgya'ang dam tshig yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7519: phyag rgya'ang sbyor ba yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7520: sbyor ba'ang phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7522: de la dam tshig ni mi 'da' ba' mtshan nyid yin la /
NK052(zi)001:7523: phyag rgya zhes bya'ang mi 'da' ba'i mtshan nyid yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7524: de bas na 'dir bdag nyid gcig ste /
NK052(zi)001:7525: phyag rgya nyid dam tshig yin pas phyag rgya la dam tshig ces bshad do //
NK052(zi)001:7526: phyag rgya sbyor ba yin pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7527: 'di ltar phyag rgya rnams la yid 'byor ba rnal 'byor zhes kyang bshad na /
NK052(zi)001:7528: 'di gnyis kyang rang bzhin tha dad pa med de /
NK052(zi)001:7529: gang du sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar gnas pa de nyid rnal 'byor ces bya ba yin la /
NK052(zi)001:7530: de bzhin du rnal 'byor gang yin pa de'ang phyag rgya yin no //
NK052(zi)001:7531: de la sbyor ba'i bye brag 'di dag kyang gong du rtog pa gnyis par bshad pa bzhin /
NK052(zi)001:7536: shin tu sbyor ba rnams su bstan pa'i bye brag dang /
NK052(zi)001:7537: de la yang rab tu sbyor ba dang rjes su
NK052(zi)001:7538: sbyor ba dang shin tu sbyor ba rnams ni nyer
NK052(zi)001:7539: bar sbyor ba'i yan lag tu gyur pa yin par
NK052(zi)001:7541: gzhung 'di dang cha mthun pa'i rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gzhan las /
NK052(zi)001:7546: shin tu sgrub pa dang lnga gsungs pa la sogs
NK052(zi)001:7547: pa gong du rgyas par bshad pas de nyid 'dir
NK052(zi)001:7549: khrag ni me tog yin par bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7550: ces bya ba la sogs ni /
NK052(zi)001:7551: sbas pa'i brda zhes kyang grags te /
NK052(zi)001:7552: brda thams cad kyang sbas pa yin mod kyi gsang
NK052(zi)001:7553: ba' rdzas rnams khyad par du gsang bar bya bar
NK052(zi)001:7554: bstan pa'o // bdud rtsi lam gyi yan lag brgyad //
NK052(zi)001:7556: rdzas brgyad po 'di nyid la bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7558: mdangs la sogs par sa ya na'i rdzas 'di rnams
NK052(zi)001:7559: dza gad dpa' bo dang sbyar ba ni dam tshig
NK052(zi)001:7560: gi rdzas bdud rtsi'i lam dang sgor gyur pa'i yan
NK052(zi)001:7562: de la dza gad dpa' bo la yang rgyu rang
NK052(zi)001:7563: chas su grub pa rnams la gcig pu dpa' bo
NK052(zi)001:7565: 'bras bu chen po lnga'i brda bstan pa las 'dir chos kyi 'bras bu lngar bshad de /
NK052(zi)001:7566: a smra smin pa grol bar bshad //
NK052(zi)001:7567: de bzhin bde bar nyal ba dang //
NK052(zi)001:7568: bde bas rab tu rmongs pa dag /
NK052(zi)001:7569: ces bya ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po la gnas te /
NK052(zi)001:7570: rnam par mi rtog pa ni grol ba ste a smra'o //
NK052(zi)001:7571: 'bras bu chen po sa na ya //
NK052(zi)001:7573: de'i 'bras bu chen po ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK052(zi)001:7574: rgun 'brum khu ba khu ba'i mchog /
NK052(zi)001:7576: bcud thams cad kyi mchog ni byang chub kyi sems gdod ma nas grol pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7577: de ni chos kun gyi bcud dam pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7578: na le ge re dngos grub che //
NK052(zi)001:7580: dngos grub chen po'i bye brag thams cad do //
NK052(zi)001:7581: dam chos 'bras bu a ru ka /
NK052(zi)001:7583: dam pa'i chos la mnga' brnyes pa'i dngos grub bo //
NK052(zi)001:7584: de ltar na 'bras bu lnga po 'di ni /
NK052(zi)001:7585: bdud rtsi'i 'bras bur bstan pa yin la /
NK052(zi)001:7586: yan lag brgyad ni bdud rtsi'i lam dang rgyu bstan pa yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7588: yan lag brgyad kyi rdzas la brten te bsgrub pas 'bras bu rnam pa lnga 'thob /
NK052(zi)001:7590: de zhes bya ba mkha' 'gro yi //
NK052(zi)001:7591: khams gsum 'di ni rnam par brtags //
NK052(zi)001:7592: nam mkha' 'gro ba'i phyag rgya dag /
NK052(zi)001:7593: mkha' 'gro zhes ni rab tu grags //
NK052(zi)001:7594: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7595: gong du bstan pa bzhin du yi ge da dang
NK052(zi)001:7596: de'i sgra dag mkha' 'gro'i sgrar 'jig rten du grags
NK052(zi)001:7597: te / nam mkha' 'gro ba'i phyag rgya gang yin pa de mkha' 'gro zhes grags so //
NK052(zi)001:7599: kun tu sna tshogs phyag rgya ni //
NK052(zi)001:7600: thams cad nam mkha' 'gro ba ste //
NK052(zi)001:7604: de'i phyag rgya thams cad mkha' 'gro yin te /
NK052(zi)001:7606: sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro ma /
NK052(zi)001:7608: sgyu ma'i gar dbang grub pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:7609: a ral+li zhes ming du btags //
NK052(zi)001:7611: chos sgyu ma la mnga' brnyes te /
NK052(zi)001:7612: gzhi med pa sprul pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7613: yod pa gzhan du sgyur ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7614: snang ba dang mi snang ba bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7615: mi snang ba snang bar ston pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7616: rten med par gzugs mi lhung ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7617: gzugs kyis gzugs mi zin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7618: dus gcig tu gnas kun tu phyin pa la sogs pa grub la a ral+li zhes btags so //
NK052(zi)001:7619: mkha' 'a gro ma yang a ral+li //
NK052(zi)001:7621: d+aa ki ni zhes bya ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7622: a ral+li zhes bya ba 'dra ste /
NK052(zi)001:7623: d+aa ki ni zhes bya ba yang a ral+li'i don de lta bu grub pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7624: de bas na sgyu ma thams cad la mnga' brnyes
NK052(zi)001:7625: pa sna tshogs thams cad kyi gar gyi dbang phyug
NK052(zi)001:7626: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la yang
NK052(zi)001:7629: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya dag /
NK052(zi)001:7630: dam tshig gsum gyi dam pa yin //
NK052(zi)001:7632: dam tshig gsum ni sku gsung thugs te /
NK052(zi)001:7633: de'i phyag rgya ni rdo rje dril bu'o //
NK052(zi)001:7634: dam tshig gsum gyi snying po ni /
NK052(zi)001:7636: thams cad mkhyen par gyur pa dang //
NK052(zi)001:7637: de bzhin bde bar mkhyen pa ni //
NK052(zi)001:7638: sarba bid ces bshad pa ste //
NK052(zi)001:7639: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7640: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi brda ston pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7641: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa'i yul can gyi sgo nas kun rig ces bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7642: ko ta k+sha ko ta ba zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7643: rdo rje 'dzin pa he ru ka'i brda ste /
NK052(zi)001:7644: de la 'di ni ming bcu pa zhes bya ba
NK052(zi)001:7645: dpal phyag na rdo rje la gnod sbyin gyis skad
NK052(zi)001:7647: yi ge 'di dag gi sgra ni /
NK052(zi)001:7648: 'jig rten tha mal pa'i sgra dang thun mong ma yin zhing /
NK052(zi)001:7649: kun gyis rigs par dka' ba /
NK052(zi)001:7652: sgra yan lag mang ba la 'jug pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7653: phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i tan+t+ra las gsungs pa'i ming bcu dang /
NK052(zi)001:7654: pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK052(zi)001:7656: rlung bcu la sogs pa brda tha dad du bstan pa rnams kyi gzhi gyur pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7657: mtshan 'di brjod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK052(zi)001:7658: yul dang dbang por bcas pa'ang phyag na rdo rje'i rang bzhin du gyur la /
NK052(zi)001:7659: rdo rje mtshon cha bo di dang //
NK052(zi)001:7660: dgra bo dag tu rab grags pa //
NK052(zi)001:7661: de yi phyag rgya rdo rje 'gyur //
NK052(zi)001:7663: dgra bo nyid kyang rang gi phyag rgya rdo rjer 'gyur la /
NK052(zi)001:7664: 'jig rten dag na rdo rje mtshon cha gang dag
NK052(zi)001:7665: yod par de dag thams cad kyang de'i rigs kyi
NK052(zi)001:7668: lag na rdo rje zhes kyang bya /
NK052(zi)001:7672: badz+ra p+aa ni zhes bya bar ma zad kyi /
NK052(zi)001:7673: ba ti ra ba na zhes kyang bya /
NK052(zi)001:7676: yak+sha ni yad kiny+tsa t+k+aa ya yak+sha zhes bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7677: gang su yang rung ba zad pas gang zad ces bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7678: de las 'dir nyon mongs pa gang su yang rung ba dang /
NK052(zi)001:7679: dgra gang su yang rung ba zad pas yak+sha /
NK052(zi)001:7681: yak+sha'i sgra gzhan du bshad pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7683: sbyin pa byed pas gnod sbyin zhes bya ste /
NK052(zi)001:7684: rgyud khro ba dang nor la dbang thob pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7685: he ru dpal ni rdo rje che //
NK052(zi)001:7686: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7687: phyag na rdo rje de nyid dpal he ru kar sprul pa ste /
NK052(zi)001:7690: kha t+w+aam ga yang rgyal mtshan che //
NK052(zi)001:7691: thod pa kham por pad+mo snod //
NK052(zi)001:7692: khrag chen dang ni sbrang rtsi che //
NK052(zi)001:7694: dpal he ru ka'i phyag bzhi'i phyag mtshan bzhi'o //
NK052(zi)001:7695: dkar mo rkun byed rab rmongs dang //
NK052(zi)001:7696: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7697: gong du rgyas 'debs ma dang snying 'dren ma la sogs pa'i ming du grags pa de /
NK052(zi)001:7698: 'dir go'u ri dang tso'u ri la sogs par bstan to //
NK052(zi)001:7699: lha mo bdun du bstan pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7700: lha mo sma sha ni yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+air bstan pa'o //
NK052(zi)001:7701: srungs shig ces bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7702: lha mo rnams kyi las so //
NK052(zi)001:7703: rgyal po spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug /
NK052(zi)001:7704: ces bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7705: pad+ma rigs lha mo dang bcas pa'i barda'o //
NK052(zi)001:7706: nam mkha'i snying po thams cad phyogs //
NK052(zi)001:7707: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7708: de bzhin du rdo rje nyi ma'i'o //
NK052(zi)001:7709: sna tshogs pad+mo thams cad spyan //
NK052(zi)001:7710: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
NK052(zi)001:7713: zhes bya ba la sogs ni /
NK052(zi)001:7715: brda ye shes kyi phyag rgya bshad zin to //
NK052(zi)001:7716: de ni ye shes kyi phyag rgya ston to //
NK052(zi)001:7718: rjes su chags par bya'o zhes //
NK052(zi)001:7719: cha lugs shes pa bzhin byed cing //
